The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 MNVN Laceless Analog is a product of the long-running collaboration between German sports apparel, wear, and shoe manufacturer adidas and the brand affiliated with Chicago-born musician and designer Kanye West,  Yeezy.

The Laceless Analog adidas Yeezy Boost 700 MNVN is a rendition of the iconic adidas Yeezy Boost 700 MNVN first debuted in 2018. Dressed in variations of grey and black, this shoe boasts off-white synthetic uppers. The synthetic uppers are contrasted by dark overlays and a black tongue. Additional details visible on the upper include 3M reflective metallic silver 700 branding and markings on the heel and around the toe. This shoe’s upper sits a top of a white sculpted Boost sole unit. Underfoot, it boasts black rubber outsoles.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 MNVN Laceless Analog was first introduced on 6th October 2022. At the time, it retailed at $220.

name: Blue Oasis Real Pink
title: New Balance 9060 Blue Oasis Real Pink
description:
The New Balance 9060 Blue Oasis Real Pink combines retro aesthetics with modern flair to create a beautiful, bold, versatile look and feel. This design balances vibrant colors and premium materials, which reflects New Balance’s creative approach to casual footwear inspired by its heritage.

The Blue Oasis/Real Pink 9060 by New Balance highlights a suede and mesh upper in a striking blend of blue, pink, and beige tones. The layered makeup improves depth, while reflective accents are there to give you extra visibility. Dual-density midsoles are there to offer cushioning, and the split heel design references New Balance’s 990 lineage. They were first introduced as a modern twist on classic running silhouettes; the 9060 series bridges thoughtful designs with futuristic concepts.

Something we love about the New Balance 9060 Blue Oasis Real Pink is the unique split-heel detail for an added dimensional layer and the breathable mesh panels that improve airflow. Released on 22nd May 2024, this model retailed at $150.

name: JJJJound White
title: adidas Samba OG JJJJound White
description:
The adidas Samba OG JJJJound White is a sneaker designed as a collaboration between adidas and JJJJound, a minimalist design and art studio based in Montreal.

This iteration of the adidas Samba OG is made with a textured white leather base. A suede toe cap in light gray runs up to the laces. The iconic adidas three stripes adorn the sides of the shoe in black leather, while the JJJJound brand name appears in gold lettering above the first stripe on the lateral side. The heel collar is also black leather, and the black tongue has textured lines. The classic gum rubber outsole completes the look of this simple sneaker.

What we think stands out about this shoe is the minimal adidas branding compared to other iterations. The only adidas branding present is the classic three stripes. The adidas Samba OG JJJJound White was released on March 27, 2024, for a price of $250.

name: Black White
title: adidas Samba Leather Black White
description:
The adidas Samba Leather Black White showcases a timeless classic colorway of the soccer trainer, originally crafted in 1949 by adidas founder Adi Dassler.

The sleek Black White adidas Samba silhouette features a black leather upper, reinforced with a tonal suede overlay across the forefoot. Contrasting white details adorn the serrated leather three-stripes and heel tab. Resting on a robust, non-marking gum rubber sole, these trainers provide a stylish step for the season, enhanced by the embossed EVA midsole for added comfort. Infused with football heritage, this refined style includes a secure lace-up fastening and a vibrant logo patch on the tongue. Elevating the Samba trainers further is the gold foil embossing, providing a distinctive and polished finish.

The standout characteristic of the adidas Samba Leather Black White is its semi-translucent gum rubber sole. This unique visual element not only offers traction and support but also contributes to the shoe's overall design, creating a distinct and appealing aesthetic. The shoe debuted for $75 on December 8th, 2020.

name: Navy Castlerock
title: New Balance 2002R Navy Castlerock
description:
The New Balance 2002R Navy Castlerock boasts a luxurious upper construction with mesh, shaggy suede, and leather in a dark-gray colorway.

The base of the Navy Castlerock New Balance 2002R features mesh in Castlerock with layers of premium leather and shaggy suede overlays in navy, Castlerock, and a darker-gray hue. The shaggy suede gives the sneaker a more rugged look than can be achieved with traditional suede. Although the padded tongue is crafted from mesh in Castelrock, the laces come in an off-white tone that matches the midsole. Thanks to the ABSORB and ABSORBS SBS heel cushioning, the sneaker protects against impact and offers stability. Rounding out the technical specs, the N-ergy sole works with the midsole and absorbs shock.

Our experts at StockX like that the sneaker draws inspiration from New Balance’s catalog, including the technical silhouettes from the running shoes of the 2000s. The New Balance 2002R Navy Castlerock was released on January 11, 2024, and sold for $160.

name: Onyx
title: adidas Yeezy QNTM Onyx
description:
The adidas Yeezy QNTM Onyx features a black and dark grey Primeknit upper with neoprene collars and suede toe caps, offering a secure fit. At the base, a semi-translucent midsole and triple black outsole complement its marled upper.

The adidas Yeezy QNTM Onyx released in September of 2021 and retailed for $250.

name: Ochre
title: adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Ochre
description:
DISCLAIMER: US and UK sizing is the same and does not require any conversion. The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Ochre features a golden Ochre one-piece EVA foam construction. Oval cut-outs throughout the design provide ventilation, while a cushioned footbed offers support.

The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Ochre released in August of 2021 and retailed for $80.

name: Stone Sage
title: adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Stone Sage
description:
The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Stone Sage features a sculptural EVA foam and algae blended construction that arrives in a Stone Sage monochromatic color scheme. From there, a grooved outsole provides traction and support.

The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Stone Sage released in March of 2022 and retailed for $90.

name: Ronnie Fieg Knicks
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 12.1 Ronnie Fieg Knicks
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 12.1 Ronnie Fieg Knicks comes from the mind of Kith founder Ronnie Fieg and adds several updates while maintaining the core of the Gel-Kayano 12.1. This sneaker comes in a colorway of blue, silver, and orange that celebrates the New York Knicks.

At the Ronnie Fieg Knicks ASICS Gel-Kayano 12.1, While the upper keeps the original Gel-Kayano 12 mesh and leather construction, the midsole features tooling from the Nimbus 17. Designed for distance running, the Nimbus 17 midsole gives the sneaker a performance-driven aesthetic. The signature tiger stripe overlays feature Cream and silver, which complements the subdued Cream base and allows the splashes of orange and blue to stand out.

Our experts appreciate the meaning behind the design elements embroidered on the tongues. The left shoe displays ‘Kayano’ in Japanese, which celebrates the designer behind the original Gel Kayano series, while the right shoe features ‘Friend’ in Japanese, which pays tribute to Kith’s slogan. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 12.1 Ronnie Fieg Knicks was released on June 24, 2024, and retailed for $180.

name: Light Grey White (Kids)
title: adidas Campus 00s Light Grey White (Kids)
description:
The adidas Campus 00s Light Gray White (Kids) is a children’s sized sneaker from the adidas Campus 00s line that is dressed in a light gray and white color scheme.

The Campus 00s feature a fresh design that introduces the latest generation to adidas. This kid sized sneaker was inspired by the skateboarding culture, with sports design elements such as a chunky white midsole, short toebox, and lush padded heel collar. Crafted with premium materials, the primarily light gray upper is made of suede. adidas branding is seen with debossed Trefoils on the tongue and heel counter while the iconic Three Stripes on the quarter side panels boast some unique jagged lines.

We think that the fuzzy suede on the upper of this sneaker is what sets it apart. It adds a tactile sensation that little fingers will just want to touch. The adidas Campus 00s Light Gray White (Kids) sneaker retailed for $110 when it was released on March 1, 2023.

name: Soot
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Soot
description: DISCLAIMER: US and UK sizing is the same and does not require any conversion.

name: Marblehead Light Aluminum
title: New Balance 2002R Marblehead Light Aluminum
description:
The New Balance 2002R Marblehead Light Aluminum was originally released in 2005. Its minimalist features shades of grey colorway.

The stylish and versatile New Balance 2002R Marblehead Light Aluminum top features several colors of grey. Its design is of the platinum fabric base and supple leather details. It consists of a netting top with a plain, perforated ashy faux leather surface. It also displays a matching outsole that complements the finishing. The New Balance 2002R Marblehead Light Aluminum has ABZORB innovation and N-ergy padding underfoot.

The New Balance 2002R Marblehead Light Aluminum was released in September of 2020 for a price of $140.

name: Licorice
title: New Balance 1906R Licorice
description:
The New Balance 1906R Licorice is a performance shoe whose design was inspired by the 2000s era of running style.

This unique colorway of the New Balance 1906R comes with a white and off-white mesh upper. Synthetic overlays in gray and a pink licorice color cross the upper, sectioning off the toe box and forming supports above the arches. The New Balance "N" logo appears on both sides with NLock branding. The heel is supported by a beige TPU heel counter with an NB logo at the back. The midsole features ABZORB technology for extra comfort, and the white, gray, and yellow rubber outsole complete the shoe's look.

What stands out about this sneaker is the streamlined licorice colorway of the overlays, as each color complements the other without being too bold. The New Balance 1906R Licorice was released on March 1, 2024, for a price of $155.

name: White Black Gold
title: Onitsuka Tiger Tokuten White Black Gold
description:
The Onitsuka Tiger Tokuten White Black Gold fuses innovation with heritage in its bold colorway and classic low-profile silhouette. It's a stylish shoe made from top-class materials. This continues the brand's reputation for creating elevated streetwear.

These Onitsuka trainers have a pure leather upper with an off-white colorway. The hallmark Onitsuka stripe pattern flows across this in black. A metallic gold back heel tab adds just a touch of bling. A cushioned footbed assures comfort, and the rubber outsole is grippy and durable.

Our reviewers love the simplicity of this shoe. It's pure distilled Onitsuka tech in a classy-looking casual trainer with the evergreen design of the famous court shoes of the 1980s. One appreciates the premium materials immediately on first wearing. This perfectly balances a sports-inspired sneaker and a stylish casual shoe. The Onitsuka Tiger Tokuten White Black Gold was released on 1 August 2023, priced at $70.

name: Black White
title: Puma Suede Classic XXI Black White
description:
Like its predecessors, the Puma Suede Classic XXI Black White boasts a construction made of soft suede. However, this suede is sourced from an environmentally sustainable leather manufacturer.

The Black White Puma Suede Classic XXI pays homage to the original Suede released in 1968 through its upper design. The sneaker’s Puma Black and Puma White colorway gives the shoe a retro feel, while the rubber outsole provides extra traction and grip. In terms of branding, ‘PUMA SUEDE’ in gold lettering runs along the side overlays and matches the Puma logo on the heel tab. The suede tongue peeks out from behind the laces and displays a logo tag with ‘PUMA’ and the Puma logo.

Our experts like the full lace closure with black laces that secures the low-top shoe without adding bulk to the sleek silhouette. The Puma Suede Classic XXI Black White was released on February 19th, 2021, and retailed at $70.

name: Resin
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 MNVN Resin
description:
Constructed of a mint green neoprene upper with bold, reflective "700" text, the adidas Yeezy Boost 700 MNVN offers a springtime feel. An enclosed cord lacing system allows easy slip-on, slip-off accessibility for those on the go. From there, a thick Boost sole provides cushioning and responsiveness.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 MNVN Resin released in February of 2022 and retailed for $220.

name: Utility Black
title: adidas Yeezy 500 High Tactical Boot Utility Black
description:
The adidas Yeezy 500 Tactical Boot Utility Black is a monochromatic military-inspired model that is designed to be a sporty and stylish unisex sneaker. It is a high-top pair of shoes that falls past the top of the wearer’s ankle and has classic shoelaces that go to the very top.

This adidas Yeezy 500 model is completely black. It is primarily composed of several different materials, including suede, mesh, and Nubuck, which is a top-grain leather. While the model is entirely black, from certain perspectives, it reveals anthracite reflections from the very top of the shoe down to the sole.

A feature that our group of experts loves about the adidas Yeezy 500 model is the adiPRENE sole that is meant to provide the wearer with additional support and comfort. This pair of shoes first was released onto the market on August 14th, 2023, with a starting retail price of $300.

name: Jack Harlow Rose Runner (Special Box)
title: New Balance 1906R Jack Harlow Rose Runner (Special Box)
description:
The New Balance 1906R Jack Harlow Rose Runner (Special Box) is an update on the original sneaker, marking the rapper's first collab with NB. A striking shoe, it sold out immediately on first release due to its luxury materials and unusual design.

This version retains all the hallmarks of the New Balance 1906R. It has the ABZORB cushioning in the heel, with proprietary Acteva Lite midsole padding, and the outsole has NB's N-ergy impact absorption technology. The pink upper colorway is a metallic tint floral print made from embroidered cotton textiles with pink leather overlays. Contrasting this is a chunky sea-green heel and sole.

We see this as a serious collectible for any New Balance connoisseur. It comes in a limited-edition Rose Runner box, giving it a designer touch. The colorway is imaginative and has a very high-quality feel. A velvety tongue completes this unique shoe. The New Balance 1906R Jack Harlow Rose Runner (Special Box) was released on 31 October 2024, priced at $180.

name: Black White Gum (Women's)
title: adidas Gazelle Bold Black White Gum (Women's)
description:
The adidas Gazelle Bold Black White Gum (Women's) takes an iconic indoor court silhouette from the 1970s and injects it with an exaggerated street style that delivers eye-catching fashion and all-day comfort. This sneaker is specifically sized for women.

This reimagined classic features an upper of black suede, with a black suede T-toe overlay as well as an eye stay overlay. Black laces criss-cross over a white tongue with black trefoil branding. The white textile sock liner is echoed in the white leather heel tab, the white leather serrated three stripes on the side panel, and the white Gazelle branding on the lateral side. The gum rubber sole unit features an outsole lugged with trefoils and circles for traction and an easy ride.

The feature of this women’s shoe that we most enjoy is the triple-stacked platform outsole, where the three layers are clearly marked in a step-like configuration going up the sidewall. The adidas Gazelle Bold Black White Gum (Women's) was released on December 1, 2023, for a retail price of $120.

name: What The Paul
title: Nike SB Dunk Low What The Paul
description:
The Nike SB Dunk Low What The P-Rod pays homage to past Nike SB collaborations and releases from the P-Rod signature line. Its mismatched upper comes in an array of mesh, leather, suede, patent leather, and woven materials. Paul Rodriguez’s signature on the tongue and special edition metal deubrés complete the design.

The Nike SB Dunk Low P-Rod released in May of 2021 and retailed for $150.

name: Plum Eclipse (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Plum Eclipse (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Plum Eclipse W was released as an individual colorway for the Nike Dunk Low silhouette and was specifically designed for women sizing.

The Plum Eclipse Nike Dunk Low W is constructed with high-quality leather and is perforated at the toe box for breathability. The sneaker also features a padded collar and tongue for extra comfort. The shoe has a Nike Zoom Air unit in the heel for added cushioning and support. The midsole is made of lightweight and durable foam that provides shock absorption and responsiveness. The outsole extends up around the toe and heel of the sneaker to provide extra protection and durability.

We think that the standout feature of Nike Dunk Low Plum Eclipse W is its unique colorway. The combination of Plum and Coconut Milk on the leather and suede upper makes for a fashionable and appealing sneaker. The Nike Dunk Low Plum Eclipse W was released on June 8th, 2023 at a retail price of $120.

name: UNC (PS)
title: Nike Dunk Low UNC (PS)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low UNC 2021 PS sneaker is dressed in two main color schemes; university blue and white hues.

The upper part of this Low Nike Dunk for pre-school is crafted from 100% leather material that is accented with a blue Swoosh and matching blue overlays. The nylon tongue of this shoe sports a woven Nike tag while its sole is made from Nike's rubber cupsole. A white midsole lies on a university blue outsole and a blue lacing system completes the design of this silhouette.

The Nike Dunk Low UNC 2021 PS was first made available for sale on June 24, 2021, at a suggested retail price of $65.

name: Sparrow Flat Taupe
title: New Balance 9060 Sparrow Flat Taupe
description:
The New Balance 9060 Sparrow Flat Taupe sneakers are always ready for action. Whether chosen for their refreshing color palettes or the standard street cred with NB, these refined sneakers continue to deliver.

New Balance’s 9060 series is an additional expression of the innovative design that stemmed from the original 99X range. Slick and slim-fitting, the shoes’ textile uppers combine unique colorways in this range, with taupe, sparrow, and vintage rose being the primary colors on this design. Combined with a beige and white chunky midsole, the shoes come together as a work of art. With a lace enclosure and the traditionally bold and solid N logo on the outside of the shoe, the inside has an outlined version of the same logo. The shoes also boast Abzorb cushioning in the midsole for a bouncy step and great rubber outsoles for traction.

We love that the New Balance 9060 Sparrow Flat Taupe is a unisex shoe that can be worn by men and women alike. When released on 19 November 2024, it had a retail price set at $150.

name: Turtledove
title: New Balance 550 Turtledove
description:
The New Balance 550 Turtledove updates a classic basketball silhouette introduced in 1989 and dresses it in creamy shades that blend together to create a monochromatic sneaker that glides along with subtle style.

The Turtledove / Angora colorway of the New Balance 550 features an upper of turtledove-colored mesh overlaid with soft Angora-colored leather, sporting microperforations on the side panel and across the vamp. Other leather overlays cover the toe cap, heel counter, and collar. Angora-colored laces cross over a turtledove mesh tongue adorned with an Angora-colored tongue patch. The two-toned matching rubber cupsole has a foam wedge on the medial side and sits atop a matching two-toned rubber outsole with a traction pattern comprising circles, ridges, and misshapen blocks.

What we love most about this sneaker are the tonal hits of New Balance branding subtly placed across the sneaker. The classic side-panel N is cut out, the words "New Balance" appear embossed on the midsole and outsole, a flying NB appears on the midsole, heel counter, and insole, and a 550 is stamped on the vamp. The New Balance 550 Turtledove was released on April 6, 2023 for a retail price of $120.

name: Georgetown (GS)
title: Nike Dunk Low Georgetown (GS)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Georgetown GS is a Georgetown Hoyas-themed Nike Dunk Low. Boasting a dark obsidian, wolf gray, and total orange color scheme, this shoe features a gray leather base upper. It also features navy-colored overlays, tongue tag, inner lining, embroidered heel, and rubber outsole. The total orange color of this shoe appears on its branded insole. For breathability, this grade school-sized shoe has several perforations on its toe box, and for comfort, it has a cushioned midsole.

The Nike Dunk Low Georgetown GS was released in November 2021. At the time of its release, its retail price was $100.

name: Undefeated Multi-Patent Pink Prime
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low SP Undefeated Multi-Patent Pink Prime
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low SP Undefeated Multi Patent Pink Prime is special project sneaker in collaboration with UNDEFEATED.

The upper section of this Low SP Air Force 1 model is constructed of various colors of patent leather. The sky blue tongue, black and white insole, and purple heel sport the 5-strike logo and the black laces feature an "UNDFTD" design in a hot pink that matches the Swoosh emblem. The sea foam green midsole atop a kelly green outsole features Air branding.

The Nike Air Force 1 Low SP Undefeated Multi Patent Pink Prime was released on November 18th, 2022 at $160 retail.

name: Wheat Grass Cacao Wow
title: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Wheat Grass Cacao Wow
description:
The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Wheat Grass Cacao Wow is a sneaker from the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 lineup in a ‘Wheat Grass’ colorway.

The upper features a low-top construction with an open mesh base and leather overlays. The quarter panel is made of plastic, overlaid by the trademark Swooshes. More plastic detailing features on the heel counter. Other details include 3M reflective hits on the leather overlays, Bill Bowerman graphic on the insole, ‘NIKE VOMERO 5’ branded tongue tags, heel branding, and white round laces. A Zoom Air-cushioned sole unit with multidirectional treads on the rubber outsole rounds out the design.

What our experts love about this sneaker is its colorway and construction. The color combination gives this shoe a warm and earthy look, ideal for the fall season, while the richly layered design creates a unique and stylish look. The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Wheat Grass Cacao Wow was made available for purchase on February 10th, 2023, for a retail price of $160.

name: White Party
title: adidas Harden Vol. 8 White Party
description:
The adidas Harden Vol. 8 White Party is an innovative collaboration between the iconic sneaker company and legendary NBA shooting guard James Harden.

This elite basketball shoe begins with a white textile upper surrounded by a white EVA cage. A white leather toe cap and a white synthetic heel counter add protection and support with every move. The gray sock-like cuff offers a comfortable snug fit and pull tabs at the heel and tongue facilitate on-off. A midsole crafted from white Jet Boost offers cushioning for landings and springy energy return for takeoffs. The rubber outsole features a classic James Harden traction pattern surrounded by herringbone grooves.

The standout aspect of this sneaker is the dual branding on the heel. James Harden branding on the gray pull tab sits just above the iconic adidas three stripes in gray rubber coursing down the heel. The adidas Harden Vol. 8 White Party was released on April 1, 2024, for $160 retail.

name: Triple Black
title: Nike Air Max Scorpion FK Triple Black
description:
Dressed in an all-Black color scheme, the Nike Air Max Scorpion FK Triple Black is one of the market's Air Max Scorpion FK editions.

The Triple Black Nike Air Max Scorpion FK sneaker showcases a sleek, all-black Flyknit upper that offers a sock-like fit, providing unparalleled comfort and flexibility. Its Triple Black colorway exudes a sophisticated and modern aesthetic, making it suitable for sports and casual wear and for versatile use. The sneaker’s upper also features a Nike Swoosh lacing system and the pull tab on the heel. Concluding the design is the durable rubber outsole with a patterned tread for traction and stability on various surfaces.

What our experts think is the special feature of the Nike Air Max Scorpion FK Triple Black that debuted on the 8th of December 2022 with a recommended retail price of $250 is the iconic Air Max technology integrated into the midsole. It delivers superior cushioning and shock absorption, enhancing performance and reducing strain during wear.

name: Sacai Black Patent Leather
title: Nike Blazer Low Sacai Black Patent Leather
description:
The Nike Blazer Low sacai Black Patent Leather features a black white patent leather construction with matte black leather overlays and white Swooshes. Doubled tongues, eyestays, and laces emphasize sacai's focus on reconstruction and abstract design. From there, a stacked white midsole completes the design.

The Nike Blazer Low sacai Black Patent Leather released in April of 2022 and retailed for $120.

name: Denim Leopard
title: Nike Air Max 1 Premium Denim Leopard
description:
The Nike Air Max 1 Premium Denim Leopard combines animal designs with a DIY aesthetic. The upper is made of textured white material with 2 different tones of dark blue denim construction on the mudguard and quarter panels.
​
​Textile overlays at the heel are decorated with leopard spots, and the collar features a red and gold floral pattern. The vamp is covered in woven cheetah print overlays, while the crisp white handcrafted stitching and repetitive pattern of little Swooshes that is fanning out in the insoles add accents to the overall design. The sneaker also has a red-tinted Max Air unit tucked down in the heel and is supported by a white polyurethane midsole.
​
​What our experts especially love is the braided rope-like laces, tan leather tongue tabs, and gold eyelets which add sophisticated accents adorning the richly textured oriental-inspired silks visible throughout the red heel tab and yellow embroideries. The Nike Air Max 1 Premium Denim Leopard released on 28th April 2023 retailed at $160.

name: Track Red Smoke Grey
title: Nike Air Max 95 Track Red Smoke Grey
description:
The Nike Air Max 95 Track Red Smoke Grey takes the retro Nike Air Max 95 silhouette and applies a pigmented colorway of Black, Smoke Grey, Anthracite, and Track Red.

Like other Air Max 95 models, the Track Red Smoke Grey edition finds inspiration in the running aesthetic of the 1990s as well as the human form. Although Black, Smoke Grey, and Anthracite make up the dominant tones, Track Red provides eye-catching pops of color. A small Swoosh embroidered near the lateral heel, part of the "Air Max" tongue tag, and the visible Nike Unit in the heel come in Track Red. Although the upper is made of mesh, wavy leather side panels make the shoe stand out.

Our experts love the bulk created by the foam midsole and chunky rubber outsole. The Nike Air Max 95 Track Red Smoke Grey was released on July 27th, 2023, and retailed at $185.

name: Black Croc (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low LX Black Croc (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low LX Black Croc (Women's) crafts a classic silhouette in deluxe materials in a contrasting colorway that pops with undeniable style. This sneaker has been specifically sized for women.

This Luxe sneaker builds upon an upper base of smooth white leather. Perforations spatter the toe box for enhanced comfort with every step. Black patent leather with a crocodile pattern forms the side panel Nike swoosh as well as the iconic overlays at the toe cap, midfoot, eye stays, collar, and heel. The white textile sock liner is padded for ankle comfort and matches the white insole with black Nike branding. The white foam midsole provides cushioning and support underfoot and rests atop a gum rubber outsole that offers a multidirectional grip.

The standout detail of this eye-catching women's sneaker that we most enjoy is the tongue tag branding, which sparkles in metallic gold. The Nike Dunk Low LX Black Croc (Women's) was released on April 5, 2024, for a retail price of $135.

name: Sun Glow Team Sky Blue
title: New Balance 9060 Sun Glow Team Sky Blue
description:
The New Balance 9060 Sun Glow Team Sky Blue dresses the 9060’s technical silhouette in vibrant Sun Glow with accents in Team Sky Blue, pink, black, and green.

Maintaining its visible tech look and contrasting upper, the Sun Glow Team Sky Blue New Balance 9060 boasts molded pods on the outsole in off-white, pink, and Team Sky Blue. The chunky, dual-density midsole has responsive ABZORB and ABZORB SBS cushioning for long-lasting shock absorption. Sun Glow covers the mesh base and some of the layered pig-suede overlays, while black darkens part of the midsole, the laces, and the tongue. Splashes of Team Sky Blue add brightness to the overlays, the eyestays, and the breathable lining.

Our experts at StockX like the signature New Balance "N" logos. The outer side features a standard "N" and the inner side boasts a reverse "N" logo. The New Balance 9060 Sun Glow Team Sky Blue was released on May 24, 2024, and sold for $150.

name: Black Neon
title: Nike Air Max 95 Black Neon
description:
The Nike Air Max 95 Black Neon adds a vintage colorway of Volt, black, Anthracite, and Smoke Gray to the Air Max 95 classic silhouette.

This heritage colorway presents as black and gray with splashes of Neon Yellow. Like other Air Max 95 models, the "Black Neon" version boasts an upper made of mesh and suede. Overlapping suede panels create a color gradient along the side panels, fading from black to Smoke Gray. Hints of Volt peak out from behind the mesh upper and complement the small Swoosh logo near the heel. In addition, the black laces wind through nylon loops that come in Volt and secure the sneaker’s lace closure.

Our experts at StockX like the way the addition of Volt in the midsole makes the Air units in the forefoot and heel stand out. The Nike Air Max 95 Black Neon was released on September 13th, 2023, and retailed at $175.

name: Salehe Bembury Prosperity Be The Prize
title: New Balance 530 Salehe Bembury Prosperity Be The Prize
description:
The New Balance 530 Salehe Bembury Prosperity Be The Prize is a shoe designed as part of a collaboration between the brand and luxury streetwear designer Salehe Bembury.

The Salehe Bembury Prosperity Be The Prize version of the New Balance 530 has an upper made of mesh in a celery-green color. This material makes up the base, while dusty-yellow nubuck leather overlays form the toe cap and cross the sides in curves, supporting the upper. The New Balance N makes an appearance on each side in gray with a fingerprint pattern inside, while the lateral heel contains 530 and Salehe Bembury branding. The heel is supported by yellow overlays and has a pull tab, while the tongue contains more NB branding. The shoe sits on a light-brown midsole with ABZORB cushioning and a purple outsole.

What stands out about this sneaker is the bold color scheme—the mix of green, yellow, red, and purple is truly eye catching. The New Balance 530 Salehe Bembury Prosperity Be The Prize was released on October 29, 2024, for $150.

name: Hangul Day
title: Nike Air Max 1 Premium Hangul Day
description:
The Nike Air Max 1 Premium Hangul Day has become one of the most popular models in the Nike Air Max brand since its release.

The Nike Air Max 1 Premium Hangul Day comes in white, Coconut Milk, Sail, and Summit White colorways which completes the texture. The sneaker is made from leather, rubber, and suede materials. It features a small Swoosh at the quarter and at the sides of the toe box. It has an air unit and a Nike logo at its heel.

The Nike Air Max 1 Premium Hangul Day was released on November 17, 2022 at a suggested retail price of $160.

name: Industrial Blue
title: Nike Dunk Low Industrial Blue
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Industrial Blue combines a classic leather construction with revitalized colorways on the classic Dunk Low silhouette.

The Industrial Blue Nike Dunk Low, constructed using a classic white leather foundation, features overlays of nubuck leather in both black and Industrial Blue shades. The branding is prominently displayed on the blue panel Swooshes, offering a distinctive burnt effect, while a subtle black hue outlines the edges of the checks. Further detailing can be spotted on the Nike tongue tag, insoles with branding, and the white embroidered Nike heel logo. These elements come together atop a white midsole and black outsole, while the shoe is elegantly tied together with black laces for a coordinated and polished appearance.

What our experts find outstanding about the Nike Dunk Low Industrial Blue is its exceptional color blocking. This sneaker showcases a captivating blend of white, black, and Industrial Blue hues, masterfully arranged to create a visually striking design. The sneaker was released on August 11th, 2023, for $110.

name: MX Carbon
title: adidas Yeezy Foam RNR MX Carbon
description:
The adidas Yeezy Foam RNR MX Carbon features a pink, yellow, purple, and dark grey marbled EVA foam and recycled algae construction with ventilation holes throughout the design. At the base, a sculptural sole adds cushioning and support. Please note that the pattern may vary.

The adidas Yeezy Foam RNR MX Carbon released in August of 2022 and retailed for $90.

name: White Sweet Pink
title: ASICS GT-2160 White Sweet Pink
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 White Sweet Pink is an athletic shoe with a mesh fabric upper in White, accented by silver and Sweet Pink overlays. Sweet Pink accents encase the heel, displaying GEL and GT-2160 branding, while additional ASICS branding adorns the tongue. The linear carved White midsole showcases the outsole, which intersperses Sweet Pink and gray tread.

Japanese athletic wear brand ASICS has been perfecting its skill at crafting sneakers for various sports and lifestyle wear since 1949. With its GEL technology midsole inserts, ASICS has refined its performance cushioning for superior comfort while running. Beyond that, the GT-2160 adheres closely to the GT-2000s from the 2010s era, continuing the lineage of the shoe’s signature design elements.

In our opinion, the best feature of the Sweet Pink GT-2160 is its multicolored outsole, which emphasizes the Sweet Pink color story. The ASICS GT-2160 White Sweet Pink released on May 1, 2024, and retailed for $120.

name: AMBUSH Flash Lime
title: Nike Dunk High AMBUSH Flash Lime
description:
Rendered in a neon green, the Nike Dunk High AMBUSH Flash Lime arrives with tonal color blocking similar to the Active Fuchsia colorway. Most of its upper is monochromatic, except on the black Swoosh that accentuates its re-imagined proportions.

The Nike Dunk High AMBUSH Flash Lime released in July of 2021 and retailed for $180.

name: Adobe
title: Nike SB Dunk Low Adobe
description:
The Nike SB Dunk Low Adobe was made available in a mix of suede, canvas, and leather materials. 

The sneaker comes in a colorway made up of adobe and clay red tones, which give the panels and upper a tonal appearance. White intricate stitching and the Nike logo can be found on the heel as well as on the mesh tongues. The eyelets, eye stays, and laces also display an adobe colorway. The insole of the shoe features skateboard-inspired designs, and the gum rubber outsole completes the look.

The Nike Dunk Low Adobe was released on on January 3rd, 2023. The pair retailed at $110.

name: PSG
title: Nike Air Max Plus PSG
description:
In collaboration with the Paris Saint Germain football club, once again, Nike plays tribute to these great players with the Nike Air Max Plus PSG sneaker, representing the team’s home kit.

This PSG tribute to Nike Air Max delivers a dynamic shoe in the team's traditional colors, blending midnight blue, red, white, and black with gold accents. The show mimics the lines of the team’s jersey on the upper textile. The outer shoe boasts a gold Swoosh, while the structural cage of the shoe provides integrity, which is synonymous with this comfortable, highly supportive shoe. The PSG logo sits on the heel and insole, while Air cushioned units pump up the midsole of this durable and bouncy shoe. 

What we think is the standout feature of the Nike Air Max Plus PSG is the dynamic pattern displayed all over the upper, in a design that resembles waves in the three colors. When released on 1 August 2024, it was priced at $200.

name: Midnight Navy Total Orange
title: Nike Air Max Plus Drift Midnight Navy Total Orange
description:
The Nike Air Max Plus Drift Midnight Navy Total Orange reimagines Sean McDowell’s original Tuned Air design to offer an eccentric shoe with a dynamic feel and iconic underfoot cushioning.

The upper of this brightly undulating sneaker is a Vibrant Blue mesh that offers both ventilation and a lightweight feel with every step. A light blue TPU cage outlined by dark TPU covers the foot offering support and a singular style. An orange lateral heel Nike Swoosh matches the tinted Air in the visible midsole cassettes. The rubber outsole features bright blue lugs with hits of both orange and aqua for multi-surface grip.

Our favorite feature of this sneaker is the midfoot plate, the centerpiece of this mesmerizing shoe. Bisecting the midsole, the orange support plate appears in the shape of a whale's tail outlined by both light and dark blue TPU. The Nike Air Max Plus Drift Midnight Navy Total Orange was released on April 1, 2024, for a retail price of $185.

name: Photon Dust Light Iron Ore
title: Nike Air Max 90 Photon Dust Light Iron Ore
description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Photon Dust Light Iron Ore provides high performance running durability while taking style inspiration from a '90s running shoe aesthetic.

The upper of the Air Max 90 in a Photon Dust/Light Iron Ore colorway starts with a base of ghostly white ribbed textile. Tumbled leather overlays in a creamy tan adorn the toe box and side panel, while smooth chocolate brown leather forms the mud guard. Hits of sail TPU appear in a cut-out window on the lateral side panel as well as on the eye stays and heel counter. Nike Air branding appears on the heel and white mesh insole, Air Max branding in the side-panel window, and Nike branding on the tongue tag.

What our shoe experts appreciate most about this sneaker is its high-octane sole unit. Sail foam and tan TPU form the midsole that houses a visible Zoom Air unit for cushioning and reactive support. The waffle lugs on the sail and tan rubber outsole offer impact absorption and grip. The Nike Air Max 90 Photon Dust Light Iron Ore was released on August 12, 2023, for $130 retail.

name: Light Melon Orange
title: Nike LeBron Witness 6 Light Melon Orange
description:
The Nike LeBron Witness 6 Light Melon Orange was released as part of the Nike LeBron Witness series.

The Light Melon Orange Nike LeBron Witness 6 is designed with a lightweight, breathable mesh upper that offers ventilation and durability on the court. It features a TPU mudguard for added protection and stability, ensuring that you can make quick cuts and moves without the worry of sliding or slipping. The foam midsole ensures that the shoe will keep your feet cushioned and comfortable, protecting them from the impact of the ground. The outsole of the shoe is made of rubber and is designed with a unique traction pattern that provides grip and traction on the court.

Our experts say that one of the significant features of the Nike LeBron Witness 6 Light Melon Orange is the Zoom Air cushioning technology in the sole, which provides a responsive and comfortable feel during those high jumps and dives. The shoe was released on October 12th, 2021 at a retail price of $110.

name: Recraft Rose (Women's)
title: Nike Air Max 90 Recraft Rose (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Recraft Rose W is a variation of the Nike Air Max 90 sneaker made for women.

The Recraft Rose W Nike Air Max 90 has a sole that features Air Max technology in the heel to provide responsive cushioning. The outsole is made of a durable rubber material with a waffle tread pattern, and the tongue and collar of the shoe are padded for additional comfort. The upper is made of a combination of premium leather and breathable mesh materials, with white, gray, and rose colors.

The Nike Air Max 90 Recraft Rose W was released on February 1, 2020 at a retail price of $120.

name: Splash Volt
title: Nike Dunk Low SE Splash Volt
description:
The Nike Dunk Low SE Splash Volt is a special edition colorway of the Nike Dunk Low sneaker catalogue.

The Splash Volt Nike Dunk Low SE features an upper that is made from leather and suede. The sneaker includes a padded collar and tongue to provide a comfortable fit for all-day wear, while the lace-up closure ensures that the shoe stays securely in place.

We think that one of the key features of the Nike Dunk Low SE Splash Volt is its vibrant luminous upper. The unique upper is made of synthetic leather that has been treated with a special reflective material, making it glow in the dark. The shoe features a Volt colorway with a mix of Green Strike, black, and Total Orange hues. This gives the shoe a unique and eye-catching appearance that is perfect for those who love to make a statement with their footwear. The Nike Dunk Low SE Splash Volt was released on June 14th, 2023 at a retail price of $110.

name: Coconut Milk
title: Nike Dunk Low Coconut Milk
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Coconut Milk features an off-white tumbled leather upper with pale yellow overlays and white Swooshes. Woven tongue labels and heel embroideries nod to the original 1985 design. From there, a matching Air sole at the base completes the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Coconut Milk released in March of 2022 and retailed for $100.

DISCLAIMER: Yellow may appear different in various lighting situations.

name: Action Green Altitude Green
title: Nike Air Max Waffle Racer SP Action Green Altitude Green
description:
The Nike Air Max Waffle Racer SP Action Green Altitude Green is a performance shoe equipped with both Air Max and waffle technology.

This iteration of the Nike Air Max Waffle Racer SP has a lightweight textile upper in Action Green, allowing for breathability and flexibility. Suede overlays, also in green, form the toe cap, eyestays, and the sides of the heel. Black leather Nike Swooshes adorn both sides of the shoe. The heel counter and collar are made of black leather, with a Tuned Air logo and the Nike brand name appearing in Total Orange. The tongue also bears a Nike Air logo. An Air Max unit can be found under the heel, while the black outsole creeps up over the heel and forefoot with its waffle traction pattern.

What stands out about this shoe is the fact that it combines the best elements of both types of technology, giving it even more function. The Nike Air Max Waffle Racer SP Action Green Altitude Green was released on November 14, 2024, for $140.
model: Nike Air Max Waffle Racer SP

name: Aqua Blue
title: Nike Air Max Plus Aqua Blue
description:
The Nike Air Max Plus Aqua Blue is a striking addition to the iconic Air Max line, offering a fresh take on a classic silhouette. This eye-catching sneaker features a vibrant aqua blue upper, creating a bold contrast against the black accents. The signature wavy TPU overlays, a hallmark of the Air Max Plus design, add depth and texture to the shoe while providing structural support.

Engineered for both style and comfort, this sneaker boasts Nike's renowned Air cushioning technology in the heel and forefoot. The visible Air units not only enhance the shoe's aesthetic appeal but also deliver responsive cushioning with every step. The breathable mesh upper ensures ventilation, while the padded collar and tongue provide a snug, comfortable fit. Finished with a durable rubber outsole, these shoes offer excellent traction and durability for everyday wear.

Us at StockX believe this product is great for those seeking a perfect blend of retro style and modern comfort. The vibrant colorway makes it an ideal choice for sneaker enthusiasts looking to make a statement while enjoying the legendary Air Max cushioning.

name: Championship White Red
title: Nike Dunk High Championship White Red
description:
Similar to classic Dunks from the mid-1980's, the Nike Dunk High Championship White Red carries a more traditional look with a two-tone color blocked leather upper. At the base, a matching Air sole completes the design.

The Nike Dunk High Championship White Red released in May of 2022 and retailed for $115.

name: Earth Strata Wonder White Off White (Women's)
title: adidas Gazelle Earth Strata Wonder White Off White (Women's)
description:
These sporty adidas Gazelle Earth Strata Wonder White Off White (Women's) have stood the test of time since 1991, bringing you decades of street culture in a sporty yet stylish shoe. With a minimalistic, sleek design made for dancing and city living, the Gazelle is the ultimate sneaker for modern women on the move.

Put your best foot forward with adidas Gazelle Earth Strata. This comfortable, retro-inspired design with a mocha-colored hairy suede outer has a white tongue and ankle collar with off-white 3-Stripes branding. The gold Gazelle branding lies alongside the stripes, while an embossed white Trefoil sits on the back collar. With a rubber outsole for excellent traction, supported midsoles, and a lace enclosure, these beautifully crafted sneakers are perfect for urban adventures.

We can’t get enough of the classy look of the suede uppers of these adidas Gazelle sneakers. Steeped in tradition and as relevant as ever, the earth tones bring a Boho-inspired look to any outfit. The adidas Gazelle Earth Strata Wonder White Off White (Women's) was released on 6 April 2024 and retailed at $100.

name: White Pure Platinum (2021)
title: Nike Air Huarache White Pure Platinum (2021)
description: The Nike Air Huarache White Pure Platinum 2021 is a sleek and stylish sneaker that combines comfort and performance. The upper is made of a breathable mesh material that provides ventilation and support, while the neoprene inner sleeve offers a snug and comfortable fit. The white and pure platinum colorway gives the shoe a clean and modern look that is perfect for any occasion. The shoe features a Phylon midsole and Air-Sole unit in the heel for cushioning and shock absorption. The rubber outsole provides traction and durability. The Nike Air Huarache White Pure Platinum 2021 was released on August 15, 2021, and retails for $120. This shoe is a must-have for anyone looking for a comfortable and stylish sneaker that can be worn for any occasion.

name: Anthracite
title: Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Anthracite
description:
The Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Anthracite adds a black-on-black colorway of Anthracite to the signature Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit silhouette.

This sneaker boasts a durable woven upper made from Flyknit, which conforms to the foot’s shape while allowing the foot to breathe. This material stretches around the contours of the foot and creates a seamless design. In addition, a perforated sockliner adds to the snug yet comfortable fit. A front-closure lace system secures the sneaker, while the heel tab allows for easy removal and application of the shoe. However, what makes this sneaker stand out is the one-piece Air unit, which provides responsive cushioning and spans the length of the foot.

Our StockX experts like the subtle Swoosh logo printed across the Flyknit upper because it doesn’t distract from the sneaker’s minimalist aesthetic. The Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Anthracite was released on September 26, 2023, and sold for $210.

name: Dark Team Red Croc (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low LX Dark Team Red Croc (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low LX Dark Team Red Croc (Women's) is a luxury edition of the classic Dunk Low design, featuring a smooth premium leather upper in a dark Team Red croc print colorway.

A phantom colored upper in leather is the base for the luxe detailing of the dark Team Red crocodile print that wraps and winds its way around the toe cap, up through the eyestay, down through to the ankle, and then on the heel counter as well. Against the smooth white, the red print provides contrast and depth. The midsole is sail and sits upon a gum light brown outsole. An elegant shiny metallic gold Nike logo is printed on the foam tongue.

Our experts think that the standout feature of this sneaker are the matching flat laces, they round out the shoe’s aesthetic. When it made its retail debut on April 11, 2024, the Nike Dunk Low LX Dark Team Red Croc (Women's) sold for $135 retail.

name: Green Grey
title: New Balance 1000 Green Grey
description:
The New Balance 1000 Green Grey is a performance shoe with a retro design that comes in layers.

The Green Grey New Balance 1000 contains an upper made of leather, ripstop fabric, and suede. The top of the shoe around the laces is white leather, while the heel tab is made of asymmetric white mesh. The heel tab carries a New Balance "N." Under this sea-salt white layer is a thin layer of gray ripstop, which snakes around from the heel where New Balance branding is, to the toe, and up the other side. Underneath this layer of ripstop is Mallard Green suede and leather, which dominate the bottom half of the shoe. The leather toe cap and suede supports on the side are accented with white and contain 1000 branding. The New Balance "N" also appears on the sides in white. The midsole and outsole are also green.

Our favorite thing about this shoe is the asymmetric design of the heel and the branding present there, which adds an extra bit of style. The New Balance 1000 Green Grey was released on September 11, 2024, for $150.

name: Suede Panda
title: Nike Dunk Low Retro SE Suede Panda
description:
As classic as you can get, the Nike Dunk Low Retro SE Suede Panda is a durable and always-on shoe ready to be taken out regardless of the occasion.

These black and white low-rise basketball-inspired shoes have stood the test of time with Nike fans and once again deliver the goods in stylish suede and leather textiles. The upper colorways are a bold contrast of black and white, hence the Panda name. Foam midsoles offer lightweight and highly responsive cushioning for extended wear. The rubber outsole provides durable traction for quick responses when you need to stay light on your feet. The padded collar adds extra comfort, and the Nike Swoosh sits on the outside of the shoes while the tongue boasts the Nike name.

Where will you take your favorite Dunk Low Retros? We love the bold contrast of this classic sneaker cut, making it one of the most contemporary pairs of Nike sneakers for everyday use. The Nike Dunk Low Retro SE Suede Panda was released on 12 July 2024, priced at $125.

name: Dark Blue Bliss Orange
title: adidas Gazelle Indoor Dark Blue Bliss Orange
description:
The adidas Gazelle Indoor Dark Blue Bliss Orange blends a modern dark blue, bliss orange and preloved ink color colorway with the iconic 1960s design of the adidas Gazelle Indoor silhouette.

This low-top profile exudes classic, timeless aesthetic. The dark blue upper is made from natural leather and synthetic materials. A furry texture, like a terry cloth towel, covers most of the upper, while smooth lighter blue overlays adorn the toe cap and eyelet. The collar is padded for durability where the heel rubs most, while the perforated tongue boasts a bliss orange adidas branded patch. White flat laces match the three white stripes with jagged detailing on the side panels.

In our opinion, a standout feature of the adidas Gazelle Indoor Dark Blue Bliss Orange colorway would have to be the gum-colored mudguard with embossed adidas branding on the side that doubles as the outsole with adidas trefoil lugs underfoot. Originally released on August 23, 2024, this shoe was priced at $120 retail.

name: White Maroon Banner
title: ASICS Gel-1130 White Maroon Banner
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 White Maroon Banner features an upper composed of at least 20% recycled material and a sock liner constructed to reduce both water usage and carbon emissions, making this stability runner environmentally-friendly, as well as stylish and comfortable.

The White Maroon Banner ASICS Gel-1130 running shoe builds upon an upper base of white mesh that is overlaid with strips of synthetic leather in shades of silver, sail, and maroon. The toe cap and heel are especially fortified. The tongue is white and maroon mesh, while the flat white laces contrast with the maroon mesh sock liner. GEL branding hits both a heel overlay and the tongue tag. The foam midsole in sail is enhanced with GEL technology for ultimate cushioning. The sneaker rides on a dark purple and maroon rubber outsole vented with grooves to enhance flexibility as you run.

The detail that we enjoy most on this sneaker is the silvery TRUSSTIC SYSTEM midfoot plate that helps provide arch support and foot stability. The ASICS Gel-1130 White Maroon Banner was released on July 30, 2024, for a retail price of $95.

name: Triple Black (Women's)
title: Nike Air Max 270 Triple Black (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Max 270 Triple Black (W) is another sleek addition to the Air Max collection. It is a sneaker made with a rubber sole and aerated top that makes sure your feet are able to breathe.

The Nike Air Max 270 release for women is displayed in black color. It features a web-like top material rubber outsole and lace-up closure. The shoe has a netted and fabricated top, a fluff midsole, and an elastic inner sole.  

The Nike Air Max 270 Triple Black (W) sneaker sold at a retail price of $150 and was out in the market on August 2, 2018.

name: White Black
title: adidas Forum Low White Black
description:
The adidas Forum Low White Black is a basketball-inspired sneaker.

The Forum Low White Black features a strap system on the side panels and a padded tongue and collar, as well as a cushioned insole. The sole of these shoes are made from durable rubber, providing excellent traction on different surfaces. The shoe features a combination of white and black leather on the upper, with a white midsole and a black rubber outsole. The adidas logo is displayed on the side and on the strap that goes across the tongue.

We think that the notable feature of the adidas Forum Low White Black sneakers is their classic basketball-inspired design. This iconic sneaker features a distinctive ankle strap for added support, with details such as a low-cut silhouette and perforated toe box for breathability. The adidas Forum Low White Black was released on May 5, 2021 at a retail price of $110.

name: Black Phantom
title: New Balance 1906R Black Phantom
description:
The New Balance 1906R Black Phantom is a sleek and stylish addition to the renowned 1906R lineup. This men's sneaker showcases a sophisticated all-black colorway, making it a versatile choice for various occasions. The upper is crafted with a combination of premium materials, including breathable mesh and durable synthetic overlays, ensuring both comfort and longevity. The iconic 'N' logo adorns the sides, adding a touch of brand recognition to the minimalist design.

Featuring New Balance's innovative cushioning technology, the 1906R Black Phantom offers exceptional comfort and support for all-day wear. The midsole incorporates the brand's signature ABZORB foam, providing responsive cushioning and impact absorption. The rubber outsole delivers reliable traction on various surfaces, making these sneakers suitable for both casual wear and light athletic activities. With its modern silhouette and performance-driven features, the New Balance 1906R Black Phantom is an excellent choice for sneaker enthusiasts seeking a blend of style and functionality.

Our experts state this product is great for those who appreciate a minimalist aesthetic combined with advanced comfort technology, perfect for urban explorers and style-conscious individuals alike.

name: Patta Waves White
title: Nike Air Max 1 Patta Waves White
description:
The Nike Air Max 1 Patta Waves White is a sneaker that was released as a collaboration between Nike and Patta as a commemorative the 1-of-1 "ROMAN FOREVER" iteration, remembering Patta co-founder Edson Sabjo’s late son.

The White Nike Air Max 1 Patta Waves has a mix of white leather and blue-tinted grey mesh that features a distinct wavy leather overlay above cream-colored Air bubble midsoles. Logos of "Patta Air Max" are found on the tongue tabs and the insoles are blank. Nike Air emblems round out the design on the heel and white waffle outsoles. 

The sneaker was released on the 26th of August, 2022, with a retail price of $160.

name: Triple Black Shiny Toe
title: Nike Air Presto Triple Black Shiny Toe
description: The Nike Air Presto Triple Black Shiny Toe is a sleek and stylish addition to any sneaker collection. This shoe features a black-on-black colorway with a shiny toe cap for added texture and depth. The upper is made of a breathable mesh material, while the midsole provides cushioning and support for all-day comfort. The outsole is made of durable rubber for traction and grip on any surface. Released on February 4th, 2021, this shoe retails for $130. Whether you're hitting the gym or running errands, the Nike Air Presto Triple Black Shiny Toe is a versatile and fashionable choice.

name: Purple Burst
title: adidas Harden Vol. 8 Purple Burst
description:
The adidas Harden Vol. 8 Purple Burst is a colorway that will burst on the court. Presenting in purple burst, core black and silver metallic color scheme, this futuristic looking silhouette is designed to revolutionize how you play basketball.

This bold colorway will turn heads thanks to its smooth lines and energetic color. The upper of this basketball shoe features a liner that fits like a sock. This helps natural movement. EVA side cages are in purple to provide support and help with dynamic angles and quick footwork. The back heel area has ribbed reinforcement and a cascading aesthetic. A black toe box adds contrast, while three black stripes adorn the heel for a change. Matching laces in purple burst complete the look.

Our favorite feature of the adidas Harden Vol. 8 Purple Burst is the full length JETBOOST, which boasts small, firm energy capsules for supreme energy return and stability. This shoe was released on October 1, 2024, and retailed for $160.

name: Gorge Green
title: Nike Dunk Low Gorge Green
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Gorge Green is a low-cut sneaker from the lineup in a gorge green, team red, white, and gum medium brown color scheme.

This shoe features an all-leather upper with a white base, gorge green overlays, and team red on the Swooshes and inner lining. Other details include a perforated toe box, a lace-up closing system with white laces, and NIKE branding on the heel, tongue tab, and green insole. Rounding out the design is a white midsole that rests on a gum rubber outsole.

The Nike Dunk Low Gorge Green was released on October 1st, 2022, retailing at $110.

name: Black Sail
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Vintage Black Sail
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 Vintage Black Sail sneaker has hung around for nearly 50 years.

Nike Blazer Mid 77 Vintage Black Sail silhouette is constructed from a foam-infused nylon tongue with suede accents and leather uppers, including cotton laces and a vulcanized (hardened) rubber sole. Originally a basketball shoe, Nike Blazer Mid 77 Vintage Black Sail’s comfortable and classic look. The Nike Blazer Mid 77 Vintage Black Sail silhouette features plenty of retro hoops style and a basketball-inspired silhouette .

The Nike Blazer Mid 77 Vintage Black Sail model was released in October 2020, retailing at $100.

name: White Oyster Grey
title: ASICS Gel-NYC White Oyster Grey
description:
The ASICS Gel-NYC in White Oyster Gray is a running shoe that combines elements of other ASICS Gel sneakers to create a comfortable and high-performance hybrid. The shoe comes in a white, beige, and gray colorway, making the shoe versatile.​
​​
​This sneaker’s upper is inspired by the ASICS Gel-NIMBUS 3 and MC-PLUS V sneakers. The upper is made of mesh with suede and synthetic leather overlays. It also contains Gel technology in the heel and forefoot to provide comfort, both while running and during everyday wear. ​
​​
​What we at StockX like most about this running shoe is its light and simple colorway that allows for wear with almost any outfit. Whether you’re hitting the track or running errands, this shoe is ideal for almost any situation. The ASICS Gel-NYC in White Oyster Gray was released on July 14, 2023, for a retail price of $130.

name: Light Orewood Brown
title: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Light Orewood Brown
description:
The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Light Orewood Brown is a blend of retro design elements with cutting-edge running technology that gives you a visually dynamic and performance-oriented trainer. Thanks to its neutral tones and layered makeup, it appeals to everyone, whether looking for a trendy kick or a sports shoe.

The Light Orewood Brown Zoom Vomero 5 by Nike comes with a breathable mesh upper complemented by synthetic overlays for added depth. Its Light Orewood Brown base is accented by lighter details that add to the contrast. A Zoom Air midsole gives you responsive cushioning, while the textured outsole offers some extra grip. The Vomero line was introduced in the mid-2000s and quickly became popular among runners.

One thing we, the experts, love about the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Light Orewood Brown is its combination of Zoom Air technology for lightweight cushioning, the toe cap and the criss-cross laces set. Released on 1st September 2024, it retailed at $160.

name: Rattan Sea Salt
title: New Balance 550 Rattan Sea Salt
description:
A striking blend of retro appeal and modern design, the New Balance 550 in the Rattan Sea Salt colorway made its mark on the scene on June 1, 2023. This sneaker serves nostalgia with a twist.

The Rattan Sea Salt upper is a feast for the eyes, the natural earth tones create a fresh and clean aesthetic. Equipped with New Balance's renowned comfort and durability, this shoe is ready for whatever the day brings.

The New Balance 550 Rattan Sea Salt gives you the style edge. Launched on June 1, 2023, with a retail price of $120, it's a worthwhile addition to any footwear collection.

name: Off-White Sheed
title: Nike Air Force 1 Mid SP Off-White Sheed
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Mid SP Off-White Sheed is part of the legacy of the late designer Virgil Abloh. He designed the shoe to pay homage to NBA player Rasheed Wallace, who often wore the AF1 and contributed to the shoe’s popularity.

The "Sheed" comes in an all-black design with a shiny, patent leather upper. The bright white laces, swoosh, midsole, and branding details contrast the deep black base. The sneaker features the number ‘30’ embroidered onto the ankle strap as well as Rasheed Wallace’s silhouette stitched onto the heel. The outsole boasts track spikes on the forefoot that, when combined with the bold stitching on the Swoosh, give the sneaker an edgy appearance.

Our StockX experts love the visible Nike Air unit in the heel, which adds a splash of red to the sneaker. The Nike Air Force 1 Mid SP Off-White Sheed was released on September 8, 2023, and retailed at $205.

name: Steel Grey
title: New Balance 530 Steel Grey
description:
The New Balance 530 was originally released in 1992, and the New Balance 530 in Steel Grey is a recreation of the company’s classic running shoe designs.

The New Balance 530 Steel Grey boasts of a synthetic mesh upper construction with steel grey leather overlays appearing on most of the upper. The signature N logo appears in white, and the white continues to the laces and the chunky ENCAP midsole and ABZORB heel cushioning. The adjustable lace closure provides a comfortable fit, and the ABZORB heel cushioning provides comfort.

The New Balance 530 Steel Grey was released in January 2021 and originally retailed for $110.

name: Cloud White (Non-Reflective)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cloud White (Non-Reflective)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cloud White (Non-Reflective) combines shades of cream and bluish-white to recreate the hue of a fluffy cloud. A hard sole offers a contrast to the elastic shoelaces and knitted fabric upper. Instead of separate overlays, the upper has the appearance of a single stitched-together piece. One side of the sneaker offers a transparent strip, and the other highlights the blue-and-white patterns. The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cloud White (Non-Reflective) uses Primeknit to create a woven textile appearance.

adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cloud White (Non-Reflective) released in September of 2019 and retailed for $220.

name: Nori
title: New Balance 9060 Nori
description:
New Balance first introduced the 9060 model in 2022. It was inspired by New Balance’s 99x series, and it led to the development of sneakers like the New Balance 9060 Nori.

This New Balance 9060 sneaker features a green synthetic upper with hits of white and grey. The upper also swipes the sway bars from the New Balance 990 to help create the wavy lines in its design that make it appear as though it’s always in motion. This New Balance 9060 has a dual-density midsole as well as that is equipped with both ABZORB and SBS cushioning for added comfort, and it even includes things like a tongue logo that was inspired by the lace jewel found in the New Balance 991.

But the thing our experts like most about this New Balance shoe might be what it has on the bottom of it. The outsole has a diamond pattern inspired by the New Balance 860 that helps differentiate it further from other New Balance sneakers. The New Balance 9060 Nori was released on August 12, 2023, for $150.

name: MiUSA Patta Keep Your Family Close
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Patta Keep Your Family Close
description:
The New Balance 990v3 Patta Keep Your Family Close arrives in an olive and bright green color palette.

The New Balance 990v3 Patta Keep Your Family Close features an upper that is constructed from suede and mesh for breathability. The shoe's midsole features New Balance's trademark ENCAP technology for cushioning. The outsole is constructed using a tough rubber mixture for durability. On the sides of the shoe, you can find the "N" logo, while the tongue displays the inscription "new balance USA." Additionally, the heel of the sneaker showcases the lettering "USA P" and the brand name "new balance."

The New Balance 990v3 Patta Keep Your Family Close was released on September 30, 2022, and retailed for $220.

name: Black Dark Grey
title: New Balance 2002R Black Dark Grey
description:
The New Balance 2002R Black Dark Grey arrives in a monochrome suede with a leather and mesh construction.

The New Balance 2002R Black Dark Grey has got the "N" logo placed on both sides of the shoe and also on the front part of the shoe's outsole. The New Balance 2002R Black Dark Grey mesh uppers have overlays of black leather and suede engulfing the silhouette. The design includes a grey and black sole unit, a bright white midfoot motif, and metallic silver rears. 
  
  The New Balance 2002R Black Dark Grey was released in June 2022 and retailed for $140.

name: Metallic Teal New Spruce
title: New Balance 1906R Metallic Teal New Spruce
description:
The New Balance 1906R Metallic Teal New Spruce is a running shoe inspired by the 2000s era of runners’ style with a bold color blocking scheme.

This iteration of the New Balance 1906R is made with a white and off-white mesh base for breathability. The shoe features overlays of Metallic Teal running across the sides of the shoe as well as the toe box. The toe box is rounded out with a perforated metallic silver overlay. The classic New Balance N logo appears on each side of the shoe in brown with "NLock" branding. 1906R branding can also be found on the lateral side of the heel on the overlay. The heel is supported by a khaki plastic heel counter complete with a small NB logo. What provides most of the support, though, is the ABZORB midsole. The outsole is a combination of gray, beige, and yellow and is branded with the Nergy logo.

Our favorite thing about this shoe is the presence of Stability Web technology in the outsole, which provides additional support to the arch. The New Balance 1906R Metallic Teal New Spruce was released on March 24, 2024, for a price of $160.

name: Aime Leon Dore White
title: New Balance 1000 Aime Leon Dore White
description:
The New Balance 1000 Aime Leon Dore White is Aime Leon Dore’s preppy and urban take on the iconic 1000. It dresses the 1000 in an off-white colorway without any splashes of color or significant adornments.

This limited-edition Aile Leon Dore White New Balance 1000 features co-branded elements on the tongue and subtle ‘NEW BALANCE,’ ‘1000,’ and ‘abzorb’ branding on the heel. The upper is crafted from perforated leather in off-white with synthetic, gray leather overlays and metallic accents. This color combination maintains Aime Leon Dore’s polished approach to streetwear and preference for organic color combinations. The thick Abzorb midsole gives the sneaker a slightly chunky silhouette and provides responsive cushioning, while the Stability Web shank offers support.

Our experts at StockX like the asymmetrical New Balance ‘N’ logo on the side panel. Its shape harks back to archival designs and the off-white color emphasizes the sneaker’s worn-in, vintage aesthetic. The New Balance 1000 Aime Leon Dore White was released on June 5, 2024, and sold for $165.

name: Iron Grey
title: Nike Air Max 90 Iron Grey
description:
Originally designed as running shoes, the Nike Air Max 90 Iron Grey sticks to its roots with the Waffle sole, a textile/leather upper, and classic TPU details.

The Nike Air Max 90 Iron Grey features a textile upper with leather and synthetic overlays. Most of the sneaker is in iron grey, with the Swooshes appearing in white on the lateral and medial sides. The low top also includes a padded tongue and collar for maximum comfort, and underfoot, Max Air cushioning provides cushioning, while the Waffle sole adds traction and durability.

The Nike Air Max 90 Iron Grey was released in January 2020 and retailed for $120.

name: Black White (Women's)
title: Nike Air Max 270 Black White (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Max 270 Black White (W) comes in a black and anthracite-white color scheme.

The Nike Air Max 270 Black White for women features an upper comprised of mesh and synthetic materials, making it lightweight and breathable. The shoe's heel is cushioned and stabilized with a full-length Max Air unit. The foam in the midsole is responsive and makes for a nice, snug fit. The grip and sturdiness of the shoe are provided by the rubber outsole. The sneaker features a pull button on the back for easy on-and-off. The shoe's collar and tongue are cushioned for enhanced comfort. The shoe features a Nike Swoosh on either side.

The Nike Air Max 270 Black White (W) was released on March 22, 2018, and retailed for $150.

name: Sporty & Rich Green
title: adidas Handball Spezial Sporty & Rich Green
description:
The adidas Handball Spezial Sporty & Rich Green is part of Sporty & Rich’s fourth pack with adidas. This sneaker is one of three Handball Spezial models reimagined by Emily Oberg in pastel colorways.

Featuring a pastel green colorway with white accents, the indoor Sporty & Rich Green adidas Handball Spezial shoe has a soft suede upper. The 3-Stripes and the heel mustache come in smooth, white leather, while the rubber outsole boasts thick gum. The ‘SPORTY & RICH’ lettering along the 3-Stripes logo is printed with gold foil that stands out against the green base. Other branding details include the rectangular Sporty & Rich logo tag stitched onto the flat, suede tongue.

Our StockX experts like the way the suede material brings out the softness in the pastel green, giving the sneaker a premium feel. The adidas Handball Spezial Sporty & Rich Green was originally released on May 23, 2024, and was priced at $100.

name: White Vast Grey (Women's)
title: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 White Vast Grey (Women's)
description:
The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 White Vast Grey (Women's) is a shoe in women’s sizes with a monochromatic colorway.
  
The White Vast Grey (Women's) Nike Zoom Vomero 5 is made with a breathable and durable white mesh upper enhanced with TecTuff technology. Supportive artificial overlays form the toe cap and mudguard, while white TPU cages are seen on each side of the shoe with the Nike Swoosh on top. The heel counter also features a supportive cage with a crisscross pattern, along with subtle Nike branding at the back. A Nike Vomero 5 logo patch appears on the tongue, while Zoom Air cushioning in the midsole provides responsiveness and energy return. The midsole is a combination of white and Vast Grey, while the rubber outsole is black and white. 
 
What we appreciate most about this shoe is the Zoom Air cushioning subtly built into the model, which provides functionality and comfort. The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 White Vast Grey (Women's) was released on March 25, 2024, for $160.

name: Cream Black Leopard (Women's)
title: adidas Gazelle Bold Cream Black Leopard (Women's)
description:
The adidas Gazelle Bold Cream Black Leopard (Women's) is a striking addition to adidas' iconic Gazelle line, blending modern design with classic influences. It features leopard-print accents set against cream and black tones, and redefines casual footwear while maintaining its old-fashioned appeal.

The Cream Black Leopard Gazelle Bold for women by adidas is designed with premium faux grain leather and suede overlays for a textured look. The upper features a beige foundation complemented by bold black leopard patterns along the signature 3-Stripes and heel tab. The platform sole adds both height and modern flair. The Gazelle line started in 1966 and has continuously evolved by blending innovative ideas with its original look and feel.

As experts, one feature we appreciate about the adidas Gazelle Bold Cream Black Leopard (Women's) is its reinforced heel counter for added stability and the platform sole, which improves comfort and boosts the design. When this model was initially released on May 1, 2024, it retailed at $110.

name: Sporty & Rich White Collegiate Burgundy
title: adidas Samba Sporty & Rich White Collegiate Burgundy
description:
The adidas Samba Sporty & Rich White Collegiate Burgundy is a classic soccer shoe designed in collaboration with the Sporty and Rich brand.

This timeless shoe features a white leather upper with Collegiate Burgundy accents on the iconic 3-Stripes pattern and the back tab. It is lined in satin for a luxurious feel that aligns with the Sporty & Rich brand, whose name appears in gold foil letting on the shoe’s side. Also featured in this model is a rubber toe cap for protection and a high-grip, gum outsole for traction. Co-branding on the tongue nods to this third collaborative effort between adidas and Sporty & Rich.

What our experts love most about the adidas Samba Sporty & Rich White Collegiate Burgundy is the subtle cream tones in the forefoot, laces, and interior liner that adds a touch of elegance to the overall aesthetic. This shoe was first released on November 10, 2023, with an initial price tag of $120.

name: Penny PE
title: Nike Air Foamposite One Penny PE
description:
The Nike Air Foamposite One Penny PE features a combination of white, metallic silver, black, cobalt bliss, and racer blue hues.

The Foamposite One Penny PE Nike Air showcases an upper crafted from Nike's Foamposite material, known for its durability. Its molded construction ensures a secure and comfortable fit. The lacing system is designed to offer customization in fit. For cushioning and impact protection, the midsole incorporates a full-length Zoom Air unit that is highly responsive. To deliver traction and stability, the outsole is made of translucent rubber with a herringbone pattern. An adjustable fit is facilitated by straps located on the tongue and heel. A small white Nike Swoosh adorns one side of the upper.

The player-exclusive sizing of the Nike Air Foamposite One Penny PE was released on April 7, 2023, and retailed for $240.

name: Undefeated Multi-Patent Total Orange
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low SP Undefeated Multi-Patent Total Orange
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low Undefeated Multi Patent comes in contrasting colors and has a shiny finish.

The paneled upper, which is made of patent leather, is finished in a patchwork of colors, including blue, fuchsia, crimson, purple, and black. Branding includes a laser engraved Nike Air logo on the heel tab and UNDFTD lace dubrae in addition to an embroidered orange Swoosh. The lateral heel and sewn tongue tag feature the Five Strikes logo of Undefeated. The low top is reinforced by a translucent rubber outsole and is built on a white midsole with encapsulated Air-sole.

The Nike Air Force 1 Low Undefeated Multi Patent was released on December 9th, 2022, retailing at $160.

name: HUF Brilliant Orange
title: Nike Air Max 1 SP HUF Brilliant Orange
description:
The Nike Air Max 1 SP HUF Brilliant Orange is part of a HUF x Nike collaboration that finds inspiration in iconic North American cities. This version of the Air Max 1 is inspired by San Francisco and offers a colorway of Brilliant Orange, Medium Gray, Anthracite, and Gunsmoke.

The HUF Brilliant Orange Nike Air Max 1 SP boasts a premium leather construction with a light gray base and overlays in Medium Smoke or Gunsmoke. The soft gray hues mimic the color of the fog that frequently covers San Francisco. Touches of Brilliant Orange brighten the Swoosh logo, the inner lining, the logo tag on the tongue, and part of the rubber outsole. The thin laces also include a combination of Brilliant Orange and Anthracite.

Our experts like the co-branding on the tongue because it represents both Nike and HUF. The Nike Air Max 1 SP HUF Brilliant Orange was originally released on June 15, 2024, and retailed at $160.

name: Triple White (TD)
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low LE Triple White (TD)
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low LE Triple White (TD) is a limited-edition sneaker and is an iteration of the Air Force 1.

The Air Force 1 Low LE Triple White (TD) comes in toddler sizes and features a padded collar and tongue, which provides extra comfort and support. The Nike Air unit in the sole of the shoe provides cushioning to absorb shock and protect from impact. Additionally, the rubber outsole provides traction, making the sneaker suitable for various terrains. The sneaker also features perforations on the toe box for added breathability.

We think that one of the most notable features of the Nike Air Force 1 Low LE Triple White (TD) is its clean and minimalist design. The shoe is completely white, from the leather upper to the rubber sole, creating a sleek and classic look. The shoe was released on March 29th, 2021 at a retail price of $48.
