name: Michigan State Satin (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Michigan State Satin (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Michigan State Satin (Women's) introduces a low-top iteration inspired by the 2020 Michigan State Dunk.

The Michigan State Satin Nike Dunk Low for women’s most notable alteration is seen in the construction of the base layer. Rather than the usual leather, the toeboxes, side panels, and heels are crafted from a satin material. A Spartan Green shade adorns elements like the Swooshes, laces, inner linings, overlays, as well as the Nike branding on the tongues and heels. To balance the color scheme, a clean white tone is applied to the toeboxes, quarter panels, tongues, and collars. Moving downward, the midsoles remain devoid of color, resting atop green outsoles to round off the design.

What our experts love about the Nike Dunk Low Michigan State Satin (Women's) is the striking Michigan State color scheme. This sneaker's bold and vibrant green and white color combination pays homage to the university's iconic hues, capturing the spirit of Michigan State University. The sneaker debuted for $110 on August 11th, 2023.

name: White Black
title: Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 White Black
description:
The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 White Black is a classic sneaker that pays homage to its heritage as a design created for the Japanese national team during the 1968 Mexico City Olympics.

This shoe features a sleek and minimalist design, with a low-top profile and clean lines that give it a versatile aesthetic. The upper is crafted from premium leather and suede for durability and a high-end look and boasts a solid white colorway against which contrasting black elements pop on the heel tab, tongue, and the iconic Onitsuka Tiger stripes at the sides. A cushioned midsole teams up with a padded collar and tongue to provide support and shock absorption, delivering comfort during all-day wear. Reinforced stitching ensures that this shoe maintains its structure and shape despite frequent use.

What our experts most enjoy about the Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 White Black, however, is the way its design draws inspiration from the brand’s roots for a timeless appeal. This shoe originally retailed for $120 on January 24, 2022.

name: Lunar New Year (Women's)
title: Nike Air Max 90 Futura Lunar New Year (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Futura Lunar New Year (Women's) is a reimagining of the Nike Air Max 90 with splashes of bright color and overlapping overlays. As a celebration of the Lunar New Year, the sneaker also pays homage to traditional Chinese culture through eye-catching details.

The colorway includes a variety of vivid tones, including Fuchsia, Baltic Blue, Cosmic Fuchsia, White, and Vivid Orange. Red tones represent wealth and prosperity. The White mesh upper is covered in colorful overlays with a wide black mudguard that wraps around the shoe. The chunky, White midsole features Max Air cushioning, which can be seen through a molded plastic window that comes in Baltic Blue. The plastic window tonally matches the Baltic Blue tread on the toe.

Our experts love the heel tab's delicate, cursive "AIR" lettering. The women’s size Nike Air Max 90 Futura Lunar New Year (Women's) was released on March 1st, 2023, and retailed at $130.

name: Yankees
title: ASICS Gel-NYC Yankees
description:
The ASICS Gel-NYC Yankees takes inspiration from GEL silhouettes of the past, and dresses it in the colors of the New York Yankees.

This retro-looking running shoe features an upper inspired by the GEL-Nimbus 3 and the GEL-MC Plus V. A white mesh upper that promotes maximum airflow is overlaid with synthetics and suede in shades of dark blue. Synthetic and leather overlays in shades of gray course across the side panel give this sneaker the distinctive ASICS look. The midsole in white and shades of gray combines GEL technology in both the forefoot and the rear foot in order to provide springy cushioning and energy return with each step you take. The white outsole with pods of gray rubber is grooved for grip and vented for flexibility.

The detail we appreciate most on this very New York pair of kicks is the subtle ASICS branding in white that hits a blue overlay just below the lateral collar. This branding pops even as it blends into the aesthetic of the shoe. The ASICS Gel-NYC Yankees was released on March 3, 2023, for an original retail price of $130.

name: Indigo Haze (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W is an addition to Nike's Dunk lineup of sneakers in women's sizing. 

The Indigo Haze Nike Dunk Low W has a low-cut silhouette that allows for easy movement of the foot, while the padded collar and tongue offer additional cushioning and support around the ankle. Additionally, the shoe features a rubber sole that provides grip and durability, making it suitable for a wide range of activities. The toe box is perforated for added ventilation while the Nike name branding is visible on the tongue and heel tag. The Nike Swoosh is on both sides in Indigo Haze.

We especially love the Low Nike Dunk in Indigo Haze for Women for its striking colorway. The sneaker has a Sail upper with contrasting Indigo Haze overlays and Coral Chalk accents which creates a sleek and stylish look. The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W was released on March 31st, 2023 at a retail price of $110.

name: Fade Carbon
title: adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Fade Carbon
description:
The adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Fade Carbon features a red-to-purple gradient Primeknit upper with semi-translucent TPU lace cage unit and light grey reinforced toe wrap. The gradient theme continues on the EVA foam sole, where red on the heel transitions into a light grey. A black mesh collar and lace system completes the design.

The adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Fade Carbon released in May of 2022 and retailed for $210.

name: Supreme Black
title: Nike Air Force 1 Mid Supreme Black
description:
Another dynamic collaboration between streetwear giants Nike and Supreme comes in the form of the Nike Air Force 1 Mid Supreme Black. Slick, durable, and tough, this sneaker was designed for urban warriors.

The Nike Air Force 1 Supreme collab is a hard-working high-top made from full-grain leather in sleek all-black coloring. The shoe is understated and classic, with only a simple embroidered red box with the Supreme logo on the back outer heel. Velcro straps give double support over the lace enclosure, which travels up the length of the high-top. Extra-cushioned, with back heel collars and thick midsoles, the shoes are chunky with a rubber outsole. Additional co-branding is on the lace lock and tongue label and a debossed Nike swoosh on the outer shoe.

Be at your most comfortable, whether during a tough game on the courts or a night out, with these iconic high-tops. The mid-high of the shoe is what our team likes the most about the Nike Air Force 1 Mid Supreme Black. They were released on 29 August 2024, priced at $133.

name: Mono Cinder
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Mono Cinder
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Mono Cinder arrives with a Cinder lightweight mesh upper with a tonal side stripe and perforations exposing an interior skeletal frame. A Cinder Boost sole and heel loop completes its monochromatic look.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Mono Cinder released in June of 2021 and retailed for $220.

name: Calcite Glow
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Calcite Glow
description:
Yeezy added a new colorway to their expanding 380 line with the Yeezy 380 Calcite Glow, now available on StockX. While 380 releases following the Alien colorway are known for their brown, earth-toned look, the Calcite returned to the design’s roots with a ghostly vibe just in time for Halloween.

The Yeezy 380 Calcite Glow is reminiscent of the very first Yeezy 380 release, the Yeezy 380 Alien. Similar to the Alien, the Calcite Glow features a white and grey perforated Primeknit upper. The main difference between the two colorways is that the Calcite Glow primarily features white throughout, with grey detailing. Also, the Calcite comes with a translucent, glow-in-the-dark sole that is guaranteed to add some extra glow to your feet.

The Yeezy 380 Calcite Glow released in October of 2020 and retailed for $250.

name: Black Yellow
title: adidas Harden Vol. 8 Black Yellow
description:
The adidas Harden Vol. 8 Black Yellow is a basketball shoe designed with American basketball star James Harden.

The Black Yellow adidas Harden Vol. 8 has a black mesh base for breathability and airflow. Yellow TPU supports appear on each side in a teardrop shape, standing out against the black and allowing for stability. A leather toe cap adds even more stability, while the TPU supports extend around the heel. The adidas 3-Stripes are also seen creeping up the back of the heel from the outsole. The socklike cuff and pull tabs on the tongue and heel allow for easy on and off, and Harden’s branding is found on the heel pull tab.

What we like most about this sneaker is the contrast between the black and yellow colors, which allows it to stand out. The adidas Harden Vol. 8 Black Yellow was released on August 1, 2024, for $160.

name: Year of the Dragon 2.0
title: Nike KD 4 Year of the Dragon 2.0
description:
The Nike KD 4 Year of the Dragon 2.0 celebrates the Chinese Lunar New Year and the Year of the Dragon through significant colors and design details. The sneaker is also part of a collaboration between Nike and NBA player Kevin Durant.

The faux leather upper comes in Khaki and Sesame, which serves as a backdrop for the dragon motif. This graphic winds around the Noble Red Swoosh and ‘KD’ lettering embroidered on the heel. Noble Red accents can also be found on the collar, the inside of the tongue, and the laces. While red symbolizes good luck and good fortune, the yellow on the outsole represents prosperity and wealth. Like other KD models, this sneaker boasts a strap that crosses from the ankle to midfoot.

Our StockX experts like the woodgrain pattern on the strap. It sets the sneaker apart from other models and complements the shoe’s tan tones. The Nike KD 4 Year of the Dragon 2.0 was released on February 7th, 2024, and retailed at $150.

name: Turtledove
title: New Balance 9060 Turtledove
description:
The New Balance 9060 Turtledove reimagines the classic 99X models with a nod to the futuristic tech sneaker aesthetics from the early 2000s.

The Turtledove colorway of the New Balance 9060 begins with an upper base of lightweight, breathable ivory mesh. Suede and soft leather overlays in gradient shades from creamy white to tan ripple across the upper in wavy strips, calling to mind a feeling of motion. A translucent CR device at the heel helps add to foot stability, while the white lace closure over the ivory tongue provides a secure fit with every step. The side panel N is stitched on to the outer side and embroidered on the inner.

The aspect of this eye-catching sneaker that impresses us most is the high-octane sole. The four-tone foam midsole features ABZORB underfoot and SBS ABZORB under the heel for cushioning and energy return. The black rubber outsole with diamond-shaped beige rubber pods is a nod to the 860 silhouette. The New Balance 9060 Turtledove was released on June 21, 2023, for $160 retail.

name: Black Gym Red
title: Nike Air Max 2 CB '94 Black Gym Red
description:
The Nike Air Max 2 CB '94 Black Gym Red is an athletic shoe endorsed by former basketball player Charles Barkley.
  
This version of the Nike Air Max 2 CB '94 is made with a Gym Red nubuck upper with perforations on the side panel and toe box for breathability. Black tumbled leather overlays form the t-shaped toe cap and run down from the eyestays to the midsole on each side. Black leather also forms the heel. Perforations in the black leather coming from the eyestays reveal white leather underneath, while the Nike brand name is seen across the lateral side. The heel and tongue also feature white Nike Air branding. The eyestays have a heavy-duty look to them, and the shoe sits on a white midsole containing a black swoosh under the lateral heel. A transparent Air Max unit also sits under the heel.   

Our favorite things about this shoe are the eyestays, which give the sneaker a hardcore and durable look. The Nike Air Max 2 CB '94 Black Gym Red was released on June 1, 2024, for $170.

name: Triple Red
title: Nike Air Max 270 Triple Red
description:
The Nike Air Max 270 Triple Red is part of the Nike Winter 2019 collection.

The Nike Air Max 270 Triple Red footwear has a color scheme of University Red and Black. It has a front-lace-up system with a pull tab at its heel, so it can be slipped on. Its upper part comprises woven mesh and synthetic fabric made of 100% polyester. Its two-piece midsole is foam, while the flat Air Max sole is made of 100% rubber. The heel has the Nike visible Air window.

The Nike Air Max 270 Triple Red had a retail price of $160 and was released on 1 December 2019.

name: Protection Pack High Desert
title: New Balance 2002R Protection Pack High Desert
description:
The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack High Desert is an athletic sneaker featuring a dark khaki ripstop nylon base, overlaid with suede in coordinating dark khaki and olive green. The midsole is done in Golden Cream, accented by a black tread outsole. The New Balance logo appears on the sides in black, complemented by black toggle-fasten laces.

New Balance’s Protection Pack series was conceptualized by designer Yue Wu, who delved into the New Balance archives to update classic styles after observing how their forms retain their shape after years of wear. The updated 2002 series has been designed like an heirloom, built to last with durable materials and functionality, nestled under multiple layers for longevity.

In our opinion, the best feature of the 2002R High Desert is its nature-inspired color palette, which will remain a classic, in keeping with its construction. The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack High Desert released on September 21, 2023, and retailed for $160.

name: Bold Orange (Women's)
title: adidas Gazelle Indoor Bold Orange (Women's)
description:
Dressed in Bold Orange, the adidas Gazelle Indoor Bold Orange (Women's) is a retro-inspired offering from the adidas Gazelle Indoor lineup in women’s sizing.

This sneaker features a Bold Orange suede upper highlighted by the trademark 3-Stripes on the laterals and medial in white leather. More leather detailing appears on the white heel pull tab. ‘Gazelle’ branding features on the sides etched in gold next to the 3-Stripes. Other details include a branded tongue tag with the adidas Trefoil logo, flat Bold Orange laces, and a perforated tongue. The upper rests on a translucent wrap-around gum outsole, with the signature ‘adidas’ Trefoil logo on the heel.

What our experts love about this retro-inspired sneaker is its design and colorway. The bold tones on the upper with contrasting details and premium materials give this classic sneaker a timeless look. The adidas Gazelle Indoor Bold Orange (Women's) was made available on January 2nd, 2023. Initially, it retailed at $120.

name: HUF San Francisco
title: Nike SB Dunk Low HUF San Francisco
description:
The Nike SB Dunk Low HUF San Francisco is a collaborative sneaker made of a tumbled leather upper.
​
​The upper has a white base that goes along with black overlays. Printed on the toe vamp of the shoe is a "HUF" text with a metallic Swoosh passing across it. Additional branding details include the standard Nike SB tongue imprint, texts reading "FOREVER" and "KEITH" on the right and left of the heel, respectively, and a reflective skyline of the San Francisco city at the rear. A hidden tie-dye pattern is also found in white and orange.
​
​The Nike SB Dunk Low HUF San Francisco debuted on November 16th, 2022, and retailed at $130.

name: Scarlet Gum
title: adidas Handball Spezial Scarlet Gum
description:
Inspired by indoor sports, the adidas Handball Spezial Scarlet Gum is a retro-inspired sneaker from the adidas Handball lineup in a "Spezial Scarlet Gum" colorway. 

This adidas Handball Spezial sneaker features a Scarlet Red soft suede upper with contrasting hits of white on the jagged edge three stripes branding, branded tongue tag, and heel collar panel. Metallic Gold accents on the  "SPEZIAL" Trefoil branding on the lateral next to the three stripes and the adidas branding on the tongue tag add more contrasting hues to the upper. The iconic T-toe overlay appears on the toe and forefoot. A white branded insole, Scarlet Red round laces, and a Gum sole unit round out the design. 

What our experts particularly love about this adidas Handball Spezial offering is its upper construction and color scheme. The eye-catching color combination and premium materials contribute to its unique and stylish appearance. The adidas Handball Spezial Scarlet Gum was released on July 10th, 2023, retailing at $110.

name: Supreme Rammellzee
title: Nike SB Dunk High Supreme Rammellzee
description:
Introducing the much-anticipated Nike SB Dunk High Supreme Rammellzee, released on August 31, 2023. This latest collab brings the legendary streetwear brand and art together, showcasing Rammellzee's iconic, vibrant artwork across the majority of the sneaker’s upper.

This bold sneaker fuses an abstract color palette throughout most of the sneaker fused with subtle white suede overlays on the mudguard and swoosh. Every angle of this shoe shouts Supreme's audacious style meshing with Rammellzee's legendary artistry. The heel counter, toe box, and mid panel all integrate eye-catching designs that align seamlessly with the overall aesthetic.

Launched on August 31, 2023, the Nike SB Dunk High x Supreme Rammellzee was an instant classic, retailing at $148.

name: Corduroy Baltic Blue
title: Nike Air Max 1 Corduroy Baltic Blue
description:
The Nike Air Max 1 Corduroy Baltic Blue is a retro-inspired sneaker and a colorway addition to the Air Max 1 collection.

The upper of the Air Max 1 Corduroy Baltic Blue features a responsive cushioning system that uses Air-Sole units in the heel and forefoot to provide a comfortable and supportive ride. The midsole is made of lightweight foam, which adds to the overall weight of the sneaker. The Nike Swooshes on the side are in a sesame color, with additional Nike branding on the heel tab and tongue.

We think that the notable feature of the Nike Air Max 1 Corduroy Baltic Blue is the soft and textured corduroy upper in a cool Baltic Blue colorway. The shoe's upper is complemented by a suede toe cap and heel counter, adding a touch of premium style to the overall design. The Nike Air Max 1 Corduroy Baltic Blue was released on March 17th, 2023 at a retail price of $160.

name: Resilient
title: Nike LeBron 21 Cool Grey
description:
The Nike LeBron 21 Resilient dresses the LeBron 21 silhouette in an all-gray colorway with accents in metallic silver. The sneaker boasts a seamless upper and showcases LeBron James’s signature stitched on the tongue.

Like other LeBron 21 versions, the Resilient embodies aspects of LeBron James’s life, in this case, his ability to overcome obstacles. In addition, the sneaker pays tribute to his daughter through the 360-degree zonal cabling system, which mimics the lines on an oyster shell. Just as an oyster protects its pearl, LeBron James protects his daughter. The cabling system reinforces the upper, while the Zoom Air units in the heel and forefoot provide cutting-edge cushioning. Completing the technical additions, full-length Cushlon foam delivers superior comfort.

Our experts at StockX like the molded, chrome-plated Swoosh logo on the outer side panel. It stands out against the Cool Grey upper and adds a premium touch. The Nike LeBron 21 Resilient was released on March 15, 2024, and sold for $200.

name: White Light Purple
title: Nike KD Trey 5 IX White Light Purple
description:
The Nike KD Trey 5 IX White Light Purple is part of Kevin Durant’s 5th edition collaboration with Nike. Like other Nike KD 5 IX models, this high-top basketball shoe comes with a Zoom Air unit in the midsole and a rubber outsole with wave traction.

What makes the KD Trey 5 IX White Light Purple stand out is the clean white base with hints of purple along the outsole. The Swoosh on one side of the shoe is green, while the Swoosh on the other side boasts half green material and half purple thread. The sneaker comes with the ‘KD’ logo embossed on the side, and a flexible mesh upper with a woven appearance.

Something our experts love is the logo debossed tongue which also houses a neon green pull tab with Nike branding. The Nike KD Trey 5 IX White Light Purple was released on June 9, 2021, and retailed at $90.

name: Collegiate Green Gum
title: adidas Handball Spezial Collegiate Green Gum
description:
The adidas Handball Spezial Collegiate Green Gum finds inspiration in indoor handball shoes from the 1970s and updates the silhouette with a vibrant, varsity colorway.

While Collegiate Green is the dominant color across the upper, Cloud White details add contrast. The serrated 3-Stripes logo on the side panels, the collar lining, and the heel tab come in Cloud White. The sneaker also features retro-inspired branding, including ‘SPEZIAL’ printed along the 3-Stripes logo on the lateral side panel in metallic silver lettering. The tongue’s logo tag displays a rectangular logo tag that reads ‘adidas HANDBALL SPEZIAL’ in Cloud White lettering. Like other Handball Spezial models, the "Collegiate Green Gum" version features a semi-transparent gum rubber outsole.

Something our StockX experts like is the inclusion of Cloud White laces. The color choice gives the sneaker tonal balance. The adidas Handball Spezial Collegiate Green Gum was released on August 7th, 2023, and retailed for a price of $110.

name: Lmnte
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Lmnte
description:
Yeezy applied the pressure during the 2020 holiday season and released another 380 colorway with the Yeezy Boost 380 Lmnte. This release follows Yeezy’s reputation of earth-toned colorways, balancing dark and light tones throughout the silhouette, similar to the look of fallen leaves on the forest floor.

The Yeezy Boost 380 Lmnte is composed of a tonal brown camo-print Primeknit upper with a golden spot on the lateral foot. A dark grey translucent Boost midsole, golden yellow outsole, and rope laces channel hiking boot vibes, while retaining the comfortable runner identity that the 380 is known for.

The Yeezy Boost 380 Lmnte released in December of 2020 and retailed for $230.

name: White Metallic Silver
title: Nike Air Max Dn White Metallic Silver
description:
The Nike Air Max Dn White Metallic Silver is a sleek shoe with a futuristic design, featuring the newest version of Air Max technology.
   
The White Metallic Silver Nike Air Max Dn has an upper made of white mesh for breathability. A raised haptic pattern appears in curves across the upper, giving it a textured look. A small Nike Swoosh sits at the bottom of the laces on top of the toebox. White film forms the mudguard, which rounds out the shoe, and the arches are supported and bear small white Nike Swooshes. The gray heel area has Air Max Dn branding, as does the tongue. The shoe sits on a white midsole, and under the heel you can find four transparent Air Max Dn tubes for support and cushioning. The outsole is gray. 

What stands out most about this sneaker are the subtle branding elements, which let the futuristic design speak for itself. The Nike Air Max Dn White Metallic Silver was released on May 3, 2024, for $160.

name: Phantom Light Iron Ore (Women's)
title: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Phantom Light Iron Ore (Women's)
description:
The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Phantom Light Iron Ore (Women's) is a shoe in women’s sizes with a colorway perfect for summer wear. 
   
The Phantom Light Iron Ore (Women's) Nike Zoom Vomero 5 has an upper constructed with an off-white mesh featuring a slightly darker layer underneath. Off-white leather overlays support the toecap and forefoot, while the sides feature Light Iron Ore Gray TPU support cages. The Nike Swoosh appears outlined in black on top of each of the cages. The heel counter is also supported by TPU in a crisscross pattern with Nike branding above it. Nike Vomero 5 branding can be seen on the tongue, and the shoe sits on an off-white midsole with Zoom cushioning for energy return. The outsole is black.

What we love most about this sneaker is the simple colorway, which provides contrast and is bright for summer. The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Phantom Light Iron Ore (Women's) was released on June 1, 2024, for $160.

name: Black Graphite Grey
title: ASICS Gel-NYC Black Graphite Grey
description:
The ASICS Gel-NYC Black Graphite Grey is a performance running shoe that combines elements from heritage and contemporary sneakers in the ASICS catalog.

The upper of the Black Graphite Grey ASICS Gel-NYC draws inspiration from running shoes from the early 2000s, including the Gel-Nimbus 3, while adding embellishments sourced from the MC-Plus V.  Black mesh serves as a base for synthetic leather overlays in Graphite Grey and metallic silver. The rounded edges of the overlays give the metallic silver a fluid look that resembles mercury or liquid metal. Reflective accents increase visibility in low lighting, while the front lace closure secures the fit. In contrast to the retro-inspired upper, the tooling system comes from the Gel-Cumulus 16. This midsole includes gel technology inserts and a combination of lightweight foams.

Our experts at StockX like the molded rubber outsole, which gives the sneaker a technical look. The ASICS Gel-NYC Black Graphite Grey was released on December 1, 2023, and sold for $130.

name: What the Duck Home University of Oregon PE
title: Nike Dunk Low What the Duck Home University of Oregon PE
description:
The Nike Dunk Low What the Duck Home University of Oregon PE pulls off an ambitious stunt. Its colorway is an archive of University of Oregon football uniforms. What makes it unique is that the left and right shoe each has its own colorway.

This Nike Dunk Low model portrays over nine different uniform designs. On one side is a mix of forest green with a burnt orange Swoosh, plus black and gray panels with a bright yellow sole. The other has a black and gray colorway punctuated with ice white, a pink Swoosh, and a neon-green sole. It's a low-profile trainer with an all-leather upper.

We love the very concept of these shoes. Wearing a different colorway on each foot is a fun novelty. More importantly, it makes them very desirable. Of course, Ducks students and alums will immediately covet these. The Nike Dunk Low What the Duck Home University of Oregon PE was released on 11 October 2024, priced at $275.

name: Silver Metallic Collegiate Navy (Women's)
title: adidas SL 72 OG Silver Metallic Collegiate Navy (Women's)
description:
The adidas SL 72 OG Silver Metallic Collegiate Navy (Women´s) delivers a modern take on an iconic running silhouette. This shoe blends vintage aesthetics and premium materials by combining heritage design with modern upgrades, giving you a retro athletic style you can wear every day.

The women´s Silver Metallic Collegiate Navy SL 72 OG by adidas has a metallic silver nylon upper complemented by collegiate navy suede overlays, giving you texture and contrast. The serrated 3-Stripes branding adds a classic touch. The EVA midsole offers lightweight cushioning. The SL 72 is an emblem of adidas' rich athletic history that was initially introduced for the 1972 Olympics and combines performance-driven design with a bold look and feel.

We, the experts, appreciate the combination of the grippy rubber outsole for traction and the breathable nylon upper for extra comfort. The adidas SL 72 OG Silver Metallic Collegiate Navy (Women´s) debuted on 14th August 2024 and retailed at $100.

name: Black (Women's)
title: Nike Shox R4 Black (Women's)
description:
The Nike Shox R4 Black (Women's) dresses the Shox R4 in an all-black colorway, toning down the sneaker’s Y2K design elements.

Originally released in 2000, the Shox R4 silhouette has maintained an understated presence in the retro sneaker scene. However, the women's black iteration replaces the usual bright colorways with a stark black upper and accents in Max Orange. Part of the modified waffle sole, the branding on the tongue, and the line of dots on the heel come in Max Orange. The textile-and-synthetic upper features laser-cut perforations and design lines highlighting the sneaker’s molded design. However, the stand-out feature is the Nike Shox column under the heel. It provides shock absorption while distributing weight across the foot.

Our experts at StockX like that the upper is almost identical to the model from 2001, paying homage to the Shox legacy. The women-sized Nike Shox R4 Black (Women's) was released on April 3, 2024, and sold for $140.

name: Sail Wolf Grey
title: Nike P-6000 Sail Wolf Grey
description:
The Nike P-6000 Sail Wolf Grey is a performance shoe whose design comes largely from the original version of the 2006 Pegasus.

This iteration of the Nike P-6000 features a white mesh upper for breathability. Wolf Grey overlays cross the shoe’s upper horizontally on each side while an off-white overlay forms the toe cap. Off-white overlays also run over the upper vertically, stretching from the sole up to the laces, while a black overlay forms the mudguard above the sole on each side. A black Nike swoosh appears on the toe box, while each side of the shoe is adorned with a large white swoosh outlined in gray thread. The heel counter is formed with an off-white overlay with a small black Nike swoosh and a few perforations, while the tongue also bears the Nike brand name. A white outsole completes the look.

Our favorite thing about this shoe is the hits of black that accent the otherwise white and gray design. The Nike P-6000 Sail Wolf Grey was released on August 29, 2020, for $110.

name: Black White Pebbled Leather
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 Black White Pebbled Leather
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low 07 Black White Pebbled Leather is a low-top AF1 '07 sneaker in a Black/White colorway.

This sneaker features a Black pebbled leather upper with matching stitching highlighted by a White Swoosh and heel tab. Other details include a perforated toe box, ‘NIKE AIR’ branding on the tongue tags, and a lace-up closure system. A solid White midsole with tonal "AIR" branding on the laterals sits on a matching rubber outsole with the signature Air Force One heritage hoops pivot circles for traction.

The Nike Air Force 1 Low 07 Black White Pebbled Leather was released on 1st April 2021, it retailed at $90.

name: Black Gum
title: adidas NMD R1 Primeblue Black Gum
description: The adidas NMD R1 Primeblue Black Gum is a sleek and stylish sneaker that combines comfort and performance. Made with recycled materials, the Primeblue upper is a nod to sustainability, while the Boost midsole provides cushioning and energy return. The black colorway is versatile and easy to pair with any outfit, while the gum outsole adds a touch of contrast. Released on June 3, 2021, this sneaker retails for $140. Whether you're running errands or hitting the gym, the adidas NMD R1 Primeblue Black Gum is a reliable and fashionable choice.

name: Malachite (Women's)
title: Nike Air Max 1 '87 Malachite (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Max 1 ’87 Malachite (Women's) adds a Neutral Gray base with vibrant accents in Malachite to the retro-inspired Air Max 1 ’87 silhouette.

As the name implies, this sneaker pays homage to the first Air Max 1, which debuted in 1987. Like the original, the Malachite version features a wavy mudguard and visible Nike Air units in the heel. While the base is constructed from a woven synthetic material in white, the layered overlays come in Neutral Gray. Something that makes this sneaker stand out is the use of shiny satin on the mudguard and signature Swoosh logos. In terms of accents, Malachite can be found on the mudguard, the Swoosh logos, the tongue’s logo tag, the eyelets, and the "NIKE AIR" lettering stitched on the heel.

Our experts at StockX like the rubber outsole, which includes white, black, and Malachite. The women’s size Nike Air Max 1 ’87 Malachite (Women's) was originally released on March 7, 2024, and sold for $140.

name: Metallic Platinum Blue Tint (Women's)
title: Nike Shox TL Metallic Platinum Blue Tint (Women's)
description:
The Nike Shox TL Metallic Platinum Blue Tint Women's sneaker is a stylish and innovative footwear option that combines Nike's Shox technology with modern design elements.

This shoe delivers a sleek and futuristic design that sets it apart from traditional athletic shoes. The upper is constructed from a combination of synthetic materials, mesh, and leather overlays to provide durability, breathability, and support. A standout cushioning system, which consists of small, hollowed-out columns in the midsole, provides responsive cushioning and energy return with every step. A padded collar and cushioned footbed ensure all-day comfort while a multidirectional patterned rubber outsole offers reliable traction on a variety of surfaces.

What our experts especially enjoy about the Nike Shox TL Metallic Platinum Blue Tint Women's, however, is its metallic platinum and blue tint colorway which gives it a sophisticated aesthetic. This shoe originally retailed for $170 when it was released on July 1, 2023.

name: Triple Black (GS)
title: Nike Air Max Plus Triple Black (GS)
description:
The Nike Air Max Plus Triple Black (GS) joined Nike’s brands in the market as a specific variation of the Nike Air Max Plus silhouette designed for grade schoolers.

The Triple Black GS Nike Air Max Plus features an all-black color scheme. Its black upper is constructed with a combination of mesh and synthetic materials. The sneaker’s upper also features thermoplastic polyurethane (TPU) overlays, giving it the iconic wavy design. The sneaker’s design also incorporates Tuned Air technology-inspired individual pods in the midsole to provide targeted support and cushioning. Concluding the design is the rubber outsole that traction and grip on different surfaces.

When joining the market on February 1st, 2020, Nike Air Max Plus Triple Black (GS) retailed at about $145.

name: Denim Aura (Women's)
title: Nike Air Max 1 '87 Denim Aura (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Max 1 ’87 Denim Aura (Women's) takes a retro silhouette, dresses it in different shades of denim, and sizes it specifically for women.

The Women's Nike Air Max 1 ’87 in a Denim Aura colorway has an upper with a base of midnight navy denim. Lighter denim with a faded, over-washed look overlays the side panel, eyestays, and heel. Overlays of white denim with brown stitching adorn the mudguard. Brown laces that match the mudguard stitching crisscross over a brown denim tongue with exposed foam. The sock liner is midnight navy, while the insole is brown with sail-colored Nike Air branding. We also see Nike Air branding embroidered on the brown leather tongue patch and on the denim heel counter.

What we particularly enjoy about this shoe is that this eclectic upper rests atop a dependable sole. A midsole of sail-colored foam houses visible air and sits on a midnight navy rubber outsole patterned with flex grooves and waffle lugs that absorb impact and offer traction. The Nike Air Max 1 ’87 Denim Aura (Women's) was released on November 1, 2023, for $160 retail.

name: Two Tone Grey
title: Nike Dunk Low Two Tone Grey
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Two Tone Grey arrives with a light grey leather upper with darker tonal overlays and white Swooshes. A nylon tongue with a woven Nike label offers flexibility and comfort. At the base, a white and grey Air sole completes the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Two Tone Grey released in 2022 and retailed for $100.

name: Cinder
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cinder
description:
Yeezy adds another colorway of its most popular design with the adidas Yeezy 350 Cinder, now available on StockX. This 350 V2 stays true to Yeezy’s signature palette, sporting dark earth tones that provide a natural feeling.

This Yeezy 350 V2 is composed of a cinder Primeknit upper with a tonal side stripe. A cinder Boost cushioned midsole sole and gold outsole completes the design. These sneakers released in March of 2020 and retailed for $220.

name: Black Moonbeam (Women's)
title: New Balance 327 Black Moonbeam (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 327 Black Moonbeam (W) arrives in a white and black color palette, and a brown rubber sole provides contrast.

The New Balance 327 Black Moonbeam for women features a black suede upper that is accentuated by a white 'N' logo on the lateral sides. The shoe features a mesh toe box that makes it lightweight and breathable. The sneaker also has a sturdy rubber outsole for traction and grip. The shoe's design is completed with a cushioned, supportive foam midsole sitting on the brown rubber outsole.

The New Balance 327 Black Moonbeam (W) was released on July 21st, 2021, and sold for a retail price of $90.

name: Supreme White
title: Nike Air Force 1 Mid Supreme White
description:
Sneaker giants Nike and Supreme join forces for the city-slicking shoe drop that is the Nike Air Force 1 Mid Supreme White. Bold yet simple, this sneaker collaboration has taken four years to hit the streets.

Pure white full-grain leather on the toebox keeps it breezy while velcro straps support the ankles. With a lace enclosure that includes a steel dubrae, the shoe is branded appropriately with the two labels’ logos. Find the Nike swoosh on the medial and lateral walls and the Supreme red box logo on the back heel. 

We love the Nike X Supreme Air Force 1 sneakers for their classic white freshness that comes with this style. With the red Supreme logo popping out against the monochrome background, the clever collaboration between these two masters of streetwear makes the anticipation of this release all that sweeter. Perfect for energized fans of freedom and movement. The Nike Air Force 1 Mid Supreme White sneakers were released on 29 August 2024 and retailed at $133.

name: Triple Black
title: Nike ACG Rufus Triple Black
description:
The Nike ACG Rufus Triple Black is a rugged mule in a Triple Black colorway from the Nike All Conditions Gear (ACG) collection.

The upper of the Triple Black Nike ACG Rufus is a soft suede. It boasts a debossed Nike Swoosh on the lateral side and a heavily padded topline. There is a Summit White Swoosh at the top of the toe guard. The black midsole houses foam and has raised elements, giving this slip-on an edgy aesthetic. Underfoot, the grippy outsole is a myriad of colors with Hot Curry and Light Bone forming a claw-like image, and there is a University Red ACG logo encased in a transparent design element.

Our expert opinion is that this mule will be an excellent companion on your next camping trip or outdoor adventure, whether you wear it around the campsite or decide to break it in on more rugged terrain. Debuting with a recommended retail price of $110, the Nike ACG Rufus Triple Black was released on June 20, 2024.

name: Cracked Orange (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Cracked Orange (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Cracked Orange (Women's) is an iteration of the Nike Dunk Low, which was originally introduced as a basketball shoe in the 1980s, as part of the Nike Dunk series.

It features a high-quality leather upper, and a foam midsole provides responsive cushioning. There are strategically placed perforations on the toe box for ventilation, and a thick, treaded, rubber sole offers high traction. Nike pays equal attention to this shoe's aesthetic as its function, using colorways of laser orange and safety range over a muted, light bone body for a high contrast effect. A Nike logo on the heel and tongue prominently displays the brand's identity.

But what our experts love most about the Nike Dunk Low Cracked Orange (Women's) is its low-cut silhouette, which offers a wide range of unrestricted movement. These shoes first emerged on the scene on August 12, 2023, with a price tag of $120.

name: Rick & Morty Adventures
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Rick & Morty Adventures
description:
Rick and Morty are back for 2023 NBA All-Star Weekend, collaborating with Puma and LaMelo Ball for the release of the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Rick & Morty Adventures sneaker.

LaMelo Ball's signature sneaker is getting a mismatch treatment with the right sneaker coming in a red to yellow gradient colorway, and the left featuring a gradient purple to green. Rick Sanchez sits on top of the tongue of the left sneaker while Morty Smith is placed on the right.

The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Rick & Morty Adventures released February 17, 2023, with a retail price of $130.

name: Protection Pack Mirage Grey
title: New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Mirage Grey
description:
The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Mirage Grey is a fresh take on this brand’s classic sneaker. ​
​​
​The sides feature a brownish-grey fabric, with blue mesh underneath. The tongue is the same brownish-grey color, along with the laces. On the side of each shoe, you will see the iconic New Balance logo that the brand has become famous for. With a cushioned and supportive sole, the New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Mirage Grey can be used for working out, playing a game of basketball, or even just walking around town. The shoe has a classic rugged and modern design that looks effortlessly broken in.​
​​
​First released in May of 2022 for $150.

name: Layers of Love
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low Layers of Love
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low Layers of Love was released ahead of Valentine’s Day and features a romantic colorway with various shades of red, including University Red, Burgundy Crush, Gym Red, and Team Red.

As the name implies, the sneaker is crafted from layers, or, in this case, panels of suede. The panels line up in a way that fades from Burgundy Crush, on the heel, to Gym Red, on the toebox. Team Red details can also be found on the Swoosh logos, the panels by the lace cage, the laces, and the tongue. In addition, the woven tongue logo tag displays two shades of red, while NIKE AIR is embroidered on the heel tab in a University Red thread.

Our StockX experts like the choice of a dark red midsole instead of the traditional Core Black. The Nike Air Force 1 Low Layers of Love was originally released on February 13, 2024, and sold for $125.

name: Triple Red
title: Nike Air VaporMax Plus Triple Red
description:
Nike offers cushioning, comfort, and style with the Nike Air VaporMax Plus Triple Red.
​
​The Nike Air VaporMax Plus triple red features TPU overlays along the upper of the midfoot. The shoe also incorporates neoprene mesh all over the shoe. Its well-padded upper complements the VaporMax Air midsole. The model is entirely draped in Red and neoprene heels, branding, and midsole. The Nike Air VaporMax Plus triple red also features a full-length VaporMax Sole unit with the signature "VM" branding on the heels and the insoles.
​
​The Nike Air VaporMax Plus Triple Red was launched on the 14th of February, 2020 at a retail price of $190.

name: White Pure Platinum
title: Nike Air Presto White Pure Platinum
description:
The triple white-looking Nike Air Presto White Pure Platinum made its debut as one of Nike’s Air Presto silhouettes in May 2016.

The Nike Air Presto White/Pure Platinum is dressed in  pure platinum/white makeup. The Air Presto silhouette's upper features a stretchable mesh, TPU caging, heel loops, and padded collar. In addition, the sportswear boasts the visible side panel Swooshes, the rear's Nike Air branding, elastic laces on its upper, and a white rubber outsole. The design is completed by the heel's pure platinum branding.

During its debut in May 2016, the Nike Air Presto White/ Pure Platinum retailed at $130.

name: Concepts Heavy
title: Nike Air Max 1 SP Concepts Heavy
description:
PLEASE NOTE: Print Patterns May Vary. Nike and Concepts joined forces once again for the 1970's inspired Nike Air Max 1 SP Concepts Heavy.

The Nike Air Max 1 SP Concepts Heavy nods to youth culture of the 1970's and their style. Bleached denim, bandana, corduroy, and tiger camo M-65 jacket material make up the upper, offering a playful look. On the Swooshes, embroidered flowers add a vintage-inspired styling. From there, a speckled white midsole with a gum outsole completes the design.

The Nike Air Max 1 SP Concepts Heavy released in March of 2022 and retailed for $170.

name: Optimism
title: Nike LeBron 21 Optimism
description:
The Nike LeBron 21 Optimism brings a psychedelic, mismatched color gradient to the LeBron 21 silhouette.

The left shoe of the Optimism Nike LeBron 21 fades from Bliss Pink to Laser Orange, while the right shoe displays a color gradient from Photo Blue to Vapor Green. The mesh upper boasts a 360-degree zonal cabling system—a series of wavy lines that radiate from the midsole and provide superior containment. These multicolor lines create an optical illusion, giving the upper a more molded appearance. Contrasting vibrant hues can also be found on the Phylon midsole, which houses Zoom Air cushioning in the heel and forefoot. Finally, the TPU shank plate supports the foot and provides structure.

Our experts at StockX like the symbolism behind the exposed cabling system. The lines resemble the ridges on an oyster shell and symbolize LeBron’s desire to protect and shelter his daughter. The Nike LeBron 21 Optimism was released on May 1, 2024, and sold for $200.

name: Orb Pink
title: New Balance 2002R Orb Pink
description:
Released in time for Spring, the New Balance 2002R Orb Pink expands the 2002R collection with a Pastel Orb Pink colorway.

Inspired by running shoes in New Balance’s 2000s catalog, the Orb Pink New Balance 2002R boasts a layered, mixed-material upper with pigskin suede, mesh, and leather. The base is crafted from Orb Pink mesh with gray undertones, while the overlays come in Shadow Gray and Orb Pink. The Signature New Balance ‘N’ features a gray hue with metallic silver accents that catch the light. In terms of technology, the ABZORB cushioning decreases impact stress, while the ABZORB SBS heel cushioning provides stability. Completing the technical features, the N-ergy outsole absorbs shock and the Stability Web supports the arch.

Our experts at StockX like the balance between comfort, style, and performance capabilities delivered by this sneaker. The New Balance 2002R Orb Pink was released on April 16, 2024, and sold for $145.

name: White Black
title: New Balance 9060 White Black
description:
The New Balance 9060 White Black comes in traditional colors with slightly off-white and black tones just like its name suggests. 

The shoe is made out of a suede overlay, a base made of perforated leather, and a smooth leather body. The pitch-dark tone present throughout its sidewalls contrasts with the white appearance of its perforated leather base layers and smooth leather overlays. The "N" emblems on its profiles are proudly finished in black, exactly as the zonal traction below. Rounding off the sneaker's design is the midsole, featuring an off-white and gold-tone.

The New Balance 9060 White Black was released on 1st March 2023 and retailed at $150.

name: Undefeated Hall of Fame
title: Nike Kobe 5 Protro Undefeated Hall of Fame
description:
The Nike Kobe 5 Protro Undefeated Hall of Fame arrives in gold, purple, and black, a colorway that pays homage to the Mamba and his Lakers legacy. The Nike Kobe 5 Protro Undefeated Hall of Fame features a gold-colored, textured upper with mesh toe boxes and side paneling. Snakeskin-textured overlays add nuance on the tops, and each shoe is accented with a purple Swoosh on the right side panel and pink Swoosh on the left, with the numbers 24, 10, and 8 inscribed on the pink Swoosh. Below, Zoom Air provides additional cushioning.

The Nike Kobe 5 Protro Undefeated Hall of Fame was released in May, 2021, at a retail price of $190.

name: Halloween (2022) (GS)
title: Nike Dunk Low Halloween (2022) (GS)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Halloween GS 2022 comes in different mixes of colors; phantom, safety orange, and black as the major hues.

This Halloween-themed sneaker for grade-schoolers features a smooth leather upper with white hits scattered throughout the underlays. The midfoot panel, collar, as well as toebox are made of white leather, whereas the eyestays, heel overlay, and mudguard are made of orange leather. Orange laces complement the sockliner and go up the white tongue to a tag with the Nike logo in orange and black.

The Nike Dunk Low Halloween GS 2022 retailed for $90 on its debut in September 2022.

name: Haute Coffee Frosted Ivory (Frosted Ivory Tongue Logo)
title: Puma Speedcat Archive Haute Coffee Frosted Ivory (Frosted Ivory Tongue Logo)
description:
The Puma Speedcat Archive Haute Coffee Frosted Ivory dresses the low-to-the-ground Puma Speedcat silhouette in a warm-brown colorway straight from the label’s archives.

Originally envisioned as a Formula 1 racing shoe with a fireproof finish, the Speedcat has evolved into a streetwear staple. The upper construction features soft suede in the specialty color Haute Coffee with reinforced tonal stitching. The sturdy toe box overlay and the tongue also come in Haute Coffee suede. Puma’s signature Formstrip extends from midfoot to heel and is a Frosted Ivory hue. The shoe boasts three jumping cat logos in white: one on the toe, another on the heel, and the final cat on the tongue. Adding contrast, the rubber outsole comes in black.

Our experts at StockX like that the lining is crafted from textile, keeping the foot cool and dry. The Puma Speedcat Archive Haute Coffee Frosted Ivory was released on October 12, 2024, and sold for $100.

name: Moonbeam
title: New Balance 530 Moonbeam
description:
The New Balance 530 Moonbeam is a retro running shoe that works just as well as a lifestyle shoe. This sneaker features Y2K-era tech details and a chunky, vintage feel with every stride.

This low-top running sneaker in an understated, subtle colorway begins with an upper of creamy Moonbeam-colored lightweight, breathable mesh as its base. Tonal leather overlays circle across the upper, layering over each other. Perforations at the toe cap and side panel help enhance the comfort afforded by breathability. Tonal rope laces cross over a cream-colored mesh tongue for a secure fit. A beige pull tab at the heel with cream-colored stripes helps ease on and off this pair of kicks. An ABZORB midsole in different shades of cream provides springy cushioning, while a cream-colored and tan rubber outsole offers flexible grip and impact absorption.

Our favorite aspect of this elegant, monochromatic shoe is the subtle 530 branding that courses across an overlay at the lateral collar, thus locking in the classic look. The New Balance 530 Moonbeam was released on April 12, 2021, for $95 retail.

name: Cobalt Bliss
title: Nike Air More Uptempo 96 Cobalt Bliss
description:
The Nike Air More Uptempo 96 Cobalt Bliss is constructed from leather and synthetic materials, ensuring durability and support on and off the court. The predominantly white base color allows the Cobalt Blue branding to stand out even more prominently. The shoe features a high-top silhouette, providing excellent ankle support and protection.​
​​
​A black tongue, laces, and inner lining contrast the predominantly white upper, while the outsole combines Cobalt Blue and white, tying the colorway together. The outsole is equipped with a durable rubber material with a herringbone pattern of traction. This design provides excellent grip on various surfaces, enhancing stability and safety during gameplay. The Nike Air More Uptempo 96 Cobalt Bliss signature feature is the oversized "AIR" lettering on the sides, outlined in Cobalt Bliss color and filled with white.​
​​
​What truly sets the Air More Uptempo '96 apart, as recognized by our team of experts, is the midsole, which houses Nike's renowned Air-Sole cushioning technology. This technology offers exceptional cushioning and impact protection, ensuring a comfortable ride on and off the court. The Nike Air More Uptempo '96 Cobalt Bliss hit the shelves on February 17th, 2023, with a price of $170.​
​​
​

name: Orbit Grey Chalk White
title: adidas Harden Vol. 7 Orbit Grey Chalk White
description:
The adidas Harden Vol. 7 Orbit Gray Chalk White is part of a collaboration between adidas and NBA player James Harden.

This futuristic shoe features a bootie-like fit with a knit cuff that fits securely above the ankle. The sneaker doesn’t have a traditional lace cage, but offers a pull tab on the heel that assists the wearer in removing and putting on the shoe. The sneaker features quilted, textile side panels that create a shell-like fit and are fortified by a synthetic toe cap. Synthetic suede wraps around the heel, creating a padded appearance without weighing the foot down. In terms of technology, the sneaker has a Jet Boost cushioning in the heel and a responsive LightStrike midsole.

Our StockX experts like the subdued colorway of Orbit Gray, Gray Four, and Chalk White, which allows the design to stand out. The adidas Harden Vol. 7 Orbit Gray Chalk White was released on November 1st, 2023, and retailed at $160.

name: Natural Indigo
title: New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo
description: The New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo is a stylish and comfortable sneaker that is perfect for everyday wear. Made with high-quality materials, this shoe features a natural indigo colorway that is both unique and eye-catching. The upper is constructed from premium suede and mesh, while the midsole is made from lightweight REVlite foam for superior cushioning and support. The outsole is made from durable rubber, providing excellent traction and grip on any surface. This sneaker was released on September 9th, 2022, with a retail price of $150. Whether you're hitting the streets or just running errands, the New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo is a must-have addition to your sneaker collection.

name: Mimi Plange Ceremony
title: Nike LeBron 20 PRM Mimi Plange Ceremony
description:
The Nike LeBron 20 Premium Mimi Plange Ceremony was released to honor culture and mark two decades of collaboration between LeBron James and Nike.

Dressing a textile knit on the upper, the Nike LeBron 20 features vibrantly colored bright crimson floral patterns on the vamp. More scarlet flowers are embroidered on the quarter panels, covering most of the midfoot. Also on the panels are the Nike swooshes, which intertwine on the lateral side. The heel extends the bright Crimson-on-White colorway but introduces some branding. LeBron’s crown logo is plastered on a reed patch on the heel counter, while Mimi Plange’s brand motif is embroidered on the red mustache in a bold berry tone.

The lace-up closure on the Nike LeBron 20 Premium Mimi Plange Ceremony is among its most outstanding features. Multicolor laces inspired by the Maasai community of Tanzania rest on a woven, bold-berry-colored tongue. This shoe was released on September 9th, 2023, for $250.

name: LEGO
title: adidas ZX 8000 LEGO
description:
To put an interesting and original twist on the 2020 A-ZX series, adidas collaborated with the LEGO Group to make a new LEGO-themed shoe working off the ZX 8000’s silhouette. The origins of the adidas ZX 8000 LEGO dates back to 1984, when adidas initially inaugurated its ZX franchise.

The adidas ZX 8000 LEGO’s overall look is unforgettably striking. The design draws inspiration from the classic LEGO brick. It’s arrestingly multicolored, boasting blue, green, red, yellow, white, black and gray in a variety of combinations that may differ from version to version of the shoe. References to LEGO’s legendary blocks are located on the shoe’s lace cage, deubré, and heel cup.

The adidas ZX 8000 LEGO released in September of 2020 and retailed for $130.

name: Above the Clouds Chocolate Brown
title: ASICS GT-2160 Above the Clouds Chocolate Brown
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 Above the Clouds Chocolate Brown is a low-top athletic shoe with a futuristic design.
   
The Above the Clouds Chocolate Brown ASICS GT-2160 has a mesh upper, with the top part being white and Chocolate Brown underneath. The forefoot also features a shiny iridescent layer underneath and is crossed by silver snakeskin synthetic overlays. A snakeskin Chocolate Brown overlay forms the toe cap. The signature ASICS stripes appear on each side in silver outlined in Chocolate Brown, while the Cream heel overlay carries a light pink GT-2160 on the outer side. Gel branding is on the back of the heel, and an ASICS logo appears on the tongue. The midsole is equipped with Gel technology for comfort and responsiveness, accented in red. The midsole is white, and the outsole is a cream color. 

What we like best about this sneaker are the pink accents, which bring a softer look to the otherwise brown colorway. The ASICS GT-2160 Above the Clouds Chocolate Brown was released on July 19, 2024, for $150.

name: Metallic Gold (2024)
title: Nike Air Flightposite Metallic Gold (2024)
description:
The Nike Air Flightposite Metallic Gold (2024) is a performance shoe designed to deliver unrivaled support.

The Metallic Gold (2024) Nike Air Flightposite has an upper made of black textile around the ankle and where the laces normally would be, while the rest of the upper is covered in the polyurethane Flightposite material. The polyurethane portion of the shoe is Metallic Gold with vertical curves to make this portion resemble flowing liquid. The arch support on the outer side is Metallic Silver. In lieu of laces, the shoe features a single zipper that goes up under the tongue. The black portion features a subtle Nike Swoosh on the outer side, while the tongue also carries a Swoosh. The heel has one final white Swoosh under the pull tab.

What makes this shoe stand out is the liquid gold design of the Flightposite portion, which adds an extra element of style, especially during movement when it catches the light. The Nike Air Flightposite Metallic Gold (2024) was released on October 30, 2024, for $240.

name: New Americana Washed Denim
title: Nike Dunk Low New Americana Washed Denim
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Washed Denim White Midnight Navy mixes the original Nike Dunk model with a contemporary style. The upper part of the shoe is made from leather, while the bottom is the brand’s classic rubber gum sole.

The Low Nike Dunk Washed Denim in White Midnight Navy is designed to have an aged workwear aesthetic. It is a low-top model that is made from leather and rubber. The rubber gum sole has a neutral earth color, while the body of the shoe is a bright white. The Nike Swoosh symbol on the side appears in a distressed denim pattern. This distressed pattern can also be found on the heel of the Nike Dunk shoe.

Our experts love the feature of the thick off-white midsole that was added to provide support, as well as the perforated toebox for breathability. The Nike Dunk Low Washed Denim White Midnight Navy was first put onto the market on July 4th, 2023, for a retail value of $120.

name: Glacier Blue
title: Nike Air Max 90 Glacier Blue
description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Glacier Blue presents the classic Tinker Hatfield silhouette dressed in frosty hues, inspired by the landscapes of the Arctic.

This sporty lifestyle sneaker builds upon a base of white mesh adorned with gray suede overlays at the toecap, side panel, and lower eyestays. A stone-colored suede side panel Swoosh is just above a leather mudguard in a shade of rich blue, inspired by the deep ice of the Arctic Ocean. This same deep blue is echoed in the TPU at the upper eyestays and the branding on the heel. The white foam insole provides cushioning and houses a visible unit of springy Air under the heel. The black rubber outsole with pods of Glacier Blue is deeply lugged for traction.

Our favorite aspect of this shoe is the addition of Glacier Blue TPU that gives this sneaker its locked-in icy look. The midsole Air unit frame, the side-panel Air Max branding window, the heel tab, and eyestay overlay all contribute to this sneaker’s signature wintry look. The Nike Air Max 90 Glacier Blue was released on March 20, 2024, for a retail price of $130.

name: White Grey
title: Nike Air Max Terrascape 90 White Grey
description:
The Nike Air Max Terrascape 90 White Gray draws inspiration from the classic Air Max 90, revitalizing its iconic design with contemporary materials and a semi-translucent midsole, with the silhouette getting an overall white/gray color scheme.

The White Gray Nike Air Max Terrascape 90 prioritizes sustainability, utilizing recycled materials throughout. The sneakers incorporate a durable translucent outsole that extends around the mudguard, enhancing overall durability. Meanwhile, the upper section remains breathable thanks to the mesh construction, ensuring a fresh feel. These sneakers maintain their design's essence by featuring a Crater Foam midsole with a Max Air unit, providing unmatched comfort. Notable updates include the introduction of the new Terrascape logo on the tongue and the addition of sleek triple-stitching around the collar. Completing the modern look, a contemporary Swoosh design extends to the rear of the shoe.

What our experts love about the Nike Air Max Terrascape 90 White Gray is its sustainable construction. These sneakers showcase a commitment to environmental responsibility by utilizing recycled materials, with at least 20% recycled content by weight incorporated into the mixed-material upper. The sneaker debuted for $140 on December 16th, 2022.

name: Deep Royal Blue
title: Nike Air Max 1 Deep Royal Blue
description:
The Nike Air Max 1 Deep Royal Blue sneaker showcases the groundbreaking cushioning system that made its debut in 1987, notably featuring a visible Air-sole unit encased within the heel of a white polyurethane midsole.

In this iteration, the Deep Royal Blue Nike Air Max 1 comes in a combination of white, black, and Deep Royal Blue hues. The Nike Air Max 1 is crafted using a blend of mesh and suede materials, while the majority of the upper is a Crisp White and the mudguards feature eye-catching Royal Blue accents. Additionally, light gray overlays and heel sections complement the black Swoosh. These Royal Blue elements extend to the inner lining and tongue trim. To complete the design, the shoe rests on a white midsole and is grounded by a black rubber outsole.

What our experts love about the Nike Air Max 1 Deep Royal Blue is its homage to the roots of the Air Max series. This iconic sneaker pays tribute to the original Air Max 1 silhouette, which revolutionized the world of footwear in 1987 with its visible Air-sole unit. The sneaker debuted for $140 on August 10th, 2023.

name: Breast Cancer Awareness
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Breast Cancer Awareness
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Breast Cancer Awareness is a visually striking and technologically advanced basketball shoe, showcasing an all-pink colorway that symbolizes a commitment to breast cancer research and awareness.

The Breast Cancer Awareness Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 upper features distinctive rocket ship flames erupting from the collar, a unique design element paying homage to LaMelo Ball's spaceship tattoo on his leg. Notable Melo-branded "Not From Here" accents, such as his signature wings and the "1 of 1" motto, adorn the shoe. With a galactic sole and cutting-edge PUMA Hoops technology, including NITROFOAM, the shoe is ready for the court. The NITROFOAM technology, known for its responsiveness and lightweight cushioning, for optimal performance. This edition of the shoe also supports 'Breast Cancer Awareness' with a ribbon featured on the tongue.

The highlight of the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Breast Cancer Awareness edition is its innovative NITROFOAM technology, providing unmatched comfort and responsiveness, making it a premier choice for basketball performance. The sneaker debuted for $152 on September 29th, 2023.

name: Sporty & Rich White Bold Gold
title: adidas Samba Sporty & Rich White Bold Gold
description:
The adidas Samba Sporty & Rich White Bold Gold is part of the third collaboration between adidas and Sporty & Rich, a lifestyle brand known for its timeless, sporty aesthetic.

The shoe takes Samba’s classic silhouette and applies luxury details, including a satin lining, and dual branding elements. The upper is made of Cloud White leather with the three stripes in Bold Gold running up the side of the shoe. Branding details include ‘SPORTY & RICH’ in Bold Gold replacing the usual ‘SAMBA’ lettering. The adidas Trefoil and ‘SPORTY & RICH’ can be found on the heel counter and across the tongue logo tag. Like other Samba models, the sneaker boasts a gum rubber outsole that wraps around the base of the shoe.

Our experts like the use of suede in Cream White on the toe overlay. It balances out the vibrant Bold Gold details. The adidas Samba Sporty & Rich White Bold Gold was released on November 10, 2023, and retailed at $120.

name: Gore-Tex Medium Olive
title: Nike Air Max 90 Gore-Tex Medium Olive
description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Gore-Tex Medium Olive dresses a classic silhouette in stealthy camo colors and reinforces the design with all-weather enhancements.

The Medium Olive Gore-Tex x Nike Air Max 90 is a durable, winterized AM90 with an upper base of light olive tightly woven mesh integrated with Gore-Tex for water-resistant durability. Leather overlays in shades of brown, olive, and yellow run across the upper, creating a visually striking aesthetic, as well as overall foot support. Olive TPU hits the eyestays, yellow TPU hits the heel tab, and black TPU hits the side panel. A lighter olive TPU surrounds the cassette of visible Air in the yellow foam midsole. The olive and black rubber outsole sports thick waffle lugs for all-weather traction.

The aspect of this sneaker that we most enjoy is the Gore-Tex branding on the tongue and side-panel window that takes the place of typical Nike and Air Max branding. The Nike Air Max 90 Gore-Tex Medium Olive was released on October 20, 2023, for a retail price of $160.

name: Sea Salt Leopard Pantera (Women's)
title: New Balance 327 Sea Salt Leopard Pantera (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 327 Sea Salt Leopard Pantera (Women's) is a unique colorway of the New Balance 327, a lifestyle sneaker with a retro-inspired design which first debuted in April 2020.

The upper of this shoe is crafted using a combination of leather, suede and synthetic materials and features an off-white color scheme which closely resembles the color cream. It has a thick midsole which provides cushioning and comfort and a gum rubber outsole. Branding elements on this New Balance 327 include the iconic ‘N’ logo on the side which showcases a leopard print, the ‘NB’ logo on the tongue and more branding on the lateral side of the heel.

One of the stand-out features on this New Balance 327 Sea Salt Leopard Pantera (Women's) is the outsole, which has studs on the underfoot to help improve grip and traction during everyday activities. The women’s sized shoe was released for retail priced at $130 on the 14th of February 2023.

name: Kiko Kostadinov Grey Floss Brown Storm
title: ASICS UB6-S GT-2160 Kiko Kostadinov Grey Floss Brown Storm
description:
The ASICS UB6-S GT-2160 Kiko Kostadinov Grey Floss Brown Storm is a performance running sneaker combining elements from Kiko Kostadinov Studio and ASICS SportStyle designs.

The Kiko Kostadinov Storm ASICS UB6-S GT-2160 in gray and brown draws inspiration from the natural world, which can be seen in the dark earthy colorway and wavy lines on the sides. The mixed-material upper features lightweight mesh and synthetic materials in colors ranging from Grey Floss to Brown Storm to eggplant-purple. The metallic ASICS formstrip streaks across the side panel and complements the glossy finishes. The sneaker’s straightforward silhouette is reminiscent of ASICS running shoes from the 2010s and includes design details borrowed from the GT-2000 series. Finally, the segmented midsole houses Gel technology for advanced cushioning.

Our experts at StockX like the dark sole unit because it reflects the natural inspirations that inform the sneaker’s design. The ASICS UB6-S GT-2160 Kiko Kostadinov Grey Floss Brown Storm was released on March 8, 2024, and sold for $150.

name: Black Anthracite
title: Nike Air Terra Humara SP Black Anthracite
description:
The Nike Air Terra Humara SP Black Anthracite is an updated version of the original Air Terra Humara that was released back in 1997. This modern take sports a black and Anthracite color combination.

This Air Terra Humara SP is a special project of Nike’s, and it boasts a mixture of textured overlays that give it a rugged and daring look. Presenting with a primarily black upper, the lower part is made out of suede while Anthracite mesh material is seen on the toebox, sides, and throat. Nike branding hits are in the usual spots such as heel, tongue, and side panels.

StockX experts note the use of reflective material near the front toe, on the quarter with a design that resembles a moon and stars, the heel, and heel tab. This is a great safety feature for walking and exploring in conditions with less light. Released on August 20, 2024, the Nike Air Terra Humara SP Black Anthracite sold for $150.

name: CLOT By Edison Chen White Crystal Sand
title: adidas Superstar CLOT By Edison Chen White Crystal Sand
description:
The adidas Superstar CLOT By Edison Chen White Crystal Sand is part of a collaboration between adidas and Edison Chen, a Hong Kong-Canadian performer, and the founder of the streetwear label CLOT.

The sneaker features the Superstar’s signature silhouette and design elements that match Edison Chen and CLOT’s aesthetic. The combination of these elements creates a shoe with a rich history and streetwear updates. For example, the midsole is stacked and finds inspiration in dress shoes. The upper is made of glossy patent leather in white, while the serrated 3-Stripes are crafted from black patent leather. Other elegant elements include perforations on the heel tab and between the 3-Stripes that look like broguing, and a leather tassel attached to the laces.

Our StockX experts like the saw-like traction design on the bottom of the outsole. The adidas Superstar CLOT By Edison Chen White Crystal Sand was released on February 23rd, 2024, and retailed at $200.

name: Black White
title: Nike Free RN 2018 Black White
description:
The Nike Free RN 2018 Black White was released as part of the Nike Free RN series, which is a line of minimalist running shoes designed to simulate barefoot running. 

The upper of the Free RN 2018 Black White is made from a breathable, lightweight mesh that allows for increased airflow to keep your feet cool and dry throughout your workout. The sneaker includes Flywire cables in the midfoot area to provide a secure, locked-in fit. The midsole is made from Nike's signature Free foam, which is designed to dynamically adapt to your foot movements, providing a cushioned, responsive ride that mimics the feeling of running barefoot. 

We think that the notable feature of the Free RN 2018 Black White by Nike is its flexible and responsive sole. The shoe has a tri-star outsole pattern that expands and contracts with every step, providing a natural range of motion and promoting foot strength. The Nike Free RN 2018 Black White was released on January 1st, 2018 at a retail price of $100.

name: USA (Women's)
title: Nike Sabrina 2 USA (Women's)
description:
The Nike Sabrina 2 USA (Women's) celebrates athletic innovation and patriotism with a bold design inspired by Olympic aesthetics. This silhouette was designed for basketball performance and showed off advanced technology while representing Sabrina Ionescu's contributions to Team USA.

The USA Sabrina 2 for women by Nike has a striking Sport Red upper with white accents on the Swoosh and branding, balanced by a College Navy sole. Subtle patterns along the sides and front add depth to the design. Built with Zoom Air cushioning in the forefoot and Cushlon 3.0 foam, the shoe offers improved comfort and support. Nike continues its tradition of high-performance shoes inspired by elite athletes like Sabrina Ionescu, aligning this model with her role on Team USA.

As the experts, one thing we enjoy about the Nike Sabrina 2 USA (Women's) is the Zoom Air for responsive cushioning. We also appreciate the breathable, textured materials that keep you comfortable on the court. This model was released on August 1, 2024, for $130.

name: White Blue
title: New Balance 550 White Blue
description:
The New Balance 550 White Blue is a redefined version of the classic basketball shoe released by New Balance in 1989. Released as part of the Conversations Amongst Us, for grade schoolers US pack, this shoe boasts several highlights.
​
​Some of the highlights of the New Balance 550 White Blue features include a lace closure, an upper made out of leather, synthetic, and mesh, a cushioned midsole that improves its coziness, and a rubber outsole that enhances the traction of the shoe.
​
​The rejuvenated New Balance 550 White Blue was released in December 2020. At the time of this shoe’s release, it commanded a retail price of $110.

name: Flash Aqua
title: adidas Harden Vol. 7 Flash Aqua
description:
The adidas Harden Vol. 7 Flash Aqua is an offering from James Harden’s 7th signature shoe with adidas Basketball in a ‘Flash Aqua’ colorway.

This Harden Vol. 7 sneaker features an upper crafted from textile, leather, and knit. Quilted textile inspired by puffer jackets is used on the side panel, while synthetic leather on the toe cap and heel provides extra durability. This sneaker has a knit interior with a sock-like finish for a secure fit. Other details include partially hidden laces, 3-Stripes branding at the rear, and a heel pull tab with James Harden’s signature logo. A LightStrike JET BOOST midsole, a TPU propulsion plate on the side for extra support, and a herringbone-patterned rubber outsole round out the design.

Something we love about this sneaker is its bold and eye-catching design and responsive cushioning technology, which enhances comfort and performance. The adidas Harden Vol. 7 Flash Aqua was made available on August 15th, 2023, for a retail price of $160.

name: Sea Salt Pine Green
title: New Balance 550 Sea Salt Pine Green
description: The New Balance 550 Sea Salt Pine Green is a stylish and versatile sneaker that combines classic design with modern materials. The upper is made of premium leather and suede, with a sea salt and pine green colorway that adds a touch of sophistication to any outfit. The midsole is cushioned for comfort, while the rubber outsole provides excellent traction and durability. This sneaker is perfect for everyday wear, whether you're running errands or hitting the gym. The New Balance 550 Sea Salt Pine Green was released on February 5th, 2023, with a retail price of $120. Don't miss out on this must-have addition to your sneaker collection.

name: White Black Outline Swoosh
title: Nike Air Force 1 '07 Low White Black Outline Swoosh
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 '07 Low White Black Outline Swoosh is an iteration of Nike’s low-top Air Force 1 '07 in a "White Black Outline Swoosh" colorway. 

This version of the Air Force 1 features a predominantly white smooth leather upper with black accents on the Swoosh outline, Nike branding on the tongue tag, the miniature Swoosh embroidered on the vamp, and "NIKE AIR" branding embroidered on the heel tab. Other details include white laces, toebox perforations, an "AF1" christened Metallic Silver lace dubrae, and black insoles with white Nike branding. The upper rests on a white midsole with black "AIR" branding at the heel and a black rubber outsole. 

Something we love about this Air Force 1 is its distinctive and stylish look, which makes it a versatile option for various outfits and occasions. The Nike Air Force 1 '07 Low White Black Outline Swoosh was released on July 1st, 2023, for a retail price of $110.

name: Bart Simpson
title: Nike SB Dunk Low Pro Bart Simpson
description:
While the Nike SB Dunk Low Bart Simpson is not an official collaboration with The Simpsons, it channels color inspiration to the rambunctious character and follows a similar format to the Nike SB Dunk High Marge Simpson and the Nike SB Dunk Low Homer Simpson.

The Nike SB Dunk Low Bart Simpson features a yellow leather upper with orange Durabuck overlays and a white Swoosh. Hits of blue on the sock liner and outsole add a cool-toned contrast to the shoe's warm palette. At the base, a Zoom sole provides comfort and support.

The Nike SB Dunk Low Bart Simpson released in May of 2022 and retailed for $100.

name: Deadpool & Wolverine Deadpool
title: adidas Rivalry Low Deadpool & Wolverine Deadpool
description:
The adidas Rivalry Low Deadpool & Wolverine Deadpool is a celebration of the movie "Deadpool & Wolverine" and part of an adidas x Marvel Studios capsule collection.

The Deadpool & Wolverine Deadpool adidas Rivalry Low is one of two Deadpool & Wolverine–inspired Rivalry Low sneakers released in the days after the film’s July premiere. With a silhouette inspired by 1980s basketball shoes, the sneaker boasts an upper designed to look like Deadpool’s iconic suit. Team Power Red 2 dominates the suede upper, while Core Black covers the 3-Stripes logo and the heel tab. Other details include an image of Deadpool’s face on the heel tab and a brown pouch over the laces that pays tribute to the character Merc With A Mouth. Finally, the Core Black and Team Power Red 2 speckled outsole completes the superhero-inspired shoe.

Our experts like the attention to detail, including the speech bubbles on the Ortholite sockliner. The adidas Rivalry Low Deadpool & Wolverine Deadpool was released on August 1, 2024, and sold for $110.

name: Unearthed
title: Nike Air Max 95 Unearthed
description:
The Nike Air Max 95 Unearthed is a limited-edition colorway from the Nike Air Max 95 that features cascading overlays in summit white, cacao wow, light british tan, and velvet brown that allude to the layers of the earth.

Starting with the wave inspired upper, you’ll notice synthetic and mesh layers that lead up to white speed lacing eyelets and white laces. Air Max branding hits are in the form of an embroidered logo on the tongue and Swoosh on the lateral ankle side. Air units are visible under the heel and forefoot in a blue color, a nod to water. The cascading overlays are earthy tones and different on both sides.

Our experts think that the fact that the lateral and medial sides of the upper boast different color palettes is this shoe’s prominent feature. While the lateral side pulls inspiration from rocks and minerals, the medial side has soil-inspired tones, and together they add to the colorway’s Unearthed motif. When it was released, the Nike Air Max 95 Unearthed retailed for $175.

name: Toxic
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Toxic
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Toxic effortlessly combines style and functionality, taking inspiration from an extraterrestrial realm. The design integrates bold elements such as slime and claw marks, creating a visually aggressive aesthetic.

With slime-inspired rubber wrap-ups and an engineered knit upper featuring scratch cutout, the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Toxic showcases a vibrant Purple Glimmer-Green Gecko color combination.
