The spotlight is on NITROFOAM, a nitrogen-infused foam providing responsive cushioning in a lightweight configuration. The durability and comfort of the shoe are enhanced by the engineered mesh upper and TPU heel counter. A high abrasion, non-slip rubber outsole guarantees excellent traction, and personalized LaMelo Ball branding adds a distinctive touch.

The standout feature of the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Toxic is the NITROFOAM Infused midsole, introducing innovative technology that delivers superior responsiveness and comfort while maintaining a lightweight profile. The sneaker was originally sold for $125 on October 27th, 2023.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Sea Salt Black
title: New Balance 993 MiUSA Teddy Santis Sea Salt Black
description:
The New Balance 993 MiUSA Teddy Santis Sea Salt Black reinvigorates the NB 993 under the creative direction of Teddy Santis, best known as the founder of Aime Leon Dore.

Like other models in the Made in the USA line, the MiUSA Teddy Santis Sea Salt Black New Balance 993 is crafted using premium materials, including velvet nubuck, pigskin suede, and high-quality mesh on the upper. The off-white mesh base serves as the perfect backdrop for the overlays, which primarily showcase Seasalt, but also feature touches of black. The gum rubber outsole provides traction underfoot, while the ABZORB midsole protects against impact.

Our experts like the signature New Balance branding on the side panel. It completes the sneaker’s soft aesthetic with a small black ‘N’ that stands out against the creamy white and Seafoam hues. The New Balance 993 MiUSA Teddy Santis Sea Salt Black was released on May 1, 2024, and sold for $220.

name: Valentine's Day (Women's)
title: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Valentine's Day (Women's)
description:
The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Valentine's Day (Women's) reimagines a retro running shoe silhouette, sizes it specifically for women, and dresses it in shades reminiscent of romance.

The Women's Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Valentine’s Day features an upper composed of cream-colored layered materials. The base is lightweight, breathable mesh overlaid with synthetic leather. The side panel and heel each sport a plastic cage that adds both structure and ports for ventilation. The white Nike side-panel Swoosh in synthetic leather matches the heel overlay. We see hits of deep red along the tongue and in the sock liner and insole. 3M reflective detailing on the tongue adds a bit of sparkle. This upper rests on a white foam midsole containing Zoom Air and a deep red rubber outsole lugged for traction.

The detail of this sneaker that we most enjoy is the Nike Valentine logo adorning both the insole and heel overlay. A light pink Nike Swoosh is inside a dark red heart, which is inside a pink flower. The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Valentine's Day (Women's) was launched on February 14, 2024, for $160 retail.

name: Halloween
title: Nike Book 1 Halloween
description:
The Nike Book 1 Halloween is a basketball shoe designed in collaboration with basketball player Devin Booker for the Halloween season.

The Halloween Nike Book 1 is made of smooth leather on the upper in black, with a bit of a glittery sheen to it. The toe box features perforations for breathability, while overlays in the same color and material form the toe cap and heel counter. The Nike Swoosh, designed to look like poorly done monster stitching in white thread, appears on the sides. The tongue features Clay Orange Book branding and two matching metal eyelets at the top. The heel features a pull tab adorned with white text reading "Chapter One," and the shoe sits on a black and white midsole.

What we think stands out about this shoe is the branding, which is truly in a Halloween spooky stitching style. The Nike Book 1 Halloween was released on October 30, 2024, for $140.

name: Year of the Rabbit White Rabbit (2023)
title: Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM Year of the Rabbit White Rabbit (2023)
description:
Inspired by the Chinese Year of the Rabbit Zodiac, the Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM Year of the Rabbit White Rabbit (2023) is a limited-edition sneaker in a White/Crimson Varsity Royal colorway.

This Dunk Low features an upper made of a Light Grey suede base with White leather overlays. Chenille fabric Swooshes, Red on the lateral and Blue on the medial, highlight the shoe’s design. Special details include a rabbit graphic on the insole and lateral heel and a Chinese Year of the Rabbit character on the tongue. Each pair features a White midsole with a transparent outsole displaying the years 2011 and 2023 on the left and right shoes, respectively.

The Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM Year of the Rabbit White Rabbit (2023) was released on January 18th, 2023, for a retail price of $130.

name: Fossil Rose
title: Nike Dunk Low Fossil Rose
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Fossil Rose features a Fossil grey premium suede upper with Rose suede Swooshes and heel wraps. A woven Nike tongue label and contrasting white and rose Air sole add the finishing touch.

The Nike Dunk Low Fossil Rose released in May of 2022 and retailed for $110.

name: Gone Fishing Chinook Salmon
title: Nike Dunk Low SE Gone Fishing Chinook Salmon
description:
The Nike Dunk Low SE Gone Fishing Chinook Salmon silhouette was created to blend basketball inspirations into a low-top sneaker. This "Gone Fishing" model is constructed in a paneled design and has the iconic low-top style, as well as a reflective scaled Swoosh detail and fish logo patch at the tongue.

The Nike Dunk Low Gone Fishing Chinook Salmon Swooshes feature a somewhat fishhook-like tip at the medial. The glossy construction complements the heel tab, while the shoe's upper has a durable white ripstop. A tongue tag with a fish illustration and the inscription "Nike Beaverton 1972" match the design of the sockliner. Finally, a yellowed off-white appears on the laces and midsole, which sit on top of a light gray rubber outsole.

The midfoot panels and patterned ripstop toe with a heat map-like pattern are what experts appreciate about The Nike Dunk Low SE Gone Fishing Chinook Salmon was originally released on June 16th, 2023 for $110.

name: Fast Pack
title: Nike ZoomX Vaporfly 3 Fast Pack
description:
The Nike ZoomX Vaporfly 3 Fast Pack is designed to elevate your running performance with its advanced features and bold design. The volt, scream green, barely volt, and black colorway ensures you stand out on the track. This sneaker is crafted for runners who seek both speed and style in their footwear.

Featuring Nike's ZoomX foam and a full-length carbon plate, the Vaporfly 3 offers exceptional energy return and propulsion, making each stride more efficient. The lightweight upper provides breathability and a secure fit, ensuring maximum comfort during your runs. This combination of innovative technology and striking design makes the Vaporfly 3 a must-have for serious athletes.

Released on April 5, 2024, the Nike ZoomX Vaporfly 3 Fast Pack retailed at $260. Its vibrant volt, scream green, barely volt, and black colorway highlights Nike's dedication to performance and aesthetics. Enhance your running experience with the Vaporfly 3, where speed and style converge.

name: White Light Gold Metallic
title: New Balance 530 White Light Gold Metallic
description:
The New Balance 530 White Light Gold Metallic is a retro-inspired running shoe from the New Balance 530 lineup in a "Light Gold Metallic" colorway. 

This New Balance 530 features an upper made of a white mesh base with synthetic overlays dressed in Light Metallic Gold and black. Different iterations of New Balance branding appear throughout, including the signature "N" logos on the sides, "530" on the lateral heel, and "NB running" on the tongue. Other details include a heel pull loop, white laces, and a padded mesh lining. The upper is anchored on a white ABZORB midsole atop a black rubber outsole. 

Something we love about this New Balance 530 is its stylish colorway, the combination of durable and breathable materials, and the fusion of heritage design with modern technology, which make it a timeless and versatile sneaker suitable for various occasions, from casual wear to athletic activities. The New Balance 530 White Light Gold Metallic was released on January 18th, 2023, for a retail price of $100.

name: Semi Pink Spark Preloved Scarlet (Women's)
title: adidas Gazelle Indoor Semi Pink Spark Preloved Scarlet (Women's)
description:
The adidas Gazelle Indoor Semi Pink Spark Preloved Scarlet (Women's) takes a silhouette originally designed for handball and fashions as an elegant, vibrant lifestyle sneaker. This eye-catching shoe has been specifically sized for women.

This low riding adidas Gazelle Indoor features an upper with a base constructed of light pink hairy suede. Pale Scarlet suede forms the T-toe overlay, the eyestay overlay, and the heel tab. The signature serrated 3-stripes on the side panel are crafted from contrasting green suede that pops. Light pink laces match the light pink sock liner. The sole unit is also light pink, appearing translucent on the side walls. The outsole sports a traction pattern composed of circles and adidas trefoils.

The aspect of this stylish women’s sneaker that we enjoy the most is its textured tongue. This light pink tongue also features dark pink adidas trefoil branding and perforations to add comfort and breathability. The adidas Gazelle Indoor Semi Pink Spark Preloved Scarlet (Women's) was released on May 1, 2024, for $120 retail.

name: Black Opti Yellow
title: Nike Dunk Low Black Opti Yellow
description:
The Nike Dunk Low has been released in a variety of colorways since first being introduced more than two decades ago. The Nike Dunk Low Black Opti Yellow was one of the many versions of the sneaker unveiled in 2023.

This particular colorway featured a white leather base with black leather overlay panels along with bright yellow Swooshes on both sides that really popped against the black and white background. It also had a bright white tongue with a black and yellow tongue tag that was complemented by a pair of black laces. It was finished off with a white midsole and a black outsole to complete the look.

But it's the yellow embroidered Nike logo on the back of the shoes (a detail that we absolutely love) that helped tie this entire Dunk Low sneaker together. The Nike Dunk Low Black Opti Yellow was released on July 11, 2023, for $110.

name: Dusty Cactus
title: Nike Air Max 180 Dusty Cactus
description:
The Nike Air Max 180 Dusty Cactus offers comfort with its revolutionary 180° Air Max unit that is sure to turn heads with its arresting look.

The upper of the Dusty Cactus Nike Air Max 180 begins with the base of black mesh textile overlaid with strips of black suede. A teal TPU heel counter provides rear foot stability and matches both the tongue tag and the Nike Air embroidered branding on the heel. The black polyurethane midsole provides cushioning, encloses the Air unit, and sports a teal frame around the Air unit. The black rubber sole with a modified waffle traction pattern includes pods of teal and translucent blue.

The aspects of this eye-catching sneaker that we most enjoy are the cream-colored hits that add contrast. The side-panel Nike Swoosh, sock liner, tongue lining, and toe of the outsole provide these softer touches. The Nike Air Max 180 Dusty Cactus was released on June 1, 2024, for a retail price of $150.

name: Oil Green Terra Blush (Women's)
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LX Oil Green Terra Blush (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LX Oil Green Terra Blush (Women's) updates the Air Force 1 Low with a textile base and an earthy colorway of Oil Green, Terra Blush, Sesame, and Pale Ivory.

In total, six colors can be found across the upper, which gives the sneaker a patchwork, color-blocked aesthetic. The upper is made of canvas with stitched suede heel and forefoot overlays. The heel tab and the tongue come in corduroy, while the inner lining is made of soft textile. Pale Ivory Swoosh logos in shaggy suede check across the side panels and add a contrasting texture. This low-cut sneaker features a foam midsole that absorbs impact and Air cushioning.

Our StockX experts like the perforations across the midsole, which allow the foot to breathe. The women’s size Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LX Oil Green Terra Blush (Women's) was released on January 9th, 2024, and retailed at $125.

name: Icey Pink Auburn (Women's)
title: adidas Gazelle Bold Icey Pink Auburn (Women's)
description:
The adidas Gazelle Bold Icey Pink Auburn (Women's) is a sneaker for women with a unique design on the midsole and outsole.

The Icey Pink Auburn (Women's) adidas Gazelle Bold is made with a suede upper in an Auburn color. The overlays forming the small t-shaped toe cap and the eyestays are the same color and material. Icey Pink overlays form the adidas 3-Stripes on each side, as well as the heel collar. The Gazelle brand name appears on the outer side in gold letters, and the tongue features a logo patch. The midsole has three layers of classic gum rubber, each of them branded and overlapping the other.

What we like best about this shoe is the midsole, which has three layers and provides a platform for the wearer. The adidas Gazelle Bold Icey Pink Auburn (Women's) was released on August 1, 2024, for $120.

name: Bicoastal
title: Nike Air Peg 2K5 Bicoastal
description:
The Nike Air Peg 2K5 Bicoastal is a stylish and versatile sneaker that combines retro charm with modern comfort. Featuring a coconut milk upper with bicoastal accents, this sneaker offers a fresh and sophisticated look. Originally designed for running, the Air Peg 2K5 has been updated to provide both style and performance for today's fashion-conscious crowd.

First introduced in the mid-2000s, the Nike Air Peg 2K5 quickly gained popularity for its innovative design and comfortable fit. The Bicoastal colorway highlights the shoe's sleek design and intricate detailing, making it a standout choice for both athletes and style enthusiasts. Nike's commitment to quality and performance is evident in every detail, from the durable materials to the advanced cushioning.

Priced at $150, the Nike Air Peg 2K5 Bicoastal was released on April 5, 2024. This sneaker offers a perfect blend of nostalgia and modernity, making it a must-have for any sneaker enthusiast. Don't miss out on this iconic model that captures the essence of Nike's heritage and innovation.

name: Wolf Grey Black
title: Nike Air Max Plus Tiempo Wolf Grey Black
description:
The Nike Air Max Plus Tiempo Wolf Grey Black is an athletic shoe with a curved, stitched leather upper in Wolf Grey, featuring a large foldover tongue. The Nike Swoosh in Black appears on the tongue and sides, while Tiempo branding appears on the rear heel and outsole. The chunky Black outsole displays four visible Air units, and a Metallic Silver tip completes the look.

Nike, the predominant force in American sneaker design, pioneered its Air Max technology beginning in 1987, with the series going on to add another triumph to the brand's innovations. The Air Max Plus Tiempo’s foldover tongue is inspired by traditional football sneaker design, while the Air Max technology in the sole offers solid comfort on the pitch.

In our opinion, the best feature of the Air Max Plus Tiempo is its chunky sole, which balances the aesthetic of the foldover tongue. The Nike Air Max Plus Tiempo Wolf Grey Black released on July 12, 2024, and retailed for $190.

name: Aragonite
title: Nike LeBron 21 Aragonite
description:
The Nike LeBron 21 Aragonite applies a denim-like upper and accents in Terra Blush to the LeBron 21 silhouette.

Like other LeBron 21 models released in 2024, the Aragonite version is inspired by minerals and materials from the sea—in this case, aragonite. Aragonite symbolizes LeBron’s ability to perform in the face of adversity, just like the mineral develops under pressure in marine environments. The Terra Blush hue represents aragonite on the rubber outsole, the tongue, the heel tab, and the Swoosh logos. The upper is crafted from distressed canvas washed with Jade Ice and features perforations on the side panels for breathability. Zoom Air cushioning in the heel provides a propulsive feel, while the 360-degree zonal cabling system lies beneath the canvas upper.

Our experts like the mismatched Swoosh logos. The Swoosh on the outer side is a single, embroidered line, while the one on the inner side outlines Emerald Rise with Terra Blush. The Nike LeBron 21 Aragonite was released on February 8, 2024, and sold for $200.

name: White Collegiate Green Gum (Women's)
title: adidas Sambae White Collegiate Green Gum (Women's)
description:
The adidas Sambae White Collegiate Green Gum (Women's) reimagines the Sambae silhouette with a varsity inspired colorway of Crisp White with Collegiate Green details.

Collegiate Green details can be found on the 3-Stripes logo and the heel tab. Although this sneaker finds inspiration in the classic adidas Sambae, it boasts several differences. For example, the upper is made of smooth leather instead of suede in white. In addition, the 3-Stripes logos aren’t made of leather – they’re embroidered with durable white thread. Another feature that makes this sneaker stand out is the gum rubber sole. Not only does it provide traction, but it also extends over the upper material and is semi-translucent.

Our StockX experts like the contrast between the leather base and the nubuck T-shaped toebox. The women’s size adidas Sambae White Collegiate Green Gum (Women's) was released on December 1st, 2023, and retailed at $110.

name: White (Travis Scott Cactus Jack Utopia Edition) (Women's)
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 White (Travis Scott Cactus Jack Utopia Edition) (Women's)
description:
Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 White (Travis Scott Cactus Jack Utopia Edition) (Women's) is a collaboration between Nike and Los Angeles-based hip-hop artist Travis Scott. It celebrates the release of Scott’s album "Utopia" and paints the Air Force 1 Low in an all-white colorway.

The women’s size sneaker boasts an upper created entirely from leather with tonal overlays and an understated Swoosh. Providing breathability and detailing, perforations can be found across the vamp and along the side panels. The word "utopia" and Cactus Jack branding in curving gold letters are screened onto the heel. These are the only elements identifying this sneaker as a Travis Scott collaboration.

Our experts like the Nike Air midsole, which also comes in a clean white. The Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 White (Travis Scott Cactus Jack Utopia Edition) (Women's) was released on July 29th, 2023, and retailed at $150.

name: Lunar New Year
title: New Balance 1906U Lunar New Year
description:
The New Balance 1906U Lunar New Year is a utility-orientated take on the classic 1906 model that was released in celebration of the Chinese New Year holiday.

This shoe is constructed of premium leather and mesh for durability and support and employs a cushioned midsole that is typical of the New Balance brand for lasting comfort. A standard lacing system ensures a secure fit, while perforations in the toe region help to regulate the internal temperature of the shoe.

What our experts agree is a standout feature of the New Balance 1906U Lunar New Year, however, is its rich color scheme, which uses white and gray tones as the dominant colors so that bright hues like Angora, Blue Laguna, and Orb Pink can pop against the heel and along the outer sole. This shoe originally retailed with a price tag of $160 when it was released on January 1, 2024.

name: Black (GS)
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low LE Black (GS)
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low LE Black (2021) (GS) arrives in an all-black colorway.

The Black Nike Air Force 1 Low LE (2021) (GS) has an upper that is crafted from leather - providing durability. The shoe is fitted with a lace-up closure system, ensuring a customizable and secure fit. The shoe also features perforations on the toe box, providing breathability and ventilation. The shoe's midsole is built with Nike's Air cushioning technology, providing impact reduction, responsive cushioning, and comfort. The shoe's outsole is made of durable rubber material, providing traction and stability. The sneaker has an "AIR" inscription on a metallic plate fitted on the laces and a Nike Swoosh on the lateral sides.

What we like about the Nike Air Force 1 Low LE Black (2021) (GS) is its timeless and iconic design. The Air Force 1 is one of Nike's most iconic and enduring sneaker silhouettes, and the "Black 202" colorway adds a sleek and versatile option to the lineup. The grade schooler’s sizing of the Nike Air Force 1 Low LE Black (2021) was released on March 18, 2021 and retailed for $90.

name: Athletic Department Picante Red
title: Nike Dunk Low Athletic Department Picante Red
description:
Stepping straight out of the archive and onto the street, the Nike Dunk Low Athletic Department Picante Red hit the scene on March 4, 2023. A nod to Nike’s storied sports heritage, this Dunk was made for those who defy the mainstream.

Featuring an ambitious colorway, the upper of the sneaker flaunts a seamless blend of suede and canvas materials, making it a standout. Its Picante Red Nike swoosh offers a daring contrast to the versatile Sail backdrop.

A perfect mix of comfort and style, these kicks encapsulate Nike's dedication to superior athletic performance. Whether you're a hardcore sneakerhead or a casual wearer, this Nike Dunk Low has the makings of a staple in your collection.

The Nike Dunk Low Athletic Department Picante Reddropped with a retail price of $110 on March 4, 2023.

name: Black
title: Nike Hyperdunk 2017 Low Black
description:
The Nike Hyperdunk 2017 Low Black is a performance basketball sneaker with a lightweight design and a monochromatic colorway of black and white.

The Low Black Nike Hyperdunk 2017 boasts a variety of technical features designed to support on-court play. For instance, the midsole houses Nike React foam that is 13 percent more responsive and 11 percent softer than the previous softest Nike cushioning. The pressure-mapped outsole provides targeted traction based on where the foot puts the most pressure. The black upper is crafted from a lightweight woven material that increases breathability, while the inner half-sleeve provides a secure fit. In terms of detailing, the Swoosh logo comes in black, blending into the upper’s woven material.

Our experts at StockX like the contrast between the crisp white outsole and midsole and the all-black upper. The Nike Hyperdunk 2017 Low Black was released on August 1, 2024, and sold for $130.

name: Orlando (2022)
title: Nike Air Max Penny 1 Orlando (2022)
description:
The Nike Air Max Penny 1 Orlando is a reissue of the model designed by Penny Hardaway.

The Nike Air Max Penny 1 Orlando is made in black and white fabric and has a sculptural white mudguard. It also features a jeweled Nike logo. The final touch is added by the while stitching over the black frabric. And finally, it features a woven striped tongue.

The Nike Air Max Penny 1 Orlando released in August of 2022 and retailed for $170.

name: Olive Aura (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Olive Aura (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Olive Aura (Women's) is a women’s low-top shoe featuring the Nike Dunk Low design that was produced as part of Nike’s Next Nature line in an Olive Aura colorway.

Nike is doing its part to become more sustainable when making shoes, and when Next Nature appears in the shoe’s name, it means that it was made with recycled materials. In this women’s Dunk Low, you’ll notice the speckled outsoles as evidence of the company doing its part to reduce their carbon footprint. The smooth Olive Aura color throughout is balanced with Neutral Sail, Coconut Milk, and white accents. The signature Swoosh adorns both sides in the tonal Olive Aura. Matching flat laces round out this shoe.

Our experts think the eco-friendly aspect of this sneaker doesn’t take away from its style and comfort. When it debuted on May 16, 2024, the Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Olive Aura (Women's) had a recommended retail price of $115.

name: Pure Platinum Wolf Grey (Women's)
title: Nike V2K Run Pure Platinum Wolf Grey (Women's)
description:
The Nike V2K Run Pure Platinum Wolf Grey (Women's) updates the Vomero silhouette with shiny metallics and layered details.

The base is crafted from a loose weave mesh in Pure Platinum and sits on a bulky, dual-density midsole in an off-white hue. This color gives the sneaker a worn-in appearance, which goes with its ’00s aesthetic. Synthetic leather overlays in Metallic Cool Grey and Wolf Grey are stitched across the upper, while a plastic strap in Cool Grey reaches from the midsole to the lace cage. In terms of branding, the Swoosh logo sits on top of the plastic strap, and the woven tongue tag reads NIKE.

Our StockX experts like the oversized heel, which is a throwback to technical running shoes from the early 2000s. The women’s size Nike V2K Run Pure Platinum Wolf Grey (Women's) was released on December 12, 2023, and sold for $110.

name: Gucci Original GG Beige Brown
title: adidas Gazelle Gucci Original GG Beige Brown
description:
adidas and Gucci teamed up to release a collaborative collection filled with apparel, footwear, and accessories in 2022. The adidas Gazelle Gucci Original GG Beige Brown was one of the shoes to come out of this collection.

This adidas x Gucci sneaker featured the adidas Gazelle silhouette that was first introduced in the 1960s, covered with Gucci’s instantly recognizable GG print. It had a light-brown canvas upper with white leather Three Stripes, and a red leather tab on the heel that included both the adidas Trefoil and the word "GUCCI" in metallic gold.

But the best part about this adidas x Gucci sneaker may have been the translucent cupsole that helped showcase even more of the Gucci branding on it. It allowed the GG print on the upper to breathe and let it be known that this wasn’t just any ordinary adidas Gazelle. The adidas Gazelle Gucci Original GG Beige Brown was released on June 7, 2022, for a $850 retail price.

name: Ale Brown Black
title: Nike Lunar Force 1 High Duckboot Ale Brown Black
description:
The Nike Lunar Force 1 High Duckboot Ale Brown Black is a men’s shoe that was originally designed for high-performance basketball.

The Nike Lunar Force 1 High Duckboot in Ale Brown Black features an Air unit, which brings about a lightweight cushioning. Cold and dampness are kept away by the tongue folding around the ankle. The sneakers are designed with a lace-up, a slip-on, and a width, which allows a snug fit. The upper is made of water-resistant leather on its heel and quarter panel. A studded synthetic material is used on the forefoot.

We think that the top feature of the Nike Lunar Force 1 High Duckboot Ale Brown Black is the design and color combination, which makes it suitable for casual wear school activities and workwear. It’s also flat-heeled making it perfect for an all-day wear. The shoe was released on September 24th, 2016, at a retail price of $140.

name: Summit White Light Bone
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low Luxe Summit White Light Bone
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low Luxe Summit White Light Bone has a white leather upper with a cushioned mesh collar, wavy eye stays, and a perforated toe box. 

The rubber outsole, heel tab and "Air" branding on the midsole all have hints of Light Bone. The Nike Swoosh branding is printed on both sides of the sneakers and their heels. Additionally, it features a padded tongue, a round toe cap and rugged soles with Nike branding and a large Swoosh emblem on its laterals. Full-length AIR units are included on the soles.

The Nike Air Force 1 Low Luxe Summit White Light Bone was released on February 16th, 2022, and retailed at $130.

name: Grey White
title: New Balance 574 Grey White
description:
The New Balance 574 Grey White takes the iconic low-top design that first debuted in 1988 and revamps it with performance trailing running technology.

The sneaker features an ENCAP midsole, which provides cushioning with a durable rim that supports the foot. Like other 574 variations, the Grey White (2022) edition comes with a rippled outsole that grips the ground and provides additional traction. This running shoe boasts a breathable mesh base with large, suede overlays that form a lace cage. The understated colorway displays White, Grey, and Silver, but grey is the dominant tone. The branding details are minimal, including the ‘N’ on the side panel, ‘NEW BALANCE’ written across the heel, and a New Balance label on the tongue.

Our StockX experts love the way the white laces stand out against the grey-tone upper and the silver detailing on the heel and the ‘N’. The New Balance 574 Grey White (2022) was released on April 15, 2022, and retailed at $95.

name: Flax
title: Nike Air Force 1 Mid '07 Flax
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low Flax is inspired in the classic work boot.

The boot has rope laces and monochromatic camel color. Is features a matching Flax Air sole in a lighter camel color, as well as the Nike logo. A comfy boot made for those looking for comfort.

The Nike Air Force 1 Low Flax was released in September of 2019 at a related price of $100.

name: Ash Pearl
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Ash Pearl
description:
Trailing the 2021 releases of the Ash Blue and Ash Stone colorways, Yeezy extended the Ash theme with the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Ash Pearl. The Ash Pearl colorway builds off of previous models, utilizing material selection to create a stylish and responsive design.

Similar to the Ash Blue and Ash Stone releases, the upper of the Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Ash Pearl features a two-tone construction. White and black Primeknit make up the lower portion of the upper, while cream and tan make up the upper half. Dividing the two sections of the upper is a tan mesh stripe that runs across the lateral side of the shoe. A white and gum Boost sole adds the cushioning and responsiveness that the 350 is known for.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Ash Pearl released in March of 2021 and retailed for $220.

name: Black White Gum
title: adidas Gazelle Black White Gum
description:
The adidas Gazelle Black White Gum is a unique remake of the classic adidas Gazelle model that was initially released in the year of 1966. It has a neutral color palette and is an ode to the style of the 1960s.

This adidas Gazelle iteration has a black upper body that is made from Nubuck leather. The tongue is made from a textured black leather, while the back of the shoe has smooth white leather overlays. The three classic stripes that adidas is famous for appear on the side of the shoe in white leather.

One characteristic that our team particularly enjoys about the adidas Gazelle Black White Gum is the rubber gum sole, as it is designed to provide traction and prevent the wearer from slipping. This pair of shoes was initially made available for purchase on July 13th, 2022, with a retail price that started at $150.

name: Valentine (Women's)
title: adidas Sambarose Valentine (Women's)
description:
The adidas Sambarose Valentine (Women's), a sneaker specifically sized for women, takes the classic adidas Samba silhouette and dresses it up with romantic color and style.

The Women's Valentine adidas Sambarose sports a white leather upper with the classic adidas 3 serrated stripes in black leather. The toebox has a T-shaped white suede overlay. The eye stay overlays and sock liner are also white leather, and the heel tab is black leather. Red adidas tree foil branding graces the white tongue. The platform midsole and outsole are both pink rubber.

What our sneaker experts enjoy most about this shoe are the hearts that accent both the upper and the outsole. One red heart is on the lateral side panel alongside the top stripe, and several hearts are visible through the pink translucent outsole. The adidas Sambarose Valentine (Women's), a sneaker specifically sized for women, was released on January 18, 2020, for a retail price of $125.

name: Pepper
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Pepper
description:
Yeezy expanded their 380 line with the Yeezy Boost 380 Pepper, now available on StockX. The colorway is reminiscent of the Yeezy 380 Mist, only this time it trades darker hues for a light earth-toned look.

The Yeezy 380 Pepper features a light grey and blue Primeknit upper with a light brown side spot. As usual, a dark translucent BOOST sole provides the ultimate cushioning experience that keeps Yeezy fans coming back for more.

The Yeezy Boost 380 Pepper released in September of 2020 and retailed for $230.

name: Halloween (2022)
title: Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM Halloween (2022)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Swoosh Shadow Iron Grey is made out of a mix of canvas, suede, and leather materials, coated in an iron grey, phantom and scream green color palette.

The sneaker has a gray leather base that is highlighted by gray suede inserts on the mudguard, quarter panel, eyelets and side Swoosh. It has a tonal Nike branding on the tongue and heel tab. This upper of the Low Nike Dunk is supported by a green outsole and a contrasting off-white midsole.

The Nike Dunk Low Swoosh Shadow Iron Grey was released on the 27th of October 2022 and originally retailed for $120.

name: Ronnie Fieg Cream Pure Aqua
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 12.1 Ronnie Fieg Cream
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 12.1 Ronnie Fieg Cream Pure Aqua takes elements from Ronnie Fieg’s signature design style and applies them to the iconic Gel-Kayano silhouette.

In keeping with Ronnie Fieg’s penchant for minimal branding, the technical Ronnie Fieg Cream Pure Aqua ASICS Gel-Kayano 12.1 displays discreet Gel-Kayano branding on the overlays. While the web of crisscrossing overlays comes in supple calf leather, the base features an airy mesh in Cream. The front lace closure system secures the shoe and houses Cream-colored laces. Dark Pure Aqua accents on the overlays stand out against the neutral-toned mesh and complement the off-white midsole. The lightweight FluidRide midsole features a dual-layer design that absorbs shock, while the rubber outsole provides traction.

Our experts at StockX like the sparing application of Pure Aqua, which gives the sneaker the minimalist look found in Ronnie Fieg’s signature street wear designs. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 12.1 Ronnie Fieg Cream Pure Aqua was released on June 24, 2024, and sold for $180.

name: Super Pop Pink (Women's)
title: adidas Gazelle Bold Super Pop Pink (Women's)
description:
The adidas Gazelle sneaker has been around since the 1960s, and for the most part, its design has remained unchanged outside a few updates to the materials used to make it. adidas did, however, make one noticeable alteration to this iconic sneaker while putting together the adidas Gazelle Bold Super Pop Pink (Women's).

At first glance, this adidas Gazelle might look like many of the Gazelles that came before it. It has a pink suede upper with adidas' three stripes done up in white to provide some contrast on the sneaker. It also has a comfortable synthetic lining on its interior that offers superior comfort.

But what our experts love best about this Gazelle is its chunky rubber outsole. It's three layers high and provides a fresh take on the classic Gazelle silhouette. The adidas Gazelle Bold Super Pop Pink (Women's) was released on December 2, 2022, when it initially retailed for $120.

name: Earth Fossil (Women's)
title: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Earth Fossil (Women's)
description:
The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Earth Fossil (Women's) is a women’s shoe designed for peak performance, with extra support around the upper.

This version of the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 is made with an off-white mesh upper for breathability throughout. Dark brown and silver overlays run around the toe box and up to the midsole, lining the dark brown TPU cage that can be seen reaching from the arches to the laces for extra support. The heel is also supported by a crisscrossing brown TPU pattern. The Nike swoosh appears on both sides in brown outlined in white, the heel features a silver swoosh, and the tongue sports a Nike logo patch. The rubber outsole features different shades of brown and light blue found under the heel, bringing the design together.

What we like best about this sneaker is the hit of blue on the outsole under the heel, which adds a welcome pop of color against the otherwise brown design. The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Earth Fossil (Women's) was released on December 22, 2022, for a price of $160.

name: Black Wolf Grey
title: Nike React Pegasus Trail 4 Gore-Tex Black Wolf Grey
description:
The Nike React Pegasus Trail 4 Gore-Tex Black Wolf Gray is trail running sneaker with waterproof features.

Something that makes this shoe stand out is the Gore-Tex along the upper. It helps keep the foot dry without adding weight or sacrificing comfort. The sneaker boasts an all-black construction with Wolf Gray and reflective detailing. Flecks of reflective material in the laces and a strip along the side panels improve visibility in low lighting and add a pop of silver. Unlike other trail running sneakers, this version of the React Pegasus Trail 4 has less rubber on the outsole. This allows the runner to transition from rough terrain to pavement. Other notable features include the full-length Boost unit in the midsole and the grippy traction pattern underfoot.

Our StockX experts like that some versions of the sneaker feature ‘JUST DO IT’ along the midsole, while others display ‘JUST RUN IT.’ The Nike React Pegasus Trail 4 Gore-Tex Black Wolf Gray was released on August 9th, 2022, and retailed at $160.

name: Haribo Goldbears Cloud White
title: adidas D.O.N. Issue #6 Haribo Goldbears Cloud White
description:
The adidas D.O.N. Issue #6 Haribo Goldbears Cloud White is one of three colorways from the D.O.N. Issue #6 line that pay homage to one of Donovan Mitchell's sweet treats, Haribo gummy bears.

One of Donovan Mitchell’s key phrases is "Determination Over Negativity" which is evident on and off the court. In the design of these sneakers, a positive perspective and fun attitude were in place and it's evident in the final product. The upper is primarily cloud white, which is the perfect light, fluffy background for the Haribo inspired pastel colors that float throughout the shoe. Three gummy consistency inspired solar green stripes appear on the sides and Haribo branding is seen on a heel pull tag and underfoot on the outsole. There is a squishy Spida logo on the tongue in solar green and red.

Our specialists note the ultra-lightweight cushioning of Lightstrike Pro and the zoned traction that the uniquely designed outsole provides as standout features of the adidas D.O.N. Issue #6 Haribo Goldbears Cloud White. This shoe was released on October 31, 2024, with a $130 retail price tag.

name: White Wonder Clay Gum (Women's)
title: adidas Samba OG White Wonder Clay Gum (Women's)
description:
The adidas Samba OG White Wonder Clay Gum (Women’s) is a women’s exclusive iteration of the Samba OG, a vintage sneaker by adidas with a history that dates back to the mid-20th century.

The shoes have a low-top silhouette and feature a predominantly cream/off-white upper with Wonder Clay accents, which is a color almost similar to a light shade of red, borderline orange. The upper is made from leather material with suede overlays on the toe box, while the sole unit is made from gum rubber. The shoe maintains a few branding elements seen on the adidas Samba OG silhouette including the iconic three stripes on the sides and an adidas logo on the tongue.

One thing we love about the adidas Samba OG White Wonder Clay Gum (Women’s) is the combination of leather and suede materials on the upper, which not only adds to the overall aesthetic of the shoes but also gives a luxury feel. The women’s sized shoes were released for retail priced at $120 on 15th May 2023.

name: Kicki Yang Zhang Pink Cream Pure Silver
title: ASICS Gel-NYC Kicki Yang Zhang Pink Cream Pure Silver
description:
The ASICS Gel-NYC Kicki Yang Zhang Pink Cream Pure Silver is an athletic shoe designed in collaboration with Kicki Yang Zhang, a makeup artist and fashion personality based in Berlin.

The Kicki Yang Zhang Pink Cream Pure Silver ASICS Gel-NYC is made with a cream mesh upper as its base. Semi-metallic white overlays cross the sides of the shoe for support and also form the eyestays. The toe cap is metallic silver, and the ASICS design runs across each side in metallic silver and pink. A shiny pink mudguard supports each side and forms the heel, and the ASICS logo is white on the lateral side. Gel branding can also be found at the heel. The tongue also bears a simple ASICS logo, and the shoe sits on a chunky pink midsole equipped with slightly darker Gel technology for energy return.

What we like best about this shoe is the bubblegum pink color, which adds a nice feminine touch. The ASICS Gel-NYC Kicki Yang Zhang Pink Cream Pure Silver was released on September 26, 2024, for $130.

name: Bad Bunny Cream
title: adidas Campus Light Bad Bunny Cream
description:
adidas and Bad Bunny are back again in 2023 with a new collaboration on the adidas Campus model. Bad Bunny originally previewed his adidas Campus sneaker in his El Apagón music video.

Bad Bunny did not disappoint with his first adidas Campus model which comes in a cream and cloud white colorway. The sneakers come with a longer suede material, and feature a stacked heel tab and tongue with Bad Bunnys logo located on the tongue. The sneakers also come with extra white laces and a dustbag.

The adidas Campus Bad Bunny Cream released January 28, 2023, with a retail price of $150.

name: Valentine's Day (2024) (Women's)
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 SE PRM Valentine's Day (2024) (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 SE PRM Valentine's Day (2024) (Women's) celebrates Valentine’s Day by applying Team Red and Medium Soft Pick details to the AF 1 Low silhouette.

This low-top sneaker boasts a leather upper in Sail with tonal leather overlays and perforations across the vamp. The Medium Soft Pink Swoosh on the lateral side panel is filled with glitter in the shape of hearts and flowers, while the Swoosh on the medial side panel comes in off-white leather. The laces feature transparent Team Red and Medium Soft Pink beads in the shape of flowers and stars that add to the sneaker’s Valentine’s Day aesthetic.

Our experts at StockX like the use of Team Red on the rubber outsole, which matches the color of the padded collar. The women’s size Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 SE PRM Valentine's Day (2024) (Women's) was released on February 14th, 2024, and retailed at $130.
model: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 SE PRM

name: Prussian Blue (GS)
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Prussian Blue (GS)
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 Prussian Blue (GS) is a stability running shoe with a Clean White base and sporty accents in Prussian Blue, metallic silver, black, and orange.

Designed for grade school-aged children, the Prussian Blue (GS) ASICS Gel-1130 features a lightweight mesh upper in white with a web of overlays in Prussian Blue, metallic silver, and black. Orange accents add splashes of color on the tongue and ‘GEL’ lettering on the heel. Featuring numerous heritage elements, this version of the Gel-1130 draws inspiration from models in the GEL-1000 series and has roots in early 2000s designs. However, it also includes contemporary upgrades, such as Gel technology in the heel. This supportive cushioning transforms the Gel-1130 from a running shoe into a sneaker for urban environments.

Our experts at StockX like the padding in the collar and tongue because it contributes to the sneaker’s retro runner aesthetic. The grade school-sized ASICS Gel-1130 Prussian Blue (GS) was released on June 1, 2024, and sold for $85.

name: Black White Gum (Women's)
title: adidas Samba OG Black White Gum (Women's)
description:
Inspired by indoor soccer shoes from the 1950s, the adidas Samba OG Black White Gum (Women's) showcases the Samba heritage through its design and premium materials.

The full-grain leather upper in Core Black gives the Black White Gum (Women's) adidas Samba OG a durable exterior, while the T-shaped suede toebox overlay reinforces the toe area. Touches of Cloud White on the leather serrated 3-Stripes logo and the leather heel tab stand out against the Core Black upper and suede overlays. In addition, the insole and the thick laces also come in Core Black. In terms of branding, the tongue showcases a retro-inspired adidas logo tag in blue, while ‘SAMBA’ in gold foil runs along the 3-Stripes logo.

Our experts at StockX like the addition of dark brown instead of tan on the gum rubber cupsole because it completes the sneaker’s dark aesthetic. The women’s size adidas Samba OG Black White Gum (Women's) was released on December 1, 2023, and was priced at $100.

name: Wonder Silver Gum (Women's)
title: adidas Handball Spezial Wonder Silver Gum (Women's)
description:
The adidas Handball Spezial Wonder Silver Gum (Women's) is built upon an indoor court silhouette launched in 1979, reimagined for a modern-day street-style sensibility, and sized specifically for women.

This fashionable low-top features an upper of soft gray suede with overlays in the same gray suede adorning the eyestays and toecap. White leather forms the iconic serrated side panel with three-stripes, as well as the heel tab. White flat laces cross over a gray suede tongue and match the white leather sock liner designed to keep your foot cool. The gum rubber cupsole features embossed adidas trefoil branding on the sidewall and grooved outsole.

Our favorite aspect of this women’s sneaker is the signature Spezial branding tongue tag. White with pale gray branding, this adds a subtle touch of distinction to the tongue. The adidas Handball Spezial Wonder Silver Gum (Women's) was released on August 20, 2022, for $110 retail.

name: Triple Black
title: New Balance 574 Triple Black
description:
The New Balance 574 Triple Black is an iteration of the New Balance 574 sneaker in a Core Black colorway.

This sneaker features an all-Black upper made of a mesh base with suede overlays on the forefoot, mid-panel, and heel. The mesh material used on the vamp, tongue, and ankle collar is made of 100% recycled polyester. Smooth, reflective material in a contrasting dark tone highlights the ‘N’ logo, upper eyestays, and heel tab. This shoe rests on a tonal ENCAP-cushioned midsole and a rubber outsole made of 5% recycled rubber. 

The New Balance 574 Triple Black (2022) was made available on January 13th, 2022. Initially, it retailed at $95.

name: LaFrancé
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.04 LaFrancé
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.04 LaFrancé is a cool mid grey and team light blue colorway from LaMelo Ball’s signature shoe line with Puma, this being the MB.04 version.

LaMelo Ball is a dynamic basketball player, and this is a fitting sneaker that pays homage to his abilities and hard-working ethos. The team's light blue hues and tentacle-like overlays combined with a spaceship image and "Not from here" wording embedded underfoot on the outsole adds to the out of this world theme. LaFrancé is LaMelo’s middle name, and references to it are seen on at the bottom of the tongue and on the heel. Ball’s signature winged 1 logo is prominent on the tongue.

It is our expert opinion that the 5D printing technology added dynamic elements and intricate patterns that incorporated words such as MELO, RARE, and LOVE on the upper and a tiny phrase is even embedded on the tip of the toe. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.04 LaFrancé hit the shelves on September 12, 2024, with $125 as the recommended retail price.

name: Yecheil (Non-Reflective)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Yecheil (Non-Reflective)
description:
Yeezy adds a flare to one of its most well-known designs with the adidas Yeezy 350 Yecheil Non-Reflective, now available on StockX. This 350 V2 strays away from the usual earth tones with a colorful palette, making it stand out from previous releases. This model was released in both reflective and non-reflective variations.

This Yeezy 350 V2 is composed of a black upper with white, red, yellow, and blue accents. A black Boost cushioned sole and black side stripe completes the design. These sneakers released in December of 2019 and retailed for $220.

name: Clear Sky (Women's)
title: adidas Gazelle Bold Clear Sky (Women's)
description:
adidas hasn't tinkered with the design of its iconic Gazelle sneaker very much since first unveiling it back in the 1960s. The company has, however, experimented with its appearance from time-to-time, to create special versions of it. The adidas Gazelle Bold Clear Sky (Women's), which is a women's-exclusive sneaker, is one of the best examples of this.

This Gazelle Bold features many of the things people have come to know and love about the Gazelle over the years. It has the same suede upper and the same T-toe overlay and Three Stripes that it had back in the beginning. But this version of the Gazelle takes things to the next level, quite literally, with a triple-stacked rubber outsole that makes it stand taller than ever before.

Our experts appreciate adidas finding innovative ways to breathe new life into its timeless Gazelle. It should help this sneaker stick around for another 60 years. The adidas Gazelle Bold Clear Sky (Women's) was released on June 15, 2023, for a $120 retail price.

name: Rain Cloud (GS)
title: New Balance 9060 Rain Cloud (GS)
description:
The New Balance 9060 Rain Cloud (GS) for grade schoolers reinterprets the original 9060 model with futuristic elements to give grade schoolers a fresh iteration of a classic shoe.

This sneaker features a sleek and modern design with clean lines and minimalist aesthetics. Its upper is crafted from durable and breathable materials including premium mesh, suede, and synthetic leather. These materials provide ventilation to keep the feet cool and comfortable throughout the day while offering support and protection against wear and tear. Cushioning technology in the midsole delivers energy return and shock absorption, while a padded collar and tongue add comfort around the ankle area. A patterned rubber outsole ensures grip on pavement, grass, and a number of indoor surfaces.

What our experts most appreciate about the New Balance 9060 Rain Cloud (GS) for grade schoolers, however, is its combination of Rain Cloud and Castlerock grays that imbue it with a timeless aesthetic. This shoe originally retailed for $110 on November 26, 2023.

name: Castlerock
title: New Balance 9060 Castlerock
description:
The New Balance 9060 Castlerock combines elements of other New Balance silhouettes to create an eye-catching high-octane running shoe.

The Castlerock New Balance 9060 has an upper with a base of white and gray mesh overlaid with wavy strips of black and gray leather, an aesthetic borrowed from the 990 to give a sense of visible motion. The side-panel N is embroidered in small stripes while a solid N is embroidered at the base of the black laces. NB branding is also embroidered on the heel above the translucent CR device. The black leather tongue with gleaming red branding hearkens back to the 991.

The feature that makes this running shoe stand apart is the exaggerated sculpted pod midsole made of ABZORB to absorb impact and provide cushioning. The ABZORB SBS in the heel offers comfort and stability. The black rubber outsole with red diamonds pays homage to the 860. The New Balance 9060 Castlerock was released on July 26, 2023, for $150 retail.

name: Vermillion
title: adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Vermillion
description:
The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Vermillion features an all-red one piece EVA foam construction with oval cut-outs to provide ventilation. At the base, a cushioned footbed offers support and stability.

The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Vermillion released in October of 2021 and retailed for $80.

name: Wonder Beige
title: adidas Campus 00s Wonder Beige
description:
The adidas Campus 00s Wonder Beige upgrades the original Campus from the 1980s with a neutral colorway of Off-White, Cream White, and Wonder Beige, and 2000s-inspired design details.

This low-top sneaker finds inspiration in chunky skate shoes from the early 2000s. For example, additional padding along the collar and tongue gives the sneaker a bulky appearance. The pillowy tongue pushes against the laces, allowing the adidas trefoil logo embroidered onto the tongue to stand out. The upper is crafted from soft suede in Wonder Beige, while the serrated 3-Stripes and the heel tab come in Off-White suede. Branding details include a large trefoil on the heel and ‘CAMPUS’ printed along the 3-Stripes in dark beige ink.

Our experts at StockX appreciate the use of Cream White on the rubber outsole instead of Light Gum Brown or Gum. The adidas Campus 00s Wonder Beige was released on September 3rd, 2023, and retailed at $110.

name: MiUSA Navy White
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Navy White
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Navy White features a streamlined upper with layers of mesh and suede in a dark colorway of Navy.

The MiUSA Navy White New Balance 990v6's breathable mesh underlays, soft suede overlays, suede mudguard, tongue, and part of the rubber outsole come in Navy. However, splashes of gray break up the dark hues on the signature New Balance "N," the laces, the overlays near the heel, and the lining. In addition, the "990," "New Balance 990" on the tongue tag, and other branding details come in gray. In the midsole, FuelCell technology increases propulsion, and ENCAP cushioning acts as a foam wedge under the heel.

Our experts at StockX like the layered stripes of gray, white, and light gray on the midsole because they bring tonal unity to the colorway. The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Navy White was released on October 6, 2023, and sold for $200.

name: Dexter's Laboratory
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Dexter's Laboratory
description:
Embark on a journey of style and performance with the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Dexter's Laboratory edition. Inspired by the animated charm of Dexter's Laboratory, this sneaker is a vibrant mix of Poison Pink and Fluro Orange Pes, creating a visually striking appearance. Designed for dynamic play, the MB.03 Dexter's Laboratory edition offers superior cushioning, agile support, and a playful yet bold aesthetic that stands out both on and off the court.

Reflecting the energy and uniqueness of LaMelo Ball's personality, this sneaker is more than just footwear; it's a statement. Its sleek design, combined with the advanced performance features of Puma, ensures comfort and style. The sneaker's color palette and theme are a tribute to those who embrace their individuality and dare to be different in their fashion choices.

Launched on December 22, 2023, with a retail price of $135, the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Dexter's Laboratory is a must-have for sneaker enthusiasts. It's a perfect blend of modern basketball technology and a touch of nostalgic animation, bringing a unique twist to the sneaker game.

name: CLOT Linen Khaki
title: adidas Gazelle CLOT Linen Khaki
description:
The adidas Gazelle CLOT Linen Khaki is a shoe designed as part of a collaboration with the fashion brand CLOT.

This iteration of the adidas Gazelle has an upper made of nubuck leather and raffia, a palm tree native to tropical Africa. These woven raffia fronds make up the base of the upper in a Linen Khaki color, while nubuck leather overlays in the same color form the t-shaped toe cap, the eyestays, and the heel. The adidas three stripes appear on each side in beads in varying shades of blue, and blue stitching is seen at the heel, trimming the tongue, and attaching the upper to the braided midsole. The shoe sits on a classic rubber sole.

The most intriguing thing about this shoe is its raffia construction, which is unique for sneakers. The adidas Gazelle CLOT Linen Khaki was released on August 23, 2024, for $160.

name: Clear Sky Gum
title: adidas Campus 00s Clear Sky Gum
description:
The adidas Campus 00s Clear Sky Gum is an adidas Campus 00s sneaker sporting a Clear Sky, blue, and gold metallic color combination.

The signature design of the adidas Campus 00s builds upon the Campus 80s legacy, twisting and turning it into its own being. This iteration is a Clear Sky Gum colorway that found inspiration in skateboarding culture. There is the chunky off-white midsole, a padded heel collar, and the short toebox. The premium leather upper is a Clear Sky color, and you’ll spot the serrated three strips with gold metallic CAMPUS branding alongside them. There is a white trefoil on the foam tongue in white and a blue one on the heel tab.

We think that the terry textile lining is a unique aspect of this sneaker, adding a plush feeling and comfort. The adidas Campus 00s Clear Sky Gum released on July 1, 2024, with a $110 price tag.

name: Enflame Amber
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Enflame Amber
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Enflame Amber features a pale yellow mesh, leather, and suede upper with brown and teal overlays located over the forefoot. 3M detailing on the heel and a bright orange Boost sole finishes off this colorful design.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Enflame Amber released in June of 2021 and retailed for $240.

name: Charcoal Black
title: adidas Campus 00s Charcoal Black
description:
The adidas Campus 00s Charcoal Black adds a dark colorway of Charcoal and Core Black to the retro-inspired Campus 00s silhouette.

Like other Campus 00s models, the Charcoal Black version draws inspiration from the chunky skater shoes of the early 2000s. Padding around the tongue and collar contributes to the retro skater aesthetic, while the use of premium suede hearkens back to the Campus’s varsity athletics heritage. The upper is crafted from soft suede in Charcoal, while Core Black details can be found on the laces, the heel tab, the collar, and the 3-Stripes logo. Another element that makes this sneaker stand out is the foam sole unit. It’s slightly thicker than the ones found on other models and curves up at the toe.

Our StockX experts like the metallic CAMPUS branding running along the 3-stripes logo. The adidas Campus 00s Charcoal Black was released on December 22, 2023, and originally sold for $110.

name: Royal Blue
title: adidas Harden Vol. 7 Royal Blue
description:
The adidas Harden Vol. 7 Royal Blue, the seventh signature silhouette of James Harden, blurs the boundaries between performance and lifestyle, introducing a knit bootie adorned with textile quarter panels.

The Royal Blue textile upper of the adidas Harden Vol. 7 is accented with tonal stitching and reinforced by a tonal synthetic suede toe cap, featuring an interior knit bootie for a snug and comfortable fit. The iconic 3-Stripes adidas branding embellishes the two-layer heel counter. The caged midsole incorporates Jet Boost in the heel and LightStrike cushioning in the forefoot, delivering on-court responsiveness with each step. The sneaker's foundation is a rubber outsole with a multi-directional herringbone pattern, providing stop-and-go traction.

The wow factor of the adidas Harden Vol. 7 Royal Blue lies in its groundbreaking and responsive Boost cushioning technology. This innovative technology ensures exceptional impact absorption and energy return, delivering a comfortable and dynamic experience. The sneaker debuted for $160 on July 12th, 2023.

name: Pirate Black (2023)
title: adidas Yeezy 950 Pirate Black (2023)
description:
The adidas Yeezy 950 Pirate Black (2023) is a distinctive fusion of duck boot and military boot, culminating in a hybrid silhouette that carves its niche in the sneaker realm.

The 2023 adidas Yeezy 950 boasts a monochromatic theme, with the entirety of its structure, including the upper and midsole, enveloped in a sleek Pirate Black hue. Fashioned from ballistic nylon mesh and durable black rubber, the high-cut upper ensures durability and sturdy support. Enhanced with leather and canvas lining, the shoe provides durability and support. Notable features encompass a rugged rubber base encircling the mudguard and toe box, along with a convenient heel pull tab for easy wear. Anchored by a substantial rubber midsole and a lug-patterned rubber outsole, the sneaker ensures reliable traction.

The remarkable aspect of the adidas Yeezy 950 Pirate Black (2023) lies in its hybridized silhouette that blends design elements from both a duck boot and military boot. This distinctive amalgamation sets it apart within the sneaker landscape, offering an unconventional and standout footwear option. The shoe debuted for $600 on August 17, 2023.

name: Kith Marvel Villains Spider-Man/Venom Battle Spectra Pack Sealed Box (Comic Included)
title: ASICS GT-2160 Kith Marvel Villains Spider-Man/Venom Battle Spectra Pack Sealed Box (Comic Included)
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 Kith Marvel Villains Spider-Man/Venom Battle Spectra Pack Sealed Box (Comic Included) is a two-pair set of athletic shoes featuring mesh and synthetic leather uppers in two gradient color palettes, Red, Blue. Black, and Cream and Black with Purple-Blue. Spider-Man and Venom illustrations appear on the lining, while Marvel and ASICS branding adorns the left shoe. Kith and Fieg logos decorate the right shoe.

Asics is a Japanese athletic wear brand known for its running shoes, while Kith is an American lifestyle brand founded in New York in 2011. Comics giant Marvel has released many iconic comic series, featuring characters like Spider-Man and Venom. This tri-brand collaboration nods to the special edition nature of comics with its UV-printed Marvel Kith double box and the shoes packaged in custom mylar bags. An accompanying exclusive comic book completes the theme.

Our experts feel that the best feature of the GT-2160 Kith Marvel Villains is that it's a two sneaker set, featuring branding and packaging found nowhere else. The ASICS GT-2160 Kith Marvel Villains Spider-Man/Venom Battle Spectra Pack Sealed Box (Comic Included) released on August 9, 2024, and retailed for $350.

name: MiUSA JJJJound Military Urban Grey Angora
title: New Balance 993 MiUSA JJJJound Military Urban Grey Angora
description:
The New Balance 993 MiUSA JJJJound Military Urban Grey Angora is a premium collaboration that combines classic design with contemporary style. This limited edition sneaker features a sophisticated color palette of military urban grey and angora, creating a versatile look that's perfect for both casual and elevated outfits. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, the shoe boasts high-quality materials and expert construction, ensuring both comfort and durability.

Made in the USA, this New Balance 993 showcases the brand's commitment to superior craftsmanship. The shoe incorporates New Balance's renowned ENCAP midsole technology, providing exceptional cushioning and support for all-day wear. The upper is constructed with a blend of premium suede and mesh, offering breathability and a luxurious feel. The JJJJound collaboration brings a minimalist aesthetic to the iconic 993 silhouette, resulting in a sneaker that's both timeless and modern.

Us at StockX believe this product is great for sneaker enthusiasts and fashion-forward individuals who appreciate quality construction and understated style. The New Balance 993 MiUSA JJJJound Military Urban Grey Angora offers the perfect balance of comfort, performance, and sophisticated design.

name: MiUSA Cream
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Cream
description:
The New Balance 990 series is known for its premium craftsmanship, comfort, and versatility. The "v6" in the model’s name indicates that it is the sixth version in the series. The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Cream features high-quality materials in its construction, including a combination of suede, mesh, and leather. The use of premium materials contributes to the durability and overall quality of the shoe.

This New Balance model in MiUSA Cream has a color palette that is primarily composed of neutral shades, including yellow, white, taupe, gray, and light brown. New Balance's ENCAP technology is incorporated into the midsole, providing a balance of cushioning and support. The design of the 990v6 maintains the classic aesthetic that has been a hallmark of the 990 series. It's known for its clean lines, iconic "N" logo on the sides, and a versatile silhouette.

One feature that our experts love about the New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Cream is its comfortable cushioning, making it suitable for both casual wear and light athletic activities. It was released on July 7th, 2023, for $220.

name: Golden Child
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Golden Child
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01Golden Child is a limited-edition sneaker inspired by NBA star LaMelo Ball’s first sneaker with Puma. From the basketball player’s Rare Reserve Collection, this sneaker was once player-exclusive (PE).

The Golden Child iteration of the LaMelo Ball x Puma MB.01 features an upper of dusty gold monomesh with welded metallic gold overlays that lend both support and structure. An embroidered rocket ship flame design adorns the collar, a nod to Melo’s spaceship tattoo. Metallic TPU in gold covers the midsole composed of Puma NITROFOAM, designed for ultimate responsiveness and superior lightweight comfort. The outsole is made of a non-slip rubber compound patterned for impact absorption, enhanced durability, and multidirectional traction.

What we enjoy most about these Puma sneakers are the hits of LaMelo branding. His signature wings grace the tongue and his motto "1 of 1" is printed on the medial side toe cap. The word RARE appears in orange beneath the translucent rubber of the outsole. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01Golden Child was released on November 24, 2023, for a retail price of $140.

name: Haribo Goldbears Lucid Red
title: adidas D.O.N. Issue #6 Haribo Goldbears Lucid Red
description:
In celebration of NBA star Don Mitchell and his love of gummy bears, the adidas D.O.N. Issue #6 Haribo Goldbears Lucid Red is a unique limited-edition collab between adidas and global sweet maker Haribo.

These vibrant sneakers from adidas and Haribo celebrate the sweet tooth of famous baller Don Mitchell and his love of the Goldbears range of sweets. The midsole has Lightstrike Pro cushioning to give superior bounce on the court, while the translucent sole has a gummy effect. The shoe is a deep red with neon green accents. It has mesh sides for ventilation, and the 3-Stripes branding can be seen on the sides through the uppers. The pull tag on the ankle includes the Haribo logo, and the Trefoil logo appears on the heel guard.

We love the playfulness of these exclusive sneakers—not just the color combo, but the nod to gummy bears extending from the shoe design to the packaging. The adidas D.O.N. Issue #6 Haribo Goldbears Lucid Red released on October 31, 2024, priced at $130.

name: Clay Grey Pure Silver
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Clay Grey Pure Silver
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 Clay Grey Pure Silver arrives in a sleek clay grey and pure silver colorway, drawing design inspiration from the Gel-Kayano 14, a standout in the ASICS lineup.

The upper of this ASICS Gel-1130 is crafted from a mix of materials, including breathable mesh and synthetic overlays that mimic leather. A dynamic design sees the clay grey mesh base accented with pure silver details flowing across it, while metallic silver highlights add a polished touch. The iconic ASICS stripes feature prominently on both sides, tying the look together. True to its heritage, this low-profile running shoe incorporates ASICS’ signature Gel cushioning for reliable comfort. Matching clay grey laces complete the look.

We think one of the shoe’s defining features is the silver-colored TRUSSTIC support system, a shank positioned between the forefoot and rearfoot that enhances stability. Released on September 1, 2024, the ASICS Gel-1130 Clay Grey Pure Silver hit shelves at a retail price of $95.

name: Sporty & Rich USA
title: adidas Samba OG Sporty & Rich USA
description:
The adidas Samba OG Sporty & Rich USA is an adidas Samba OG shoe in a USA colorway that was released to commemorate the 2024 Summer Olympics and Team USA’s appearance in them.

This "USA" colorway was designed in collaboration by adidas and the Sporty & Rich brand that specializes in athleisure wear. The premium leather upper dresses the heel overlay, side panels, eyestay and tongue in a cloud white hue. The heel tab features a suede night indigo with a white trefoil and Sporty & Rich branding. The iconic three stripes are jagged on this model and alternate between night indigo and collegiate red. The t-toe overlay is a tan suede, while a gum-colored outsole and off-white shoelaces round out this silhouette.

Our experts think the standout feature of the adidas Samba OG Sporty & Rich USA is the golden metallic branding that is seen near the Three Stripes and the insole. Inspiration to go for the gold. When it was released on July 29, 2024, this shoe retailed for $120.

name: Cream Pepper (Women's)
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Cream Pepper (Women's)
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Cream Pepper (Women's) is a shoe in women’s sizes designed for performance running and inspired by the explosion of lightning.
  
This iteration of the ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 is made with an upper of breathable white mesh in a Cream shade. Silver artificial leather overlays form the toe cap and outline the toe box, while also forming the eyestays and the heel. The ASICS classic design crosses the sides of the shoe in Pepper overlays, while the tongue bears an ASICS logo. There are metallic-blue overlays on each side of the ankle that run back to the heel, and the silver overlay on the heel contains Gel branding. Gel technology is visible underfoot in the midsole in blue, and a Pepper rubber outsole completes the look.
 
What we like best about this sneaker are the metallic-blue overlays, which add a touch of color to the otherwise neutral tones of the shoe. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Cream Pepper (Women's) was released on March 1, 2024, for $150.

name: Unlimited Pack White Fawn
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Unlimited Pack White Fawn
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Unlimited Pack White Fawn is part of the Unlimited Pack and blends the classic Gel-Kayano 14’s performance capabilities with contemporary colors.

The lightweight, mesh upper of the Unlimited Pack White Fawn ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 comes in clean white and serves as a backdrop for the synthetic overlays in Fawn and metallic silver. Unlike other models in the Unlimited Pack, the "White Fawn" incorporates a traditional lacing system instead of a quick lace system. However, the sneaker still offers a full-length foam midsole with visible Gel technology in the forefoot and heel. The signature Trusstic support system prevents the shoe from twisting and provides stability in the midsole.

Our experts at StockX like the Gel technology’s slightly dark pink color. It makes the underfoot area stand out and matches part of the padded tongue. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Unlimited Pack White Fawn was released on March 18, 2024, and sold for $150.

name: Sulfur
title: adidas Yeezy 450 Sulfur
description:
The adidas Yeezy 450 Sulfur features a monotone Sulfur sock-like Primeknit upper with a cinched collar and thick rope laces that appear to be braided into the forefoot. At the base, a sculptural sole that grips the upper provides structure and support.

The adidas Yeezy 450 Sulfur released in May of 2022 and retailed for $200.

name: Ash Grey
title: adidas Yeezy 500 Ash Grey
description:
Drawing inspiration from 90s hiking shoes, the adidas Yeezy 500 Ash Grey features a layered upper constructed with Ash Grey mesh, suede, and leather. At the base, a sculptural brown adiPRENE sole adds responsiveness and support.

The adidas Yeezy 500 Ash Grey released in December of 2021 and retailed for $200.

name: Black
title: ASICS ACTIBREEZE 3D Sandal Black
description: The ASICS ACTIBREEZE 3D Sandal Black is a versatile and comfortable footwear option for those who prioritize both style and functionality. The sandal features a 3D-printed upper that provides a snug fit and breathability, while the EVA midsole offers cushioning and support. The outsole is made of durable rubber, ensuring traction and stability on various surfaces. The black colorway adds a sleek and modern touch to the sandal, making it suitable for both casual and athletic wear. The ASICS ACTIBREEZE 3D Sandal Black was released on July 21, 2022, and is priced at $80. Overall, this sandal is a great choice for those who want a comfortable and stylish option for their summer footwear collection.

name: Eclipse Navy
title: New Balance 2002R Eclipse Navy
description:
The New Balance 2002R Eclipse Navy version here uses a more subdued palette of neutral tones for its design. 

The sneaker is dressed in an "Eclipse" tone, and creamy pig suede overlays are attached to the midfoot, heels, tongues, and front ends of the shoes. The "Castlerock" accent tracks are brought in to decorate the extra overlays that disappear from the collars and toe boxes. The midsole parts are divided into panels with ivory heels and forefoot and are equipped with the brand's NERGY cushioning underneath. To complete its appearance are the "N" logos found on the quarter dressed in grey with a white outline and an eclipse color scheme on its outsole tip.

The New Balance 2002R Eclipse Navy was released on the market on 2nd September 2022 and retailed at $120.

name: Aminé Benson Tech
title: New Balance 740v2 Aminé Benson Tech
description:
The New Balance 740v2 Aminé Benson Tech is a performance shoe designed in collaboration with American rapper Aminé.

The Animé Benson Tech New Balance 740v2 has a base of Persimmon Orange mesh for breathability. Calf leather overlays in Snorkel Blue form the toe cap and heel and support the sides. The New Balance N appears in orange on each side, while BCEE branding is found on the outer heel. The back of the heel also contains Benson branding in the form of BN lettering. The blue midsole is equipped with ABZORB cushioning, and the outsole is orange. There are shiny translucent pockets around the toe box and heel, adding another element of style.

What stands out about this shoe is the style of the laces, which have a toggle on top instead of the traditional ties. The New Balance 740v2 Aminé Benson Tech was released on November 1, 2024, for $120.

name: Moonbeam True Blue (Women's)
title: New Balance 327 Moonbeam True Blue (Women's)
description:
As elegant a sports shoe as you’ve ever seen, the New Balance 327 Moonbeam True Blue (Women's) are ready to elevate your sports game and your capsule shoe wardrobe, too.

A stunning, sophisticated color palette of ‘moonbeam’ grey and ‘true’ blue with a white base brings these New Balance 327s to life. Combining suede on the colorways with textile, the signature N of this iteration show pops in a blue that is only again matched on tiny accents such as the tongue branding and the inner heel text of New Balanced. With signature NB midsoles providing a bouncy step, the robber outsoles provide traction for even the wettest roads or courts.

We love how New Balance has combined a subtle color palette to deliver a durable women’s shoe. The serrated outsoles are another distinctive key visual. The New Balance 327 Moonbeam True Blue (Women's) New Balance 327 Moonbeam True Blue Women’s sneaker was released on 12 April 2024, priced at $100.

name: White Arctic Night
title: adidas Handball Spezial White Arctic Night
description:
The adidas Handball Spezial White Arctic Night takes a silhouette that was originally designed for top-tier handball players in 1979 and reimagines it with colors and fabrics that make it an ideal lifestyle shoe.

The White Arctic Night colorway of the adidas Handball Spezial features an upper with a base of white tumbled leather. Off-white suede overlays adorn the toe cap and heel, while white leather overlays accent the eyestays and deep green leather forms the serrated side panel three stripes. Rich burgundy leather forms the heel tab and matches the sock liner and insole. This elegant upper sits atop a pebbled sail-colored midsole and a sail rubber outsole that has been intricately grooved for multi-directional traction.

An aspect of this sneaker we particularly enjoy is its subtle branding. adidas branding appears in gold script on the tongue, while Spezial branding appears in gold script on the side panel. adidas trefoil branding adorns the insole in white and is embossed on both the sidewall and outsole. The adidas Handball Spezial White Arctic Night debuted on August 1, 2023, for $110 retail.

name: White Black Gum
title: adidas Handball Spezial White Black Gum
description:
The adidas Handball Spezial White Black Gum is a classic sneaker that pays homage to adidas' rich heritage in handball footwear.

This shoe features a clean and minimalist design, with an upper constructed from premium suede and leather. Classic adidas three-stripe branding is prominently displayed in black coloring on the sides, which pops against the predominantly white colorway. Black accents can also be found on the tongue and heel, over which additional branding elements can be found. A cushioned midsole provides support and shock absorption, ensuring all-day wear, while a padded collar and tongue add to the overall comfort of the shoe. The breathable lining helps to regulate the shoe’s internal temperature, keeping feet cool and dry.

What our experts most appreciate about the adidas Handball Spezial White Black Gum, however, is its namesake gum rubber outsole, which provides excellent traction on a number of surfaces, which adds a touch of vintage flair to the shoe's design. This shoe retailed with an original price of $110 when it was released on July 15, 2023.

name: Mushroom Aluminum
title: New Balance 9060 Mushroom Aluminum
description:
The New Balance 9060 Mushroom Aluminum was released as part of the New Balance’s brand catalog in the spring season featuring aluminum and mushroom tones.
​
​ The sneaker features a porous mesh base with several suede overlays stretching from the front to the back. The mesh base takes on dove grey and mushroom colors, with the latter hue appearing on the lateral side. Varying shades of mushroom-like tone engage the more extensive overlays along and across the upper, while the N symbol and the accents around the heel portray a simple grey aspect. New Balance offered an off-white/​grey rugged sole unit on the underfoot to complete the classic design.
​
​The New Balance 9060 Mushroom Aluminum was released on March 4th, 2023, and retailed at $150.

name: MiUSA Joe Freshgoods 1998 Intro
title: New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods 1998 Intro
description:
The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods 1998 Intro represents a collaboration between the Chicago streetwear designer and the New Balance ultimate running shoe. This sneaker gets its inspiration from the film Belly and the XXL magazine cover featuring DMX, Ja Rule, and Jay-Z.

The Intro New Balance 99v4 Joe Freshgoods sports an upper with a black mesh base overlaid in sandy-colored suede. A black leather N adorns the side panel while 1998 and Made in the USA branding grace the heel tab. New Balance branding also appears on the heel. Joe Freshgoods branding appears on one red insole while New Balance branding appears on the other. Dual branding also appears on each tongue tag.
