The aspect of this sneaker that our shoe experts appreciate the most is the ENCAP midsole with its lightweight foam and durable polyurethane rim that provides ultimate cushioning and energy return. This sits atop a black and gray rubber outsole with grooves and a waffle pattern for traction. The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods 1998 Intro was released on December 15, 2023, for $220 retail.

name: Birch Green Red Yellow
title: Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 Birch Green Red Yellow
description:
Meet the iconic Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66, now surfing the trend waves in the Birch Green/Red/Yellow colorway. This sneaker tells tales of legendary style, resurrected for the modern trailblazers.

Presented in various shades, it brings together a perfect blend of birch green with hits of red and yellow, making it a timeless masterpiece. The upper, crafted with premium materials, reflects class and durability, setting it apart in the sneaker world.The design pays a harmonious tribute to the iconic Onitsuka Tiger stripe alongside the logo nestled on the tongue and the heel.

Dive into the world where the past meets the present with this undeniable trendsetter. Released at a retail price of $120, the Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 is an investment in timeless style.

name: Cordura Preloved Brown
title: adidas Campus 00s Cordura Preloved Brown
description:
The adidas Campus 00s Cordura Preloved Brown is a contemporary reinterpretation of a timeless silhouette, featuring a pair of sneakers predominantly dressed in brown, with off-white accents highlighting the stripes.

The Cordura Preloved Brown adidas Campus 00s is characterized by a synthetic Cordura fabric base in a deep brown shade. This is offset by three bold, broken white leather stripes on the side panel, a signature element of the brand. The front of the silhouette and the heel tab are embellished with a leather design that alternates between shades of brown and gray. The shoe also features a Campus branding on the lateral side, a nod to this iteration. The rubber outsole ensures extra grip, instilling confidence with every step.

The most distinctive feature of the adidas Campus 00s Cordura Preloved Brown is the three bold broken white leather stripes on the side panel. This design detail adds a contrasting touch and is a hallmark of the adidas brand. The sneaker debuted for $110 on October 2nd, 2023.

name: White Fjord Grey
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 White Fjord Grey
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 White Fjord Grey is a premium running shoe that combines style and performance. Featuring a sleek white upper with fjord grey accents, this sneaker offers a clean and versatile look suitable for both athletic pursuits and casual wear. The Gel-Kayano 14 incorporates ASICS' renowned GEL technology in the heel and forefoot, providing superior shock absorption and cushioning for a comfortable stride.

Built with durability and support in mind, the Gel-Kayano 14 boasts a robust construction that caters to various foot types. The engineered mesh upper ensures breathability, while the reinforced heel counter promotes stability during movement. With its blend of cutting-edge technology and timeless design, this shoe is ideal for runners seeking a reliable and stylish option for their daily training or long-distance runs. Our experts state this product is great for athletes looking for a perfect balance of comfort, performance, and aesthetic appeal in their running footwear.

name: Dark Brown Preloved Yellow
title: adidas Samba OG Dark Brown Preloved Yellow
description:
The adidas Samba OG Dark Brown Preloved Yellow takes an iconic silhouette designed in 1949 and dresses it in a colorway that pops with contrast and catches the eye with its undeniable style.

The Dark Brown/Preloved Yellow/Gum colorway of the adidas Samba OG features a luxe upper with a base of tumbled Dark Brown leather with padding at the collar to enhance ankle comfort. Dark Brown suede forms a T-toe overlay to provide support and aesthetic elegance, while the eye stay overlay is crafted from the same tumbled leather as the base. Flat Dark Brown laces close over a Dark Brown leather tongue with gold branding, echoing the gold branding on the lateral heel. The gum rubber sole unit encapsulates cushioning foam and sports waves, grooves, and concentric circles in its traction pattern.

Our favorite aspect of this sneaker is the hits of goldenrod yellow leather that make the upper stand out. This leather forms the serrated side panel, three stripes, and the unbranded heel tab. The adidas Samba OG Dark Brown Preloved Yellow was released on December 1, 2023, for $100 retail.

name: Off White Clear Sky
title: adidas Gazelle Indoor Off White Clear Sky
description:
The adidas Gazelle Indoor Off White Clear Sky reimagines a classic design with a cheeky color palette. Blending vintage inspiration with modern detailing, this smart silhouette offers a fresh take on one of the classic adidas sports shoes.

The Off-White Clear Sky Gazelle Indoor by adidas combines a suede upper in a light off-white tone with contrasting blue accents on the 3-Stripes and heel tab. A translucent gum sole adds a retro touch while ensuring durability and traction. The Gazelle line was introduced in the 1960s and has evolved from its performance roots into a fashionable and versatile shoe, highlighting adidas' commitment to giving you functional footwear that looks good.

Something we, the experts, enjoy about the adidas Gazelle Indoor Off White Clear Sky is the translucent gum sole, which is long-lasting with a retro edge. Another key detail is the suede upper, which gives added texture and a premium finish. It retailed at $120 when it was released on 1st July 2024.

name: Clay
title: adidas Fear of God Athletics '86 Lo Clay
description:
As part of a partnership between adidas and Fear of God, the adidas Fear of God Athletics '86 Lo Clay combines the two labels’ house codes, creating a minimalist sneaker with a neutral colorway.

Drawing inspiration from the adidas Rivalry Low’s silhouette, designer Jerry Lorenzo kept some of the basketball shoe design elements. However, he also added a thick sole in Clay and crafted the upper using premium, tonal materials. For example, the upper boasts a premium-suede build, including the signature 3-Stripes logo, the eyelets, and the heel counter. Thin laces in Clay wind through the lace cage, while padding around the heel pays tribute to the Rivalry Low.

Our experts like the stark differences between the branding of adidas and Fear of God. For instance, the adidas trefoil is embossed into the heel, while " FEAR OF GOD" lettering appears on a dark rectangle on the midsole. The adidas Fear of God Athletics '86 Lo Clay was released on December 3, 2023, and sold for $200.
model: adidas Fear of God Athletics '86 Lo

name: Italy
title: adidas Gazelle Italy
description:
The adidas Gazelle Italy updates the classic Gazelle silhouette with details that celebrate Italy. It features a primarily Royal Blue colorway with accents in Off White.

Originally designed as a soccer shoe, the adidas Gazelle has earned a place in sports history, and the Italy iteration continues the legacy. The low-top sneaker boasts an upper crafted from premium suede in Royal Blue, including the T-shaped toebox overlay and the panels that form the lace cage. A traditional front lace closure secures the sneaker and houses crisp laces in Royal Blue. Leather accents in Off White can be found on the heel tab and the signature serrated 3-Stripes logo. In addition, the ITALIA branding printed on the suede tongue comes in Off White.

Our StockX experts like the bold GAZELLE lettering in Metallic Gold displayed along the side panel. The adidas Gazelle Italy was released on November 12, 2023, and retailed at $100.

name: Moonbeam Black Red
title: New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Black Red
description:
The New Balance CT 302 Moonbeam Black Red takes inspiration from the silhouette of the CT300 and reimagines it with an exaggerated design.

The New Balance CT 302 in a Moonbeam / Black / Team Red colorway features a moonbeam-colored lightweight mesh upper with tonal suede overlays. The heel tab and the exaggerated N branding covering the side panel are made of black tumbled leather, and the toe cap is cream-colored rubber. Moonbeam laces match the moonbeam padded collar, sock liner, and insole with team red CT302 branding. The stacked-height midsole is supported by a moonbeam rubber outsole with a traction pattern of wavy lines.

The feature our sports shoe experts appreciate most about this sneaker is the moonbeam tongue with exposed foam that sports a white tongue tag with red New Balance branding. The New Balance CT 302 Moonbeam Black Red was released on March 25, 2023 for an original retail price of $90.

name: Kith Black
title: New Balance 1906R Kith Black
description:
The New Balance 1906R Kith Black is a technical running shoe with a moody colorway of black, Bordeaux, and Champagne that is at once premium and performance-centric.

The upper features loose-weave mesh in black with thin, synthetic leather overlays in black and metallic Champagne. The use of mesh adds to the sneaker’s technical prowess by reducing the overall weight, while the addition of ACTEVA LITE cushioning in the midsole and the ABZORB SBS heel provides responsive cushioning and stabilization. Another noteworthy technical feature is the N-ergy outsole, which comes in black with splashes of Champagne on the arch. This outsole contributes to the sneaker’s technical silhouette while providing traction and grip.

Our StockX experts like the Bordeaux accents, including the laces that wind through the New Balance N logo on the side panel. The New Balance 1906R Kith Black was originally released on March 11, 2024, and retailed at $170.

name: MiUK JJJJound Grey Olive
title: New Balance 991 MiUK JJJJound Grey Olive
description:
JJJJound is making a return in 2023 with another New Balance collaboration, working for the first time with New Balances 991 MiUK silhouette.

New Balances 991 JJJJound Grey Olive was made in the United Kingdom and is constructed of a brown and grey premium suede and mesh upper. JJJJound branding sits on the sneakers heel and insole. The sneakers are dressed with cream laces, in addition to coming with extra black polyester laces.

The New Balance 991 MiUK JJJJound Grey Olive released February 9, 2023 with a retail price of $250.

name: Pink Corduroy (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Pink Corduroy (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Pink Corduroy (Women's) features the classic Dunk Low silhouette and showcases a predominantly pink colorway, with various shades and textures of pink ‘corduroy’ material.

The Pink Corduroy Nike Dunk Low for women features a white leather upper, contrasted by Pink Foam suede overlays that sport a textured finish reminiscent of corduroy. Nike's branding can be spotted on the woven tongue tag, the heel tab, and the sock liner. Providing the foundation for this sneaker is a rubber cup sole, which boasts stitched sidewall construction and an internal foam wedge, ensuring a blend of durability and lightweight cushioning. The shoe features a rubber outsole with a classic herringbone traction pattern, ensuring dependable grip.

What our experts love about the Nike Dunk Low Pink Corduroy (Women's) is its unique and eye-catching use of ‘corduroy’ material, adding both texture and personality to the classic Dunk silhouette. The sneaker was released on August 8th, 2023, for $110.

name: Core Black Gum
title: adidas Samba OG Core Black Gum
description:
The adidas Samba OG Core Black Gum adds an all-black colorway to the Samba silhouette, maintaining its classic design and heritage details.

Originally created for soccer players, the Core Black Gum adidas Samba OG boasts a smooth leather construction with suede accents on the toebox overlay. However, the main upper, the 3-Stripes logo, the eyelets, the tongue, and the heel mustache all come in Core Black leather. The Core Black laces thread through the eyelets and secure the front closure. The ‘SAMBA’ lettering in metallic gold and the blue Samba Originals tongue logo interrupt the black-on-black colorway. Finishing the look, the rubber outsole provides traction underfoot.

Our experts like that the 3-Stripes logo comes in tonal Core Black instead of a contrasting hue, because it contributes to the sleek design. The adidas Samba OG Core Black Gum was released on December 15, 2023, and sold for $100.

name: White Malachite Green Off White Midsole (Women's)
title: ASICS Gel-1130 White Malachite Green Off White Midsole (Women's)
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 White Malachite Green Off White Midsole (Women's) elevates the retro-inspired Gel-1130 with bright Malachite Green.

Although the White Malachite Green Off White Midsole (Women's) ASICS Gel-1130 draws inspiration from models in the GEL-1000 series, it offers modern upgrades and a contemporary colorway. Gel cushioning in the heel provides superior shock absorption, while the white mesh underlays and synthetic leather overlays maintain the sneaker’s design from 2008. In addition, the Trusstic support system in the midsole is borrowed from stability running shoes from the late 2000s. Splashes of Malachite Green can be found on the formstripe, the branding, and the segments on the heel, giving the sneaker a modern upgrade.

Our experts at StockX like the touch of metallic silver on the overlays and tongue because it contrasts the worn-in look provided by the Off White midsole. The women’s size ASICS Gel-1130 White Malachite Green Off White Midsole (Women's) was released on May 13, 2024, and sold for $95.

name: Central Cee Live Yours
title: Nike Air Max 95 Central Cee Live Yours
description:
The Nike Air Max 95 Central Cee Live Yours is a performance shoe equipped with Air Max technology, designed as part of a partnership with British rapper Central Cee.

The Central Cee Live Yours Nike Air Max 95 has an upper constructed with a breathable black mesh base up around the laces. The sides are supported by four layers of matte dark-gray leather that curve from the toe back to the heel, while the toe cap is also dark-gray leather. The Nike Swoosh appears on the lateral heel in Metallic Red Bronze, while a vertical strip is seen on the back of the heel in the same color. A Nike Air logo can be found on the heel collar, while an Air Max logo adorns the tongue. The black midsole contains Air Max units under the heel and forefoot.

What we think stands out about this shoe is the Metallic Red Bronze heel, which adds a nice pop of color to the otherwise dark shoe. The Nike Air Max 95 Central Cee Live Yours was released on October 24, 2024.

name: Cosmic Clay
title: Nike Dunk Low Retro Cosmic Clay
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Retro Cosmic Clay applies an orange inspired color combination to the Dunk Low Retro silhouette.

This Nike Dunk Low stays true to the iconic color blocking that the silhouette is known for when one main color is featured. This shoe has a clean white leather upper with perforations on the toe box for enhanced breathability. Cosmic clay then takes over and flows from the toe cap and forefoot, to the eyelet, and then wraps down around the heel. The signature flanks both sides, also in cosmic clay. A padded tongue, matching cosmic clay laces and outsole complete this lifestyle shoe’s design.

Our experts think the lightweight foam padding in the midsole adds comfort while absorbing impact. Combined with the heritage pivot circle on the outsole, your feet can handle whatever comes their way. When the Nike Dunk Low Retro Cosmic Clay was released on October 14, 2024, it retailed for $115.

name: Oreo
title: Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Oreo
description:
The Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Oreo is a performance-oriented footwear option with a distinctly futuristic aesthetic. The Oreo Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit introduces a fundamental two-tone color scheme to this lifestyle running shoe, which is equipped with a full-length Air cushioning system.

Classic laces ensure a secure fit for the black Flyknit upper, enhanced by striking white threads, and reinforced with robust synthetic overlays on the forefoot and heel. The inclusion of a flexible, sock-like collar ensures a comfortable and snug fit. A convenient webbing pull tab is positioned at the heel for easy on and off. The shoe's lightweight construction is complemented by a responsive Air-sole unit that extends along the entire length of the rubber outsole.

What our experts love about the Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Oreo is its futuristic design. This sneaker not only embraces cutting-edge performance technology but also exudes a sleek, modern look that's ahead of its time. The sneaker was released on the 18th May of 2023 for $210.

name: Cobblestone Flat Pewter (Women's)
title: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Cobblestone Flat Pewter (Women's)
description:
The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Cobblestone Flat Pewter W features a greyscale color palette with hints of sage green.

This shoe in women sizing showcases a durable sole with a tread pattern designed for traction and grip on various surfaces. The iconic Nike Swoosh logo is prominently featured on the sides of the shoe, adding a touch of sporty style. The tongue of the shoe is adorned with a Nike branding label, showcasing attention to detail and brand authenticity. The laces are included with the shoe and provide a secure and customizable fit, allowing you to adjust the tightness to your preference. The midsole of the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 offers responsive cushioning and shock absorption, providing a comfortable and supportive ride.

The shoe's plastic caging elements are a standout feature that our experts love. The caging wraps around the midfoot, offering a secure lockdown fit that reduces the chances of foot slippage during dynamic movements. The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Cobblestone Flat Pewter W was released on 14th December 2022 with a retail price of $160.

name: Calabasas Core Black
title: adidas Yeezy Powerphase Calabasas Core Black
description: The third colorway of the series, this adidas Yeezy Powerphase Calabasas features a monochromatic core black color palette. There is also Adidas branding in green next to a red Trefoil logo. This classic colorway released in March 2017 for $120.

name: Sketch and Exploration
title: Nike Dunk Low Sketch and Exploration
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Sketch and Exploration appears to have taken inspiration from fall foliage and the harvest season, as this colorway mixes rugged textures and natural colors to deliver a stylish shoe that will pair well with jeans, cords, and flannels.

The upper of this Dunk Low boasts natural and earthy tones. You’ll spot a tastefully balanced mix of burnt sunrise, sanddrift, celestial gold, thunder blue, wheat, and light crimson. Added to this are overlays made out of corduroy, leather, and suede. Altogether, the final result is a ten out of ten. Nike branding hits appear in the usual spots, namely the side panels, tongue, and heel.

Our experts think the edgy, almost eroded, burnt sunrise-colored Swooshes on the side panels imply that these shoes are meant for exploring and enjoying the great outdoors. When the Nike Dunk Low Sketch and Exploration was released on October 1, 2024, it retailed for $125.

name: Eclipse Raincloud
title: New Balance 2002R Eclipse Raincloud
description:
The New Balance 2002R Eclipse Raincloud updates the 2002R with a stormy colorway that mimics the sky’s color right before it rains or the darkness of an eclipse.

Featuring padding in the collar and tongue, this sneaker draws inspiration from the 2000s technical running shoes. However, its grayscale colorway and lack of metallic overlays give the sneaker a contemporary look. The base is crafted from tightly woven mesh in Eclipse, while the layered, pig-suede overlays come in Rain Cloud, Graphite, and light gray. Perforations along the leather side panels allow the foot to breathe, while the ACTEVA LITE foam and N-ergy technology absorb shock and provide cushioning. In addition, Stability Web technology stabilizes the foot and ankle.

Our StockX experts like the shiny "N" logo on the side panel, which adds a metallic detail to the otherwise matte sneaker. The New Balance 2002R Eclipse Raincloud was released on July 13, 2023, and sold for $140.

name: Paisley Pack Orange (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Essential Paisley Pack Orange (Women's)
description:
As part of the 2022 Nike Dunk Low Paisley Pack, the Nike Dunk Low Paisley Pack Orange features a white leather upper with orange leather overlays and paisley textile Swooshes. From there, a paisley heel tab, woven Nike tongue label, and matching Air sole complete the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Paisley Pack Orange released in May of 2022 and retailed for $120.

name: Championship Red (GS)
title: Nike Dunk Low Championship Red (GS)
description:
Dressed in a University Red, White, and Total Orange, this Nike Dunk Low University Red (GS) is available in grade school sizing. This Nike Dunk Low University Red (GS) features a University Red leather base with contrasting overlays in white. Matching white also lands on the signature Swoosh logo, laces, heels, tongue tags, and lining, while the red extends to the nylon tongues, tongue and heel branding, and insoles. The low top is rounded off with a solid white midsole and a crimson rubber outsole providing traction.

The Nike Dunk Low University Red (GS) was released in September 2021 and retailed for $100.

name: Wonder White Green Gum (Women's)
title: adidas Gazelle Wonder White Green Gum (Women's)
description:
The adidas Gazelle Wonder White Green Gum (Women's) adds a neutral colorway of Wonder White and Cream White with green accents to the classic Gazelle silhouette.

Paying tribute to its athletic roots, this version of the Gazelle retains several retro-design features sourced from the original 1991 sneaker. For example, it features a low-top design with the signature serrated 3-Stripes on the side panel and a pronounced heel tab. The upper and toebox overlay are crafted from velvety suede in Wonder White, while leather accents in Cream White can be found on the 3-Stripes. What makes this sneaker stand out is the use of silky satin in green on the heel tab. It adds a premium element to the sneaker and complements the green trefoil on the tongue.

Our StockX experts like the classic metallic gold "GAZELLE" lettering on the outer side panel. The women’s-size adidas Gazelle Wonder White Green Gum (Women's) was released on May 19, 2023, and sold for $100.

name: Black Clear
title: Nike SB PS8 Black Clear
description:
The Nike SB PS8 Black Clear is a skateboarding sneaker featuring an upper with textured leather at the heel, tip, lace panel and Nike Swoosh, grounded by mesh underneath. The upper is done in monochrome Black, accented by a Clear mid- and outsole, which displays hints of blue and orange from within. Additional Nike branding appears on the tongue and rear heel.

American athletic shoe brand Nike created its skateboarding offshoot Nike SB in 2002, which sought to better understand the landscape of skateboarders’ needs and culture. The PS8’s name originates from Problem Solver 8, an alias of Sandy Bodecker, who was on the original launch team of Nike SB in 2002 and passed away in 2018. The PS8's hefty midsole and leather offer rugged durability for street skating.

In our opinion, the best feature of the PS8 is its Clear sole, which looks fresh and adds crucial functionality. The Nike SB PS8 Black Clear released on August 8, 2024, and retailed for $120.

name: Black White Gum
title: Nike Dunk Low Pro SB Black White Gum
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Pro SB Black White Gum is a sleek and stylish addition to the iconic SB Dunk line. Featuring a classic color combination, this shoe boasts a black leather upper with contrasting white accents on the Swoosh, heel tab, and midsole. The gum rubber outsole adds a touch of warmth and provides excellent traction, making it perfect for skateboarding or casual wear.

Designed with both style and functionality in mind, the Nike Dunk Low Pro SB incorporates premium materials and advanced cushioning technology. The padded collar and tongue offer enhanced comfort and support, while the Zoom Air unit in the heel delivers responsive cushioning. The durable construction ensures long-lasting wear, whether you're hitting the skate park or navigating city streets. Us at StockX believe this product is great for skaters and sneaker enthusiasts alike, offering a versatile and timeless design that can elevate any outfit.

name: Mesh Black Metallic
title: New Balance 2002R Mesh Black Metallic
description:
The New Balance 2002R Mesh Black Metallic is a low-top sneaker boasting a black and metallic color scheme from the Boston footwear and athletic apparel brand.

Dressed in a monochromatic black, this shoe has a modern and vintage aesthetic going on at the same time. The upper is made out of black breathable mesh with black leather overlays where reinforcement is usually needed. Namely, the toe cap, side panels, eyelet, mudguard area, and the whole back heel panel. It is packed with New Balance innovations such as the ABZORB insole, an N-Durance rubber compound under the heel, and an N-Ergy outsole Branding hits are seen at the heel tab, tongue, side panels and toe tip.

Our experts think that the minimalistic color scheme, the tonal all over black with metallic accents, is what makes this stylish New Balance 2002R Mesh Black Metallic stand out. It hit the shelves on September 1, 2024, with a recommended price of $150.

name: Turtledove White
title: New Balance 550 Turtledove White
description:
The New Balance 550 Turtledove White is a sneaker with a design that pays homage to the original design, which debuted in the 80s and was inspired by basketball culture.

This iteration of the New Balance 550 features a paneled off-white upper made entirely of calf leather. Both the toebox and the side panels feature perforations for extra breathability. The New Balance N Motif graces the sides in white outlined in perforation detailing, while 550 branding appears on the lateral side panel under the laces. The heel counter contains an NB logo, while the heel collar appears in white. The cushioned tongue also contains a New Balance logo patch. The off-white rubber sole is also layered and contains the NB logo and the New Balance brand name on the lateral side. The outsole is a light gray color.

Our favorite feature of these sneakers is the perforated detailing present on the entire upper. It gives the shoe extra visual appeal, while also increasing the functionality. The New Balance 550 Turtledove White was released on July 7, 2023, for a price of $120.

name: Preloved Brown
title: adidas Samba OG Luxe Preloved Brown
description:
The adidas Samba OG Luxe Preloved Brown takes inspiration from the original 1949 Samba design and adds a vintage street style.

The Preloved Brown colorway of the Luxe adidas Samba OG features an upper of rich brown suede with padding at the collar for enhanced comfort. Brown suede overlays adorn the eyestays and the toebox in a T-toe formation. Cream-colored leather is used to craft both the heel tab and the iconic side-panel three stripes. The brown laces and brown textile sock liner, along with the brown suede tongue, complete the look of this elegant upper. The brown rubber outsole features undulating grooves and concentric circles in order to provide traction and shock absorption, and this rubber runs up the sidewalls, as well.

The aspect of this distinctive shoe that we appreciate the most are the hits of a lighter brown on the upper. Light brown edging graces the right side of each of the three stripes and matches the adidas tongue tag with trefoil branding. The adidas samba OG Luxe Preloved Brown was released on January 12, 2024, for $150 retail.

name: Metallic Copper
title: Nike Air Max 90 Metallic Copper
description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Metallic Copper boasts a 90s aesthetic from heel to toe thanks to the various textured overlays and retro design.

Giving the iconic Air Max line a fashion forward lift, this fun silhouette debuts with a metallic copper, dark russet, and black color scheme. The color blocking seamlessly blends iridescent hues with black solid accents. Metallic copper flows from the toe cap, to the forefoot and quarter overlays and is seen on the back heel as well as in the liner with the printed branding. A hit of dark russet is seen on the eyelet, as well the Nike patch on the tongue. A visible Air unit in the heel completes this sneaker.

We think that the Nike Air Max 90 Metallic Copper’s standout feature has to be how the iridescent upper’s colors will change dependent upon the light source and angles. When it was released to the public on October 31, 2024, this sneaker’s price tag was $140.

name: Hyper Pink Laser Orange (Women's)
title: Nike ZoomX Vaporfly 3 Hyper Pink Laser Orange (Women's)
description:
The Nike ZoomX Vaporfly 3 Hyper Pink Laser Orange (Women's) takes a distinctive racing silhouette, dresses it in an eye-catching gradient colorway, and sizes it for women.

The Women's Nike ZoomX Vaporfly 3 in a Hyper Pink/Laser Orange/Black colorway features an upper of lightweight Flyknit yarns in pink that transition to orange around the mudguard. Offset pink laces for foot stability begin in the center of the shoe at the top of the pink tongue, but then lean toward the outside for a unique look. Hits of black come in the side-panel Nike Swoosh, a mini-Swoosh on the bottom of the eyestays, and branding on the tongue and insole.

What we enjoy most about this racer is the tech underfoot. A carbon plate provides stability, while a thick midsole made of ZoomX for cushioning, as well as springy energy return, extends beyond the heel to provide stability with every stride. The outsole has been designed with a reduced amount of rubber to make each step even lighter. The Nike ZoomX Vaporfly 3 Hyper Pink Laser Orange (Women's) was released on April 1, 2023, for $250 retail.

name: White Incense Driftwood
title: New Balance 550 White Incense Driftwood
description:
The New Balance 550 White Incense Driftwood dresses an iconic basketball silhouette in a subtle colorway. Originally launched in 1989, the 550 has been reimagined with a design that streamlines the '80s features yet retains its classic look.

The White Incense Driftwood iteration of the New Balance 550 features an upper with a base of white suede. This is overlaid with undulating layers of perforated white suede, smooth white leather, light tan suede, and a darker tan suede. The collar is composed of breathable tan mesh that matches the sock liner and the lining of the white mesh tongue. The sail-colored foam midsole rests on a darker tan rubber outsole that has circles and grooves for multidirectional traction.

What we enjoy most about this sneaker are the various hits of New Balance branding, including the tan NB on the white leather heel, a darker tan suede N in a cut-out window, and 550 embroidered near the bottom of the lateral laces. New Balance branding is also embroidered on the tongue tag and embossed on the midsole. The New Balance 550 White Incense Driftwood was released on August 23, 2023, for $120 retail.

name: Slim Reaper
title: Nike KD 16 Slim Reaper
description:
The Nike KD 16 Slim Reaper is a bold and daring colorway in the Nike KD 16 model, which is part of Kevin Durant’s signature shoe line.

The Nike KD line is known for its durability and excellent fit. This is a special colorway named the "Slim Reaper" which is a moniker used for Kevin Durant and his playing style. Black is the base color of the upper on this basketball sneaker seen on the tongue, throat, side panels, medial side panel, toe cap, and mudguard. The toe box area and heel collar overlay take center stage with a bright crimson pattern that can be likened to tiger stripes. A thunder blue outsole completes the shoe.

What would we say is the standout feature of the Nike KD 16 Slim Reaper colorway? Why the sleek metallic silver branding such as the Nike Swooshes and the Slim Reaper heel emblem on the heel counter. Originally released on March 1, 2023, it retailed for $160.

name: Off Noir Smoke Grey
title: Nike Dunk Low Retro SE Off Noir Smoke Grey
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Retro SE Off Noir Smoke Grey is a sleek and stylish addition to the iconic Dunk lineup. This men's sneaker features a sophisticated color palette, combining off-noir, smoke grey, anthracite, and black hues for a versatile and modern look. The upper is crafted with premium materials, showcasing Nike's commitment to quality and durability. The low-top silhouette offers both comfort and flexibility, making it an ideal choice for everyday wear.

Designed with both style and functionality in mind, this Dunk Low Retro SE boasts the classic features that have made the Dunk a fan favorite. The padded collar and tongue provide enhanced comfort, while the perforated toe box ensures breathability. The signature Swoosh adorns the sides, adding a touch of brand recognition to the understated colorway. The rubber outsole offers excellent traction and durability, making these sneakers suitable for various surfaces and activities. Us at StockX believe this product is great for those seeking a versatile, stylish sneaker that seamlessly blends classic design with contemporary colorways.

name: Black White
title: Nike ZoomX Invincible Run 3 Black White
description:
The Nike ZoomX Invincible Run 3 Black White is part of the Nike ZoomX Invincible Run 3 lineup of running shoes. Although the colorway is Black, White, Dark Grey, and Coconut Milk, the Invincible Run 3 Black White presents as a dual-tone black and white sneaker.

This sneaker stands out from others due to the amount of cushioning underfoot. ZoomX foam cushioning in the midsole conforms to the foot shape and added foam height provides a soft underfoot feel. The lightweight Flyknit upper is both breathable and durable. In terms of branding, a Swoosh made of stripes graces the side panel, another Swoosh covers the vamp, and lettering along the heel spells out ‘NIKE INVINCIBLE RUN 3’. In addition, the midsole features an orange rectangle with Nike ZoomX foam branding.

What do our StockX experts love about this sneaker? It is comparatively light weighing approximately 310 grams. The Nike ZoomX Invincible Run 3 Black White was released on January 5, 2023, and retailed at $180.

DISCLAIMER: There are two different variations of text shown on the heel of the Nike ZoomX Invincible Run 3 Black White (DR2615-001). The "Nike Invincible Run 3" text, as shown, as well as "Nike ZoomX" text variations are both passable under this product page.

name: Kyanite
title: adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Kyanite
description:
In a similar fashion to their 2020’s Azareth release, adidas and Yeezy bring back the favored blue design with the 700 V3 Kyanite in 2021.

The adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Kyanite features familiar qualities that fans of the 700 V3 will appreciate. The upper is composed of Primeknit material that is enshrined in a glow-in-the-dark TPU cage. From there, a cream-colored EVA foam midsole adds a tonal element to the sneaker’s design. Lastly, a herringbone-patterned outsole provides traction for the wearer while stepping out on the street.

The adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Kyanite released in March 2021 for $200.

name: Semi Frozen Yellow
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Semi Frozen Yellow
description: The Semi Frozen Yellow adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 was rumored as early as May of 2017-some blogs even claimed they would be mostly glow-in-the-dark-but it was when photos of Kanye West wearing them first surfaced on the web later in the year that confirmed the release. This colorway steps outside of the comfort zone of previous 350 Yeezy sneaker releases, which have remained subtle and mostly neutral primary colors and bright accents.  The official colorway of the 'Frozen Yellow Yeezys' is actually Semi Frozen Yellow, Raw Steel and Red and features both of adidas pinnacle technologies, Boost cushioning and Primeknit sock-like upper. The hype for the yellow colored Yeezys was pushed to the roof before launch as Kanye West appeared with Kid Cudi and Takashi Murakami as 'Ye and Cudi toured the iconic artist's studio on a trip to Tokyo. In addition, the rumors throughout the sneaker world suggested the Frozen Yellow Yeezy would be an extremely hard to get release. As expected, the Semi Frozen Yellow was announced officially on November 13th, 2017 and released in limited quantities on November 18th, 2017. Sizes of the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Semi Frozen Yellow are available now.

name: USA Night Indigo
title: adidas AE 1 Low USA Night Indigo
description:
The adidas AE 1 Low USA Night Indigo is the premiere signature shoe of NBA star and Olympic gold medal winner Anthony Edwards.

This high-octane basketball sneaker builds upon an upper base of indigo blue breathable, lightweight mesh. The side panels are enclosed in a tonal TPU cage with honeycomb venting that reveals red mesh underneath. The toecap is reinforced with red TPU, while the heel is bolstered with translucent TPU that sports the iconic adidas 3-Stripes in white. The side-panel cage extends all the way down to the midsole, where it encloses LightStrike foam in the forefoot and Boost cushioning in the rear foot. This sneaker rides on a rubber indigo outsole with an enlarged herringbone traction pattern vented for midsole expansion and flexibility.

The detail on this sneaker that we enjoy the most is the Anthony Edwards logo in white that hits the tongue pull loop. This subtle note of branding exudes class and style. The adidas AE 1 Low USA Night Indigo was released on August 15, 2024, for $110 retail.

name: Smoke Grey
title: ASICS Gel-NYC Smoke Grey
description:
Taking upper inspiration from the GEL-NIMBUS 3 and the GEL-MC PLUS V, and getting tooling inspiration from the GEL-CUMULUS 16, the ASICS Gel-NYC Smoke Gray offers a high performance running shoe with retro aesthetics.

The Smoke Gray ASICS Gel-NYC built for comfort starts with a base of Smoke Gray mesh that offers lightweight breathability. Smoke Gray leather winds its way all over the upper, and is itself overlaid by cream-colored leather and cream-colored suede at both the mudguard and eyestays. Cream-colored laces help ensure a snug closure over the mesh tongue. Cream-colored undulating foam forms the cushioning midsole that features shiny gray GEL inserts in both the forefoot and heel for ultimate cushioning. This sneaker rides on an outsole created from gray rubber pods situated between deep grooves that offer flexibility.

Our favorite detail on this pair of kicks is the addition of light blue hits on the upper. Light blue suede forms the heel tab and peeks out at the edges of the tongue for a subtle note of whimsy. The ASICS Gel-NYC Smoke Gray was released on April 1, 2024, for a retail price of $130.

name: Pure Platinum Court Blue
title: Nike Air Max Plus Pure Platinum Court Blue
description:
The next-generation Nike Air Max Plus Pure Platinum Court Blue continues the evolution of this game-changing trainer model. It delivers even more cushioned comfort, athletic performance and supportive stability than before.

The throwback '90s design is still there. The mesh platinum panels are streaked with black detailing, and the soles have clear cut-outs to reveal the now-legendary Nike Air Max cushioning technology. This contoured style folds around the foot to provide a reassuringly snug fit. A breathable synthetic upper is melded to an extremely durable rubber outsole.

We've always been fans of Air Max technology, and this trainer uses it to optimal effect by placing these capsules in both the heels and forefeet. The foam midsoles add extra comfort, and provide good arch support. From the outside, they look the part too, with a sleek and sporty profile. This is accentuated by a shiny black toe cap that wouldn't look out of place on a space boot. It's a highly appealing aesthetic. The Nike Air Max Plus Pure Platinum Court Blue was released on 23 April 2024, retailed at $180.

name: Year of the Dragon (2024)
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 Year of the Dragon (2024)
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 Year of the Dragon (2024) is a premium sneaker that features elaborate embroidery and dragon imagery.

This low-top sneaker celebrates the Chinese Lunar New Year and the Year of the Dragon through color and design. An embroidered dragon made of metallic silver and gold threat graces the left shoe, while a phoenix can be found on the right shoe. The phoenix symbolizes harmony, and the use of gold represents prosperity and happiness. Other symbolic elements include the Chinese character on the heel and the design on the tongue. The base is made of a cream-colored textile that resembles jacquard fabric and displays flower motifs.

Our StockX experts like the way the textile extends over the midsole, allowing the jacquard-like fabric to cover the shoe. The Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 Year of the Dragon (2024) was launched on February 14th, 2024, and retailed at $365.

name: MiUSA Joe Freshgoods Prom Blue
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods Prom Blue
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods Prom Blue is an athletic shoe with an overlaid leather, suede, and mesh upper in monochrome Blue, accented by coordinating laces and the New Balance N logo on the side. New Balance and Joe Freshgoods branding appears on the tongue and rear heel, while a 990.6 branded lace charm accents the lace panel. The monochrome Blue carved mid- and outsole complete the aesthetic.

Massachusetts-based New Balance’s heritage dates to 1906, and the brand has long been identified with their classic, performance-driven silhouettes. Joe Freshgoods is a Chicago-based lifestyle and clothing boutique. For a limited edition 990v6 MiUSA designed for Joe Freshgoods, New Balance shouted out the retailer with the Made for Us message imprinted on the rear heel.

Our experts feel that the best feature of the 990v6 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods is its tonal Blue color story, which stands out from typical New Balance colorways. The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods Prom Blue released on July 27, 2024, and retailed for $220.

name: Static Black (Reflective)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Static Black (Reflective)
description: Light up in the sky while rocking a pair of the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Static Black Reflective. This Yeezy Boost 350 V2 comes with a black upper plus reflective accents, black midsole, and a black sole. These sneakers released in June 2019 and retailed for $220. Grab these fire Yeezys on StockX today.

name: Midas Gold
title: Nike Dunk Low Midas Gold
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Midas Gold features a Midas Gold leather upper with Tough Red overlays and Swooshes. From there, matching woven tongue tags and soles complete the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Midas Gold released in October of 2021 and retailed for $100.

name: Mirage V2 (White Outsole)
title: Nike Book 1 EP Mirage V2 (White Outsole)
description:
The Nike Book 1 EP Mirage V2 (White Outsole) is NBA player Devin Booker’s first signature shoe with Nike and the Nike Book 1 EP’s second colorway. This sneaker boasts a grayscale colorway with Ashen Slate, Light Carbon, Football Grey, and Summit White base notes and accents in Safety Orange.

However, the outsole, which comes in midsole-matching Summit White instead of a semi-translucent hue, sets this sneaker apart from other Book 1 EP modes. The upper is crafted from velvety suede and a soft knit material in Ashen Slate, while a tonal Swoosh runs across the side panel. The collar also comes in Light Carbon suede and boasts a series of small perforations. Safety Orange details can be found in the BOOK lettering on the tongue tag and on the insole.

Our StockX experts like the layered heel pull tag, which displays ’96, Booker’s birth year. The Nike Book 1 EP Mirage V2 (White Outsole) was launched on February 29, 2024, and sold for $140.

name: Hemp Coconut Milk
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low LV8 EMB Hemp Coconut Milk
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low LV8 EMB Hemp Coconut Milk applies an earthy colorway of Coconut Milk, Sesame, and Hemp with Baroque Brown accents to the Air Force 1 Low’s signature silhouette.

This low-top sneaker integrates elements from the Nike Air Force 1 ’07, while updating the sneaker with a modern colorway and premium materials. For example, light padding around the collar gives the sneaker a slightly boxy appearance without emulating a skateboarding shoe from the early 2000s. The underlays are made of premium leather in Hemp, while the overlays are crafted from soft suede in Sesame. Something that makes this sneaker stand out is the Baroque Brown hue on the toebox, which matches the leather heel tab and collar lining. The Coconut Milk midsole rests on the Baroque Brown outsole, creating a layered effect.

Our StockX experts like the use of corduroy on the tongue. It gives the sneaker a premium feel. The Nike Air Force 1 Low LV8 EMB Hemp Coconut Milk was released on September 21st, 2023, and retailed at $135.
model: Nike Air Force 1 Low LV8 EMB

name: Midnight Navy Gum
title: Nike Air Max 90 Midnight Navy Gum
description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Midnight Navy Gum is built on an iconic silhouette that has been delighting people around the world for over three decades. This iteration is heritage and its details and fresh in its colorway.

The upper of this sneaker is crafted from tightly woven black mesh with a padded collar to enhance comfort. The tongue is navy-blue mesh, offering subtle contrast. Black leather forms the mud guard, while navy blue leather forms an overlay that stretches from the toe cap to the collar. Navy blue TPU overlays hit the side panel with Air Max branding, the eyestays, and the heel with Nike Air branding. The black tongue tag also sports white Nike Air branding. Besides the panel, Nike swoosh and flat laces are also white. This upper rides on a white foam midsole that houses a visible Air cassette surrounded by a navy blue TPU window.

What we most appreciate is the gum rubber outsole with its vintage waffle traction pattern. This outsole locks in the old-school, time-honored, legendary aspect of this silhouette. The Nike Air Max 90 Midnight Navy Gum debuted on December 27, 2023, for $130 retail.

name: AMBUSH Black
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low SP AMBUSH Black
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low SP AMBUSH Black is a sneaker by Nike designed by Yoon Ahn.
​
​This Low Nike Air Force 1 has an all-leather upper in black. It came as a result of a collaboration between Nike Air Force 1 and the Japanese label, AMBUSH. On the sides there is an exaggerated Nike Swoosh and the tongue that is black, features as well a Nike Swoosh and the word AMBUSH underneath in white to contrast. The sneaker has co-branded metallic lace dubraes and for cushioning, the AF1's chunky Air midsole.
​
​The Nike Air Force 1 Low SP AMBUSH Black was released on 28th February 2023 with its retail price set at $190.

name: All-Star
title: Nike Kyrie 8 All-Star
description:
The Nike Kyrie 8 All-Star is a shoe designed as a collaboration with American basketball star Kyrie Irving, which was released for All-Star Weekend.
   
The All-Star Nike Kyrie 8 has a multicolored breathable and flexible fabric upper. The top of the upper gets the multicolor treatment, featuring shades of pink, black, and gray. The mudguard, wrapping around the entire bottom of the shoe, is a solid Pink Foam color. A large multicolored Nike Swoosh outlined in gold appears under the lateral ankle, while under the inner ankle a small white Swoosh can be found. Irving’s branding can be found in orange stitching on the inner side of the heel, and the tongue also contains his logo. The shoe sits on a thick textured off-white midsole with Zoom Air cushioning and an off-white outsole.

The most interesting feature of this shoe is the multicolored Swoosh on the lateral side, which is eye-catching against the colors of the rest of the design. The Nike Kyrie 8 All-Star was released on November 1, 2022, for $140.

name: Black Anthracite
title: Nike Free RN 2018 Black Anthracite
description:
The Nike Free Rn 2018 Black Anthracite was released in auxetic shapes to allow natural foot splaying while also providing balanced cushioning underfoot. The black/anthracite colorway is updated to deliver a more adaptive fit than before.

The release features a circular-knit upper with spandex, a dynamic heel system, and a Tri-Star outsole pattern to give you a natural movement. The Nike Free Rn 2018 Black Anthracite achieves durability and comfort from its co-molded midsole with softer injected Phylon (IP), slightly firmer injected unit sole, and core foam direct underfoot that also delivers a smooth ride.

The Nike Free Rn 2018 Black Anthracite was released at a retail price of $100 on February 16, 2018.

name: White Clay Grey
title: ASICS Gel-1130 White Clay Grey
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 White Clay Grey, the 9th installment of the GEL-1000 series, is an updated stability running shoe originally launched in 2008.

The White Clay Grey colorway of the ASICS Gel-1130 features an upper of breathable and lightweight white mesh. Synthetic leather strips in shades of gray and tan course across the upper, contributing to the distinctive ASICS style and adding structural support to the shoe. White rope laces crisscross over a white mesh tongue that sports gray ASICS branding. A gray mesh dope-dyed padded sock liner surrounds a brownish-gray mesh insole that features white ASICS branding.

What we enjoy most about this retro-looking running shoe is its high-performance sole. A thick, sail-colored foam midsole houses GEL technology for supreme cushioning and ultimate shock absorption. The TRUSSIC support system adds stability, while the rubber outsole in gray and tan offers grip with every stride. The ASICS Gel-1130 White Clay Grey was released on March 15, 2023, for $95 retail.

name: White Black
title: Nike Court Air Zoom Vapor Pro HC White Black
description:
The Nike Court Air Zoom Vapor Pro HC White Black is an athletic shoe featuring a White mesh upper, accented by the Nike Swoosh in Black alongside Vapor Pro branding and Nike branding on the tongue. The Zoom foam midsole features clear detailing on the upper, grounded by a White outsole imprinted with Zoom branding.

American sportswear brand Nike is dedicated to crafting the ideal athletic shoes for numerous sports, and tennis is no exception. The Court Air Zoom Vapor Pro HC features a low silhouette, and its designers removed all unnecessary rubber for extreme lightness. The style features a Zoom Air unit in the forefront for added cushioning, all in service to the needs of tennis players.

In our opinion, the best feature of the Court Air Zoom is its stylized midsole, which adds interest to its minimal, lightweight design. The Nike Court Air Zoom Vapor Pro HC White Black released on April 8, 2021, and retailed for $120.
model: Nike Court Air Zoom Vapor Pro HC

name: White
title: Nike Air Force 1 High White
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 High White is a high-top version of the iconic Nike Air Force 1. Like the original 1980s Nike Air Force, this shoe features an all-white color scheme. Its white leather upper is made out of tumbled leather, and its outsole is constructed from rubber. To boost its breathability, the Nike Air Force 1 High White features a toe box that’s punctured, and to improve its flexibility, it offers ankle support.

The Nike Air Force 1 High White was released on 23rd May 2014. At the time, it had a retail price of $100.

name: Wonder Gold Metallic (Women's)
title: adidas Samba OG Wonder Gold Metallic (Women's)
description:
The adidas Samba OG Wonder Gold Metallic (Women's) blends retro charm with modern design in an eye-catching metallic gold tinge on the strips and heel. As part of adidas' classic Samba line, this women’s iteration shows off a bold look while staying true to the old-school heritage.

The Wonder Gold Metallic Samba OG (Women's) by adidas features a metallic gold leather upper, paired with tonal gold accents and white leather overlays for contrast. The serrated three-stripe detailing and a classic adidas tongue logo show the iconic roots of the original shoe. A gum rubber sole completes the look. The Samba silhouette has evolved into a globally recognized sneaker icon since it was first introduced in the 1950s.

What we love about the adidas Samba OG Wonder Gold Metallic (Women's) is its premium metallic white and gold leather upper, which adds a modern twist to the vintage silhouette, and the timeless and typical gum outsole. Released on 1st May 2024, the shoe debuted at a retail price of $120.

name: Light Bone Armory Blue (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Light Bone Armory Blue (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Light Bone Armory Blue (Women's) is a shoe in women’s sizing with a low top and a basketball-style influence.

This version of the Nike Dunk Low is made with a soft leather upper with a base of white. This color forms the perforated toe box, the side panels, and the ankle collar. Leather overlays in Light Bone round out the toe, form the eyestays, and make the ankle strap which runs down around the bottom of the heel. Light Armory Blue leather forms the Nike swoosh on each side as well as the heel collar, which features the Nike brand name in Light Bone. A logo patch appears on the tongue, and the shoe sits on a white midsole and Light Bone outsole. 

What we love most about this sneaker is the light colorway, which will go well with any outfit. The Nike Dunk Low Light Bone Armory Blue (Women's) was released on January 23, 2024, for a retail price of $120.

name: Blacktop Phantom
title: New Balance 1906L Blacktop Phantom
description:
The New Balance 1906L Blacktop Phantom is a striking addition to the brand's lifestyle sneaker lineup. This sleek and modern design showcases a predominantly black colorway, accented with subtle phantom hues for a sophisticated look. The upper features a blend of premium materials, including breathable mesh and durable synthetic overlays, ensuring both style and functionality. The shoe's streamlined silhouette is complemented by New Balance's signature craftsmanship, offering a perfect balance of comfort and aesthetics.

Engineered for all-day wear, the 1906L Blacktop Phantom incorporates New Balance's innovative cushioning technology in the midsole, providing exceptional support and responsiveness with every step. The outsole features a carefully designed tread pattern, offering reliable traction on various surfaces. With its versatile design, this sneaker effortlessly transitions from casual outings to more active pursuits, making it a valuable addition to any footwear collection. Our experts state this product is great for urban explorers and style enthusiasts who appreciate a blend of performance and contemporary fashion.

name: Phantom Gold Suede (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Phantom Gold Suede (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Light Curry (Women) is a variant of the Nike’s Dunk Low series.
​
The upper of Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Light Curry is made from recycled polyester, white in color, with brownish orange overlays on the ankle collar and the tongue. The pull tap and the laces are as well brownish orange. These rest on an all-white rubber midsole. The outsole of Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Light Curry is all-brown and the midsole is white.
​
The Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Light Curry was first released on March 29, 2022, at a price of $110.

name: Sanddrift (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Twist Sanddrift (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Twist Sanddrift (Women's) takes the Nike Dunk Low Twist silhouette and applies a neutral colorway of Coconut Milk, Pink Oxford, Sanddrift, and Sail.

Like other Nike Dunk Low Twist models, the "Sanddrift" variation features color-blocking across the leather upper. However, the color-blocking is subtle, featuring a contrast between Sanddrift and Coconut Milk. This retro sneaker finds inspiration in basketball shoes from the 1980s and includes a variety of throwback elements. For example, it boasts a pillowy silhouette, a padded collar, and a thin tongue design. A foam midsole provides responsive cushioning underfoot, while Nike's hoops pivot traction designs on the rubber outsole provide grip.

Our StockX experts like that the leather on the upper is designed to develop a worn-in appearance over time. The women’s size Nike Dunk Low Twist Sanddrift (Women's) was released on October 3rd, 2023, and retailed at $125.

name: White Black
title: adidas adiFOM Superstar White Black
description:
The adidas adiFOM Superstar White Black comes in a Core White and Core Black color scheme.

The White Black adidas adiFOM Superstar has an upper that is crafted from leather material for durability. The shoe features adiFOM cushioning technology in the midsole, which offers responsive cushioning and impact absorption. In addition, the shoe features an outsole made of a rubber compound, providing stability and grip. The shoe displays the signature 3-Stripes branding on the lateral sides.

The standout feature of the adidas adiFOM Superstar in White Black is its iconic design that blends timeless style with modern comfort. The shoe's leather upper offers durability and a sleek look, while the rubber shell toe adds a classic touch. With its clean white and black colorway, the adidas adiFOM Superstar is a versatile and fashionable choice. The adidas adiFOM Superstar White Black was released on December 14th, 2022, and sold for a retail price of $110.

name: White Varsity Red
title: Nike Field General '82 SP White Varsity Red
description:
The Nike Field General 82 SP White Varsity Red offers a sneaker built upon a vintage silhouette, a 1980s football training sneaker favored by many NFL players.

This Special Project low-top sneaker features an upper base of white textiles with a collar padded for comfort. Tonal leather overlays adorn the toe cap, eyestays, and midfoot for forefoot support, while a tonal leather overlay at the heel helps enhance stability. White laces criss-cross over a white tongue that sports a woven tongue tag with red Nike branding. The red leather heel tab has white embroidered Nike branding and matches the red leather Nike side-panel swoosh. The black rubber outsole features small, deep lugs ideal for traction on the gridiron.

Our favorite aspect of this sneaker is the foam midsole, in an atypical black finish. The sidewalls sport a textured pattern, another singular touch. The Nike Field General 82 SP White Varsity Red originally debuted on February 29, 2024, for a retail price of $100.

name: Silver Pack Pink (Women's)
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Silver Pack Pink (Women's)
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 Silver Pack Pink (Women's) is a shoe in women’s sizing equipped with Gel technology and a subtle colorway.
  
The Silver Pack Pink (Women's) ASICS Gel-1130 has an upper made of Cream mesh for breathability and flexibility. Polyurethane overlays in silver accented with a soft pink color cross the upper, forming the toe cap, crossing the sides in the classic ASICS design, and supporting the heel in off-kilter curves. Gel branding is also seen on the heel overlay, while ASICS Gel-1130 branding is found on the tongue. Pink gel supports the shoe within the Cream midsole, and soft pink rubber forms the outsole.

What we love most about this particular sneaker is the pink colorway, which is subtle and soft, adding a hint of elegance. The ASICS Gel-1130 Silver Pack Pink (Women's) was originally released on May 16, 2024, for an initial price of $95.

name: Bright Blue
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Bright Blue
description:
Yeezy continued its streak of vibrant colorways in 2021 with the adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Bright Blue. This release was the second 700 model to ditch the brand’s signature muted earth tones for eye-catching saturated hues.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Bright Blue features a Bright Blue leather, suede, and mesh upper with black suede overlays on the vamp and quarter. Like the Yeezy 700 Sun that released earlier this year, turquoise and teal mesh panels on the toe add contrast to surrounding suede panels. Reflective detailing on the heel panel, a bright orange Boost midsole, and a black outsole complete this Yeezy 700 colorway.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Bright Blue released in April of 2021 and retailed for $240.

name: Toronto
title: Nike Air Max 95 Toronto
description:
An iconic design among sneakers, the Nike Air Max 95 Toronto offers comfort in a highly responsive shoe that adjusts to your stride to give you the ultimate performance on the running track or in your daily life.

Step with ease, confidence, and comfort with one of Nike’s most responsive shoes yet – the classic Air Max 95. Squishy, bouncy, and durable, the Air Max is known for next-level cushioning. Breathable fabrics in the Toronto range boast colors such as black and white on the upper, silver and white, and a red-to-blue gradient on the sides. The responsive laces come with flecks of grey, and the rubberized toe panel protects your foot during tough games. The Air Max logo sits on the tongue, while the Swoosh is embroidered red on the back panel.

Looking to propel your game forward? Discover the premium look of the Nike Air Max and add swag to your game and your leisure wardrobe, a thing our team loves. The Nike Air Max 95 Toronto was released on 31 August 2024, priced at $185.

name: Billie Eilish Mushroom
title: Nike Air Force 1 High '07 SP Billie Eilish Mushroom
description:
Coming fresh off of Earth Day, Billie Eilish added an eco-friendly twist to one of Nike's most storied models with the Nike Air Force 1 Billie Eilish Mushroom.

With a recycled Durabuck upper and Nike Grind midsole, the Nike Air Force 1 Billie Eilish Mushroom takes a more sustainable approach to achieve a high-end look. Its monotone Mushroom palette emphasizes its unique, chunky mid-foot straps that borrow from both the Alpha Force Low and Air Trainer 3 designs. From there, a classic Nike Air heel embroidery completes this collaboration.

The Nike Air Force 1 Billie Eilish Mushroom released in April of 2022 and retailed for $170.

name: Pearl Pink Paw Print (Women's)
title: Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX Pearl Pink Paw Print (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX Pearl Pink Paw Print (Women's), in women’s sizes, is a low top athletic shoe featuring a White upper with Pearl Pink overlays at the lace panel, heel, and tip. The Nike Swoosh is done in Playful Pink with a raised texture. The tongue features Nike Air branding set within a raised paw print, accented by Nike Air branding on the White midsole and rear. The Pink Foam outsole completes the aesthetic.

First debuting in 1982, the Nike Air Force 1 is a timeless classic in the world of basketball sneaker design. Retaining its popularity since its release, Nike has utilized the Air Force 1 as a canvas for numerous improvisations on the shoe’s iconic design. With the AF1 ‘07 LX, Nike gave a nod to animal lovers with its sweet paw print details.

Our experts feel that the best feature of the Air Force 1 '07 LX is its pink and white color story, which emphasizes the cuteness of its paw print branding. The Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX Pearl Pink Paw Print (Women's) released on September 1, 2024, and retailed for $120.

name: Scratch 2.0
title: Nike Ja 1 Scratch 2.0
description:
The Nike Ja 1 Scratch 2.0 is a sneaker from American basketball player Ja Morant’s first signature line with Nike.
  
This model of the Nike Ja 1 has an upper made almost completely of white mesh for breathability and flexibility. Black leather overlays form the toe cap, as well as panels on each side of the forefoot leading up to the laces for support. The panel on the inner side is perforated for extra airflow. The Nike Swoosh appears in black on each side, and the heel counter is gray with Ja Morant’s logo in white. The number 12 appears in black on the white heel collar. Ja’s logo appears again on the tongue, and the shoe sits on a white midsole and a striped black and white outsole. 
 
What we think stands out about the sneaker is its simple black and white design that is both stylish and functional. The Nike Ja 1 Scratch 2.0 was released on January 3, 2024, for $140.

name: The Grinch (2023)
title: adidas Forum Low The Grinch (2023)
description:
Inspired by the fictional character "Grinch," the adidas Forum Low The Grinch (2023) is a sneaker from the Grinch x adidas Forum Low pack released for the Christmas 2023 season. 

This Forum Low features a Cream White leather upper highlighted by Collegiate Red accents on the signature three stripes on the lateral, the TPU heel tab, the midsole, and the strap holder. Solar Green hues on the suede tongue, ankle, medial three stripes branding, sock liner, and the Trefoil logo on the medial complement the upper. Other details include Grinch branding on the tongue tab and insole, hook-and-loop straps, perforations on the toebox and mid-panel, and a Grinch-branded lace dubrae. Rounding out the design is a Cream White midsole with adidas Trefoil branding on the medial heel and Solar Green rubber outsole. Each pair comes with Grinch pins and adidas ornament. 

Our experts particularly love this sneaker’s colorway and unique design elements, which make it a standout shoe for Grinch fans and other wearers. The adidas Forum Low The Grinch (2023) was made available on December 1st, 2023, for a retail price of $130.

name: 90s Backpack
title: Nike SB Dunk Low Pro PRM 90s Backpack
description:
The Nike SB Dunk Low Pro PRM 90s Backpack features a two-tone color combination of midnight navy and brown tones.  

The sneaker’s upper is dressed in midnight navy canvas color schemes on its mid panels and heel, while its forefoot is covered in brown suede. On the padded tongue, in addition to a pull tab and a suede Nike SB tag, there is a concealed stash pocket with a zip closure. Before a neutral white midsole finishes off the look below, there is a distinctive motif embossed on the footbed. 

The Nike SB Dunk Low Pro PRM 90s Backpack was released on 9th May 2023. This pair retailed at the price of $110.
model: Nike SB Dunk Low Pro PRM

name: Reflective Swoosh Cool Grey
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LV8 Reflective Swoosh Cool Grey
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low ‘07 LV8 Reflective Swoosh Cool Grey adds some eye-catching details to a signature silhouette.

The Reflective Swoosh Cool Grey iteration of the Nike Air Force 1 Low-Top ‘07 LV8 (Elevate) has an upper composed primarily of cool grey suede. The base features perforations on the toe box and side panel, and the lateral toe cap overlay sports a miniature black Nike swoosh. Black Nike branding adorns the great textile pull tab at the heel, the tongue tag, and the grey insole. The stacked black foam midsole houses iconic Air and the black rubber outsole is grooved for impact absorption and grip.

The aspect of this shoe we most enjoy is the side-panel Nike swoosh. This reflective grey textile appears in a cutout window and when it glows in the dark, you can see a number of miniature black Nike swooshes sketched into the larger reflective swoosh. The Nike Air Force 1 Low ‘07 LV8 Reflective Swoosh Cool Grey was released on September 20, 2023, for a retail price of $135.

name: White Silver
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 White Silver
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 White Silver is a signature shoe created by Lamelo Ball and Puma.

The Puma LaMelo Ball features a construction of white mono-mesh up the top of the shoe with a forefoot of tonal no-sew overlays. The low-top has its anchor from the white Nitro Foam midsole with the molded TPU frame for more stability. The padded mesh tongue is woven with a "1 of 1" tag to add sass to this iconic design. It has the LaMelo signature tagline "Not From Here" printed on the shoe vamp and the lateral collar embellished detailing.

The Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 White Silver was released in July 2022 at a retail price of $120.

name: Natural
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Natural
description:
Yeezy added a new colorway to their most popular line with the Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Natural, now available on StockX.

The Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Natural is reminiscent of the 350 V2 Cream that released in 2017. Its upper is mostly white, but instead of a monotone look, hits of light grey on the Primeknit upper give this design an identity of its own. A yellowed translucent Boost sole, a see-through side stripe, and traditional rope laces add the finishing touches to this most recent addition to the 350 V2 collection.

The Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Natural released in October of 2020 and retailed for $200.

name: Undefeated Light Menta
title: Nike Air Terra Humara Undefeated Light Menta
description:
The Nike Air Terra Humara Undefeated Light Menta is a collaboration between the iconic shoe company and the lifestyle brand that started out as a sneaker boutique in Los Angeles. The result is an eclectic, eye-catching shoe built for comfort.

The Undefeated X Nike Air Terra Humara in Light Menta sports a lightweight, breathable base of dark gray mesh that is overlaid with teal suede, synthetic leather, and TPU. The midfoot overlay with a reflective finish integrates into the lacing system, providing a snug fit across the entire foot. The midsole is composed of speckled teal and black foam and houses visible Air under the heel for ultimate cushioning. The speckled black outsole with pods of cherry and green rubber tie together the look of this vibrant and dynamic shoe.

What we most enjoy on this sneaker are all the hits of dual branding that pepper the upper, especially the blue Undefeated branding tag that adorns the black side panel Nike Swoosh. The Nike Air Terra Humara Undefeated Light Menta was released on February 24, 2024, for $170 retail.

name: Protection Pack Reflection
title: New Balance 1906D Protection Pack Reflection
description:
The upper of the New Balance 1906D Protection Pack Reflection is made of breathable, bright white suede with subtle off-white suede accents.

The plastic heel cage is dressed in black accents. In addition, it features a 1906D logo at the lateral heel, NB branding on the padded tongue, and the side 'N' logos in black accents, which are a part of the 1906's N-Lock lacing system to guarantee a snug fit. The white ABZORB-SBS midsole's N-ergy cushioning units are constructed of gold embellishments.

The New Balance 1906D Protection Pack Reflection was released on the market on 6th January 2023. It retailed at the price of $170.

name: Split Black Phantom
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LV8 Split Black Phantom
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low ’07 LV8 Split Black Phantom is a low-top sneaker that draws inspiration from 1980s basketball shoes and displays color blocking in black, Phantom, white, and Light Silver.

Smooth leather overlays in black cross the Phantom leather base and boast reinforced tonal stitching. A collection of perforations across the vamp as well as two holes on each side panel allow the foot to breathe and are a signature Air Force 1 design element. Another signature feature is the leather Swoosh in white, which streaks along the side panel and matches the midsole. Like other versions of the Air Force 1 Low ’07, the LV8 Split Black Phantom has air cushioning in the midsole and padding around the ankle.

Our StockX experts like the colorful NIKE AIR branding on the tongue’s logo tag, which elevates the sneaker to the modern age. The Nike Air Force 1 Low ’07 LV8 Split Black Phantom was released on October 20, 2023, and originally sold for $135.

name: Sequoia
title: Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM Sequoia
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM Sequoia applies a dark base to the recognizable Nike Dunk Low silhouette. It pays tribute to previous Dunk Low models from the 1980s by incorporating aged leather and padding around the collar.

Although designed as a basketball shoe, the sneaker features a flat rubber outsole that grips the ground, making it a favorite among skateboarders. The upper is crafted from aged leather, which is soft and gives the sneaker a retro feel. Tonal leather overlays and the Swoosh cross the shoe without creating a color-blocking effect. Although the Sequoia color is featured prominently across the upper, the colorway also includes Light Orewood Brown.

Our experts like the minimal Nike branding, including "Nike" stitched across the heel counter and the Nike logo on the tongue in white. The Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM Sequoia was released on August 9th, 2023, and retailed at $120.

name: All-Star (GS)
title: Nike Ja 1 SE All-Star (GS)
description:
The Nike Ja 1 SE All-Star (GS) is a shoe for grade schoolers that’s part of American basketball star Ja Morant’s collection with the brand.

The All-Star (GS) Nike Ja 1 SE has a white mesh upper with leather overlays supporting the forefoot in a metallic silver kaleidoscope design. The Nike Swoosh appears in metallic silver on the outer side and white on the inside. The heel counter is made of a light shade of blue with Morant’s branding etched into it on the outer side. The tongue bears his logo along with stars, as does the heel collar. The shoe sits atop a thick blue and white midsole, and the outsole is blue with white speckles.

Our favorite feature of this shoe is the silver prism detailing on the overlays and one of the Swooshes, which drives home the All-Star mentality. The Nike Ja 1 SE All-Star (GS) was released on February 16, 2024, for $102.

name: Munsell White
title: New Balance 530 Munsell White
description:
The New Balance 530 Munsell White arrives in a Munsell white and silver metallic colorway.

The New Balance 530 Munsell White has an upper that is crafted from a blend of leather and synthetic materials, making it both durable and lightweight. The shoe features ABZORB cushioning in the midsole for reduced impact. The outsole is constructed from sturdy rubber, making it both grippy and stable. The shoe features "N" branding on the lateral sides and an "NB" logo on the tongue.

The New Balance 530 Munsell White was made available on December 8th, 2020, and sold for a retail price of $100.

name: Masterpiece (2025)
title: Nike Kobe 9 Elite Protro Masterpiece (2025)
description:
The Nike Kobe 9 Elite Protro Masterpiece returns in all its bold, artistic glory, celebrating Kobe Bryant’s legacy with a design as dynamic as his game. This high-top silhouette features a black & multi color Flyknit upper, acting as the perfect backdrop for an explosion of bright crimson, volt, and multi-color woven details, symbolizing the creativity and precision Kobe brought to the court. A metallic silver 3M Swoosh adds a reflective edge, while the quilted leather tongue with a green Mamba logo & red Kobe signature sets this release apart from previous Kobe 9s with a distinct pop of color.

Function meets style with carbon fiber reinforcements on the midsole for added stability and paint splatter accents that enhance the sneaker’s artistic appeal. Paying tribute to Kobe’s relentless drive, the red Achilles stitch detail on the heel honors his legendary return from injury. A solid grey rubber outsole rounds out the look, ensuring durability and traction whether you’re playing or keeping them fresh in your collection. True to the Protro philosophy, this 2025 edition keeps its original aesthetic while incorporating modernized performance upgrades for today’s game.

Released on February 8, 2025, exactly 11 years after its original 2014 debut, the Nike Kobe 9 Elite Protro Masterpiece retailed at $240. Featuring a standout black, metallic silver, bright crimson, and volt colorway, this iconic sneaker made a long-awaited return, solidifying its place as one of the most unforgettable Kobe releases to date.

name: Preloved Yellow
title: adidas Samba LT Preloved Yellow
description:
The adidas Samba LT Preloved Yellow continues the lineage of one of the brand's most iconic trainers. This updated model has a striking design, while retaining that classic low profile.

The much beloved adidas Samba has been a hit all over the world since it was released a few decades ago. The simplicity of its design captures perfectly the adidas ethos, and you can now get many different colorways besides the original black with white detailing. This trainer is prized for its characteristic leather nubuck toe, and its slim, lightweight rubber outsole.

Like so many people, we're huge fans of this new model because of the upgrades on the original that make the legendary Samba even more special. What stands out most is the over-sized soccer boot-like tongue that now covers the lace-up area. It's quite a departure from the original design, but once we got used to this new look, it soon became one of our favorite features. The adidas Samba LT Preloved Yellow was released on 1 May 2024, retailed at $100.

name: Travis Scott Cactus Jack Wheat Lemon Drop
title: Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Cactus Jack Wheat Lemon Drop
description:
Joining the Gold and Brown version of Nike SNKRS is the Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Wheat Lemon Drop sneaker in baroque brown, wheat, and lemon drop colorways.

The Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Wheat Lemon Drop silhouette is constructed with a lemon-colored upper mesh and a baroque brown mudguard and heel tab. To complete the design is a baroque brown corporate branding, red rope laces, wheat-colored tongues, and overlays, including a reverse Swoosh on the lateral in a neural lemon drop hue.

The Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Wheat Lemon Drop sneaker was released on May 2022, retailing at $160.

name: Eclipse
title: New Balance 9060 Eclipse
description:
The New Balance 9060 Eclipse reinterprets elements from the iconic 99X models to craft a futuristic look, then dresses the hybrid shoe in a contrasting colorway that pops.

The upper of the Eclipse iteration of the New Balance 9060 features a base of black mesh that offers lightweight breathability. This is overlaid with undulating strips of dark navy blue suede that gives this shoe a Y2K aesthetic. Flat tonal laces cross over a navy blue leather tongue that sports a tongue tag branding window inspired by the 991 lace jewel. The dual-density midsole in shades of off-white and pale gray features layers of ABZORB and SBS cushioning. This midsole offers stark color contrast against the upper, but matches the translucent CR device that offers stability at the heel. The outsole features gray rubber pads with off-white diamonds, a nod to the 860.

Our favorite feature of this sneaker is the design of the side panel Ns. The lateral navy blue N pops with its silvery white lining, while the medial is glossy midnight blue embroidery. The New Balance 9060 Eclipse was released on August 10th, 2023, for a retail price of $150.

name: Denim Turquoise
title: Nike Dunk Low Denim Turquoise
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Denim Turquoise is a low-top shoe made with premium materials to increase athletic performance.

The denim turquoise version of the Nike Dunk Low is made of leather. White leather forms the base, the sides, the ankle collar, and the toe box, which is perforated for breathability. Leather overlays in the Denim Turquoise color form the toe cap, ankle strap, eyestays, and heel collar, which also bears the Nike brand name stitched in white.
