The Nike Swoosh also adorns each side in Denim Turquoise. Another Nike patch appears on the tongue. The shoe features a white midsole and Denim Turquoise outsole that is patterned for traction.

What we like most about the shoe is the smooth leather upper, which gives it a crisp and clean look. The Nike Dunk Low Denim Turquoise was released on June 1, 2024, for a retail price of $115.

name: Dark Royal Brown
title: New Balance 9060 Dark Royal Brown
description:
The New Balance 9060 Dark Royal Brown is a function-first running shoe with an exaggerated technical silhouette. Blue Agate dominates the sneaker, while hits of black on the midsole, mesh underlays, laces, and part of the rubber outsole add contrast.

Drawing inspiration from heritage 99X models, the Dark Royal Brown New Balance 9060 boasts layered pig suede overlays in Blue Agate and gray. The wavy lines create the illusion of movement across the upper and support the breathable mesh base. Contributing to the sneaker’s visible tech aesthetic, the sculpted midsole houses oversized pods and ABZORB and ABZORB SBS cushioning. The diamond-like shape of the outsole pattern comes from the 860 and helps evenly distribute pressure.

Our experts at StockX like the shiny tongue tag displaying New Balance branding because it resembles the lace jewel on the 991. The New Balance 9060 Dark Royal Brown was released on January 8, 2024, and sold for $150.

name: Cacao Wow
title: Nike Air Max 1 SC Cacao Wow
description:
The Nike Air Max 1 SC Cacao Wow is a colorway of the classic shoe that was inspired by Cacao and chocolate colors.

This version of the Nike Air Max 1 is constructed with a mesh upper in a Hemp light brown color. This allows breathability and flexibility for extra comfort. Leather overlays in a pale brown Dusted Clay color cross the midsoles and form the heel counter. A textured dark brown Cacao Wow leather mudguard rounds out the shoe from the inner arch around the heel, and the Nike swoosh appears across each side in Cacao Wow. A Nike Air logo is featured on the heel, while the tongue also bears an Air Max logo patch. An off-white rubber sole contains visible Air Max units in the heel while Nike Air cushioning is present in the forefoot.

Our favorite feature of this sneaker is the smooth brown colorway, which makes the shoe neutral but bold at the same time. The Nike Air Max 1 SC Cacao Wow was released on March 1, 2024, for $150.

name: White Picante Red
title: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Picante Red
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Retro White Picante Red is a brightly colored version of the original Nike Dunk model. It is meant to have a vintage look and feel that reminds the wearer of the 90s.

The Low Retro Dunk in White and Picante Red has a bright red gum rubber sole that is directly below the white rubber midsole. On top of the midsole is the white body that is made of leather and various leather overlays. The Nike ‘Swoosh’ symbol is bright red, as well as the ‘Nike’ that is embroidered on the back of the shoe.

A feature of the Nike Dunk Low Retro White Picante Red that our team of experts particularly likes is the pop of red that is on the tongue of the shoe, as well as the round toe design. These shoes first became available for purchase on July 13th, 2023, and had a starting retail price of $110.

name: Black Metallic Grey
title: Nike Air Max Dn Black Metallic Grey
description:
The Black Metallic Grey Nike Air Max Dn redefines classic design with smart colors and dynamic detailing combined in a way that accentuates the brand's tone and creativity. This release merges Nike’s signature Air cushioning with a trendy aesthetic tailored for casual and athletic settings.

The Black Metallic Grey Air Max Dn by Nike features a synthetic and mesh upper for durability and breathability, paired with metallic grey accents highlighting its modern design. The signature Nike Air unit in the midsole ensures responsive cushioning, complemented by a durable rubber outsole for reliable grip. Since its inception in 1987, the Air Max line has revolutionized footwear, blending cutting-edge technology with street-ready designs.

What our experts enjoy about the Nike Air Max Dn Black Metallic Grey is the secure lacing system that improves foot stability and its reflective accents in the heel to improve visibility in low-light conditions. This pair retailed at $160 when it debuted on 3 May 2024.

name: Gorge Green (Women's)
title: Nike Air Max 1 Gorge Green (Women's)
description:
The dominant colors that characterize the appearance of the Nike Air Max 1 Gorge Green W are Obsidian, white, Midnight Navy, and Gorge Green.

This Gorge Green Nike Air Max 1 in women’s sizing showcases a blend of Midnight Navy, Gorge Green, and Obsidian sitting on top of a traditional white midsole and gum bottom. The upper of this sneaker is constructed using a combination of different materials, namely leather, mesh, and suede. Additionally, there are design elements reminiscent of a varsity jacket that are incorporated through the Nike lettering at the forefoot, the Swoosh branding, and the heel.

A white Swoosh on a black top is one feature that our experts found to be attractive on this shoe. The Nike Air Max 1 Gorge Green W sold for $160 at the time of its launch in September 30, 2022.

name: Pure Platinum Anthracite
title: Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Pure Platinum Anthracite
description:
The Nike Air VaporMax 2023 FlyKnit Pure Platinum Anthracite gives the sneaker a snowy upgrade with a crystal-like VaporMax unit, and a colorway dominated by Pure Platinum and white.

The upper is made of stretchy FlyKnit in Pure Platinum that conforms to the foot’s shape. This durable material is lightweight and keeps the foot from overheating. However, the most noteworthy feature is the VaporMax unit, which runs the entire length of the shoe and is made from a single piece. It provides responsive cushioning and protects against impact while adding an eye-catching design element. An Anthracite Swoosh logo with bits of Pure Platinum streaks across the lateral side panel, while additional branding can be found on the insole, tongue tag, and heel.

Our StockX experts appreciate that the Flyknit is made with 20 percent recycled materials. The Nike Air VaporMax 2023 FlyKnit Pure Platinum Anthracite was released on August 1st, 2023, and retailed at $210.

name: Archeo Pink (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Archeo Pink (Women's)
description:
The women's Nike Dunk Low Archeo Pink (W) features a white leather upper with Archeo Pink overlays and Swooshes. From there, a matching woven tongue label and sole completes the design.

The women's Nike Dunk Low Archeo Pink (W) released in October of 2021 and retailed for $100.

name: Penny
title: Nike KD 17 Penny
description:
The Nike KD 17 Penny merges Nike's cutting-edge technology with nostalgic design elements, giving you a fresh take on basketball shoes. The shoe redefines comfort and style for the modern athlete by combining a bold aesthetic with performance-focused materials.

The Penny version of the KD 17 by Nike features a striking upper made with lightweight mesh and synthetic overlays that increase breathability and add to the structure. This edition comes with a deep-blue and black palette with sleek silver accents, a small nod to Penny Hardaway’s classic colors. The midsole uses full-length Nike Zoom Air cushioning for responsive support, which adds stability for dynamic movements, while a sturdy rubber outsole offers multidirectional traction. This model is an excellent addition to Nike’s basketball heritage, thanks to the innovative use of materials and bold color accents.

We appreciate the classic upper pattern resembling waves, and the round toe cap that is part of the line. Released on April 26, 2024, the Nike KD 17 Penny retailed at $150.

name: College Pack Midnight Navy
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low College Pack Midnight Navy
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low College Pack Midnight Navy arrives in a sail, midnight navy-gum medium brown color scheme.

The College Pack Midnight Navy Nike Air Force 1 Low adopts a classic silhouette with an upper that is constructed with synthetic and leather overlays. The shoe features a perforated toe box for breathability. The shoe's outsole is made of rubber for grip and sturdiness. The midsole features Nike Air technology, which offers cushioning and support. The shoe has a Nike Swoosh on either side, a "NIKE Swoosh AIR FORCE 1" inscription on the tongue, and "NIKE Swoosh Air" on the heel.

The Nike Air Force 1 Low College Pack Midnight Navy was released at a retail price of $130 on September 24, 2022.

name: Ale Brown Ostrich (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low LX Ale Brown Ostrich (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low LX Ale Brown Ostrich (Women's) is a low-top women’s shoe designed with the look of ostrich skin in mind.

This iteration of the Nike Dunk Low LX is made with a base of white leather, which forms the sides, part of the heel, and the toe box. The toe box is also perforated for breathability. Shiny Ale Brown paneled overlays can be found on the upper rounding out the toe box, running under the laces, running down from the ankle around the heel, and forming the Nike swoosh on each side. The brown overlays take on a shiny and textured feel, mimicking ostrich skin. The heel collar contains the Nike brand name, while a logo patch can also be found on the tongue. A white rubber sole and Ale Brown outsole round out the design.

What we like best about this shoe is the unique texture and shine of the brown overlays, which add extra visual interest. The Nike Dunk Low LX Ale Brown Ostrich (Women's) was released on February 17, 2024, for a price of $135.

name: Bred (2022)
title: Nike Air Max 270 Bred (2022)
description:
The Nike Air Max 270 Bred 2022 is a new colorway addition to the Air Max 270 Bred collection.

The upper of the Air Max 270 Bred 2022 is made from a mix of synthetic materials and fabric, which provides both breathability and support. The shoe also features a sock-like fit that hugs the foot and provides a snug feel. The rubber outsole is also durable and provides excellent traction, making it ideal for both indoor and outdoor activities. The sneaker comes in a black colorway with red accents on the branding and on the Air unit at the sole. 

We think that the standout feature of the Nike Air Max 270 Bred 2022 is the large Air Max cushioning in the heel. This air unit provides excellent cushioning and support, making the shoe comfortable for all-day wear. The Nike Air Max 270 Bred 2022 was released on March 17th, 2022 at a listing price of $150.

name: Jacquemus Light Bone Gold (Women's)
title: Nike Air Humara LX Jacquemus Light Bone Gold (Women's)
description:
French designer Simon Porte Jacquemus teamed up with Nike for a luxe take on the hiking-friendly Nike Air Humara.

The women's Nike Air Humara LX Jacquemus Beige is constructed of a smooth light beige leather upper with brown hairy suede overlays and striped exterior ribbons. A pendant-like golden Nike mini Swoosh graces each side of the upper in an elegant fashion. At the base, a sculptural, jagged gum outsole is versatile enough for the streets and the trails.

The women's Nike Air Humara LX Jacquemus Beige released in June of 2022.

name: From Nike To You Fir Green
title: Nike Dunk Low Retro From Nike To You Fir Green
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Retro From Nike To You Fir Green arrived ahead of the holiday season in 2023 and adds a Christmas-inspired colorway to the Dunk Low Retro’s recognizable silhouette.

The use of Fir instead of a more traditional Spruce Green on the upper complements the Team Red details. It also offers a contemporary take on the traditional Christmas color scheme. While the laces, Swoosh logo on the lateral side panel, and the heel tab come in Team Red, Coconut Milk can be found on the midsole and leather overlays. Something that makes this low-top sneaker stand out is the Swoosh logo on the medial side panel. It features light blue instead of Team Red.

Our StockX experts like the use of slightly yellow Coconut Milk on the midsole. This detail gives the sneaker a worn-in, retro feel. The Nike Dunk Low Retro From Nike To You Fir Green was released on November 21st, 2023, and retailed at $115.

name: Wales Bonner Brown Croc
title: adidas Samba Wales Bonner Brown Croc
description:
The adidas Samba Wales Bonner Brown Croc is a performance shoe designed as a partnership between the sportswear brand and British menswear fashion brand Wales Bonner.

The Wales Bonner Brown Croc adidas Samba has a calf leather upper that appears in a caramel-brown color. The shoe has a crocodile pattern throughout, which is executed by the brown scales and shiny effect. This not only forms the base, but also the overlays that are the toe cap and eyestays. The heel collar is a solid brown color with white decorative stitching around the edges, while the adidas 3-Stripes are white leather strips on each side. The tongue contains adidas branding in gold.

What we like most about this sneaker is the realistic execution of the crocodile effect, which really brings the shoe to life. The adidas Samba Wales Bonner Brown Croc was released on October 24, 2024, for $300.

name: Bad Bunny Blue Tint
title: adidas Forum Buckle Low Bad Bunny Blue Tint
description:
The adidas Forum Buckle Low Bad Bunny Blue Tint joins the Low Bad Bunny Forum launched by adidas and the Puerto Rican rapper, Bad Bunny.

These adidas blue tint shoes have leather and suede uppers. They feature a black heavy-duty metal buckle on each side secured onto the nylon straps of the shoes. The shoes have a shoe-heel drawstring chord, detachable double-stacked tongue with Bad Bunny’s branding, a protruding foam piece on the collars, icy blue rubber outsoles, partially translucent midsoles, and soft yellow and pink laces completing the design.  

The adidas Forum Buckle Low Bad Bunny Blue Tint was released in August 2022 with a retail price of $160.

name: G-Dragon Peaceminusone Para-Noise 2.0
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low G-Dragon Peaceminusone Para-Noise 2.0
description:
Disclaimer: Please be aware of paint fragility regarding the first layer of color on the upper. Due to the thin coating of paint, colors may rub off.

After a year-long hiatus, K-Pop star G-Dragon’s fashion label, Peaceminusone, teamed up with Nike once again to release the Nike Air Force 1 Low Peaceminusone Para-noise 2.0. This sequel release follows the same DIY theme as last year’s AF-1 Para-noise, only this time the colorway was flipped.

The Air Force 1 Low Peaceminusone Para-noise 2.0 features a white upper treated with a special lacquer coating that will rub off over time, revealing G-Dragon’s hidden artwork. The Peaceminusone Daisy motif is embroidered on the tongue and is accompanied by black paint streaks on the entire white sole. Black overlays, detailing, and laces complete the design.

The Air Force 1 Low Peaceminusone Para-noise 2.0 released in November of 2020 for $200.

name: Sporty & Rich USA
title: adidas Handball Spezial Sporty & Rich USA
description:
Introducing the Sporty & Rich USA adidas Handball Spezial, a collaborative reinterpretation of the 1987 Handball Spezial design. This limited-edition sneaker blends adidas’ athletic heritage with Sporty & Rich’s bold aesthetic and has been popular with people since it's release, founded by Emily Oberg in 2017.

The Sporty & Rich USA Handball Spezial boasts a vibrant red suede upper with white leather 3 stripes and navy blue back tabs. adidas’ iconic three-stripe design and trefoil logo are displayed on the sides and tongue. A semi-translucent gum sole provides traction, while an Ortholite sockliner offers comfort. This sneaker blends athletic heritage with modern style, featuring subtle Sporty & Rich branding on the heel alongside adidas’ classic design elements.

Our experts love the Sporty & Rich USA Handball Spezial’s gold accents and minimalist "adidas" on the navy blue back tabs. These details exemplify the collaboration’s attention to detail. Released on July 29, 2024, the Handball Spezial retailed at $120.

name: One Piece Buggy
title: Puma Suede One Piece Buggy
description:
The Puma Suede One Piece Buggy is a low-top sneaker that’s part of a collaboration between Puma and One Piece, an anime and manga series that centers on the adventures of a young pirate and his crew.

This sneaker features a hairy suede upper in For All Time Red with perforations on the side panels and a long lace cage. Thick laces in For All Time Red wind through the eyelets and create a secure, adjustable closure. The sides display a shaggy suede panel in Ultra Blue that looks like a wave. Hits of metallic gold can be found on the skull logo on the heel and the "PUMA SUEDE" lettering on the side panel.

Our StockX experts like that the shaggy suede tongue is debossed with Puma branding but doesn’t feature metallic gold. The Puma Suede One Piece Buggy was released on March 23, 2024, and sold for $85.

name: Ekiden Pack
title: Nike Air Zoom Alphafly Next% 2 Ekiden Pack
description:
The Nike Air Zoom Alphafly Next% 2 Ekiden Pack is a brightly colored shoe that comes with a unique mismatched design.

This version of the Nike Alphafly Next% 2 is constructed with a full mesh upper for flexibility, comfort, and breathability. The upper on one of the shoes comes in a bright yellow-green color, while the other shoe boasts a bright pink color. A black Nike Swoosh appears on the lateral side of the forefoot, and another smaller one is placed over the arch on the inside. Black laces and a black tongue with a branded pull tab appear on both shoes. The heels also feature Nike branded pull tabs. The shoes also feature ZoomX cushioning, and ZoomX branding can be seen on the chunky outsole under the heel. A transparent Zoom Air unit is also placed under the forefoot.

Our favorite thing about this shoe is the mismatched design, as the bright colors complement each other. The Nike Air Zoom Alphafly Next% 2 Ekiden Pack was released on December 1, 2023, for a price of $295.

name: Medium Ash Gum
title: Nike Terminator Low Medium Ash Gum
description:
The Nike Terminator Low Medium Ash Gum was inspired by the Nike Terminator High, which was released a year before the low-top version. The sneaker features an overall dark aesthetic with a prominent gum rubber sole.

The Ash Gum iteration boasts a black leather base with soft suede overlays. Something that makes this sneaker stand out is the black stitching that crosses part of the Swoosh but does not overlap the lace cage. The toe overlays, the lace cage, and the Swoosh all come in a grey suede that is almost shaggy. The vamp offers perforations, which allow the foot to breathe and provide aesthetic details. Lettering across the heel panel spells out ‘NIKE’ in a big, block font.

What do our StockX experts love? The red Swoosh on the tongue is the only pop of color on the entire shoe. The Nike Terminator Low Medium Ash Gum was released on October 12, 2023, and retailed at $120.

name: Miami
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Miami
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Miami is a brightly colored basketball shoe designed as a collaboration with American basketball star LaMelo Ball.

The Miami Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 has an engineered mesh upper as its base in a bright-pink color. This is visible through ragged scratches in the overlays on each side. Synthetic overlays in teal with pink swirls adorn most of the upper from the toe to the heel. The cushioned heel area is Teal with Puma, Melo, 111 and 01ofOne branding in pink, while the tongue bears the words "Rare" and "Fear" in pink. The shoe sits on a thick teal textured midsole that bleeds into the design of the upper.

What we like best about this shoe is the pink swirl pattern across the overlays on the upper, which allows the shoe to stand out. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Miami was released on July 5, 2024, for $125.

name: White Slate Grey
title: New Balance 550 White Slate Grey
description:
This New Balance 550 White Slate Gray boasts a white, Slate Gray, and Brighton Gray color combination, while channeling a retro basketball feel from the 80s.

The original New Balance 550 debuted in 1989, and since then it has been reintroduced with numerous colorways. This particular iteration boasts a mainly synthetic white upper with ventilation holes on the quarters. Suede Brighton Gray leather tips the toecap while Slate Gray is seen on the heel and large "N" branding on the sides. Other New Balance branding hits appear on the heel, tongue, and midsole, with a black 550 on the lateral quarter panel.

What we love about this shoe is its vintage aesthetic that oozes old-school basketball style. The gum outsole, thick midsole, oversized tongue and bulky feel all lend to this aesthetic. When it debuted on April 1, 2024, the New Balance 550 White Slate Gray sold for retail at $110.

name: White Metallic Silver (Women's)
title: Nike Shox R4 White Metallic Silver (Women's)
description:
The Nike Shox R4 White Metallic Silver (Women's) dresses the Shox R4 from the 2000s in a sleek colorway that complements its retro-futuristic aesthetic.

Like its 2000s predecessor, this reboot of the Shox R4 applies four pistons under the heel instead of foam or Air Max units. The pistons offer an alternative form of springy cushioning and represent how 2000s designers interpreted "futuristic" looks. Drawing inspiration from spacesuits, the synthetic leather upper features sleek likes and laser-cut perforations for an airy feel. Although white and metallic silver hues dominate the shoe, Max Orange accents disrupt the light color scheme on the heel, tongue, and rubber outsole.

Our StockX experts like the Swoosh logo embroidered on the side panel in metallic silver. It brings balance to the sneaker and allows the futuristic features to stand out. The women’s size Nike Shox R4 White Metallic Silver (Women's) was released on May 7, 2019, and sold for $140.

name: Mono Safflower
title: adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Mono Safflower
description:
Yeezy added a subtle twist to the adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Safflower with the adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Mono Safflower.

With a yellow and tonal grey Primeknit upper atop a thick EVA foam sole, the adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Mono Safflower is almost identical to the original Safflower release. However, there is one key difference: instead of a stark white TPU lace caging unit, the Mono Safflower opts for a glow-in-the-dark, cream styling, matching the warm look of the sole.

The adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Mono Safflower released in March of 2022 and retailed for $200.

name: Easter (Translucent Outsole)
title: Nike LeBron 21 Easter (Translucent Outsole)
description:
The Nike LeBron 21 Easter (Translucent Outsole) joins the Easter celebrations with a pastel colorway that looks like the faded shell of a dip-dyed egg.

The Flywire upper of the Easter Nike LeBron 21 comes in Barley Grape and works with the Light Armory Blue accents on the outsole and Swoosh logo to further the pastel aesthetic. The Swoosh logo on the outer side panel features a jewel-like finish, complementing the semi-translucent rubber outsole. Due to the Zoom Air cushioning in the midsole and the low-to-the-ground design, this sneaker boasts superior energy return. The cabling system is less pronounced on this version of the LeBron 21 but still mimics the lines in an oyster shell. The relationship between an oyster and its pearl symbolizes LeBron James’ desire to protect his daughter.

Our experts at StockX like the mismatched Swoosh logo on the inner side panel. It features embroidered lines in Lilac Bloom. The Nike LeBron 21 Easter (Translucent Outsole) was released on April 2, 2024, and retailed at $200.

name: Mineral Slate Armory Navy
title: Nike Dunk Low Mineral Slate Armory Navy
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Armory Navy was made available as a part of a special edition by the American brand.

The color "Mineral Slate" appears on the upper of this Low Nike Dunk version in several places, including the synthetic base on the side panels, the perforated toe box, the tongue, and the branding. The color "Armory Navy" appears in the leather overlays, the leather Swoosh, the laces, the tongue tag, the sock liner, the insole, and the heel tab. The collar is padded, and the outsole is made of black rubber for traction.

The Nike Dunk Low Armory Navy was released on December 13th, 2022 for a retail price of $120.

name: Photon Dust Black (Women's)
title: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Photon Dust Black (Women's)
description:
The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Photon Dust Black (Women's) blends athletic technology with a smart duotone design. This running-inspired silhouette is ideal for casual and active use and features premium materials and Nike's trusted engineering for a reliable fit.

The Photon Dust Black Zoom Vomero 5 (Women's) by Nike comes with a layered mesh and synthetic-leather upper for breathability and structure. Its dual-tone palette combines soft grays with striking black accents on the Swoosh and overlays. Lightweight cushioning is integrated into the midsole, with a rubber outsole designed for traction. Originally released in 2006, the Vomero line is renowned for its comfort-driven designs geared towards high-performance activities.

One thing we love about the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Photon Dust Black (Women's) is its well-engineered midsole that gives you consistent support. We also appreciate the sole pattern, almost like bubbles, that curves like the shape of the feet. This women's-sized shoe retailed at $160 upon its release on September 1, 2024.

name: Prototype
title: Nike Air Zoom Alphafly Next% 3 Prototype
description:
The Air Zoom Alphafly NEXT% 3 Prototype is a Nike "super shoe" designed by the iconic sneaker company specifically to enhance the speed of marathon runners.

The Prototype colorway of the Air Zoom Alphafly NEXT% 3 features an upper constructed from white to pale orange gradient Atomknit. The "V62" on the medial side collar indicates that this is the 62nd version of this lightweight fabric, while the number of the midsole refers to a Nike test runner that put the most miles on this shoe. To complete the look of this upper, an oversized black Nike swoosh is printed across the quarter panel and extends onto the midsole.

The most impressive aspect of this running shoe is its high-octane sole unit. The midsole has a carbon Flyplate pressed between two slabs of continuous ZoomX foam to provide cushioning and maximum energy return. Visible Zoom Air units under the forefoot propel momentum, and all of this sits atop a black rubber outsole designed for traction. The Air Zoom Alphafly NEXT% 3 Prototype was released on January 4, 2024, for $285 retail.

name: All Day
title: Nike Air Max Plus Drift All Day
description:
The Nike Air Max Plus Drift All Day is an athletic sneaker with a bold design and Air Max technology.
 
This version of the Nike Air Max Plus has an upper made of fabric and TPU overlays for support. The fabric base comes in Field Purple, Laser Orange, and Bright Crimson and is revealed in wavy water drop shapes under the black and red TPU overlays that cross most of the upper. A bright red Nike Swoosh is seen on the lateral side of the heel, while the tongue bears another Nike Swoosh. The arch features purple supports, while the shoe rests on a black midsole with visible Air Max units under the heel and forefoot. A black outsole completes the look.
 
What we like most about this shoe are the bold orange and red accents, which make the shoe stand out. The Nike Air Max Plus Drift All Day was released on February 15, 2024, for $185.

name: Off White Collegiate Burgundy (Women's)
title: adidas Handball Spezial Off White Collegiate Burgundy (Women's)
description:
Stay true to your athleisure stylings with the adidas Handball Spezial Off-White Collegiate Burgundy (Womens)—a nod to the old collegiate aesthetics with true adidas flair.

Get your sporty style done right with these adidas Spezial sneakers in stunning off-white and burgundy. With classic suede upper and off-white laces, the 3-Stripes branding and Spezial logo pop off in burgundy. The shoe has a burgundy leather back collar and adidas branding on the tongue. The midsoles are a gummy texture in translucent brown with an embossed adidas logo. Extra traction on rubber outsoles are placed for quick turns when playing sport on courts or fields.

We love how the Spezial sneaker is so inspired by iconic 1970s retro vibes in its design aesthetic. The perfect street shoe, add them to your comfy sneaker rotation and get an all-day wearability that doesn’t skimp on style. The adidas Handball Spezial Off-White Collegiate Burgundy (Womens) were released on 6 September 2024, priced at $110.

name: Black White
title: Nike Air Max 2017 Black White
description:
The Nike Air Max 2017 Black White is a monochromatic performance running shoe that features a color gradient across the upper.

However, what sets the Black White Nike Air Max 2017 apart from other performance running sneakers is the full-length Air-Max unit underfoot. It comes in a crystal-clear material that allows you to completely see through the underfoot area, giving the unit a bubble-like appearance. In addition, the sculpted Cushlon midsole absorbs impact and provides a springy feel. Starting from the toe, the FlyMesh and synthetic upper fades from black to white. The signature Swoosh logo is printed across the side panel in white, while ‘AIR MAX’ in bold black letters decorates the Air Max unit and the tongue showcases ‘NIKE AIR 2017’ branding.

Our experts appreciate the seamless construction of the upper, which gives the sneaker a sleek appearance and allows the color gradient to catch the eye. The Nike Air Max 2017 Black White was released on January 1, 2017, and sold for $190.

name: Industrial Blue
title: Nike Air Zoom GT Cut 2 Industrial Blue
description:
The Nike Air Zoom GT Cut 2 Industrial Blue is an aerodynamic basketball shoe designed for sharp movements on the court.

At the Industrial Blue Nike Air Zoom GT Cut 2, the rubber outsole features Smear Traction in the forefoot area, allowing the sole to stick to the court briefly and a standard traction pattern on the rest. React foam in the midsole provides responsive cushioning, while the durable mesh upper allows the foot to breathe. Something that makes this sneaker stand out is the American flag-inspired colorway, which features Industrial Blue, Bright Crimson, and white, as well as other hues. In addition, perforations on the padded leather heel resemble stars, while lines carved in the midsole resemble stripes.

Our StockX experts like the long tongue, which displays a circle bisected by two black arrows with crooked tails. The Nike Air Zoom GT Cut 2 Industrial Blue was released on July 28, 2023, and retailed for $170.

name: Black Silver (Women's)
title: Nike Air Max Sunder Black Silver (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Max Sunder Black Silver (Women's) is a shoe made for women with a unique futuristic design and plenty of technology to match.

The black and silver (Women's) Nike Air Max Sunder has a black textile upper for its top half and ha a small Nike Swoosh on the outer side. Notably, the shoe lacks laces and has a black zipper up the middle instead. Suede overlays in black form the bottom half of the shoe, which feature lighter pockets with silver perforations on each side and around the toe box. The heel tab contains Nike Air branding, while the tongue contains a simple white Swoosh. The shoe sits atop a black midsole with Air Max units under the entire foot.

What we like best about this sneaker are the silver perforations, which add nice hits of color to the otherwise black shoe. The Nike Air Max Sunder Black Silver (Women's) was released on September 19. 2024, for $180.

name: Tartan Plaid
title: Nike Dunk Low Tartan Plaid
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Tartan Plaid has become a part of the iconic collection of the brand.

The upper of the this Low Nike Dunk is made of a white leather with perforations in the toe box, a black leather Swoosh, and a black leather heel tab. The Tartan Plaid combines University Red, Stadium Grey and Light Silver overlays, and are made of textiles, as well as the eyestays. The sockliner and insole are Light Silver while the Nike Swoosh is Black. Additional branding appears on the heel tab, tongue tag, and insole.

The Nike Dunk Low Tartan Plaid was released on January 18th, 2023 for a retail price of $120.

name: Dusty Cactus (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Dusty Cactus (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Dusty Cactus (Women's) features a two-tone design in vibrant Dusty Cactus and Clean White.

This low-top sneaker is part of Nike’s sustainable Next Nature series, which aims to reduce carbon emissions. Crafted from at least 20 percent recycled materials, this iteration of the Dunk Low has a full leather construction with perforations on the toebox for breathability. The mesh tongue also increases airflow, while padding around the collar protects the ankle. The base comes in white, while Dusty Cactus accents decorate the heel and forefoot overlays, the Swoosh logo, the eyelets, the heel tab, the rubber outsole, and the laces.

Our experts at StockX like that the ‘NIKE’ embroidery on the heel comes in white, while the adidas branding on the flat tongue features Dusty Cactus lettering. The women’s size Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Dusty Cactus (Women's) was released on January 15, 2024, and was priced at $115.

name: Glacier Grey Black
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Glacier Grey Black
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 Glacier Grey Black is an athletic running sneaker featuring a Glacier Grey mesh fabric upper and lining, accented by Black and metallic silver cage overlays. The white midsole displays an ombré insert and rear heel Gel unit, while a Black outsole and ASICS tongue branding complete the look.

ASICS, the Japanese footwear brand, created their brand name from an acronym from a Latin phrase translating to sound mind in a sound body. With a deep focus on running shoes, ASICS is known for refining previous editions into new evolutions, as exhibited in the GEL-1130. The GEL-1130 pays homage to a previous version of the GEL-1000, while incorporating ASICS’ signature performance comfort.

Our experts feel that the best feature of the Gel-1130 Glacier Grey is its Glacier Grey mesh, which pops against the signature Black caging. The ASICS Gel-1130 Glacier Grey Black released on October 16, 2024, and retailed for $95.

name: Coconut Milk Metallic Silver (Women's)
title: Nike P-6000 Coconut Milk Metallic Silver (Women's)
description:
The Nike P-6000 Coconut Milk Metallic Silver (Women's) is a women’s shoe that is an updated take on the Nike Pegasus model.

This version of the Nike P-6000 is made with a white mesh upper for breathability. Textile overlays in an off-white Coconut Milk color cross the upper from front to back in 3 lines on each side. A synthetic silver overlay forms the toe cap, while synthetic silver overlays also cross over the textile overlays vertically from the laces to the sole. A black Nike swoosh outlined in silver appears on each side, while a small black swoosh also appears under the laces. P-6000 branding is seen on the lateral heel. The heel counter is formed by another synthetic silver overlay with perforations and a small black Nike swoosh. The tongue also features the Nike brand name and a black sole and white outsole complete the look.

What we like best about this sneaker are the Coconut Milk overlays, which give the shoe a simple yet eye-catching design. The Nike P-6000 Coconut Milk Metallic Silver (Women's) was released on December 2, 2023, for $110.

name: Light Silver Corduroy (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Light Silver Corduroy (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Light Silver Corduroy (Women's) is a standalone release by Nike that is designed for women.

The midsole of the Dunk Low Light Silver Corduroy (Women's) is made with foam material, which is lightweight, flexible, and durable. The outsole of the shoe is made with a rubber material that is durable and provides traction. The rubber outsole features a herringbone pattern that provides grip and stability on most surfaces. The toebox is perforated, which aids in ventilation and provides a comfortable fit. Perforations on the shoe allow air to circulate and prevent the foot from overheating during extended wear. The shoe's low-profile silhouette and classic lace-up closure ensure a secure and comfortable fit, while the lightweight design offers ease of movement.

We simply love the Nike Dunk Low Light Silver Corduroy (Women's) for its simplicity. The shoe has a white and light silver colorway. It was released on August 22nd, 2023, at a retail price of $110.

name: Desert Sage
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Desert Sage
description:
Yeezy adds another colorway of its most well-known design with the adidas Yeezy 350 Desert Sage, now available on StockX. This 350 V2 dons similar hues as the Beluga colorways, only this time ditching a bright orange side stripe and adding a highlighted interior.

This Yeezy 350 V2 is composed of a desert sage Primeknit upper with a tonal side stripe. A translucent Boost cushioned sole and orange interior completes the design. These sneakers released in March of 2020 and retailed for $220.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Reflection Marblehead
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Teddy Santis Reflection Marblehead
description:
The MiUSA Teddy Santis Reflection Marblehead New Balance 990v6 highlights premium materials and thoughtful design, giving you a harmonious mix of suede, mesh, and reflective aspects. As part of Teddy Santis' Made in USA series, these shoes are here to give the iconic 990v6 silhouette a slight facelift.

The MiUSA Teddy Santis Reflection Marblehead 990v6 by New Balance comes with a tonal grey suede upper paired with breathable underlays, giving you a layered look and improving the airflow. The reflective detailing on the "N" logo is for visibility. This design incorporates New Balance’s ENCAP midsole technology and blends foam with a polyurethane rim to strengthen them. The "Made in USA" line reflects New Balance’s commitment to American-made products.

What we love about the MiUSA Teddy Santis Reflection Marblehead New Balance 990v6 is its reflective detailing, which improves safety and visual appeal, and the ENCAP midsole for a balance of cushioning and support. Released on 15th August 2024, it retailed at $220.

name: Dark Smoke Grey Barely Green
title: Nike Dunk Low Dark Smoke Grey Barely Green
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Dark Smoke Gray Barely Green crafts Peter Moore's renowned silhouette in premium materials and dresses it in an eye-catching colorway that will turn heads with every step.

This classic low-top sneaker is built upon an upper base of tumbled dark Smoke Gray leather that features a toebox sporting the iconic perforations that facilitate ventilation and enhance comfort. The rope laces and tongue match this tumbled leather base. Overlays in mint green leather adorn the upper, matching the tongue liner and the mesh sock liner. The dark Smoke Gray tongue tag features mint-colored Nike branding and the dark Smoke Gray leather heel tab features a mint outline of a Nike wordmark echoed a total of 4 times. This sneaker rides on a traditional cupsole construction of white foam, and the outsole in matte and translucent dark Smoke Gray rubber completes this shoe.

The feature of this sneaker that we enjoy the most is the side-panel Nike Swoosh. The mint leather is outlined by translucent TPU, a singular detail that sets this shoe apart. The Nike Dunk Low Dark Smoke Gray Barely Green debuted February 8, 2024, for $125 retail.

name: Sky Blue
title: adidas Gazelle Sky Blue
description:
A reissue of the 1991 version, the adidas Gazelle Sky Blue proves why this iconic silhouette has been defining style since 1966.

The Sky Blue/White/Gum colorway of the adidas Gazelle features an upper where the base and overlays at the eyestays and T-toe are constructed of Sky Blue suede. Sky Blue laces cross over a molded tongue with debossed trefoil branding. The soft textile Sky Blue sock liner and padded collar enhance comfort. White leather accents adorn this upper in the form of the iconic serrated three stripes on the side panel and a heel tab stamped with a Sky Blue trefoil. A dark gum cupsole offers low-to-the-ground cushioning and traction.

The detail of this sneaker that we most enjoy is the Gazelle branding on the side panel. The darker hue of gold complements the sole unit, tying the look of the shoe together. The adidas Gazelle Sky Blue was released on January 1, 2024, for a retail price of $100.

name: Silver Dawn Chalk
title: adidas Samba OG Silver Dawn Chalk
description:
The adidas Samba OG Silver Dawn Chalk upgrades the classic Samba OG silhouette with a suede construction and a pastel colorway of Silver Dawn and Chalk White.

The low-top Silver Dawn Chalk adidas Samba OG stays true to original Samba designs with its gum rubber outsole and sleek silhouette. However, instead of traditional orange-tinted gum rubber, the outsole comes in off-white. Soft suede in Dawn Chalk replaces the leather on the upper and overlays, which represents another contemporary update. However, smooth leather in Chalk White can be found on the heel mustache and the serrated 3-Stripes logo. Another heritage touch is the "SAMBA" lettering printed in gold foil along the 3-Stripes.

Our experts like the oversized, blue and white adidas label on the suede tongue. It stands out against the otherwise completely pastel construction. The adidas Samba OG Silver Dawn Chalk was released on April 24, 2024, and sold for $100.

name: San Francisco Giants
title: Nike SB Dunk High Pro Premium San Francisco Giants
description:
Nike SB Dunk High San Francisco Giants, style code DO9394-100, has become one of the most celebrated footwear lines in the Nike series.

Nike SB Dunk High San Francisco Giants is a product of synthetic leather at the upper and a rubber outsole. The sneaker is embellished in a coconut milk, team orange, and black colorway. It features black with an orange Swoosh across the quarter panel to the heel notch. The white midsole and black team orange at the outsole complete the sneaker's design.

Nike SB Dunk High San Francisco Giants debuted at a retail price of $125 on July 26, 2022.
model: Nike SB Dunk High Pro Premium

name: Travis Scott Cactus Trails
title: Nike Air Max 270 React ENG Travis Scott Cactus Trails
description:
Nike and Travis Scott teamed up once again to deliver the Nike Air Max 270 React Travis Scott, now available on StockX. This is the first time La Flame has put his signature touch on an Air Max silhouette.

This Air Max 270 consists of a mesh upper with tumblr leather and suede overlays. A gold midsole, green tongue with attached lace locks, and Cactus Jack branding on the heel tabs completes the design. These sneakers released in May of 2020 and retailed for $170.

name: Sunset
title: Nike Mercurial Vapor 15 Elite FG x Air Max Plus Sunset
description:
The Nike Mercurial Vapor 15 Elite FG x Air Max Plus Sunset turns the recognizable Vapor 15 into a soccer cleat. It features a vibrant colorway of Pimento that appears to fade from bright orange to red-orange.

What makes this sneaker stand out is the series of lines that form a cage over the upper. These lines are a signature design element of Air Max Plus sneakers and often represent palm trees or flames. A ¾-length Zoom Air unit underfoot provides comfort and responsive cushioning, while tri-star studs offer multi-directional traction. The upper is crafted from Vaporposite+, which is a mesh-like material that molds to the foot’s shape without feeling restrictive. This sneaker was designed for damp pitches with short grass.

Our experts at StockX like the splash of color provided by the crimson Swoosh logos on the side panels. The Nike Mercurial Vapor 15 Elite FG x Air Max Plus Sunset was released on March 14, 2024, and retailed at $285.
model: Nike Mercurial Vapor 15 Elite FG x Air Max Plus

name: Fir Midnight Navy
title: Nike Dunk Low Fir Midnight Navy
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Fir Midnight Navy is a low-top sneaker with a color scheme inspired by the Christmas season.

This iteration of the Nike Dunk Low features an all-leather upper, the base of which is white. The toebox is perforated for breathability and air flow, and Fir Green overlays round out the toebox, under the laces, and appear running from the ankle down around the heel. The Nike Swoosh adorns both sides of the shoe in Midnight Navy. The heel collar is also Midnight Navy and contains a University Gold embroidery of the Nike brand name. There is a Nike patch on the tongue and the outsole is made of white and Midnight Navy.

What we like most about this shoe is the white, Fir Green, and Midnight Navy color scheme. The white provides welcome brightness against the darker colors. The Nike Dunk Low Fir Midnight Navy was released on December 5, 2023, for a retail price of $115.

name: Silver Metallic Nightwatch Green
title: New Balance 1906R Silver Metallic Nightwatch Green
description:
Inspired by the running shoe aesthetic of the early 2000s, the New Balance 1906R Silver Metallic Nightwatch Green sneakers are a great lifestyle shoe designed for long-wear comfort, durability, and style. These New Balance sneakers are made with mesh for breathability and a lightweight step, making them perfect for long-wear jobs and light sports.

With a white base, the silver overlays are durable and give the shoe a sheen, while the Nightwatch Green adds a sophisticated accent. The famous "N" logo sits on the outside of the shoe on both sides, while the 1906R branding sits on the back outside the heel of each sneaker. The midsole comprises N-ERGY cushioning ABZORB for a lighter, bouncy step, and the outsoles come standard with rubber for excellent traction.

We love the busy colorways and overlays on this shoe, which give it a running shoe appearance despite being more for everyday use. The New Balance 1906R Silver Metallic Nightwatch Green was released on September 6, 2024, for $155.

name: Black Coffee Silver
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Black Coffee Silver
description:
Iconic running shoes that throw a style nod back to the original Kayanos from the 2000s, these ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Black Coffee Silver deliver superior gel cushioning and midsole support for your most comfortable run yet.

The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 bring a layered mesh and leather upper, gel cushioned midsole, and an advanced TRUSSTIC™ support system for supreme bounce and support. The shoes boast signature tiger stripes, a rounded toe, a front lace enclosure, and a branded insole in a unique black, coffee brown, and silver color palette. The rubber outsole provides extreme traction for the slipperiest of surfaces. The Asics logo sits on the tongue, while the Gel logo sits on the heel pad.

These ASICS Gel-Kayano sneakers are favorites with us for their sophisticated color combo, creating a highly stylish pair of shoes that takes running into spaces of leisure with ease. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Black Coffee Silver sneakers were released on 1 August 2022, priced at $150.

name: Ivy Smoke Grey
title: ASICS Gel-NYC Ivy Smoke Grey
description:
The ASICS Gel-NYC Ivy Smoke Grey is a performance shoe whose design was inspired by the 2000s running aesthetic but still has advanced technology.

This iteration of the ASICS Gel-NYC is made with a dark gray mesh base for breathability. This material forms the toe box and is revealed under the overlays across the midsole and heel. Ivy green and gray suede overlays adorn the shoe. Ivy suede forms the toe cap and mudguard, snaking around and up the heel, while gray overlays connect the toe cap to the laces and run underneath the ASICS logo on the sides. The ASICS design appears on each side in white. The word GEL appears on the heel, and the ASICS brand name appears on the lateral heel on the green overlay. The tongue is also branded. An off-white textured outsole features Gel technology for support and cushioning.

What stands out about this shoe is the unique shapes of the Ivy green suede overlays, as they add visual interest. The ASICS Gel-NYC Ivy Smoke Grey was released on January 1, 2024, for $130.

name: White Black
title: Nike Air Zoom Tiger Woods 20 White Black
description:
With its dress-shoe aesthetic and hi-tech comfort, the Nike Air Zoom Tiger Woods 20 White Black delivers both style and performance on the golf course.

The White Black iteration of the Tiger Woods x Nike Air Zoom 20 sports a lightweight smooth white synthetic leather upper with perforations for breathability at the collar. A shiny black synthetic Nike swoosh courses across the quarter panel and complements the top-most eye stay. Red Tiger Woods branding adorns the heel tab. White laces cross over a foam-padded tongue that provides comfort, along with the foam-padded collar and sock liner. The removable spikes on the translucent white outsole with red Tiger Woods branding provide optimal grip on the green.

What we appreciate most about this pair of golf shoes is the sole unit that provides durable comfort and support. The midsole features Nike React technology for cushioning and smooth energy return. The Nike Air Zoom Tiger Woods 20 White Black was released on January 14, 2021, for $150 retail.

name: White Game Royal Photon Dust
title: Nike Air Max 90 White Game Royal Photon Dust
description:
The Nike Air Max 90 White Game Royal Photon Dust updates the original running shoe from the 1990s with a Crisp White base that features Photon Dust and Game Royal accents.

Like other versions of the Air Max 90, the "White Game Royal Photon Dust" iteration houses visible Air Max units in the heel. Providing traction and durability, the rubber outsole comes with a waffle design that was inspired by the grid-like pattern on a waffle iron. The upper is made of a combination of leather and synthetic materials with reinforced stitching. The stitched overlays and the plastic surrounding the eyelets contributes to the sneaker’s overall durability.

Our StockX experts like the Game Royal accents, which can be found on tongue’s logo tag, the ‘AIR MAX’ lettering on the side panel, the insole, the midsole, and the Swoosh. The Nike Air Max 90 White Game Royal Photon Dust was released on August 3rd, 2023, and retailed at $140.

name: Castlerock Black
title: New Balance 2002R Castlerock Black
description:
The New Balance 2002R Castlerock Black combines retro aesthetics with modern performance features.

This shoe features a classic silhouette with contemporary design elements. The upper is crafted from a combination of premium suede and mesh to provide durability and breathability. An ABZORB midsole provides exceptional shock absorption, reducing the impact on the feet and joints, while an Ortholite insert offers additional cushioning and support. Despite its retro-inspired design, the 2002R is also equipped with modern performance features such as an Ndurance rubber outsole that delivers superior traction and durability, and ENCAP technology in the midsole which provides stability and support for all-day comfort.

What our experts especially enjoy about the New Balance 2002R Castlerock Black, however, is its sleek black colorway which makes it a neutral and versatile addition to any wardrobe. This shoe originally retailed for $150 when it was first released on October 17, 2023.

name: Triple Black
title: adidas Ultra Boost Light Triple Black
description:
The adidas Ultra Boost Light Triple Black is a performance shoe designed for lightness and energy return.

This iteration of the adidas Ultra Boost Light is made with a Primeknit and textile upper to make the shoe lightweight and breathable. The upper is all black and is made partially from recycled material. The adidas three stripes logo appears on each side, running from the laces to the outsole in black. The three stripes’ construction also serves to support and stabilize the shoe. The tongue sports another adidas logo, and a thick black sole and outsole provide energy return. The shoe is equipped with Boost suspension technology and the Linear Energy Push system for extra performance enhancement.

What we like most about this shoe is the combination of lightweight materials used to build it. It provides not only comfort but also functionality. The adidas Ultra Boost Light Triple Black was released on January 3, 2024, for an initial retail price of $190.

name: White Black
title: adidas Superstar White Black
description: The adidas Superstar White Black is a classic sneaker that has been updated for modern times. This shoe features a white leather upper with black accents on the stripes and heel tab. The iconic shell toe is also present, giving the shoe its signature look. The original release date for this shoe was December 1st, 2019, and it retailed for $80. The materials used in the construction of this shoe are high-quality, ensuring durability and comfort. The adidas Superstar White Black is a versatile shoe that can be worn with a variety of outfits, making it a great addition to any sneaker collection.

name: Sea Salt Pack Black
title: New Balance 550 Sea Salt Pack Black
description:
The New Balance 550 Sea Salt Pack Black channels a vintage basketball image from the 80s while presenting in a sea salt and black color combination.

The 550 from New Balance is regularly updated, and new colorways are always appearing. This black iteration is one of four colorways that were released as part of the "Sea Salt" pack to pay homage to the sea, sand, and summer. The upper aims to provide breathability through the mesh toe box and perforated side panels. The sea salt colored base lends way to black accents throughout the shoe, which usually present as New Balance branding hits such as the puffy large Ns on the side panels.

What we love about the New Balance 550 Sea Salt Pack Black is its chunky midsole in an off-white color. It adds a retro vibe and adds an air of casualness. This shoe entered the marketplace on May 24, 2024, with a retail price of $110.

name: Cinder
title: adidas Yeezy 450 Cinder
description:
In a dark brown, monochromatic styling, the adidas Yeezy 450 Cinder utilizes a minimalist two-piece construction to achieve the futurist aesthetic Yeezy has displayed in their most recent silhouettes. A foam sole encompasses a matching sock-like Primeknit upper in a claw-like fashion. Thick rope laces and sock-like collars provide a secure fit.

The adidas Yeezy 450 Cinder released in March of 2022 and retailed for $200.

name: Silver Pebble (Women's)
title: adidas Handball Spezial Silver Pebble (Women's)
description:
The adidas Handball Spezial Silver Pebble (Women's) is a shoe made for women that’s made in Italy with the handball style in mind.

This iteration of the adidas Handball Spezial comes with an upper constructed with suede in a Silver Pebble color. The base is made of this material as well as the overlays that form the thin t-shaped toe cap, eyestays, and heel counter. The adidas 3-Stripes appear as leather overlays in white on each side, and the heel collar is also white leather. The Spezial brand name adorns the outer side alongside the trefoil logo in white. adidas Handball Spezial branding is also found on the tongue. The shoe sits on a thick, branded rubber midsole and outsole.

What stands out about this shoe is the overall suede construction, which makes the shoe visually interesting. The adidas Handball Spezial Silver Pebble (Women's) was released on May 1, 2024, for $110.

name: Triple White
title: adidas Ultra Boost Light Triple White
description:
The adidas Ultra Boost Light Triple White is a running shoe specifically designed to deliver lightweight, snug, flexible, and cushioning energy return with every step.

The Triple White adidas Boost Light features an upper with a base of white adidas PRIMEKNIT for a snug, lightweight fit around the foot. The adidas three stripes on the side panel appear in a smooth white textile overlay that works itself into the eye stays. White laces cross over a white mesh tongue with adidas branding. A smooth white molded heel counter and toe cap add support. A white stacked Boost midsole delivers ultra-lightweight cushioning and energy return with every step. An outsole of black Continental rubber provides traction on many kinds of surfaces.

The feature that delights us most about this shoe is the incorporation of recycled material from Parley Ocean Plastic into the upper. The adidas Ultra Boost Light Triple White was released on January 28, 2023, for a retail price of $190.

name: Enflame Orange
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Enflame Orange
description:
DISCLAIMER: US and UK sizing is the same and does not require any conversion.

The adidas Yeezy Slide Enflame Orange features Enflame Orange EVA foam construction with a soft footbed that offers an immediate step-in comfort. An outsole with accentuated grooves for traction and support completes the design.

The adidas Yeezy Slide Enflame Orange released in June of 2021 and retailed for $60.

name: Yeezreel (Non-Reflective)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Yeezreel (Non-Reflective)
description:
Preceding its reflective counterpart, Yeezy released the adidas Yeezy 350 Yeezreel Non-Reflective, now available on StockX. This 350 V2 is reminiscent of the Glow colorway that released in early 2019, but sets itself apart with the addition of new tones woven in the Primeknit upper. This model was released in both reflective and non-reflective variations.

This Yeezy 350 V2 is composed of a Yeezreel upper and with black and grey accents ingrained in the upper. A translucent Yeezreel Boost cushioned sole and side stripe completes the design. These sneakers released in December of 2019 and retailed for $250.

name: Kith Cream Scarab (2024)
title: ASICS GT-2160 Kith Cream Scarab (2024)
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 Kith Cream Scarab (2024) is a reissue of the ASICS GT-2160 created in partnership with New York City-based lifestyle brand Kith.

In keeping with Kith’s house codes, this technical running shoe boasts a Cream base with synthetic leather overlays in dark Green Scarab and metallic silver. Covering the side panels, the signature ASICS tiger stripes come in the same tones and support the mesh upper. The ultra-lightweight EVA midsole offers comfort, while the Gel insert absorbs shock beneath the heel. Completing the technical look, the durable rubber outsole features an advanced traction pattern and houses a TPU shank. This shank increases stability in the midfoot without weighing down the shoe.

Our experts at StockX appreciate the way the streamlined silhouette and the subtle colorway complement each other. The ASICS GT-2160 Kith Cream Scarab (2024) was released on March 28, 2024, and sold for $140.

name: Cheetos
title: Puma Scoot Zeros Cheetos
description:
The Puma Scoot Zeros Cheetos is a basketball shoe whose design was inspired by the popular snack Cheetos.

This version of the Puma Scoot Zeros is constructed with a textile upper. This material forms the sides in different shades of orange and red, with black spots of different sizes. Some black textiles are also around the bottom of the laces for breathability. The toe box is formed by a jagged orange overlay outlined in yellow, representing a flame. Orange overlays also attach the laces to the sole on the inner side. On the lateral side, we see a flame outlined in yellow, revealing red textiles with spots underneath. The heel is also formed by an orange overlay with a flame printed on the inner side. The heel also features a pull tab with a black Puma logo, while the tongue features a Scoot logo and an orange Puma. An orange and red sole and outsole complete the look.

Our favorite thing about this shoe is the minimal Puma branding elements, as these really let the Cheetos design take the stage. The Puma Scoot Zeros Cheetos was released on February 16, 2024, for $110.

name: Valentine's Day (2024) (Women's)
title: adidas Gazelle Valentine's Day (2024) (Women's)
description:
The adidas Gazelle Valentine’s Day (2024) (Women’s) is a women’s shoe with a soft design tha is meant to pay homage to Valentine’s Day and Saint Valentine.

This iteration of the adidas Gazelle comes with a soft nubuck upper in a soft pink color. The toecap overlay stays consistent with this material and color. The adidas three stripes appear on the midsoles in white leather, while the word "GAZELLE" appears in gold lettering above the first stripe on the lateral side. White leather also forms the heel collar, and the adidas trefoil logo is imprinted on in Putty Mauve. The tongue features an adidas logo in the same color, and heart-shaped eyelets appear at the top of the laces. The look is completed by a gum rubber outsole.

What we like most about this shoe are the heart-shaped eyelets. This element makes the subtle design pop a little more. The adidas Gazelle Valentine’s Day (2024) (Women’s) was released on January 15, 2024, for a price of $100.

name: White Malachite Green (Women's)
title: ASICS Gel-1130 White Malachite Green (Women's)
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 White Malachite Green (Women's) is a sneaker sized for women with a bright colorway and equipped with Gel technology.
  
The White Malachite Green (Women's) ASICS Gel-1130 features an upper made of white mesh for extra airflow. White synthetic leather forms the toe cap and part of the eyestays, and also curves from the eyestays around to the heel. The ASICS logo appears on each side of the shoe in white and Malachite Green, adding a pop of color. The eyestays and toe cap are accented with tan overlays, and Malachite Green accents form Gel branding on the curved overlay of the heel as well as on the tongue. These branding elements are also accented with metallic silver. The white midsole contains green Gel technology, and the shoe rests on a black outsole.
 
What we appreciate most about this shoe is the Malachite Green accenting, which adds a nice pop of color and makes the shoe perfect for spring. The ASICS Gel-1130 White Malachite Green (Women's) was released on January 10, 2024, for $100.

name: MiUSA Action Bronson Lapis Lazuli
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Action Bronson Lapis Lazuli
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Action Bronson Lapis Lazuli is a collaboratively designed sneaker release from New Balance and rapper Action Bronson. This shoe is part of the New Balance 990 line, which has been around since 1982.

The 990v6 MiUSA Action Bronson in Lapis Lazuli has an Eclipse and Popcorn colorway and features New Balance branding on both sides. The sneaker has a dual-density foam midsole that is a combination of a softer foam layer at the top and a firmer layer at the bottom, which provides a balance of soft comfort and firm support.

We especially love the New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Action Bronson Lapis Lazuli for its craftsmanship. The use of suede from the toe box to the heel provides extra protection and reinforcement for the areas that see the most wear and tear. A large portion of the upper is also made from mesh, which allows air to circulate within the shoe and keep the foot cool and dry. The sneaker debuted on June 22nd, 2023, and retailed for $220.

name: Pale Oak Grand Shark
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Pale Oak Grand Shark
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 Pale Oak Grand Shark combines retro aesthetics with modern functionality. This reimagined sneaker was inspired by late 2000s runners and offers a blend of age-old design and cutting-edge performance that appeals to athletes and casual wearers.

The Pale Oak and Grand Shark Gel-1130 by ASICS has a mesh upper with synthetic leather overlays. Its color palette integrates earthy Pale Oak tones with bold Grand Shark accents for contrast. The GEL® technology gives you superior cushioning, while the TRUSSTIC® system improves midfoot stability. Originally inspired by the GEL-KAYANO® 14, this model updates ASICS' running heritage with sustainable elements like dope-dyed sock liners that reduce water usage and emissions.

As experts, we enjoy the ASICS Gel-1130 Pale Oak Grand Shark's GEL® cushioning technology, which guarantees impact absorption for smooth transitions. Another standout is the TRUSSTIC® system for excellent structural support. Released on August 1, 2024, it retailed for $100.

name: Cream Caramel
title: Onitsuka Tiger Tokuten Cream Caramel
description:
High-fashion kicks don’t come cooler than the Onitsuka Tiger Tokuten Cream Caramel. The Japanese fashion brand offers a comfortable lifestyle shoe ready to elevate your footwear wardrobe.

Made from calf leather, synthetic leather, and canvas, the Totukens from the Onitsuka Tiger brand are one good-looking shoe. With a regular height midsole for support and rubber outsole for traction, the sophisticated blend of caramel and cream coloring is an earthy, trendy addition to your sneaker collection. Perfect for all seasons, the lace enclosure has cream-colored laces with branding on the tongue. Simple, classic, and elegant while still paying homage to the sports legacy that Onitsuka Tiger honors.

We love how this heritage brand has created a low-profile shoe that is contemporary and functional, all in one. Wear them casually or to give an edge to a smart outfit. The Onitsuka Tiger Tokuten Cream Caramel was released on 26 January 2022, priced at $70.

name: White Solar Red Gum (Women's)
title: adidas Samba OG White Solar Red Gum (Women's)
description:
The adidas Samba OG White Solar Red Gum (Women's) reimagines a silhouette originally designed for indoor soccer and gives it a street style that makes it a fashion icon.

This low-top in a crisp dual colorway features an upper of smooth white leather at the base and the eye stay overlays. Red leather forms the heel tab, as well as the iconic serrated three stripes that course up the side panel. The leather tongue features a red tag that sports adidas trefoil branding. Samba branding hits the lateral side panel just above the third stripe. The collar is padded to enhance ankle comfort, and the insole is white with red adidas trefoil branding. The gum rubber sole unit is reinforced for durability.

The standout aspect of the women's sneaker that we most enjoy is the T-toe overlay. In darker white nubuck, it adds a note of contrast to this shoe. The adidas Samba OG White Solar Red Gum (Women's) was released on November 19, 2023, for a retail price of $100.

name: The Grinch Cindy-Lou Who (Women's)
title: adidas Forum Low The Grinch Cindy-Lou Who (Women's)
description:
The adidas Forum Low The Grinch Cindy-Lou Who (Women's) covers the Forum Low’s basketball-inspired silhouette with an all-over bright colorway of Bliss Pink and Bright Red.

Released in time for the Christmas season, this low-top sneaker pays tribute to Cindy Lou Who, a character in "How The Grinch Stole Christmas" by Dr. Seuss. The Bliss Pink and Bright Red colorway references the holiday dress and bow Cindy Lou Who wears in the beloved Christmas book and The Grinch (2018). The premium hairy suede upper in Bliss Pink complements the splashes of Bright Red on the 3-Stripes logo and the tongue’s ‘adidas’ logo tag. Lace jewels, including a wreath, a likeness of Cindy-Lou Who, a stack of gifts, and an ornament, give the sneaker a customized look.

Our experts at StockX like the ‘THE GRINCH’ branding on the insole because it includes the Grinch’s eyes, which appear to peek out of the shoe. The women’s size adidas Forum Low The Grinch Cindy-Lou Who (Women's) was released on December 1, 2023, and sold for $130.

name: Wonder Taupe (Women's)
title: adidas Samba OG Wonder Taupe (Women's)
description:
The adidas Samba OG Wonder Taupe (Women's), in women’s sizes, is a lifestyle athletic shoe featuring a leather and suede upper in Wonder Taupe’s beige hue, accented by adidas’ signature three stripes in Footwear White. The three stripes are highlighted by Gold Metallic Samba branding, which coordinates with the tongue branding. The Footwear White heel tab and gum rubber sole tie the look together.

Part of the adidas roster since 1949, the Samba’s enduring silhouette was designed by Adolf Dassler, founder of German athletic wear brand adidas. The Samba has gone on to be produced in various iterations, and part of the lore of its iconic status is its presence in major motion pictures and TV series.

In our opinion, the best feature of the Samba OG Wonder Taupe is its neutral color palette, which is stylish and versatile. The adidas Samba OG Wonder Taupe (Women's) released on September 1, 2024, and retailed at $100.

name: Paris
title: ASICS Superblast 2 Paris
description:
The ASICS Superblast 2 Paris is a high-octane cushioned, comfortable runner that sports a colorway inspired by the dynamic hues of a Paris sunset and sunrise.

The upper of the Paris ASICS Superblast 2 running shoe is crafted from gray mesh designed to enhance air flow and increase overall foot comfort. The gusseted tongue wing fit system is also gray and designed to improve the fit across the midfoot and to reduce the chances of the tongue sliding around. The black ASICS stripes bleed on to the yellow and Melon midsole composed of FF TURBO PLUS and FF BLAST PLUS cushioning. The ASICSGRIP outsole in yellow and Melon is inspired by trampoline design to offer ultimate responsive bounce back with every step.

Our favorite detail on this pair of kicks are the reflective hits that pepper the upper, allowing you to get your steps in even in low-light conditions. The ASICS Superblast 2 Paris was released on June 25, 2024, for $200 retail.

name: Triple Black
title: New Balance 550 Triple Black
description:
The New Balance 550 Triple Black, made out of a combination of leather and mesh, comes in an all-black color theme. The smooth leather covers the upper while the mesh is maintained at the tongue and collar.

The black tone also extends to the sole unit, insoles, laces, and lining. Branding elements for the sneaker include a tag on the tongue, the "N" symbol patches on the sides, a protruding "new balance" logo on the accented grey midsole, and a signature symbol at the rear. The midsole is made from EVA foam for cushioning.

The New Balance 550 Triple Black was made available on November 3rd, 2022, and retailed at $99.

name: White Scarlet Navy
title: adidas Continental 80 White Scarlet Navy
description:
The adidas Continental 80 White Scarlet Navy has a white sole and midsole, as well as a white base. While the sole and midsole of the sneaker are made from rubber, the body of the shoe is primarily composed of leather.

The Continental 80 has French terry lining. On the side of the shoe, there are two thin strips in bright red and navy blue colors. The adidas name is written on the side of the shoe in navy with the logo displayed in red.

The adidas Continental 80 White Scarlet Navy first became available for purchase in January of 2019. This pair of sneakers had a starting retail price of $80.

name: Shadow Violet (Women's)
title: adidas Campus 00s Shadow Violet (Women's)
description:
The adidas Campus 00s Shadow Violet (Women's) upgrades the original Campus from the 1980s with design elements inspired by sneakers from the early 2000s.

Specifically, the bulky silhouette, created by the pillowy tongue and padding around the heel, gives the Campus 00s Shadow Violet a 2000s skateboarding shoe appearance. This model comes in an understated colorway of Shadow Violet with Cloud White detailing. For example, the suede upper and tonal overlays come in Shadow Violet, while the serrated 3-Stripes, the trefoil on the heel tab, and the adidas logo on the tongue boast Cloud White. Although there are no perforations on the toebox, two lines of perforations run up the side panels. This feature allows the foot to breathe.

Our StockX experts like the ‘CAMPUS’ lettering, which can only be found on the lateral side panel. The women’s size adidas Campus 00s Shadow Violet (Women's) was released on November 14th, 2023, and retailed at $110.

name: Blue Hive
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Blue Hive
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Blue Hive is a basketball shoe with a slime-inspired look designed as a collaboration with Charlotte Hornets star LaMelo Ball.

This version of the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 is made with a breathable knit textile upper. Most of the upper appears in black, while jagged scratches reveal Electric Peppermint blue underneath. A synthetic black mudguard rounds out the toe box and features "DiP" in red on the inner forefoot. The cushioned heel is black and bears Puma branding in blue as well as LaMelo Ball branding as it features "M.E.L.O" and "01ofOne" in red. The tongue also features bold branding elements and the words "Not From Here" appear at the bottom of the laces. A black-speckled rubber sole and an Electric Peppermint blue outsole bleed up onto the body of the shoe in a slime-like design.

Our favorite feature of this shoe is that the midsole is infused with NITRO nitrogen-injected foam in order to provide lightweight cushioning and responsiveness. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Blue Hive was released on December 8, 2023, for $130.

name: Moonbeam Black Gum (Women's)
title: New Balance 327 Moonbeam Black Gum (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 327 Moonbeam Black Gum (Women's) is a lifestyle shoe with a low-top profile that features an outsole that extends to the heel counter and toe tip.

This Moonbeam Black Gum colorway is from the New Balance 327 line and presents in women’s sizing. It is a stylish silhouette that provides stability and comfort, making it an everyday staple for any closet. The faux leather upper is in white while moonbeam-colored overlays adorn the toe area, eyelet, and heel area. The soft neutrals are elegant and a bold textured branding hit in the form of a large, black "N" adorns the lateral side.

Our experts think that the bubble-wrap like outsole that creeps up to the heel is what makes the New Balance 327 Moonbeam Black Gum (Women's) standout. The distinctive design is eye-catching, and the lugs provide well-needed traction. When it debuted on March 21, 2024, this sneaker had a $100 price tag.

name: Grey Matter Timberwolf
title: New Balance 9060 Grey Matter Timberwolf
description:
The New Balance 9060 Grey Matter Timberwolf is inspired by the Y2K era's modern look. 

The off-white mesh makes up the upper, and cream and colorless leather makes up the overlays. It has a dual-density midsole with SBS and ABZORB cushioning, while its heel features a translucent CR device. Completing the sneaker’s appearance is the tongue logo inspired by the original 991 lace jewel, the "N" logo in off-white on the side and in brown on the outsole tip. Further details of the sneaker include traces of brown and mossy green color schemes. The flat lace closure and padded tongue, meanwhile, ensure a snug fit. 

The New Balance 9060 Grey Matter Timberwolf was released on 3rd February 2023 and retailed at $150.

name: Solar Energy Pack
title: adidas Predator Elite Foldover Tongue FG Solar Energy Pack
description:
Designed for speed, the adidas Predator Elite Foldover Tongue F Solar Energy Pack is a football cleat with a variety of performance-enhancing features.

The sneaker boasts a HybridTouch 2.0 upper, which has a PrimeKnit collar that comes in two pieces. The durable PrimeKnit conforms to the foot’s shape and provides an airy feel. The upper also features fins made of rubber Strikeskin, a material that adds grip and supports precision shooting. Another noteworthy technical feature is the Controlfame 2.0 outsole, which is designed for play on soft ground. In terms of style, the cleat features an oversized tongue in Solar Red that folds over the lace cage. While the base comes in Core Black, the exaggerated 3-Stripes logo features Cloud White.

Our experts like the swirling pattern on the Solar Red and Cloud White outsole. The adidas Predator Elite Foldover Tongue F Solar Energy Pack was released on February 27th, 2024, and retailed at $280.
model: adidas Predator Elite Foldover Tongue FG

name: White Feather Grey
title: ASICS Gel-NYC White Feather Grey
description:
The ASICS Gel-NYC White Feather Grey is a stylish and comfortable sneaker that combines modern design with classic ASICS technology. Featuring a sleek white upper with subtle feather grey accents, this shoe offers a versatile look that can easily transition from casual to athletic wear. The Gel-NYC model incorporates ASICS' renowned GEL cushioning system in the midsole, providing superior shock absorption and comfort for all-day wear.

Built with premium materials, the Gel-NYC boasts a durable construction that can withstand daily use while maintaining its appealing aesthetic. The breathable mesh upper ensures proper ventilation, keeping your feet cool and dry during various activities. With its ergonomic design and supportive fit, this sneaker is ideal for both urban exploration and light athletic pursuits. Our experts state this product is great for those seeking a balance of style and functionality in their everyday footwear.

name: MiUK Stone Island Black
title: New Balance 991v2 MiUK Stone Island Black
description:
The New Balance 991v2 MiUK Stone Island Black is part of a collaboration between New Balance and Stone Island, a high-end Italian label known for its innovative, research-based designs. This sneaker also represents the debut of the 991v2 silhouette.

While many New Balance sneakers are designated as ‘made in USA,’ the Stone Island Black bears the name MiUK or made in UK. The sneaker features a dark, understated color palette of Black, Olive, and Grey. While tactical mesh composes the base, suede overlays wrap around the upper and form a lace-up closure. The New Balance ‘N’ can be found on the suede overlays, while Stone Island’s compass logo is stitched into the tongue.

Our StockX experts love the subtle details that make this sneaker stand out, including the oversized compass on the outsole. The New Balance 991v2 MiUK Stone Island Black was released on October 5, 2023, and retailed at $270.

name: Mist
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Mist
description:
Yeezy added a new colorway to their Boost 380 product line with the adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Mist, now available on StockX. This model was originally known to be the Yeezy Boost 350 V3, but upon release it was given its own silhouette name. The mist colorway released in both reflective and non-reflective variations.

This 380 Mist features a Mist Primeknit pattern on its upper and lacks the traditional lateral side stripe. An upgraded translucent Boost midsole and engineered gum outsole grip complete the design. These sneakers released in March of 2020 and retailed for $230.

name: Grey
title: adidas Ultra Boost 1.0 DNA Grey
description:
The adidas Ultra Boost 1.0 DNA Grey is a running shoe from the adidas Ultra Boost 1.0 DNA lineup in a gray colorway.

This Ultra Boost sneaker features a PrimeKnit upper dressed in Gray Three and Gray Five with Core Black detailing. A gray lace cage with contrasting Three stripes and a TPU heel counter with "Ultra-Boost" lettering etched on the lateral provide support to the upper. Other details include the adidas mountain logo on the tongue, gray laces, and a padded ankle collar. Underfoot, a white Boost midsole and a black rubber outsole complete the design.

  What our experts particularly love about this Ultra Boost sneaker is its classic yet versatile colorway and the combination of comfort and style it offers.
