Its timeless colorway and performance-oriented design contribute to its standout nature, appealing to individuals seeking a blend of style and functionality in a sneaker. The adidas Ultra Boost 1.0 DNA Gray was released on November 30th, 2022, retailing at $200.

name: Resin
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Resin
description:
DISCLAIMER: US and UK sizing is the same and does not require any conversion.

The adidas Yeezy Slide Resin is made of Resin EVA foam throughout the design to provide lightweight durability. From there, a soft footbed offers an immediate step in comfort. An outsole with accentuated grooves for traction and support wraps the design.

The adidas Yeezy Slide Resin released in April of 2021 and retailed for $60.

name: Song For The Mute Maroon
title: adidas Country OG Song For The Mute Maroon
description:
The adidas Country OG Song For The Mute Maroon redefines retro-inspired sneakers with a unique collaboration. Released in Fall of 2024, this design blends premium fabrics with muted tones and experimental aesthetics.

The Song For The Mute Maroon Country OG by adidas combines maroon suede with cream accents for a balanced look. Its signature serrated 3-Stripes detailing appears in brown suede along both sides, contrasting the maroon upper. A lightweight EVA midsole gives extra comfort, while the gum rubber outsole adds traction. Song For The Mute, founded in 2010 by Melvin Tanaya and Lyna Ty, is celebrated for combining storytelling and innovative fashion.

One thing we like about the adidas Country OG Song For The Mute Maroon is the carefully crafted suede upper that offers some depth in texture. Another standout detail is the gum outsole, which gives you better traction on various surfaces. This sneaker retailed at $140 when it was released on November 16, 2024.

name: White Gum
title: New Balance 550 White Gum
description:
The New Balance 550 White Gum comes in a white, gum colorway.

The New Balance 550 White Gum features an upper composed of a lightweight textile material that provides permeability and ventilation. The shoe's midsole features compression-molded EVA foam, which offers padding and impact attenuation. The outsole of the shoe is composed of rubber for grip and balance. The shoe features an "N" logo on the sides, "550" lettering on one side, and "NB" branding on the heel. The shoe's midsole features "NB new balance" on one side. The design is completed with a "new balance 550 NB" lettering on the tongue.

The New Balance 550 White Gum was released on November 1, 2022, and retailed for $120.

name: Grey
title: New Balance 9060 Grey
description:
The New Balance 9060 Grey combines innovative design with a heritage-inspired profile. Perfectly blending modern aesthetics and performance, it highlights New Balance's legacy in creating adaptable and trendy trainers. Explore how this release redefines comfort and style.

The Grey 9060 by New Balance for women features a breathable mesh upper with suede overlays in muted grey tones, which gives it a layered texture look and feel. The sculpted midsole uses ABZORB and SBS cushioning for improved responsiveness. Reflective accents on the "N" logo add extra visibility, while the exaggerated outsole tips its hat to the brand’s early 2000s running designs. The outsole comes with a herringbone tread pattern that gives you multidirectional traction.

As the experts, something we love about the New Balance 9060 Grey is how the sole is designed to offer maximum stability during quick movements and how the combination of herringbone and circular lugs on the outsole give you exceptional traction on most surfaces. Released on 1st June 2024, this versatile trainer retailed at $150.

name: Sulfur
title: adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Boot Sulfur
description:
With a cast-like construction, the adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Boot Sulfur features a woven upper with a two-way velcro enclosure. The base of the Knit RNR Boot mimics the original Knit RNR Sulfur, a low-top slip-on Yeezy that debuted earlier in the fall of 2021. From there, a sculptural sole with accentuated treads completes the design.

The adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Boot Sulfur released in November of 2021 and retailed for $400.

name: Chalky Brown Clear Pink (Women's)
title: adidas Handball Spezial Chalky Brown Clear Pink (Women's)
description:
The adidas Handball Spezial Chalky & Brown Clear Pink (Women's) blends classic design with trendy updates. Made with premium materials, this trainer stays true to the Handball Spezial's vintage roots while giving you an eye-catching color combination and age-old functionality for daily wear.

The Chalky Brown & Clear Pink Handball Spezial for women features a soft suede upper in earthy chalky brown tones, accented with subtle clear pink details on the 3-Stripes. It was originally designed for indoor handball in the late 1970s and still maintains its root charm with a gum rubber outsole for traction. Additional stitching and textured overlays improve its durability, while the lace-up design gives you a snug fit.

As the experts, one thing we appreciate about the adidas Handball Spezial Chalky & Brown Clear Pink (Women's) is the rich suede upper, which adds a premium feel to the design. Additionally, the gum sole offers a reliable grip, so it's stylish and practical. This trainer retailed at $110 when it was released on 7th October 2024​.​

name: Junya Watanabe MAN Black
title: New Balance 1906L Junya Watanabe MAN Black
description:
The New Balance 1906L Junya Watanabe MAN Black is a loafer designed as a collaboration between New Balance and Japanese fashion designer Junya Watanabe.

The Junya Watanabe MAN Black New Balance 1906L is made with a mixture of artificial leather and calf leather on the upper. The top of the toe, the tongue, and the forefoot strap are all smooth black leather, while shiny black overlays run around the toe cap, sides, and heel in typical New Balance sneaker fashion. 1906L branding is seen on the outer heel, while Junya Watanabe MAN branding appears on the tongue. The slip-on shoe has a black midsole and outsole, and ABZORB capsules are found in the heel for comfort.

Our favorite thing about this shoe is the mix of loafer and sneaker, which is tastefully done. The New Balance 1906L Junya Watanabe MAN Black was released on October 18, 2024, for $252.

name: Brighton Grey
title: New Balance 1906R Brighton Grey
description:
The New Balance 1906R Brighton Grey updates the 1906R with a grayscale colorway of black, steel, and Brighton Grey.

This early 2000s-inspired running sneaker boasts a low-top design with a polyester mesh upper in Brighton Grey. Featuring a crisscrossing design, the synthetic overlays come in Brighton Grey, dark gray, and black. The overlays across the heel have a shine that makes them look like patent leather. The EVA foam midsole houses N-ergy cushioning that protects against impact and adds a bulky aesthetic to the sneaker. The padded collar and tongue also contribute to the sneaker’s bulky silhouette. Finally, an Ndurance rubber outsole features a collection of pods and traction patterns that grip the ground.

Our StockX experts like the boxy Brighton Grey "N" logo on the side panel, which features a black outline. The New Balance 1906R Brighton Grey was released on October 14, 2023, and retailed at $155.

name: White Halo Blue
title: adidas Samba OG White Halo Blue
description:
The adidas Samba OG White Halo Blue takes the recognizable Samba silhouette originally released in 1949 and updates it with a Core White, Halo Blue, and Gum 5 colorway.

This soccer training shoe features a primarily white base with light blue accents. Halo Blue tones can be found on the heel tab and in the adidas logo on the tongue. While the upper is made of smooth leather, the toe overlays come in a soft suede. Like other Samba models, the Samba OG White Halo Blue boasts 3-Stripes with serrated borders along the side panel and a sleek design without added bulkiness along the midsole or collar.

What do our StockX experts love about this sneaker? The gum sole comes in Gum 5, which is a darker color than you usually find on a Samba. The adidas Samba OG White Halo Blue was released on August 10, 2023, and retailed at $100.

name: Wales Bonner Ecrtin Brown
title: adidas Samba Wales Bonner Ecrtin Brown
description:
The adidas Samba Wales Bonner Ecrtin Brown is a collaborative project between adidas and designer Wales Bonner. This limited-edition version of the adidas Samba sneaker features unique design elements that pay homage to both Bonner's Jamaican heritage and her London upbringing.

The Samba Wales Bonner Ecrtin in Brown features a brown leather upper with contrasting Aluminum Yellow and Ecru Tint accents. The design is present with the classic T-toe overlay and suede detailing on the toe. The heel features hand-embroidered detailing while Wales Bonner branding is visible on the side.

We think that one of the most notable features of the adidas Samba Wales Bonner Ecrtin Brown is its large tongue. This unique design element adds a touch of eccentricity and individuality to the classic silhouette. The tongue is made from soft leather and is also embossed with the adidas logo. The shoe was released on June 9th, 2023 at a retail price of $180.

name: Tea Tree
title: New Balance 9060 Tea Tree
description:
The New Balance 9060 Tea Tree is a performance shoe that takes design inspiration from the classic 99X shoe, as well as the 2000s running era. 
  
The Tea Tree New Balance 9060 has an upper made of black mesh as the base. Black mesh appears on the toebox and around the ankle, while Tea Tree green leather overlays dominate the toe cap, eyestays, side panels, and heel. The New Balance N is seen on both sides – on the lateral side as a solid gray N and on the inner side as a dashed gray N. The gray heel collar features NB branding in bold red, while the tongue bears 9060 branding. A silver support appears attaching the midsole to the heel, while the midsole itself is chunky and black with red accents on the lateral side. 

What we think is most interesting about this shoe is the Tea Tree leather that dominates it, providing both support and style. The New Balance 9060 Tea Tree was released on January 10, 2024, for $150.

name: Magic Beige Gum
title: adidas Samba XLG Magic Beige Gum
description:
The adidas Samba XLG Magic Beige Gum is an athletic shoe with all the features of the classic Samba with a few oversized elements.

The Magic Beige Gum adidas Samba XLG has a leather upper in a light-beige color. A t-shaped toe cap adorns the front of the shoe in beige suede, while a darker-tan suede forms the serrated 3-Stripes adidas logo on each side. The Samba brand name appears in gold letters on the lateral side. The overlays that form the eyestays are also a beige leather but are slightly oversized near the top. The wide and thick tongue has an adidas logo patch, and the shoe rests atop an extra-thick midsole that is gum rubber.

What we like best about this shoe is the muted colorway, which allows the oversized design to stand out on its own. The adidas Samba XLG Magic Beige Gum was released on July 7, 2024, for $120.

name: Youth of Paris
title: adidas Campus 00s Youth of Paris
description:
The adidas Campus 00s Youth Of Paris is a collaborative sneaker between adidas and fashion brand Youth of Paris, featuring the Campus 00s in a Carbon, Solar Green, and Core Black colorway.

This adidas Campus 00s features a Carbon suede upper with tumbled black leather on the heel tab and the three stripes on the sides. Solar Green hits on the upper eyelets, "YOUTH OF PARIS" branding on the lateral, the Trefoil logo at the heel, tongue branding, and the stitching details on the medial provide a contrasting tone to the upper. Other details include black stitching finishes throughout, gray laces, and a branded insole. A black sole unit with herringbone traction patterns seals off the design. Each pair comes with an extra set of green and black laces and a hang tag. 

Our experts particularly love this sneaker’s unique construction and colorway, which creates a visually striking and trendy appearance. The adidas Campus 00s Youth Of Paris was released on November 15th, 2023, retailing at $120.

name: Night Indigo Crew White (Women's)
title: adidas Samba OG Night Indigo Crew White (Women's)
description:
The adidas Samba OG Night Indigo Crew White (Women's), in women’s sizes, is a casual sneaker with a Night Indigo upper, highlighted by the signature adidas three stripes in Core White. The tip, lace panel, and heel tab coordinate with the stripes in Core White, accented by Gold Metallic branding on the side and tongue. The dark gum rubber sole completes the look.

adidas’ Samba sneaker has a heritage that dates to 1949, when the style was designed by adidas founder Adolf Dassler himself, and that is just part of adidas’ storied history that dates to 1924. Remaining a perennial classic for decades, in modern times adidas has reinvented the Samba OG by playing with limited edition color palettes.

In our opinion, the best feature of the Samba OG Night Indigo is its Metallic Gold branding, which adds a luxe touch to the aesthetic. The adidas Samba OG Night Indigo Crew White (Women's) released on October 3, 2024, and retailed at $100.

name: Wonder White Chalk White Core Black
title: adidas Campus 00s Wonder White Chalk White Core Black
description:
The adidas Campus 00s Wonder White Chalk White Core Black updates the retro Campus 00s silhouette with a light colorway of Wonder White with Chalk White and black accents.

The upper is crafted from hairy suede in Wonder White with leather details in Chalk White on the serrated 3-Stripes logo and the heel mustache. Inspired by skateboarding sneakers from the early 2000s, the Wonder White Chalk White Core Black adidas Campus 00s features padding in the tongue and collar, creating a chunky silhouette. The off-white midsole provides soft cushioning underfoot and serves as a connection to the Campus legacy. Plush terry cloth lines the shoe, contributing to the premium feel.

Our experts at StockX like the choice of shaggy suede on the upper. It increases the soft aesthetic introduced by the off-white hues and feels velvety to the touch. The adidas Campus 00s Wonder White Chalk White Core Black was released on May 15, 2024, and sold for $110.

name: Pale Oak Mantle Green
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Pale Oak Mantle Green
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 Pale Oak Mantle Green is a stylish and comfortable sneaker that combines retro aesthetics with modern performance. Featuring a sleek silhouette, this men's shoe showcases a harmonious blend of pale oak and mantle green hues, creating a versatile look suitable for various casual occasions. The upper is crafted with high-quality materials, ensuring durability and breathability for all-day wear.

At the core of this sneaker lies ASICS' renowned GEL technology, providing superior cushioning and shock absorption for enhanced comfort during every step. The Gel-1130 also boasts a sturdy rubber outsole, offering excellent traction and stability on various surfaces. With its balanced combination of style and functionality, this ASICS model is perfect for those seeking a reliable everyday sneaker that doesn't compromise on looks or performance. Our experts state this product is great for urban explorers and fashion-conscious individuals who value both comfort and trendy design in their footwear.

name: Birch Silver
title: Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD Birch Silver
description:
The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD Birch Silver takes inspiration from a vintage silhouette, and the result is an elegant shoe that elevates leisure footwear to a truly posh status.

The upper of this low-riding Birch Silver Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD is fashioned from luxe cream-colored goat leather. This same leather forms a T-toe overlay, an eyestay overlay, and the signature serrated S strips that cross at the heel. Silver leather with a metallic sheen forms the strips that course vertically down the side panel and horizontally across the side panel from the heel to the toe cap. A cream-colored midsole with a black stripe features soft cushioning and rides atop a cream-colored outsole that has cross-hatch diamond patterning for traction.

The aspect of these sneakers that we enjoy the most is the heel tab that folds over the back of the shoe. Also made from cream-colored leather, it's textured, providing a subtle difference. The tab also features Tiger branding. The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD Birch Silver was released on July 1, 2023, for $160 retail.

name: Slate Red
title: adidas Yeezy 350 V2 CMPCT Slate Red
description:
The adidas Yeezy 350 V2 CMPCT Slate Red brings out major Red October vibes with its vibrant Slate Red Primeknit upper. Brown undertones throughout the forefoot add a subtle contrast, emphasizing the design's knit structure. At the base, a red, semi-translucent Boost sole provides the model's renowned cushioning and support.

The adidas Yeezy 350 V2 CMPCT Slate Red released in February of 2022 and retailed for $220.

name: Carbon Sesame
title: adidas Fear of God Athletics I Basketball Carbon Sesame
description:
The adidas Fear of God Athletics I Basketball Carbon Sesame is part of an ongoing collaboration between adidas and the Los Angeles-based apparel label Fear of God.

Created by Jerry Lorenzo, this hybrid basketball shoe features a minimalist aesthetic and the designer’s signature muted tones. For example, the knit upper and neoprene collar come in Carbon, while the toecap and exaggerated rubber outsole feature off-white Sesame. Paying tribute to adidas’ legacy, the side panels display the 3-Stripes logo made with plastic-like material. Instead of serving as a simple logo, the 3-Stripes form a lace cage that houses durable Carbon laces.

Something our experts like about this sneaker is the lack of overt branding. For example, other than the 3-Stripes logo, the only branding is a small patch on the heel that reads ‘fear of god.’ The adidas Fear of God Athletics I Basketball Carbon Sesame was released on December 3rd, 2023, and retailed at $250.
model: adidas Fear of God Athletics I Basketball

name: Triple Black
title: adidas Ultra Boost 20 Triple Black
description:
The adidas Ultra Boost 20 Triple Black adds a monochromatic black look to the Ultra Boost collection.

The adidas Ultra Boost 20 features a black Continental outsole and Boost midsole. The midsole for these sneakers also features 20% more Boost, which offers more comfort, flexibility, and durability and allows the wearer to absorb and return more energy when running. The adidas Primeknit upper provides a supportive fit, while the heel is made with soft elastane material for comfort. Tailored Fiber Placement technology offers stitched-in reinforcement as well as a superior fit and lightweight feel.

The adidas Ultra Boost 20 Triple Black released in December of 2019 and retailed for $180.

name: Silver Green Magic Mauve
title: adidas Handball Spezial Silver Green Magic Mauve
description:
The adidas Handball Spezial Silver Green Magic Mauve is a shoe that was originally released for indoor sports in the 1970s but has now become a lifestyle staple.

This iteration of the adidas Handball Spezial is made with a textile upper textured like corduroy for breathability. A dark green color forms the toe box and the area around the ankle, while the large T-shaped toe cap comes in a light green suede. Light green suede also forms the heel counter, and corduroy of the same color runs under the laces. The classic adidas three stripes logo appears on each side in white leather with brown textiles running between the stripes. The word SPEZIAL and the trefoil logo appear on the lateral side next to the top stripe. The heel counter is mauve leather with a white trefoil logo, and the cream-colored tongue also sports an adidas logo patch. A branded gum rubber outsole finishes out the look.

What stands out about this training shoe is the corduroy texture of the upper, which adds visual interest to the shoe. The adidas Handball Spezial Silver Green Magic Mauve was released on March 6, 2024, for $120.

name: Light Blue Floral (Women's)
title: adidas Gazelle Indoor Light Blue Floral (Women's)
description:
The adidas Gazelle Indoor Light Blue Floral (Women's), in women’s sizes, is a low top athletic shoe featuring a Beige suede upper that is printed with embroidered Light Blue flowers. The adidas signature three stripes and heel tab coordinate with the print in Light Blue, accented by gold foil printed Gazelle branding. A textured Cloud White tongue and laces play off the gum rubber sole.

adidas is Europe’s largest athletic shoe producer and the second largest in the world, with a century long history dating to 1924. adidas has been producing the Gazelle, iconic for its suede upper with leather stripes, since 1966. As the style has remained a perennial classic, it has seen eras as a fashion sneaker, a direction adidas has seized with the Gazelle Indoor's Light Blue Floral pattern.

In our opinion, the best feature of the Gazelle Indoor is its embroidered Floral print, which is sweet and luxurious. The adidas Gazelle Indoor Light Blue Floral (Women's) released on January 30, 2024, and retailed at $120.

name: Iridescent
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Iridescent
description:
The Iridescent Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 aims to merge a vibrant, shimmering design with LaMelo Ball's signature style on-court, creating a basketball shoe designed to turn heads. This edition combines Puma's athletic expertise with bold aesthetics, appealing to fans and athletes alike.

The Iridescent LaMelo Ball MB.03 by Puma features a high-quality synthetic upper with iridescent overlays, which gives it a unique color-shifting effect. This model was designed in collaboration with LaMelo Ball and includes Puma’s signature Nitro Foam midsole for lightweight cushioning. LaMelo's "1 of 1" graphic is printed on the back underneath M.E.L.D. Puma’s dedication to sports innovation, established in 1948, continues with this blend of modern design and performance materials.

What we, the experts, love about the Iridescent Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 is the Nitro Foam midsole, giving you dependable comfort while playing. We also appreciate the iridescent detailing that adds dynamic color changes under light. This model retailed at $125 upon release on 29 March 2024.

name: Yu-Gi-Oh! Yugi's World (with Sealed Dark Magician Promo Card)
title: adidas ADI2000 Yu-Gi-Oh! Yugi's World (with Sealed Dark Magician Promo Card)
description:
adidas is collaborating with Japanese trading card game Yu-Gi-Oh! on their latest adidas ADI2000 model. The limited edition sneakers come with a Yu-Gi-Oh! promotional Dark Magician trading card.

The adidas ADI2000 Yugi’s World comes with an all black upper, hints of purple on the outsoles, three golden stripes, and a pink and purple mesh sockliner. adidas also included gold Yu-Gi-Oh! branded lace locks and embroidered tongues that read "King of Games" and "Time to Duel".

The adidas ADI2000 Yu-Gi-Oh! Yugi’s World (With Sealed Dark Magician Promo Card) released January 26, 2023, with a retail price of $120.

name: Focus Olive Gum
title: adidas Samba OG Focus Olive Gum
description:
The adidas Samba OG Focus Olive Gum replaces the traditional leather upper with nylon fabric, adding a touch of modernity to this classic silhouette.

As part of the adidas Nylon Pack, the Focus Olive Gum adidas Samba OG boasts nylon on the main upper, the toebox overlays, and the eyelets – all in Focus Olive 21. However, white leather accents can still be found on the heel mustache and the serrated 3-Stripes logo. In addition, the liner in Focus Olive 21 is crafted from leather, contributing a heritage design element. The gum rubber outsole provides traction underfoot, while reflective accents increase visibility in low lighting.

Our experts like the classic adidas branding on the shoe, including ‘adidas SAMBA’ printed on the side panel and the adidas Originals tongue label. The adidas Samba OG Focus Olive Gum was released on December 1, 2023, and sold for $100.

name: Neighborhood Cement Grey
title: adidas Superstar Neighborhood Cement Grey
description:
The adidas Superstar Neighborhood Cement Grey is an athletic shoe featuring a Cement Grey grained leather upper with monochrome Cement Grey suede used on the signature three stripes and heel patch. The Neighborhood logo is debossed in white on the side, and skull branding and the Neighborhood motto appear on the rear heel and heel tab. Tokyo branding within a lightning bolt on the midsole and Neighborhood shoe jewelry completes the aesthetic.

Neighborhood is a Japanese streetwear brand founded in Tokyo’s Harajuku district in 1994, known for their sleek streetwear that is crafted with pride. adidas is the world’s second-largest sneaker producer, with a heritage that dates to 1924. The two brands came together to craft a limited edition Superstar, which expresses the essence of both brands’ aesthetics.

Our experts feel that the best feature of the Superstar Neighborhood is its midsole, which stands out against the shoe’s monochrome subtlety. The adidas Superstar Neighborhood Cement Grey released on June 1, 2024, and retailed at $160.

name: Arzareth
title: adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Arzareth
description:
Please Note: Extra laces required. The Yeezy 700 V3 Arzareth welcomed a new wave of color for the ever-growing Yeezy line. Previous releases of the 700 V3 have stayed in neutral territory, making the Arzareth a stand out with its striking colorway.

The Yeezy 700 V3 Arzareth features a blue and grey Primeknit upper that is complemented by a traditional translucent glow-in-the-dark cage overlay. From there, an EVA foam midsole, grey toe cap, and black lining complete the design.

The Yeezy 700 V3 Arzareth released in August of 2020 and retailed for $200.

name: Energy Ink
title: adidas Campus 00s Energy Ink
description:
The adidas Campus 00s Energy Ink was released to update its predecessor, the Campus 80s, and features puffed-up quarter panels and tongue.

While its colorway is principally Energy Ink, the adidas Campus 00s feature a white midsole with visible stitching around the shoe. Its upper sports a leather finish in a purple hue. The Energy Ink tone also appears on the eyestay overlays with punched eyelets, wide black laces, and a padded tongue. The tongue logo is a black rubber patch with purple accents and an embossed Trefoil. The signature three stripes in core black and rugged outlines adorn the quarter panels. The lateral side displays the "CAMPUS" branding in zoomed-out white block lettering.

What do our experts love about the adidas Campus 00s Energy Ink? We think the introduction of black leather overlays and embossed Trefoil branding on the heel counter makes this sneaker outstanding. It was released on May 4th, 2023, for $110.

name: C.P. Company Cement Grey
title: ASICS Gel-Quantum 360 VIII C.P. Company Cement Grey
description:
The ASICS Gel-Quantum 360 VIII C.P. Cement Gray is a sneaker with a design inspired by formations found in nature, executed with 5D technology.

This iteration of the ASICS Gel-Quantum 360 VIII is made with a mesh upper in Cement Gray. Overlays with 5D patterning cross the midsole in the typical ASICS shape and also appear across the toecap. C.P. branding also appears on top of the toe, while the tongue contains an ASICS logo. The TPU heel counter is black and contains a small ASICS logo, as well as the C.P. Company brand name in white on the pull tab. A black rubber sole and shiny outsole complete the look. The shoe also features FF BLAST PLUS ECO cushioning for extra comfort and increased performance.

What we like most about this shoe is the shiny black outsole, which adds an extra element of visual appeal to the gray and black shoe. The ASICS Gel-Quantum 360 VIII C.P. Cement Gray was released on February 22, 2024, for a retail price of $200.

name: White Fairway
title: adidas Rod Laver White Fairway
description:
The adidas Rod Laver White Fairway boasts a tennis silhouette inspired by Rob Laver, one of Australia’s greatest tennis stars of all time. The sneaker features a Running White upper with accents in Fairway, a rich green hue.

The White Fairway adidas Rod Laver has mesh upper construction that features a loose weave to allow the foot to breathe, while the rubber outsole provides grip on the tennis court and other surfaces. Suede overlays in a light gray hue wrap around the toe area, while the heel mustache is crafted from smooth leather in Fairway. Additional Fairway details can be found on the rubber outsole and the adidas logo tag on the tongue. The woven tongue tag displays ‘adidas’ and a retro-inspired trefoil.

Our experts at StockX like the Rod Laver branding on the heel mustache, which replaces the traditional ‘adidas’ embroidery in white thread. The adidas Rod Laver White Fairway was released on July 20, 2020, and sold for $65.

name: Blue Scarlet
title: adidas SL 72 RS Blue Scarlet
description:
The adidas SL 72 RS Blue Scarlet features a sports-inspired design that draws elements from the adidas catalog.

This iteration of the SL 72 features a tightly woven mesh base in blue with tonal suede heel and toe overlays. The texturized leather tongue is blue and showcases retro "adidas" lettering and a trefoil in white. Enhancing the sporty look, additional white accents can be found on the laces, the leather heel mustache, and the serrated 3-Stripes logo. Layers of foam in blue and red form the EVA midsole, adding a heritage detail that complements the metallic "adidas SL-72" branding on the outer side panel.

Our experts at StockX like the blue adidas trefoils and lettering that form a repeating pattern on the white insole. These details add a modern touch to the sneaker’s retro design. The adidas SL 72 RS Blue Scarlet was released on March 28, 2024, and sold for $100.

name: Core Black Carbon Mesh
title: adidas Ozweego Core Black
description:
The adidas Ozweego Core Black Carbon Mesh was part of a relaunch and expansion of the adidas Originals Ozweego line.

The Core Black Carbon Mesh adidas Ozweego features a predominantly black upper made of a mix of leather, suede, and mesh. The midsole has a chunky and sculpted design that provides ample cushioning and the rugged outsole offers durability and grip. The adidas Ozweego Core Black Carbon Mesh has rounded laces and a padded collar around the neck. The laces are black and the padded collar is designed to provide additional support.

The adidas Ozweego Core Black was released on August 8th, 2019 at a retail price of $110.

name: Night Indigo
title: adidas Tobacco Night Indigo
description:
The adidas Tobacco Night Indigo is a unique performance shoe that features a monochromatic look inspired by the archival model.

This iteration of the adidas Tobacco has a soft suede upper that appears in Night Indigo throughout. A slim overlay forms the toe cap, also in Night Indigo suede, while Night Indigo leather forms the serrated adidas 3-Stripes on each side. An overlay forms the heel counter as well as the heel collar, and an adidas logo patch, subtle in that it matches in color, appears on the heel. The shoe’s textured rubber midsole and outsole also appear in the Night Indigo color.

Our favorite feature of this shoe is the soft suede of the upper, which has a bit of a sheen to it that allows it to stand out even with its monochromatic look. The adidas Tobacco Night Indigo was released on September 20, 2024, for $110.

name: White Preloved Ink
title: adidas Gazelle Indoor White Preloved Ink
description:
The adidas Gazelle Indoor White Preloved Ink is an indoor soccer shoe that has transformed into a popular lifestyle shoe over its 30+ years of being on the market.
  
This iteration of the adidas Gazelle Indoor has a white leather upper as its base. A small toe cap in a T shape appears in off-white suede, while the eyestays are made of the same material. The adidas 3-Stripes adorn the sides in Preloved Ink colors, including a navy blue and a pale purple. The Gazelle brand name is seen on the outer side next to the stripes in Metallic Gold. A Preloved Ink heel collar bears the adidas trefoil logo, while the white tongue has a patch with gold adidas branding. The branded gum rubber outsole is also a semi-transparent white color. 
 
The standout features of this shoe are the metallic gold accents, which complement the white and Preloved Ink colors nicely. The adidas Gazelle Indoor White Preloved Ink was released on April 1, 2024, for $120.

name: JJJJound Black
title: ASICS GT-2160 JJJJound Black
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 JJJJound Black is a collaboration model that was released in tandem by Montreal design house JJJJound and footwear giant ASICS that boasts visibility-enhancing features in a black colorway.

This low-profile silhouette is a special edition sneaker that found design inspiration in the GT-2000 running shoe from the 2010s. It goes without saying that ASICS proprietary Gel technology in the midsole that provides premium cushioning. The monochromatic black upper sports a mesh upper with reflective detailing on the toe, heel, and side panels. The iconic ASICS stripes are on both sides in pure silver. Branding hits are seen with JJJJound on the heel and ASICS on the tongue. Black laces complete the look.

We think that the ASICS GT-2160 JJJJound Black sticks to the design studio’s ethos of inspiring through minimal intervention and design. This high-performance running shoe was made available to the public on October 31, 2024, and priced at $190.

name: Core Black Cloud White Gold (GS)
title: adidas Superstar Core Black Cloud White Gold (GS)
description:
The adidas Superstar Core Black Cloud White Gold (GS) represents a timeless sneaker showcasing iconic features such as the distinctive, serrated three-stripes emblem, the renowned shell-style toe, and the iconic box logo, making it a true OG.

Crafted from sleek black leather, the adidas Superstar for grade school kids’ upper offers a sharp contrast against the cloud white and metallic gold accents. The iconic adidas serrated three stripes stand out prominently on the side in striking white. A metallic gold adidas brand graces the tongue tag, complemented by a Superstar wordmark on the quarter panel. Retaining its instantly recognizable shell toe, the sneaker features a traditional herringbone traction pattern on the rubber outsole. Inside, an OrthoLite sock liner enhances comfort.

We think the distinguishing characteristic of the adidas Superstar Core Black Cloud White Gold (GS) lies in its enduring iconic shell toe design that has persisted for over five decades. This design, coupled with the sneaker's distinctive color scheme, distinguishes it from other shoes in its category. The sneaker debuted for $80 on December 27, 2019.

name: Scooby-Doo
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.04 Scooby-Doo
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.04 Scooby-Doo is a playful and eye-catching collaboration that brings the beloved cartoon character to life on a performance basketball shoe. This unique design features a vibrant aquatic blue upper with lime green and fiery orange accents, perfectly capturing the essence of the Mystery Machine and its iconic crew. The sneaker's bold colorway is complemented by subtle Scooby-Doo themed details, making it a standout piece for both fans of the animated series and sneaker enthusiasts alike.

Designed for optimal on-court performance, the MB.04 incorporates Puma's latest technology to enhance comfort, support, and responsiveness. The shoe's lightweight construction and responsive cushioning system cater to LaMelo Ball's dynamic playing style, providing excellent traction and stability for quick cuts and explosive movements. With its blend of nostalgia and cutting-edge design, the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.04 Scooby-Doo offers a perfect balance of style and functionality. Us at StockX believe this product is great for basketball players looking to make a statement on the court while enjoying superior performance and comfort.

name: Shadow Brown Gum
title: adidas Handball Spezial Shadow Brown Gum
description:
The adidas Handball Spezial Shadow Brown Gum updates a vintage sports shoe and dresses it in eye-catching contrasting colors for a sneaker that pops with style and indulges with comfort.

The Shadow Brown Gum colorway of the adidas Handball Spezial sports a flexible upper of supple brown suede that is found on both the base and the overlays. Contrasting hits of white leather appear as the serrated side panel three stripes as well as the heel tab. We also see white on the laces and the textile sock liner, while the insole is brown. The foam midsole is encapsulated by brown gum rubber, which also makes up the outsole.

What we love most about this sneaker are the hits of branding that add to the vintage look. Distressed Spezial branding with an adidas graces the side panel, and adidas Handball Spezial branding with a trefoil adorns the tongue. adidas trefoil branding also appears on the insole, and trefoils make up much of the traction pattern on the outsole. The adidas Handball Spezial Shadow Brown Gum was released on July 18, 2023 for $110 retail.

name: Flax
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Flax
description:
Yeezy provided a new colorway of its most popular design with the adidas Yeezy 350 Flax, now available on StockX. This release shows slight resemblance to the 350 V2 Marsh in colorway, displaying warm tones to embody the arrival of spring. This model was released as a regional exclusive specific to the Asia Pacific and Africa.

This Yeezy 350 V2 Flax is composed of a light brown Primeknit upper with a translucent outer side stripe. A translucent Boost cushioned sole and light brown interior completes the design. These sneakers released in February of 2020 and retailed for $220. The Yeezy 350 V2 Flax released again in March of 2024 and retailed for $230.

name: Cream White
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Cream White
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 Cream White blends retro inspiration with modern updates, debuting in a neutral cream and white colorway. It draws design cues from the GEL-Kayano 14 and pays homage to the ninth iteration of the GEL-1000 series.

Originally, a 2008 stability running shoe, the Gel-1130 has been reimagined for everyday wear. Its low-profile silhouette features the beloved GEL technology in the heel, providing all-day comfort. The upper features breathable mesh and synthetic leather overlays, combining traditional and modern materials for a fresh aesthetic. White signature ASICS stripes and red-orange accents add subtle contrast to the creamy base. Cream-colored laces complete the design.

We think that the silver TRUSSTIC support system, located between the forefoot and rearfoot, enhances stability, is a standout design element. It figuratively bridges decades of ASICS’ running heritage. The ASICS Gel-1130 Cream White released to the public on September 1, 2024, with a retail price of $95.

name: Mauve
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Mauve
description: Yeezy had us on another wave with the OG wave runners, but now he’s bringing us to the sand with the adidas Yeezy 700 Mauve. These sneakers come with a mauve upper with black accents, mauve midsole with light green accents, and gum sole. This shoe released October 2018 and retailed for $300. Before Yandhi drops, cop these on StockX now.

name: Black White
title: adidas adiFOM Superstar Black White
description:
The adidas adifOM Superstar Black White takes a classic sneaker silhouette and reimagines it. Created with sustainable materials and fused with a clog design, the resulting sneaker is a singularly eye-catching lifestyle shoe you can slip on and off with ease.

The adidas adifOM Superstar In a Core Black / Cloud White / Core Black colorway sports a subtly ridged black upper made of 100% foam rubber that has been sustainably derived from sugar cane. The shell closure takes on the look of a clog, but the contrasting white signature adidas 3-Stripes on the side panel grounds this shoe firmly in its iconic sneaker origins. The black sock liner matches the insole that provides another hit of contrast with its crisp white adidas branding. Black foam rubber makes another appearance as the cushioning material composing the midsole, which rests firmly on a black rubber outsole with a herringbone traction pattern.

The detail our sneaker experts appreciate the most about this lifestyle shoe is the white heel tab that melds the embossed trefoil branding into the undulating pattern of the upper. The adidas adifOM Superstar Black White was released on December 14, 2022 for an original retail price of $110.

name: KoRn
title: adidas Campus 00s KoRn
description:
Emerge from the shadows with a nod to the '90s nu-metal wave with the adidas Campus 00s KoRn. This iconic adidas silhouette gets a head-banging update in collaboration with the legendary band KoRn, bringing a piece of the mosh pit to your sneaker collection. The Black/White-Gum colorway is a subtle yet striking palette that reflects the gritty and raw aesthetic of KoRn's music, wrapped up in a classic silhouette that's stood the test of time​.

This isn't your everyday Campus; it's a commemoration of an era, a throwback to when KoRn emerged with a sound that shook the core of the musical landscape. The Campus 00s KoRn sneakers carry the spirit of the '90s with a design that takes cues from the adidas models the band sported during their meteoric rise​. The black suede upper contrasts beautifully with the white stitching. The mismatched Korn and adidas branding on each tongue, along with the exaggerated white leather three-stripes, make this pair a tribute to the iconic band and the timeless adidas style​.

Whether you're a sneakerhead, a KoRn aficionado, or someone who appreciates the fusion of music and fashion, the adidas Campus 00s KoRn is a statement. Dropped on October 27, 2023, at a retail price of $130, this collaborative masterpiece is set to resonate with the rhythm of rebellion, in tune with the aesthetic of a generation that dared to be different.

name: Ararat
title: adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Ararat
description:
DISCLAIMER: US and UK sizing is the same and does not require any conversion.

Yeezy provides a futuristic approach to comfort wear with the adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Ararat, now available on StockX. Also known as the Yeezy Foam Runner, the Foam RNNR is comprised of a single piece of unique Yeezy material that blends harvested algae with adidas EVA materials. Its aerodynamic design features a medley of holes and ridges that take influence from the adidas Yeezy 700 V3. A white Ararat colorway covers the silhouette, staying true to Yeezys natural color palettes.

The Yeezy Foam Runner released in June of 2020 and retailed for $75 USD.

name: Semi Lucid Fuchsia (GS)
title: adidas Campus 00s Semi Lucid Fuchsia (GS)
description:
The adidas Campus 00s Semi Lucid Fuchsia (GS) is a grade school-sized shoe that takes its design inspiration from the 80s Campus shoe with a few 2000s-style updates.
   
The Semi Lucid Fuchsia (GS) adidas Campus 00s is made with a soft leather upper in Semi Lucid Fuchsia. This color dominates the toebox, side panels, eyestays, tongue, and heel area. The adidas 3-Stripes appear as thick serrated white leather overlays on each side, while the Campus brand name is found on the lateral side in silver. Two lines of perforations run up the sides between the stripes on each side for breathability. The heel collar is off-white and bears a Fuchsia adidas trefoil logo, and the tongue also bears trefoil branding. The shoe sits on an off-white midsole and a gum rubber outsole.

What we like most about this sneaker are the thick adidas stripes that appear on the sides, which add a modern element of style. The adidas Campus 00s Semi Lucid Fuchsia (GS) was released on May 17, 2024, for $80.

name: Kith Marvel Villains Green Goblin Sealed Box (Comic Included)
title: ASICS GT-2160 Kith Marvel Villains Green Goblin Sealed Box (Comic Included)
description:
Introducing the ASICS GT-2160 Kith Marvel Villains Green Goblin Sealed Box (Comic Included), a high-performance running shoe, collaborating with Kith and Marvel. This special edition honors the Green Goblin, a notorious Marvel villain. The sealed box preserves the shoe’s authenticity, featuring unique Marvel-themed packaging and design elements. 

  The ASICS GT-2160 with Kith Marvel Villains Green Goblin boasts a dark green and bright yellow color scheme, echoing the villain’s iconic mask. The upper combines mesh and synthetic materials, while the Gel inserts provide responsive cushioning. ASICS’ signature technology promotes efficient heel-to-toe transition. Kith’s collaborative branding and Marvel’s Green Goblin graphics adorn the tongue, heel, and insole, creating a unique fusion of athletics and comic book culture. 

  We love the GT-2160’s heel counter and Space Technology cushioning. The heel counter provides superior stability, while Space Technology absorbs shock and distributes impact. These features deliver a secure, responsive ride. Released on September 8, 2024, the ASICS GT-2160 with Kith Marvel Villains Green Goblin retailed at $175.

name: Oatmeal Obsidian Grey
title: ASICS Gel-NYC Oatmeal Obsidian Grey
description:
The ASICS Gel-NYC Oatmeal Obsidian Gray is a technical running shoe that finds inspiration in heritage models from the ASICS catalog.

The upper is made of breathable mesh in Oatmeal and has a construction that resembles the GEL-NIMBUS 3, a technical sneaker from the early 2000s. Featuring crisscrossing overlays on the side panels, the upper also takes cues from the MC-PLUS V. Dark suede panels in Obsidian Gray form mudguards and eyelets that contribute to the sneaker’s retro aesthetic. However, the gel and foam midsole add a contemporary element. This midsole is similar to the one installed on the GEL-CUMULUS 16 and provides more responsive cushioning than its predecessors.

Our StockX experts like the way the gel pods in the midsole look like bubbles and remind the wearer of the shoe’s lightweight construction. The ASICS Gel-NYC Oatmeal Obsidian Gray was released on May 2nd, 2023, and retailed at $130.

name: Black White (Women's)
title: adidas Samba LT Black White (Women's)
description:
The adidas Samba LT Black White (Women's) combines classic football-inspired design with modern updates. Its duo-chrome color scheme, unique materials, and historical significance as part of the Samba line highlight its long-lasting appeal.

The Black and White Samba LT for women by German sports company adidas is made from leather with nubuck accents for added texture. Its oversized tongue takes inspiration from vintage football boots, and the branding details and the cream suede toe cap contrast the predominantly black and white design. The 3-stripes are placed on the sides, and the Samba branding are features that complement the upper's aesthetic.

As the experts, one thing we enjoy about the adidas Samba LT Black White (Women's) is the retro design. Another feature is the gum sole in its natural shade, which provides reliable traction on various terrains, durability, and texture. This model was released on June 16, 2024, with a retail price of $100.

name: Dark Onyx (Infants)
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Dark Onyx (Infants)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Slide Dark Onyx (Infants) adapts the minimalist Yeezy Slide silhouette for an infant’s foot and adds an all-over colorway of Dark Onyx.

Although this slip-on shoe is informed by Kanye West’s designs, it was launched after the artist’s departure from adidas. The slide is crafted from PEVA foam, which offers a ridged, dense build and allows the foot to breathe. The curved silhouette gives the Dark Onyx (Infants) adidas Yeezy Slide a sleek aesthetic, while a sling-back strap prevents the shoe from slipping off. Featuring serrated ridges, the exaggerated rubber outsole is designed to compress with each step. However, because this is an infant shoe, it serves as a design element.

Our experts at StockX like the minimal branding – the adidas 3-Stripes logo printed on the insole. It helps the sneaker maintain its minimalist aesthetic and doesn’t distract from the simple design. The infant-sized adidas Yeezy Slide Dark Onyx (Infants) was released on March 7, 2024, and sold for $40.

name: Kith Marvel Villains Silver Surfer Sealed Box (Comic Included)
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Kith Marvel Villains Silver Surfer Sealed Box (Comic Included)
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 with Kith Marvel Villains Silver Surfer is a collaboration between ASICS, Kith, and Marvel. ASICS, founded in 1949, has a rich history of innovative running technology. This collaboration combines Kayano's supportive design with a unique aesthetic. It features a metallic silver and navy blue color scheme inspired by the iconic comic book character.

This shoe features a Silver Surfer-inspired design and a sealed box with a comic book inclusion. It combines high-performance running technology with a unique pop culture twist, appealing to comic fans. The FlyteFoam midsole offers exceptional bounce and energy return, while the Dynamic DuMax Support System delivers targeted stability for high-arched runners. These features provide a responsive and stable ride.

We love the ASICS Gel-Kayano 14's unique FlyteFoam midsole and Dynamic DuMax Support System. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Kith Marvel Villains Silver Surfer Sealed Box (Comic Included) was released on August 9th, 2024, for $190.

name: Brown
title: adidas Samba Deco SPZL Brown
description:
The adidas Samba Deco SPZL Brown reinterprets 1970s training shoes from adidas heritage catalogue and applies a colorway of Cloud White, brown, and Gum M2.

Unlike the classic Samba, this version of the Samba Deco SPZL features deco stitching on the toebox instead of a suede overlay. The heel tab on this sneaker is slightly larger than the one found on other Samba iterations. It features a trefoil-like logo with three triangles and overlapping lines. While the upper is made of suede in brown, the leather heel tab and 3-Stripes logos come in Cloud White. The suede tongue houses a woven tongue tag with ‘adidas’ in white lettering and ‘SAMBA SPZL’ in metallic ink decorates the lateral side panel.

Our StockX experts like the premium suede and gum rubber, which contribute to the sneaker’s retro appearance. The adidas Samba Deco SPZL Brown was released on November 17th, 2023, and retailed at $120.

name: Aluminum Core Black
title: adidas Gazelle Indoor Aluminum Core Black
description:
The adidas Gazelle Indoor Aluminum Core Black debuts in an aluminum, core black, and gum color palette while staying true to design elements of iconic 1960s silhouette.

Understated and timeliness, the adidas Gazelle Indoor is a low-top lifestyle shoe that can be dressed up or down depending on your mood and style. The aluminum upper is made out of cotton mesh that boasts a knit-like weave. The iconic T-toe overlay is made out of smooth suede. Three black signature adidas stripes made out of fabric adorn the sides, while the black leather lining just begs for you to slip your foot in. The black leather heel tab boasts adidas branding and the Trefoil in white. Flat white laces complete the design.

In our opinion, the gum rubber outsole, complete with Trefoil lugs, means the adidas Gazelle Indoor Aluminum Core Black is comfortable while providing traction. Originally released on June 1, 2024, this shoe retailed for $120.

name: Night Cargo Tribe Yellow
title: adidas Handball Spezial Night Cargo Tribe Yellow
description:
The adidas Handball Spezial Night Cargo Tribe Yellow is a modern version of the shoe originally created for handball players in the 1970s.
  
This iteration of the adidas Handball Spezial features a suede upper in Night Cargo, a dark-green color. The thin toe cap and the heel counter are made of the same material in the same color. The serrated 3-Stripes, the signature of adidas, appear on each side in Tribe Yellow leather, while "Spezial" and the trefoil logo are on the outer side in metallic gold. The heel collar also bears the Tribe Yellow color, while the tongue carries more adidas branding in Tribe Yellow. A dark, adidas-branded gum rubber outsole completes the design.
 
The most interesting feature of this shoe is the color scheme, which is bold yet neutral at the same time. The adidas Handball Spezial Night Cargo Tribe Yellow was released on June 9, 2021, for $110.

name: Cloud Grey (Women's)
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Cloud Grey (Women's)
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Cloud Grey (Women's) is a shoe for women that features Gel technology for comfort and was inspired by the 2000s running aesthetic.

This iteration of the ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 is made with a Cloud Grey mesh upper for breathability and flexibility. Polyurethane overlays in silver round out the toe box and run under the laces. The overlays also form the signature ASICS design across the sides of the shoe, but these overlays are also infused with a darker gray color in the middle. The heel counter overlays are also silver, and the heel is branded with the words GEL and GEL-KAYANO 14. The tongue features a classic ASICS logo. A white and gray sole and outsole complete the look. The Gel technology present underfoot provides support and shock absorption.

What stands out about this shoe is the Cloud Grey muted colorway, which provides versatility. ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Cloud Grey (Women's) was released on January 1, 2024, for $150.

name: C.P. Company Light Blue
title: adidas Manchester SPZL C.P. Company Light Blue
description:
The adidas Manchester SPZL C.P. Company Light Blue is an adidas SPZL silhouette designed in collaboration with C.P. Company that honors the city of Manchester.

This sneaker is the result of tri-collaboration between the City of Manchester, the C.P. Company, and adidas. This colorway is loaded with details. Starting with the light blue upper, you’ll spot the traditional T-toe box with a velvet-like overlay that also appears on the heel counter. Red stripes adorn the sides, with a dark blue stitching to accent them. The red leather heel tabs boast the Spezial Mod Trefoil on the left heel and C.P. Company on the right, while the tongues adorned with their raised graphics are also different on each shoe. The left tongue features C.P. Company British Sailor branding, while the right features the original and Mod Trefoil logos.

According to our experts, the dark blue laces and matching outsole complete the look and really capture the individuality of this shoe. Originally selling for $150 retail, the adidas Manchester SPZL C.P. Company Light Blue was released on November 12, 2024.

name: by Ronnie Fieg Kithmas White Black
title: adidas Clarks 8th Street Samba by Ronnie Fieg Kithmas White Black
description:
The adidas Clarks 8th Street Samba by Ronnie Fieg Kithmas White Multi represents a collaboration among designer and Kith founder Ronnie Fieg, adidas Originals and Clarks Originals.​
​​
​The Ronnie Fieg Kithmas White Multi iteration of the adidas Clarks 8th Street Samba features an upper crafted of Clarks Originals chalk white cow suede. The toe cap has a t-shaped darker suede overlay, while the leather signature adidas side-panel three stripes are in dark colors reminiscent of Christmas. The leather heel tab is dark green to match one of the stripes. Triple branding is debossed on the tongue tag and the leather heel liner. Samba branding is debossed alongside the top lateral-side stripe.​
​​
​One feature of this sneaker that our shoe experts particularly enjoy is the Clarks Originals crepe rubber outsole that gives this shoe such a distinctive look. The adidas Clarks 8th Street Samba by Ronnie Fieg Kithmas White Multi was released on December 25, 2023, for a retail price of $220.

name: Wild Pink (Womens)
title: adidas Gazelle Bold Wild Pink (Womens)
description:
The adidas Gazelle Bold Wild Pink (Women's) was first designed for indoor sports in the 1970s. Specifically sized for women, this sneaker features updates as well as classic traits that have made this silhouette iconic.

The Wild Pink adidas Gazelle Bold for women features a classic deep pink suede upper with the signature T-toe overlay in the same pink suede. The adidas three stripes on the side panel are serrated white leather, and pale pink appears at the heel. All in tonal deep pink, the laces criss-cross over a textured tongue and the sock liner is synthetic textile. adidas trefoil branding adorns the tongue tag while Gazelle branding appears above the third stripe on the quarter panel.

What we enjoy most about this iconic sneaker is the updated gum rubber soul unit which is triple stacked, with each stack featuring embossed adidas trefoil branding. The gum rubber outsole provides traction with circular and trefoil lugs. The adidas Gazelle Bold Wild Pink (Women's) was released on October 1, 2023, for retail price of $120.

name: Clay
title: adidas Fear of God Athletics I Basketball Clay
description:
The adidas Fear of God Athletics I Basketball Clay is a shoe designed as a collaboration between the sportswear brand and the luxury fashion brand.

This version of the adidas Fear of God Athletics I Basketball is made with a base of textile in a tan clay color. A neoprene layer can be found over the toe box and sides of the shoe, with a final layer of thermoplastic polyurethane on top of the sides, forming an oversized adidas 3-Stripes in the same color. The ankle has a sock-like fit and the heel features a pull tab and is supported by polyurethane as well. The midsole is thick and contains a Fear of God patch at the back of the heel.

What we like most about this sneaker is the modern take on the adidas logo, which sees it enlarged and slanted to take up the sides of the shoe. The adidas Fear of God Athletics I Basketball Clay was released on March 3, 2024, for $250.
model: adidas Fear of God Athletics I Basketball

name: Black White Gum (GS)
title: adidas Samba OG Black White Gum (GS)
description:
The adidas Samba OG Black White Gum (GS) is a grade school-sized shoe that pays homage to the classic design of the original model.

This model of the adidas Samba OG comes with a soft black leather upper. A T-shaped suede toe cap also appears in black. The traditional adidas three stripes logo is formed on each side of the shoe in white leather overlays, and the heel collar is also white leather. The Samba model name appears on the lateral side in gold foil letters next to the three stripes, and a blue adidas logo patch appears on the tongue – the only deviation from the otherwise black-and-white color scheme. A dark brown gum rubber outsole completes the design.

What we like best about this shoe is its classic and timeless look. It allows the shoe, originally intended for wear during soccer games, to be a lifestyle staple. The adidas Samba OG Black White Gum (GS) was released on August 10, 2023, for a retail price of $80.

name: White Royal Blue
title: adidas Forum Low White Royal Blue
description:
Since its first release, the adidas Forum Low White Royal Blue remains one of the highest selling variants in the adidas Forum series.

The adidas Forum Low White Royal Blue design has a white leather base and toe box with three blue stripes on each of its sides to enhance the silhouette’s retro scheme. The retro design becomes complete with the entire ensemble resting on the rubber sole engraved the adidas logo.

The adidas Forum Low White Royal Blue was first released on March 3, 2021 as the flagship basketball silhouette for adidas. The price at the time of its debut was $100.

name: Triple Black
title: adidas ADI2000 Triple Black
description:
The adidas ADI2000 Triple Black features a minimalist design, with a Triple Black color scheme.

The upper of the ADI2000 Triple Black is made of premium leather and suede, providing both durability and comfort. The adidas logo is embossed on the side for a subtle detail that showcases the brand's 3-Stripes. The logo is also visible on the heel and the tongue. It has a low-cut design that includes a heel tag. The midsole is made of lightweight foam material that provides exceptional cushioning and shock absorption, while the outsole is made of durable rubber, providing excellent traction and grip.

We think that the notable feature of the adidas ADI2000 Triple Black is its cushioned elements. It includes a cushioned tongue and collar, which both improve the overall comfort. It also features a cushioned insole that conforms to the foot for a comfortable fit. The shoe was released on September 26th, 2022, at a retail price of $110.

name: Taupe Light
title: adidas Yeezy 500 Taupe Light
description:
The adidas Yeezy 500 Taupe Light arrives in a monotone Taupe Light look with a mesh, leather, and suede upper and a sturdy adiPRENE sole. Reflective piping throughout the silhouette adds the finishing touches.

The adidas Yeezy 500 Taupe Light released in June of 2021 and retailed for $200.

name: Sean Wotherspoon Superearth Black
title: adidas Superstar AEC Sean Wotherspoon Superearth Black
description:
Sean Wotherspoon and adidas Originals revisit their first collaborative sneaker adidas Superstar Sean Wotherspoon Superearth black.

The adidas Superstar Sean Wotherspoon Superearth Black is solely made of recycled and vegan material. It features multi-colored embroidered flowers on the lateral side with hanging tassels of sky blue, purple, gold, white and orange over the midsole. At the base, adidas Superstar Swan Wotherspoon Superearth Black features black leather and black Three Stripes that can hardly be seen on the lateral side. The shoe also features decorative "S" patches of Super Earth which serve as lace accents.

Released on 22nd October 2021, adidas Superstar Sean Wotherspoon Superearth Black had a retail price of $110.

name: White Burgundy
title: Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 White Burgundy
description:
The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 White Burgundy is a training shoe whose design was inspired by the LIMBER shoe worn by the Japanese team at the 1968 Olympics.

This version of the Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 is made with a white leather upper. Beige suede overlays adorn the toe cap and form an X at the heel. Burgundy tiger stripes that have become synonymous with the brand run across the midsoles. The Onitsuka Tiger logo appears on the thin white tongue in burgundy and the word "Tiger" on the leather white heel tab, also in burgundy. A thin, flat, rubber outsole completes the streamlined look.

What we think stands out about this shoe is its simple and thin design, which will pair well with any outfit. The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 White Burgundy was first released on January 24, 2022, for an original retail price of $120.

name: Citrin (Non-Reflective)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Citrin (Non-Reflective)
description:
The Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Citrin features earth tones throughout the entire silhouette with hues of light green, yellow, and grey. A green stripe along the side of the shoe finishes off the design of this Yeezy 350 V2.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Citrin released in September 2019 and retailed for $220.

name: Ivory
title: adidas Samba Decon Ivory
description:
The adidas Samba Decon Ivory is a deconstructed version of the classic Samba with an Ivory colorway and Gold Metallic accents.

Unlike other legacy Samba models, the Ivory adidas Samba Decon removes reinforcing layers on the upper to create a straightforward, simple silhouette. The upper, including the toebox overlays, and the eyelets are crafted from smooth leather in Ivory. In addition, the heritage design elements, including the serrated 3-Stripes logo and the heel mustache, are made from Ivory leather. The all-leather construction gives the sneaker a sleek, premium feel while contributing to the deconstructed aesthetic.

Our experts at StockX appreciate the Gold Metallic branding accents because they elevate the sneaker and stand out from the Ivory base. The ‘SAMBA’ lettering along the 3-Stripes logo and the ‘adidas’ script on the tongue tag showcase Gold Metallic. The adidas Samba Decon Ivory was released on March 15, 2024, and sold for $150.

name: Black Carbon
title: adidas adiFOM Q Black Carbon
description: The adidas adiFOM Q Black Carbon is a sleek and stylish sneaker that combines comfort and performance. The upper is made of black mesh and synthetic materials, with carbon fiber accents for added durability. The adiFOM technology in the midsole provides cushioning and support for all-day wear. The outsole is made of rubber for traction and grip on any surface. The colorway is versatile and can be worn with any outfit. The release date for this shoe is October 29th, 2022, and the retail price is $120. Whether you're hitting the gym or running errands, the adidas adiFOM Q Black Carbon is a reliable and fashionable choice.

name: Slate Carbon
title: adidas Yeezy 350 V2 CMPCT Slate Carbon
description:
The adidas Yeezy 350 V2 CMPCT Slate Carbon features a sock-like black and Slate Carbon Primeknit upper with raised collars and woven eyelets. Hits of light brown add a subtle contrast to the design's dark presence. At the base, an all-black Boost sole adds cushioning and support.

The adidas Yeezy 350 V2 CMPCT Slate Carbon released in May of 2022 and retailed for $230.

name: Gold White
title: Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 Gold White
description:
The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 Gold White takes a silhouette inspired by running shoes from the 1960s and infuses it with a modern street style with undeniable pizzazz.

The upper of this low-top is crafted from premium calf leather in metallic gold. The iconic tiger stripes course across the side panel in white leather. Gold leather forms a T-toe overlay, the eyestay overlay, and overlay strips that cross at the heel. The branding on the tongue path adds another hit of sparkle to this shoe. A two-tone foam midsole in white and beige offers cushioning support, while the cream-colored outsole is patterned for traction.

Our favorite aspect of this bright sneaker is the heel tab. A flap of gold leather folds over the heel and sports white Tiger branding in a script, giving the sneaker a decided look of distinction. The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 Gold White was released on January 24th, 2022 for $120 retail.

name: Wonder White Gum (Women's)
title: adidas Sambae Wonder White Gum (Women's)
description:
The adidas Sambae Wonder White Gum (Women's) is a shoe for women with a chunky build and a neutral colorway. 
  
The Wonder White Gum (Women's) adidas Sambae is made with a leatgher light-cream upper. A thick t-shaped toe cap adorns the forefoot in cream suede, while the adidas signature 3-Stripes shows up on each side in white thread. The Samba brand name is seen in Metallic Silver on the outer side panel, next to the first stripe. The heel collar appears in white leather, and the tongue bears an adidas trefoil logo along with the brand name in white. A thick semi-transparent gum rubber outsole completes the slightly oversized design. 
 
Our favorite thing about this shoe is the cream colorway combined with the chunky elements. The colorway gives the shoe an elegant and versatile look, while the chunky design provides style. The adidas Sambae Wonder White Gum (Women's) was released on December 1, 2023, for $110.

name: White Pure Silver
title: ASICS GT-2160 White Pure Silver
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 White Pure Silver is a performance shoe that pays homage to the running style of the early 2010s era. 
   
The White Pure Silver ASICS GT-2160 has a base of white mesh for breathability. Calf leather overlays in Pure Silver appear on the upper, forming the toebox and eyestays and supporting the sides of the shoe as well as the heel. These overlays are accented with black and Pale Blue, and the Pale Blue is most prevalent on the classic ASICS design across the side panels. GT-2160 branding can be seen on the lateral heel, while Gel branding is found at the back and another ASICS logo adorns the tongue. The midsole features Gel technology for support and comfort and is accented with blue, and the outsole is black.

Our favorite thing about this shoe is the way the colors of the upper’s design bleed into the midsole on the lateral side, giving this shoe a streamlined look. The ASICS GT-2160 White Pure Silver was released on April 27, 2024, for $120.

name: The Simpsons Living Room
title: adidas Forum Low The Simpsons Living Room
description:
The adidas Forum Low The Simpsons Living Room is another collaboration between the iconic German sneaker company and the world-famous animated series. This shoe takes a classic silhouette originally designed in 1984 and dresses it in the colors and details from the living room of The Simpsons.

The base of The Simpsons Living Room X adidas Forum Low is smooth pink leather, overlaid with aqua green suede at the toe and heel, with hairy darker pink suede for the characteristic three stripes on the side panel. Mustard brown corduroy overlays mimic the couch from The Simpsons living room, while the chenille toebox recalls the carpet. adidas trefoil branding lands on the side panel and dual branding graces the insole. The white EVA foam midsole sits atop a white, yellow, and gum rubber outsole with trefoils worked into the traction pattern.

What we love most about this shoe are the embroidered details. The family dog, Santa's Little Helper, and cat, Snowball II, adorn the heels, while the picture on the living room wall is featured on the tongue. The adidas Forum Low The Simpsons Living Room debuted on November 11, 2023, for $120.

name: Kith Seoul
title: ASICS Gel-Lyte III Remastered Kith Seoul
description:
The ASICS Gel-Lyte III Remastered Kith Seoul pushes the limits of the original GEL-LYTE III design with a bold, mixed-material construction.

Released to celebrate the opening of Kith’s flagship store in Seoul, South Korea, this sneaker is the third edition of ASICS and designer Ronnie Fieg’s GEL-LYTE III Remastered. It pays homage to South Korea’s flag through the colorway, which sees the quilted-suede base dressed in Off-white with red, Chambray blue, and black accents. The overlays are crafted from hairy suede, while the stripe-like overlays are made from leather. Finally, the sneaker houses a lining made of terry cloth instead of synthetic material.

Our experts like how far the upper design strays from the typical Gel-Lyte III look. Specifically, the combination of hairy and smooth suede gives the sneaker a premium, handcrafted feel, standing out from all other models before it. The ASICS Gel-Lyte III Remastered Kith Seoul was released on May 31, 2024, and sold for $195.

name: The Grinch
title: adidas Forum Low The Grinch
description:
The adidas Forum Low The Grinch was made available as part of a special edition that came in different color codes, including green, black, and white.

Polyester is the main material used in the manufacture of this adidas Forum model. The upper of the shoe includes a long hair suede executed in the "Grinch" green colorway. The jewels on the tongue, the long green tongue, and the green rubber outsole complete the design. The 3-Stripes as well as Trefoil are visible on its sides.  

The adidas Forum Low The Grinch was first released on December 1st, 2022, with a retail price of $120.

name: Wave Runner (Kids)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Wave Runner (Kids)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Wave Runner Solid Grey Kids was released to improve Yeezy's sleek minimal aesthetic design and deliver a chunky signature, in a kids’ shoe. The sneaker comes in a Solid Grey/Chalk White/Core Black colorway.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Wave Runner Solid Grey Kids displays a layered upper crafted with nubuck and leather. Also, the shoe displays a collar and mid-panel with solid gray mesh. The quarter panel, forefoot, and mid-panel house contrasting black-hued patterns. Furthermore, this kids’ sneaker showcases a Boost unit affixed to the midsole to deliver cushioning, while a patterned herringbone on the outsole provides traction.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Wave Runner Solid Grey Kids was released on August 17th, 2017, at a retail price of $180.

name: Collegiate Green Gum (Women's)
title: adidas Sambae Collegiate Green Gum (Women's)
description:
The adidas Sambae Collegiate Green Gum (Women's) is a women’s shoe with a classic minimalistic design made of leather.

This version of the adidas Sambae is made with a Collegiate Green leather upper sectioned off with subtle stitching. Collegiate Green suede forms the toe cap, and the traditional adidas three stripes logo appears on the sides in white stitching. "Samba" is written on the lateral side in gold lettering. The heel collar is made of white leather and the tongue also sports an adidas logo patch. A thick, chunky gum rubber outsole rounds out the look of this shoe.

Our favorite thing about this sneaker is the white stitching that forms the adidas three-stripe logo on the sides of the shoe, as it provides texture and visual interest. The adidas Sambae Collegiate Green Gum (Women's) was released on December 1, 2023, for a price of $110.

name: Black Spark
title: adidas Adizero Adios Pro 3 Black Spark
description:
The adidas Adizero Adios Pro 3 Black Spark brings innovative technology and bold design to elite running shoes. This shoe is designed for speed and combines advanced engineering with a striking black, yellow, and orange aesthetic to redefine performance on the track and road.

The Black Spark Adizero Adios Pro 3 by adidas features ENERGYRODS 2.0 embedded in a Lightstrike Pro midsole for optimized propulsion. The breathable mesh upper comes in black with fiery yellow and white accents. The Continental rubber outsole offers traction on various surfaces. The adidas Adizero Adios Pro 3 was developed through extensive research and testing to optimize marathon running performance, including performance testing, materials science, and more.

As the experts, something we love about the Black Spark adidas Adizero Adios Pro 3 is the curve that molds the foot’s arc. The 3-Stripes in white and the golden detail in the outsole make these shoes one to watch in the gym or elsewhere. Retailing at $250, it was released on 17th April 2024 and combines technical precision with cutting-edge design.

name: Beam Orange
title: adidas Gazelle Indoor Beam Orange
description:
The adidas Gazelle Indoor Beam Orange is a variation of the classic adidas Gazelle sneaker, known for its heritage and timeless design. It draws inspiration from indoor sports and training shoes, particularly the original adidas Gazelle, which debuted back in the 60s.

The shoes have a low top silhouette featuring an orange upper made from leather with suede overlays on the lace eyelets and the T-toe. It is worth mentioning that the orange hue on the suede overlays is of a darker shade than the orange painted on the leather, adding some visual interest to the shoes. They also have contrasting white accents on the heel tab and serrated three stripes on the sides.

Our favorite bit on the shoes is the semi-translucent gum outsole, which not only adds to the shoe’s aesthetic but also offers optimum grip on various surfaces, including indoor surfaces. The adidas Gazelle Indoor Beam Orange was first released on March 18, 2023, retailing at $110.

name: Phosphor
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 MNVN Laceless Phosphor
description:
While the adidas Yeezy 700 MNVN Laceless Phosphor does have the same bright yellow nylon upper and reflective motocross-inspired 700 graphics as the original Phosphor release, there are two key differences. First of all, this design is laceless as stated in the name. Its slip-on entry is perfect for those who love the convenience of a Foam RNNR but want a little more protection. Secondly, its Boost midsole is white instead of black, altering the overall look but still delivering the same, premium cushioning.

The adidas Yeezy 700 MNVN Laceless Phosphor released in June of 2022 and retailed for $220.

name: White Putty
title: ASICS GT-2160 White Putty
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 White Putty is a running sneaker featuring a White mesh upper accented by linear overlays in Putty’s gray shade, accented by metallic silver. ASICS, GEL, and GT-2160 branding appear on the tongue and rear and outer heel. A sculpted midsole in White displays GEL technology inserts and is accented by a Putty outsole.

ASICS, hailing from Kobe, Japan, crafts its athletic wear based around the theme of sound mind in a sound body, inspired by a Latin phrase. With this ethos, the brand is always referencing itself, aiming to refine its signature running shoes for improved performance. The GT-2160 recalls the GT-2000 styles that released circa 2010, preserving its signature aesthetics like the curved forefront and segmented sole.

Our experts feel that the best feature of the GT-2160 is its metallic accents, which add excitement to the White Putty colorway. The ASICS GT-2160 White Putty released on April 27, 2024, and retailed for $120.

name: Cloud White Legacy Teal (Women's)
title: adidas Samba OG Cloud White Legacy Teal (Women's)
description:
The adidas Samba OG Cloud White Legacy Teal (Women's) reimagines a classic profile with fresh, modern colors. This shoe is designed to be as practical as it is stylish and a versatile choice for any event.

The Cloud White Legacy Teal Samba OG (Women's) by adidas has a crisp leather upper with cream suede overlays on the toe cap and heel. The Legacy Teal accents on the signature 3-Stripes add a subtle contrast to the white base. Its low profile is there for extra longevity and extra grip. It was created as an indoor football shoe in the 1950s but has since become a loved design by players and fashion enthusiasts alike.

As the experts, one thing we enjoy about the adidas Samba OG Cloud White Legacy Teal (Women's) is the premium suede detailing that adds texture to its design. Another key feature is the rubber sole's practical traction. When it was released on 1st July 2024, the retail price was $95.

name: 1998 All-Star Game (2024)
title: adidas Crazy 8 1998 All-Star Game (2024)
description:
The adidas Crazy 8 1998 All-Star Game (2024) is a high-top shoe that takes its inspiration from the original version of the 1990s.

This iteration of the adidas Crazy 8 features an upper made of both tumbled and patent leather in black. The adidas three stripes appear in shiny black running down each side of the shoe, while the toe box is made of black mesh and covered by a black leather toe cap. Ankle straps with a shock of gray run from the top of the laces and crisscross at the heel, while the adidas brand name can be found on the lateral ankle strap and the three stripes are found again at the back of the heel. The tongue features a deep purple adidas logo patch and a pull tab. A chunky and wavy black and white rubber outsole completes the look.

Our favorite feature of this shoe is the rubber outsole in black and white, which adds an element of visual interest to the otherwise all-black shoe. The adidas Crazy 8 1998 All-Star Game (2024) was released on February 15, 2024, for a price of $160.

name: Better Scarlet (Women's)
title: adidas SL 72 Better Scarlet (Women's)
description:
The adidas SL 72 Better Scarlet (Women's) is a shoe for women with a sleek, thin build meant to increase running performance because of its lightweight feel.
  
The Better Scarlet (Women's) adidas SL 72 features an upper made of Better Scarlet leather.
