Better Scarlet leather overlays also form the t-shaped toe cap, mudguard, and heel counter, as well as the eyestays. The classic 3-Stripes run down each side in serrated Cream White. The heel collar bears a white adidas trefoil logo, while the tongue contains a white logo patch. The midsole is enhanced with EVA foam and is branded on the lateral side, while the outsole is black.

What we like best about this training shoe is the bold Better Scarlet colorway, which immediately draws the eye. The adidas SL 72 Better Scarlet (Women's) was first released on March 28, 2024, for an original retail price of $100.

name: Bape 30th Anniversary Green Camo
title: adidas Forum 84 Low Bape 30th Anniversary Green Camo
description:
The adidas Forum 84 Low Bape 30th Anniversary Green Camo presents an intriguing collaboration between the tried and true basketball silhouette and the Japanese streetwear and lifestyle fashion brand that opened its first store in 1993.

The Bape 30th Anniversary Edition of the adidas Forum 84 in a Green Camo colorway sports a leather upper with a grainy texture and the classic Bape camo pattern. True to the Forum silhouette, a hook and loop strap secures the top of the laces and the toe box is perforated for enhanced ventilation. The EVA midsole along with the chunky rubber outsole provide cushioning, support, and bounce for the basketball court or the city streets.

What we love most about this sneaker are all the hits of dual branding, including the Bathing Ape icon nestled in the lateral side camo on the quarter panel, just behind the cut-out window featuring the iconic adidas three stripes. The adidas Forum 84 Low Bape 30th Anniversary Green Camo was released on May 20, 2023 for a retail price of $180.

name: Core Black Cloud White (Women's)
title: adidas Campus 00s Core Black Cloud White (Women's)
description:
The adidas Campus 00s Core Black Cloud White (Women's) is a sleek looking adidas Campus 00s sneaker dressed in a core black and cloud white scheme that pulls inspiration from the Campus 80s silhouette and adds bigger, bolder design elements.

The Campus 00s from adidas builds upon the design of the legacy model known as the Campus 80s. This iteration was influenced by skateboarders and their beloved style. Hence, you’ll spot a chunky off-white midsole that sits atop a gum colored outsole. The core black velvet-like upper boasts a compact toe box and extra wide tongue area. Oversized white stripes adorn the side panels, and zigzag stitching around the heel tab adds a touch of playfulness.

We think that the black and white speckled laces add a fun element to the adidas Campus 00s Core Black Cloud White (Women's) that was released on June 1, 2024, with a $110 price tag.

name: Semi Green Spark (Women's)
title: adidas Gazelle Indoor Semi Green Spark (Women's)
description:
The adidas Gazelle Indoor Semi Green Spark (Women's) is a women’s training shoe with a bright springtime colorway.

This iteration of the adidas Gazelle Indoor comes with an upper made of light Semi Green Spark suede. The same color of suede also forms the t-shaped toe cap so the difference between the two layers is subtle. The three stripes that are synonymous with the adidas brand run down each side of the shoe in off-white leather, while the same color of leather forms the heel collar. The Gazelle model name appears on the lateral side in Almost Yellow stitching. The white tongue is perforated for breathability and contains an adidas logo patch. The shoe sits on top of a classic branded gum rubber outsole.

What we like most about this sneaker is the bright colorway, which allows the shoe to stand out during spring. The adidas Gazelle Indoor Semi Green Spark (Women's) was released on December 24, 2023, for $120.

name: Black Seal Grey
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Black Seal Grey
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Black Seal Grey is a running shoe from the ASICS brand that is a retooled version of their original Gel-Kayano design that was released in 2008.

This updated silhouette maintains the beloved Gel technology cushioning that was introduced in the late 2000s and introduces some new sneaker tech to continue its evolution in performance. The upper is made with mixed materials, leather and mesh, and is dressed in a black and seal grey color scheme. Both sides feature the signature ASICS stripes with the lateral side sporting thicker seal grey outlining around the black lines than the medial side. The TRUSSTIC support system, a shank between the forefoot and rear foot, rounds out this shoe.

We think that the proprietary cushioned Gel technology providing excellent shock absorption is what gives this sneaker its pizzazz. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Black Seal Grey released on January 1, 2024, with a retail price of $150.

name: Mineral Green (Women's)
title: adidas Handball Spezial Mineral Green (Women's)
description:
The adidas Handball Spezial Mineral Green (Women's) merges classic design with updated elements to create a minimalist but striking addition to the brand's collection. Its inspiration stems from adidas's original 1979 handball shoe.

The Mineral Green Handball Spezial shoe for women shows off a corduroy and suede upper that gives extra texture and durability and comes with a 3-Stripes design in contrasting off-white. This updated edition reimagines the age-old handball silhouette with a fresh Mineral Green finish paired with a gum rubber outsole for timeless appeal. Originally designed for elite players, it balances vintage charm with everyday usability and offers reliable comfort inspired by the company´s performance and style codes.

As experts, one thing we love about the adidas Handball Spezial Mineral Green (Women's) is the combination of corduroy and suede for a unique tactile experience. Another feature that stands out for us is its gum outsole for grip. It was released on 2nd September 2024 for $110.

name: Triple Black
title: adidas Gazelle Triple Black
description:
The original adidas Gazelle Triple Black sneakers can be traced all the way back to 1966, but adidas unveiled a revamped version of these sneakers in 1991, featuring more modern materials incorporated into them. adidas also reissued this version of the Gazelle Triple Black sneakers in 2018.

These re-released sneakers have a black nubuck upper with black synthetic overlays. They also have a black tonal trim along with a black outsole and black adidas branding on the tongue. They're finished off with black laces and even a black synthetic lining.

What our experts are most impressed with when it comes to these Gazelles is that adidas managed to make them look modern without making any big changes to them. This is the true sign of a timeless sneaker that won't ever go out of style. The adidas Gazelle Triple Black was released on July 18, 2018, and retailed for $100.

name: Olympic Medals
title: ASICS GEL-Kayano 14 Olympic Medals
description:
The ASICS GEL-Kayano 14 Olympic Medals edition is a stunning tribute to athletic excellence. This men's sneaker showcases a pristine white and cream colorway, accented with gold details that evoke the prestige of Olympic medals. The shoe's design seamlessly blends style and performance, featuring ASICS' renowned GEL technology for superior cushioning and comfort.

Built for both casual wear and athletic pursuits, the GEL-Kayano 14 boasts a sleek silhouette that pays homage to its performance running heritage. The upper combines breathable mesh with supportive overlays, ensuring a secure fit and enhanced durability. The cream midsole houses ASICS' innovative cushioning system, providing responsive shock absorption for all-day comfort. Our experts state this product is great for athletes and sneaker enthusiasts alike, offering a perfect balance of style, comfort, and performance-driven design.

name: NAKED Copenhagen Lace
title: adidas Samba OG NAKED Copenhagen Lace
description:
The adidas Samba OG NAKED Copenhagen Lace is the result of an exclusive collaboration between adidas and NAKED Copenhagen that is dressed in various white textures such as leather, lace, and gritty suede.

This sneaker pays homage to the art of lace making and all its beauty. The iconic t-toe overlay of the Samba OG is flanked in an off-white suede that resembles terrycloth. It then flows up, and this same material is used for the eyelet. The smooth leather upper in white is then the base for the crystal white lace detailing used for the legendary three stripes and on the heel tab. The lateral side of the left shoe sports silver SAMBA lettering on the side panel, while the lateral side of the right shoe boasts NAKED CPH. A co-branded patch sits atop of the tongue.

If you ask us, we think the standout feature of the adidas Samba OG NAKED Copenhagen Lace is its elegant aesthetic. The combination of premium materials and exquisite design make it a versatile shoe that will pair well with casual or formal stylings. This sneaker debuted on August 7, 2024, with a retail price of $140.

name: Faded Archive
title: adidas Gazelle Faded Archive
description:
The adidas Gazelle Faded Archive is an update of the original design from the 60s with a fresh updated contemporary look.

The Faded Archive adidas Gazelle combines Dark Green, Cream White, and Off-White across its construction giving it a clean design. The sneaker has a suede upper in dark green contrasted by a white OrthoLite® sock liner with a synthetic lining and a round toe. For branding, the sneaker has high-contrast serrated adidas 3-Stripes, Trefoil logos on the heel and foam tongue, and a gold Gazelle logo on the side panels. The rubber sole incorporates midsole cushioning for added comfort, and its textured tread on the outsole ensures reliable traction.

What makes the adidas Gazelle Faded Archive so special in our eyes is the classic T-toe resting on a classic white outsole design that has been maintained from the OG model. The shoe was released on 9th December 2022 for $100.

name: Earth
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Earth
description:
Yeezy delivers a new rendition of its most popular design with the adidas Yeezy 350 Earth, now available on StockX. This 350 V2 strays from newer releases by bringing back a heel tab that is present in early 350 silhouettes. This model was released as a regional exclusive specific to the Americas.

This Yeezy 350 V2 Earth is composed of a mud Primeknit upper with a translucent outer side stripe. A mud colored Boost cushioned sole and mud interior completes the design. These sneakers released in February of 2020 and retailed for $220.

name: Bape Sand
title: adidas NRTN Bape Sand
description:
The adidas NRTN Bape Sand is a shoe designed as part of a collaboration between adidas and the fashion brand A Bathing Ape.

The Bape Sand adidas NRTN has an upper made of calf suede in a Sand Tan color. This color makes up the sides, heel, and toebox, while a dark brown suede forms the mudguard that rounds out the entire shoe, except the heel. Dark green suede panels form the eyestays, while the adidas three stripes are featured in thick white fabric down each side. The lateral side of the mudguard features a white A Bathing Ape logo, while the tongue features adidas branding. The Bape Sta logo is present on the heel, while directly underneath it on the midsole the adidas trefoil logo is found. The shoe sits on a textured tan midsole and a gum rubber outsole. 

The most interesting thing about this sneaker is the chunky design, which adds an element of modern style. The adidas NRTN Bape Sand was released on April 20, 2024, for $150.

name: Wonder Taupe Night Indigo
title: adidas Gazelle Wonder Taupe Night Indigo
description:
The adidas Gazelle Wonder Taupe Night Indigo is an indoor training shoe with a suede upper and a timeless design.

This colorway of the adidas Gazelle is made with a suede upper in a Wonder Taupe tan color. A T-shaped suede toe cap provides sectioning while subtle stitching separates the forefoot from the heel. The classic adidas three stripes logo is seen on each side in Night Indigo leather, and the word GAZELLE is written on the lateral side in gold letters. The heel collar also comes in Night Indigo leather and sports a Wonder Taupe adidas trefoil logo. The padded tongue also features adidas branding. A gum rubber outsole completes this design.

What we like most about this sneaker is its neutral colorway, which allows it to go with any outfit. The adidas Gazelle Wonder Taupe Night Indigo was released on December 1, 2023, for $100.

name: Wales Bonner Silver
title: adidas Samba Wales Bonner Silver
description:
June 2023 saw the bold arrival of the adidas Samba Wales Bonner collaboration in a glinting Silver colorway. In an homage to vintage aesthetics, adidas partners with the innovative Wales Bonner to reimagine the Samba silhouette.

Featuring high-quality leather overlays, the sneakers shimmer with a glossy Silver finish. Adidas' iconic three stripes manifest in a vibrant woven off white contrast hue, adding intrigue to the side panels. The shoe's brown sole offers a retro touch to the otherwise futuristic aesthetic. Detailed with a Wales Bonner signature charm, the collab stamps its uniqueness in the sneaker world. Boasting comfort and style, these kicks hold the power to enhance any fit instantly.

The adidas Samba Wales Bonner in Silver released on June 9, 2023, retailing at a price of $200. This blend of retro and modern vibes is a killer addition to any sneaker arsenal.

name: Piedmont Gray
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Piedmont Gray
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 Piedmont Gray takes the iconic Gel-1130 silhouette and adds a neutral Piedmont Gray and Sheet colorway.

As an evolved iteration of the Gel-1000 series, this technical running sneaker includes several contemporary upgrades. Synthetic leather replaces genuine leather on the upper, increasing durability and providing a modern feel. The base is crafted from lightweight mesh in Piedmont Gray, while Sheet accents cover the overlays. Adding responsive cushioning underfoot, Gel technology complements the midsole’s EVA foam. In addition, the rubber outsole comes in Piedmont Gray and increases traction on a variety of surfaces. Finally, off-white laces thread through the eyelets and complement the color of the midsole as well as the branding details on the tongue.

Our experts like the design similarities between this sneaker and the Gel Kayano 14, including the slightly bulky silhouette. The ASICS Gel-1130 Piedmont Gray was released on February 10, 2022, and sold for $80.

name: Cream
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 V2 Cream
description:
After a brief hiatus in 2020, the Yeezy 700 V2 made its return in 2021. adidas and Kanye West bring back the silhouette in a colorway similar to 2018’s Static 700 V2. This Cream design delivers similar tonal colors that we’ve come to expect from the Three Stripes and the artist.

The adidas Yeezy 700 V2 Cream is suited in a familiar fashion that helped garner its popularity amongst Yeezy fans. The upper showcases many reflective elements, from the lace loops to its stripe detailing. These reflective additions are met with hits of Cream-colored leather on the toe and mudguard. Lastly, mesh underlays add breathability to the wearer while a BOOST outsole brings additional comfort.

The adidas Yeezy 700 V2 Cream released in March of 2021 for $240.

name: Digital Camo
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Digital Camo
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Digital Camo is part of NBA player LaMelo Ball’s first collaboration with Puma.

The limited-edition Camo print design that contrasts the Ultra Orange outsole really makes this sneaker stand out. This outsole wraps around the shoe and features three "X" shapes that overlap the midsole. The Camo print on the lightweight mesh upper comes in Pale Khaki, giving it a desert aesthetic. Leaf-like embroidery graces the lateral side panel, while cut-out leaf shapes occupy the medial side. The sneaker houses a lace-up closure and Puma branding details on the tongue. A Puma cat logo and "M.E.L.O" lettering decorate the heel in Ultra Orange.

What do our experts like about this sneaker? The mid-boot construction provides support while creating a smooth silhouette. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Digital Camo was released on March 24th, 2023, and retailed at a price of $150.

name: Wonder Silver
title: adidas Samba OG Wonder Silver
description:
The adidas Samba OG Wonder Silver (Women's) is a performance shoe that takes its design inspiration from the original model released for football in the 1950s. 
  
The Wonder Silver (Women's) adidas Samba OG has a pig suede upper in a Pale Gray-blue Wonder Silver color. Overlays of the same color form the toe cap as well as the eyestays, and another panel forms the heel area. The serrated 3-Stripes in Chalk White appear on each side as branding elements, while the heel counter is also white. The Samba brand name can be found on the lateral side in metallic gold letters. A bright blue adidas logo patch can be found on the tongue. The classic gum rubber midsole and outsole support the shoe, but this time in an off-white color. 

What stands out about this shoe is the Wonder Silver colorway, which is neutral and subtle. The  adidas Samba OG Wonder Silver (Women's) was released on May 4, 2024, for $100.

name: Black White Dark Gum
title: adidas Samba Classic Black White Dark Gum
description:
The adidas Samba Classic Black White Dark Gum is a classic sneaker and streetwear staple.​
​​
​The Classic adidas Samba is made from premium leather and comes in a black-and-white colorway. The sneakers have the iconic serrated 3-Stripes that identify the brand, as well as the gold "Samba" and the adidas logo on the foldable tongue. It has black laces and a black gum sole. The shoe has a suede toe overlay and a woven "SAMBA" tongue label.​
​
​The adidas Samba Classic Black White Dark Gum was released on June 1, 2022, for a retail price of $70.

name: Stone Salt
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Stone Salt
description:
The upper of the adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Pyrite is constructed of tonal grey camo Primeknit with perforations on each lateral side. At the base, a white semi-translucent Boost midsole provides structure and support for the woven design.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Pyrite released in October of 2021 and retailed for $230.

name: by Ronnie Fieg Kithmas White Multi
title: adidas Clarks 8th Street Samba by Ronnie Fieg Kithmas White Multi
description:
The adidas Clarks 8th Street Samba by Ronnie Fieg Kithmas White Multi represents a collaboration among designer and Kith founder Ronnie Fieg adidas Originals and Clarks Originals.

The Ronnie Fieg Kithmas White Multi iteration of the adidas Clarks 8th Street Samba features an upper crafted of Clarks Originals chalk white cow suede. The toe cap has a t-shaped darker suede overlay, while the leather signature adidas side-panel three stripes are in dark colors reminiscent of Christmas. The leather heel tab is dark green to match one of the stripes. Triple branding is debossed on the tongue tag and the leather heel liner. Samba branding is debossed alongside the top lateral-side stripe.

One feature of this sneaker that our shoe experts particularly enjoy is the Clarks Originals crepe rubber outsole that gives this shoe such a distinctive look. The adidas Clarks 8th Street Samba by Ronnie Fieg Kithmas White Multi was released on December 25, 2023, for a retail price of $220.

name: Beluga 2.0
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Beluga 2.0
description: The Yeezy Beluga 2.0 takes Kanye West's famous adidas sneakers full circle by returning to the colors of the first adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2. While the original colorway featured a bright orange (officially Solar Red) stripe across the side, the 2017 release of the Yeezy Beluga colorway is much more subtle. This colorway utilizes the same Zebra-like stripes as the original but the SPLY-350 branding is the only part of the upper with a contrasted color-this time called Bold Orange. The Yeezy Beluga 2.0 nickname comes from the similarities to the earlier colorway but the official colorway of this adidas Yeezy release is Grey, Bold Orange, and Dark Grey. The toned down color combo made it an appealing shoe for the masses compared to some previous Yeezy colorways. Despite rumors suggesting an October drop, the official release date for the Beluga 2.0 was November 25th, 2017. Since then it has been one of the most active sneakers on StockX, continually selling well above its retail price. You can get the Yeezy Beluga 2.0 on StockX now by placing a Bid or choosing to Buy Now.

name: Team Color Green Gecko (GS)
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Lo Team Color Green Gecko (GS)
description: The Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 Lo Team Color Green Gecko GS is a stylish and functional sneaker that is perfect for basketball enthusiasts and fashion-forward individuals alike. This shoe features a green gecko colorway that is eye-catching and unique, making it a standout addition to any sneaker collection. Crafted from high-quality materials, the Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 Lo Team Color Green Gecko GS is designed to provide superior comfort and support during intense physical activity. The shoe's upper is made from a combination of synthetic leather and mesh, which allows for breathability and flexibility. The midsole is constructed from EVA foam, which provides cushioning and shock absorption, while the outsole is made from durable rubber that offers excellent traction on the court. Released on October 21, 2022, the Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 Lo Team Color Green Gecko GS is priced at $95, making it an affordable option for those looking for a high-quality basketball shoe. Something we love about the Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 Lo Team Color Green Gecko GS is its unique colorway, which is sure to turn heads on and off the court. Our experts think that the standout feature of this shoe is its combination of comfort, support, and durability, making it an excellent choice for basketball players of all skill levels. Overall, we love the Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 Lo Team Color Green Gecko GS for its style, functionality, and affordability.

name: Andrew Reynolds Chocolate
title: New Balance 480 Andrew Reynolds Chocolate
description:
The New Balance 480 Andrew Reynolds Chocolate is a skateboarding sneaker designed by skateboarding legend Andrew Reynolds.

This version of the New Balance 480 features a chocolate brown suede and leather upper with perforations in the toebox for breathability. Chocolate brown suede overlays in a slightly darker shade round the toebox, cross the midsoles, and round out the heel. The New Balance N appears on the sides in an off-white color, while the cushioned tongue features a New Balance patch with Reynolds’ name and 480 on it. The heel collar also contains the New Balance brand name. A dark brown rubber sole completes the look.

Our favorite feature of this shoe is the combination of suede and leather in different shades of brown that make up the upper. The New Balance 480 Andrew Reynolds Chocolate was released on September 18, 2023, for a retail price of $100.

name: MiUSA Bodega Here To Stay
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Bodega Here To Stay
description:
To celebrate 15 years of business, Boston-based boutique Bodega collaborated with New Balance on the 990v3. The two brands are no strangers to working together, and their last collaborative effort was on the 997S in 2020.

The New Balance 990v3 Bodega Here To Stay was inspired by the idea of preservation and people’s need to be remembered. Neutral tones make up the majority of the sneaker, with a cream ENCAP midsole and brown suede and beige leather overlays. Bodega’s logo is printed in bright crimson on the heel tab, while "2006" and "2021" are embroidered on the heel cap to commemorate the store’s 15-year anniversary.

The New Balance 990v3 Bodega Here To Stay released in June of 2021 for $220.

name: Black White
title: Puma Suede XL Black White
description:
The Puma Suede XL Black White is a low-top lifestyle shoe with a chunky base that adds height, presenting in a crisp black and white color.

The Suede XL pulls design inspiration from the original adidas Suede silhouette. While it stays true to some of the iconic elements, it mixes it up by adding a mega padded tongue and height boosting midsole. Dressed in plush black suede, the upper boasts white leather Formstrips on the side panels. A white liner and white midsole give this shoe a ying-yang appearance. Thick black laces complete the look.

What do we think is a special design element of Puma Suede XL Black White? It’d have to be the gold-colored accents that appear in the branding hits on the lateral side panel and the heel. They add just the right amount of pizzazz. This shoe retailed for $100 when it was released on April 8, 2018.

name: White Nori
title: New Balance 550 White Nori
description:
The New Balance 550 White Nori combines white, nori, and brighton grey tones with a retro basketball vibe straight out of the 1980s.

Since being introduced in 1989, the New Balance 550 silhouette re-releases in different colorways. This version features a predominantly synthetic white upper with ventilation holes on the quarters for breathability. Brighton grey suede accents the toe cap, while earthy nori green highlights the heel and the signature oversized "N" branding on the sides. Additional branding details are found on the heel, midsole, and lateral quarter panel, where a black "550" is prominently stamped.

A standout detail is the tongue logo, a basketball graphic designed to look like it's bouncing toward you, adding a playful touch to its vintage aesthetic. With its gum outsole, thick midsole, oversized tongue, and chunky build, this shoe embodies classic basketball style. Retailing for $110, the New Balance 550 White Nori launched on April 1, 2024, as a nostalgic nod to old-school sneaker culture.

name: Beef and Broccoli
title: New Balance 9060 Beef and Broccoli
description:
Hairy brown suede overlays with a rough finish dominate the New Balance 9060 Beef and Broccoli and are found on the heel counters, medials, mudguards, and tongues. 

Its base is made of black mesh, while the heels, toe boxes, and back tabs are lightly trimmed in dark green leather. In addition, the dark green hue is adorned on the top eyelets and the area around the profile "N" logos, matching the internal logo's linear design. The sneaker is finished with wavy ABZORB sole units decorated with green and black accents, as well as N logos that are printed on the lateral, medial, and toe tips.

The New Balance 9060 Beef and Broccoli was released on 14th January 2023 and retailed at $150.

name: Tail Light
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Tail Light
description:
Yeezy continues its barrage of 350 V2 releases with the adidas Yeezy 350 Tail Light, now available on StockX. This 350 V2 strays from newer releases by bringing back the heel tab that was present in early 350 silhouettes. This model was released as a regional exclusive specific to Europe and Russia.

This Yeezy 350 V2 Tail Light is composed of a grey Primeknit upper with a translucent outer side stripe that reveals hints of orange toward the heel of the upper. A translucent Boost cushioned sole and grey interior completes the design. These sneakers released in February of 2020 and retailed for $220.

name: MiUK Rock Ridge Grey
title: New Balance 991v2 MiUK Rock Ridge Grey
description:
The New Balance 991v2 MiUK Rock Ridge Gray is a handcrafted New Balance sneaker made in their UK factory in Flimby, on the Cumbria coast. This deluxe sneaker delivers cachet, style, and comfortable functionality.

The Made in England Rock Ridge Gray New Balance 991 V2 features an upper of soft gray pigskin suede with underlays of gray mesh and darker gray leather. The off-white ENCAP midsole features FuelCell foam cushioning throughout the length of the shoe and is supported by a durable polyurethane rim. The black and gray rubber outsole is lugged for impact absorption in traction and has channels, including a deep blue one running vertically, to offer flexibility and reduce the shoe’s weight.

What we enjoy most about this curated sneaker are the stand-out hits of branding that pepper the upper. A silver side panel N, 991 embroidered on the lateral collar, V2 on the heel tab, and the tongue tag emblazoned with New Balance Made in England all lend this shoe and extra note of distinction. The New Balance 991v2 MiUK Rock Ridge Gray was released on October 27, 2023, for a retail price of $250.

name: MiUSA Grey (Women's)
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Grey (Women's)
description:
New Balance first released its now-iconic 990 running sneakers back in 1982. The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Grey (Women's) offered up a modern take on these shoes and helped usher them into a new era.

The upper on this New Balance 990v6 was made out of suede with synthetic overlays and mesh underlays. It also had a texture to it to provide it with a more premium look and feel. There were also several different shades of grey incorporated into the mix that worked well with the white in part of the midsole.

But the best part about this sneaker, according to our experts, was all the technology crammed into it. It featured FuelCell foam to make it more responsive as well as ENCAP cushioning in the midsole to make it more comfortable overall. The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Grey (Women's) was released on November 4, 2022, when it retailed for $200.

name: White Dune (Women's)
title: ASICS Gel-1130 White Dune (Women's)
description:
Stepping out in pure style, the ASICS Gel-1130 for Women reveals itself in the pristine White and Dune colorway.

This sneaker stands out with an upper that artfully incorporates breathable mesh, wrapping the vamp and extending to the sides, ensuring not just a luxe look but optimum airflow too. While the majority of its form boasts this mesh, the subtleties lie in the intricate detailing and the plush cushioning of the Gel technology. Drenched in the White and Dune palette with silver accents incorporated throughout, this silhouette is more than just a sneaker; it's a statement. The design intricacies include ASICS’ renowned stripes and the Gel badge of honor on the heel. Our absolute fave? The comfort level that the Gel midsole delivers, making every step feel like walking on clouds.

Making strides in both design and tech, the ASICS Gel-1130 White Dune dropped with a price tag that of$95.

name: Earls Collection Ngāwari
title: ASICS GT-2160 Earls Collection Ngāwari
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 Earls Collection Ngāwari pays homage to Lewis Brown, the man who founded the high-end sportswear label. Created with Māori cultural touchstones, this singular sneaker pops with style grounded insignificance with every step.

Built upon an upper of natural cotton mesh, the Earls Collection x ASICS GT-2160 Earls "Ngāwari" features brown suede overlays undulating across the shoe, offering signature style and structure. Light green detailing along the heel, laces, and supportive midfoot plate are a nod to pounamu, an emerald-colored rock found in Southern New Zealand. A cream-colored EVA midsole encapsulates emerald GEL inserts in the heel for ultimate cushioning. The multi-colored outsole features lugs for tractions and grooves to reduce the weight of the shoe and facilitate flexibility.

Our favorite aspect of this sneaker is the insole design. A graphic depicts a paua, a large New Zealand sea snail. The ASICS GT-2160 Earls Collection was released on February 23, 2023, for $150 retail.

name: Randomevent The Sweetness of Kin
title: New Balance 9060 Randomevent The Sweetness of Kin
description:
The New Balance 9060 Randomevent The Sweetness of Kin is a black, blue, and brown colorway from the Sweetness of Kin pack. This iteration is a New Balance 9060 while a 1906R model was also released in the pack.

New Balance teamed up with Chinese fashion brand Randomevent to produce a tastefully designed new colorway of the 9060. "The Sweetness of Kin" nickname this colorway carries emphasizes the need for relationships and staying true to roots and ancestors. As such, this colorway debuts a warm, earthy toned brown midsole and outsole that supports a black suede mesh upper with a blue outlined "N" on the side panel. Shiny overlays on the toe area invoke the stars and universal connection that all kin share.

We particularly like that the New Balance 9060 Randomevent The Sweetness of Kin has ABZORB and ABZORB SBS cushioning tech for superior comfort. This sneaker was released on January 12, 2024, with a $170 recommended retail price.

name: Beige
title: New Balance 9060 Beige
description:
The New Balance 9060 Beige blends old-fashioned aesthetics with creative design elements. Its thoughtful makeup and distinctive details draw from New Balance’s roots to give you a functional shoe with trendy aspects.

The Beige 9060 by New Balance features a mixed-material upper that includes mesh, suede, and synthetic overlays for a layered, dimensional look. The base tone of beige is complemented by lighter and darker beige overlays for added depth. Inspired by early 2000s running silhouettes, its exaggerated sole combines ABZORB and SBS cushioning for improved comfort. This design builds on the legacy of the 990 and 860v2 series and integrates modern updates.

As experts, we enjoy the New Balance 9060 Beige's use of the ABZORB midsole, which adds an extra layer of shock absorption. Another standout feature is the oversized reflective "N" logo, which improves visibility while running. It debuted at $150 retail on July 12, 2024.

name: LaFrancé FOREVER.RARE
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 LaFrancé FOREVER.RARE
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 LaFrancé FOREVER.RARE is a vividly colored sneaker in a collaboration between Puma, LaFrancé, and NBA player LaMelo Ball.

This basketball shoe stands out for the bold graphics across the mesh upper and its colorway of Fluro Green, Green, and Luro Yellow. The mesh upper displays a fleur-de-lis pattern screened across a Fluro Green background, with claw mark-like graphics tearing into the delicate print. The semi-translucent rubber outsole wraps around the bottom of the shoe, giving the illusion of dripping goo. The outsole is crafted from a non-slip material that provides additional traction. The quilted heel counter includes "M.E.L.O," "1+1+1," and "0ofONE" in bold lettering along with a Puma emblem.

Our experts like the nitro foam midsole, which delivers cushioning without weighing the shoe down. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 LaFrancé FOREVER.RARE was released on October 6th, 2023, and retailed at $140.

name: MiUSA Joe Freshgoods Paris Red
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods Paris Red
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods Paris Red is a bold, limited-edition sneaker featuring a vibrant red colorway and collaborative design elements. New Balance, founded in 1906, has a rich history of innovation and quality, creating a notable moment in the brand's legacy with this partnership. This Made in USA shoe combines Freshgoods' signature style with New Balance's performance-driven technology and premium materials.

The JFG x New Balance 990V6 "Paris Red" features a bold, fire engine red hue with contrasting white accents. It combines Joe Freshgoods' vibrant aesthetic with New Balance's iconic 990 series, known for supportive ABZORB technology and premium materials like suede and mesh. 

We like the New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods Paris Red's unique "Paris" script logo and custom-designed tongue label. These subtle details pay homage to Joe Freshgoods' Chicago roots and Parisian inspiration, adding a layer of storytelling to the shoe's design. These shoes were released on July 27, 2024, and their retail price was $220.

name: MiUSA WTAPS
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA WTAPS
description:
The New Balance 990v6 WTAPS is a casual and neutral shoe walking shoe that combines both style and athleticism. It is a subtle take on the original style that features a mixture of suede, nubuck, and mesh fabrics on the body.

The 990v6 WTAPS is the third sneaker collaboration between WTAPS and New Balance. It is made of multiple shades of gray and has a USA graphic at the back of the shoe on the lateral side. New Balance is written on the tongue of the shoe, just underneath the gray laces. The 990v6 WTAPS model also has a tricolor ENCAP midsole.

One feature that our experts particularly love about this model is the FuelCell cushioning technology that was included to make the shoes as comfortable as possible for wearers. The New Balance 990v6 WTAPS was initially released on September 1st, 2023, for a starting retail price of $300.

name: White Rain Cloud Silver Metallic
title: New Balance 1906R White Rain Cloud Silver Metallic
description:
The New Balance 1906R White Rain Cloud Silver Metallic adds a light colorway of white, Rain Cloud, and Silver Metallic to the heritage 1906R design.

Named after the year New Balance was founded, the performance running shoe White Rain Cloud Silver Metallic New Balance 1906R has similar technologies as the 860v2 and the 2002R. For instance, the sole unit boasts responsive N-ergy cushioning gel, segmented ABZORB SBS pods in the heel, and lightweight ACTEVA LITE cushioning. The collection of curving synthetic leather overlays in metallic silver and gold contribute to the sneaker’s high-tech look while adding a dose of glamour. Like other New Balance 1906R models, the "White Rain Cloud Silver Metallic" model features a durable, white mesh upper that gives the sneaker an airy feel.

Our experts like the way the signature New Balance ‘N’ in metallic silver and gold pops out against the white mesh. The New Balance 1906R White Rain Cloud Silver Metallic was released on September 1, 2022, and sold for $155.

name: Kith Cream Sage
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 12.1 Kith Cream Sage
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 12.1 Kith Cream Sage is an athletic shoe featuring a two-tone color palette, with a Cream mesh base and translucent Sage green overlays. Sage green continues on the upper midsole, balanced by Cream and black on the outsole. The inner tip is done in metallic silver, and the tongue and heels display ASICS Gel-Kayano branding.

Japanese athletic wear brand ASICS, founded in 1949, is known for their brand ethos embedded in the company name, which translates to "sound mind, sound body," and they have made a name for themselves by refining and reissuing their signature running sneakers. Kith is an American athletic wear brand known for collaborating with brands and boutiques around the world. The Gel-Kayano 12.1 was designed in collaboration with Kith and was revealed to the public via founder Ronnie Fieg’s Instagram story.

Our experts feel that the best feature of the Gel-Kayano 12.1 is its colorway, which offers a chic update to classic ASICS styling. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 12.1 Kith Cream Sage released on October 21, 2024, and retailed for $195.

name: Carbon (Kids)
title: adidas Yeezy Foam RNR Carbon (Kids)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Foam RNR Carbon (Kids), in kids sizes, is a single unit EVA foam slip on lifestyle shoe crafted in the Carbon colorway, a dark medium gray. The Foam RNR features a sculptural silhouette with elliptical shaped perforations on both sides of the ankle, the vamp, and the upper. The monochrome sole is defined by its linear texture. 

German footwear brand adidas has over a century of heritage, crafting timeless athletic shoes. With hip hop artists commonly finding synergy in athletic wear brands, adidas partnered with American rapper, producer, and celebrity Kanye West to create the adidas Yeezy collection from 2015–2022. The Yeezy footwear collection is known for its avant-garde styling, and the Foam RNR features an algae-based foam construction, a sustainable material.

In our opinion, the best feature of the Foam RNR arbon is its Carbon hue, which is a fashion-forward neutral color. The adidas Yeezy Foam RNR Carbon (Kids) released on May 27, 2024, and retailed at $65.

name: Ash Blue
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Ash Blue
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Ash Blue features an engineered primeknit upper that blends blue, black, and gray fiber. adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Ash Blue also features a yellow hue that distinguishes the post-dyed monofilament side strip embroidered on the shoe’s side panel. The yellow hue offers a pop of color to the shoe. It also features a sock-like upper that rides on a full-length Boost Midsole. The sock upper is wrapped up in a semitranslucent rubber cage that adds stability and durability to the shoe.

adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Ash Blue was released in February 2021 at a retail price of $220.

name: Kith Marvel Villains Magneto Sealed Box (Comic Included)
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Kith Marvel Villains Magneto Sealed Box (Comic Included)
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 with Kith Marvel Villains Magneto Sealed Box (Comic Included) merges classic athletic footwear with Marvel’s iconic character, Magneto. This exclusive release gives you a bold design with vibrant colors and an added comic to make it a collector’s item.

The Purple and Orange Gel-1130 by ASICS is made with durable mesh and synthetic overlays, featuring a Magneto-inspired purple and orange color. A collaboration between Kith and ASICS, this release celebrates ASICS’ heritage in athletic footwear and brings Marvel’s universe to life. The shoe arrives in a sealed box, paired with a limited-edition Marvel comic that appeals to sneaker lovers and comic fans.

One thing we love about the ASICS Gel-1130 with Kith Marvel Villains Magneto Sealed Box (Comic Included) is the vibrant color scheme that draws attention while paying homage to Magneto. We also appreciate the inclusion of a collectible comic, a unique touch for Marvel fans. This model retailed at $155 on 9 August 2024.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Castlerock Moonrock
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Teddy Santis Castlerock Moonrock
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Teddy Santis Castlerock Moonrock blends premium handiwork and simple design elements to offer up a modern take on classic running shoes. This Made-in-USA release highlights the collaboration between New Balance and Teddy Santis, the creative director of its Made line.

The MiUSA Teddy Santis Castlerock Moonrock 990v6 by New Balance combines pigskin suede overlays and mesh panels in muted grey and beige tones. The smooth upper contrasts with a comfortable ENCAP midsole infused with FuelCell foam for responsive support. Subtle branding, including a reflective "N" logo, adds a distinctive touch. New Balance’s Made in USA series, established in the 1980s, emphasizes quality production and heritage-inspired designs.

One thing we, the experts, love about the New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Teddy Santis Castlerock Moonrock is the side N logo in white. This, along with the chunky sole that gives you exceptional cushioning and crossed laces adds to the luxurious look and feel. Released on August 15, 2024, it retailed at $220.

name: Safflower
title: adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Safflower
description:
The adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Safflower features a black premium leather upper with rubber overlays and mesh underlays. From there, a ribbed one-piece outsole and textured yellow streaks of synthetic material woven across the midfoot complete the design.

The adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Safflower released in November of 2020 and retailed for $200.

name: Bone (Infants)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Bone (Infants)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Bone (Infants) brings the iconic Yeezy profile to little feet with the same innovative design and premium materials. This neutral-toned pair blends style and comfort for infants and adds an exciting addition to the range.

The Bone Boost 350 V2 for Infants by adidas and Yeezy comes with a flexible Primeknit upper in a bone-white hue that offers a snug, sock-like fit for growing feet. The translucent rubber midsole is home to responsive Boost cushioning for exceptional comfort. A pull tab at the heel makes them easy to pull on and off, while the tonal laces complete the elegant design. Part of Kanye West's Yeezy collaboration, it shows off minimalist aesthetics and advanced technology in a design tailored for little ones.

As the experts, one thing we enjoy about the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Bone (Infants) is the monochrome aesthetic and chunky sole. Retailing at $140, this exclusive release debuted on May 27, 2024.

name: Birch Blue
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Birch Blue
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 Birch Blue debuts in a birth blue and white colorway that takes inspirational design hits from a predecessor in the ASICS lineup, the Gel-Kayano 14.

The upper of this icy cool shoe is made with mixed materials, namely mesh and synthetic materials mimicking leather. There is a lot of energy happening on this upper, as not much of the breathable mesh white material stays untouched before Birch Blue flows over or around it. The signature ASICS stripes are seen on both sides with silver metallic accents throughout. This low-profile running shoe boasts the beloved Gel tech cushioning from the ASICS brand.

We think that the silver colored TRUSSTIC support system, which is a shank between the forefoot and rear foot, provides excellent support and is this sneaker’s unique design element. The ASICS Gel-1130 Birch Blue released to the public on May 16, 2024, with a retail price of $110.

name: Protection Pack Turtledove
title: New Balance 1906D Protection Pack Turtledove
description: The New Balance 1906D Protection Pack Turtledove is a stylish and functional sneaker that offers superior protection and comfort. The shoe features a durable mesh upper and hairy suede overlays with a turtledove colorway that is both versatile and eye-catching. The shoe is designed with a protective toe cap and a Vibram outsole that provides excellent traction and durability. The sneaker also features a cushioned midsole that offers superior comfort and support. The New Balance 1906D Protection Pack Turtledove was released on January 6th, 2023, with a retail price of $165. This sneaker is perfect for those who want a stylish and functional shoe that can handle any terrain or activity.

name: Moonbeam Driftwood
title: New Balance 327 Moonbeam Driftwood
description:
The New Balance 327 Moonbeam Driftwood modernizes a classic ’70s New Balance sneaker silhouette by updating its suede and textile upper, while an oversized N logo provides a striking final touch.

The Moonbeam Driftwood New Balance 327 showcases grayish beige suede overlays enveloping the toe area, heel panel, eye stay, and mudguard. Contrasting these overlays, the mesh base appears in a crisp, pure white. The lateral side walls display bold asymmetrical tumbled leather N logos in light brown, matching the text on the insole branding, heel panel, and tongue tag. An off-white wedge midsole complements the design, paired with a trail-ready gum rubber outsole. Completing the shoe's retro-inspired look is its lace-up closure and split eye row accentuating the nylon tongue.

The distinguishing feature of the New Balance 327 Moonbeam Driftwood is its grayish beige suede overlays. The combination of these overlays with the contrasting white mesh base grants the shoe a distinctive and attractive visual appeal. The shoe debuted for $100 on June 27, 2023.

name: Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Arctic Blue
title: New Balance 993 Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Arctic Blue
description:
The New Balance 993 Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Arctic Blue arrives in an arctic blue, vintage rose color scheme.

The New Balance 993 Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Arctic Blue features an upper that is constructed from suede and leather in Arctic blue. The shoe is accented with light grey "Moonbeam" accents and the signature "N" logo on the lateral sides. The gum rubber outsole in a light brown hue provides grip and stability and complements the color scheme.

The New Balance 993 Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Arctic Blue was released on October 7, 2022, for $220.

name: Taro Plum Brown
title: New Balance 9060 Taro Plum Brown
description:
The New Balance 9060 Taro Plum Brown blends earthy tones with contemporary aesthetics and redefines what once was a classic running shoe into something much more modern. This adaptable sneaker combines age-old design elements with innovative technology to create an outstanding addition to the New Balance lineup.

The Taro Plum Brown 9060 by New Balance shows off a rich combination of breathable mesh and suede overlays. The taro plum tones dominate the upper, accented by muted brown, teal, orange, and white detailing, while reflective touches improve visibility. A chunky, segmented sole with ABZORB cushioning gives you comfort and support. First introduced in 2022, the 9060 series incorporates New Balance’s athletic roots into a forward-thinking design.

Something we can highlight about the Taro Plum Brown New Balance 9060 is its dual-density ABZORB midsole for exceptional shock absorption. Additionally, the large "N" placed in the middle of the shoe adds to the unique profile. Retailing for $150, it debuted on 6th July 2024.

name: White Nightwatch Green
title: New Balance 530 White Nightwatch Green
description:
The reintroduction to the New Balance 530 series launched in 1992, New Balance 530 White Nightwatch Green was released in 2022.

Mesh and leather are used to complete the New Balance 530 White Nightwatch Green sneaker design. White mesh serves as the foundation for the sneaker's upper. There are white leather accents at the heel and the main part. Silver-tone leather lines the nose and lacing eyelets. The underlays and the green "N" logo stand out against the white background. The 530 White Nightwatch shoes also have ABZORB technology.

The 530 white Nightwatch Green shoes were released in March 2022 at the retail price of $120.

name: Brown Storm Sienna
title: ASICS UB8-S GT-2160 Brown Storm Sienna
description:
Heritage meets innovation with the ASICS UB8-S GT-2160 Brown Storm Sienna. A classic shoe shape with retro-inspired features, it's bolstered with modern technology for your best time on the track yet.

While essentially a running shoe, this ASICS sneaker is timeless enough in design to be worn in casual social settings, with intricate overlays boasting various shades of brown, beige, and cream. The shoe has sienna red accent colorways that make it pop. The midsole has GEL cushioning tech for shock absorption and extra comfort in your step. The upper is breathable and light, and the outsole provides robust traction for trail running and hiking. The shoe has very subtle branding on the white pull tag that sits on the tongue.

We love the laid-back look of these retro-colored sneakers. Perfect for mixing with streetwear or casual outfits, the ASICS UB8-S GT-2160 Brown Storm Sienna sneaker was released on September 5, 2024, priced at $150.

name: MiUSA Grey Day (2023)
title: New Balance 998 MiUSA Grey Day (2023)
description:
The New Balance 998 MiUSA Grey Day (2023) is part of New Balance's MADE in the USA lineup for 2023. It features a neutral colorway of grey and navy with splashes of white and tan.

This sneaker incorporates several design elements from the original 998, including the responsive ABZORB cushioning underfoot. It stands out because of the shaggy suede displayed on the overlays, the tongue, and the panels around the lace cage. The shaggy suede is soft to the touch and comes in a smokey grey. Navy accents are on panels beneath the grey suede, a line down the foam midsole, and the signature New Balance "N" and "NB" embroidering on the heel.

Our experts at StockX like the "998 new balance MADE IN USA" lettering embroidered on the long tongue. The New Balance 998 MiUSA Grey Day (2023) was released on May 12, 2023, and sold for $200.

name: Pink Salt (GS)
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Pink Salt (GS)
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 Pink Salt (GS) is a shoe for grade school kids with a classic build and bold accents.
  
The Pink Salt (GS) ASICS Gel-1130 has an upper made of breathable and flexible white mesh. White and off-white leather overlays with metallic silver accents cross the shoe, forming the toecap, eyestays, and heel supports. The typical ASICS design is formed on each side by these overlays accented with a light Pink Salt color. Gel branding is seen on the heel overlay, which is outlined with a bright red color, while more ASICS branding accented in red is seen on the tongue. The shoe is built with the ASICS signature TRUSSTIC support system, and Gel technology is found underfoot for support and responsiveness. The midsole is white, accented with red at the arch and Pink Salt under the heel. 

What we like best about this sneaker are the Pink Salt accents, which are subtle but add a nice touch of elegance. The ASICS Gel-1130 Pink Salt (GS) was released on March 3, 2024, for $85.

name: Frozen Blue
title: adidas Yeezy QNTM Frozen Blue
description:
The adidas Yeezy QNTM Frozen Blue comes in a mixture colors; being frozen blue, white, and black comes the major hues.

The QNTM  sneaker by adidas and Yeezy brand adds a pop of color to this mid-top basketball-themed model. A jacquard knit upper is set on top of a bright blue RPU cage, and the toe cap is reinforced with synthetic suede. This shoe features a plain heel counter and a black neoprene around its tongue and the collar. A Boost midsole bolstered with a herringbone grip outsole and a partially transparent TPU cage completes the design.

The adidas Yeezy QNTM Frozen Blue debuted on the 23rd of December, 2020, with a recommended retail price of $250.

name: White University Blue Grey Gum
title: New Balance 550 White University Blue Grey Gum
description:
The New Balance 550 White University Blue Grey Gum is a chunky shoe with a build that’s reminiscent of the style of the late 80s. 
   
The White University Blue Grey Gum New Balance 550 has an upper constructed with a mix of white mesh, leather, and suede. White mesh appears around the ankle and heel for breathability, while white leather forms the base for the side panels and toe box. A soft suede gray overlay forms the toe cap and the mudguards on each side, which also feature small perforations. University Blue 550 branding is seen on the outer side of the forefoot, while University Blue also accents the suede overlays. New Balance "N" logos appear on each side in a bubbly cracked blue leather, and more cracked blue leather accents the ankle. The suede heel counter contains more branding, while the tongue contains a logo patch. The shoe sits on a chunky white midsole and gum rubber outsole. 

What we like best about this shoe are the cracked leather accents, which add visual interest. The New Balance 550 White University Blue Grey Gum was released on February 22, 2024, for $110.

name: White Grey Dark Grey
title: New Balance 550 White Grey Dark Grey
description:
The New Balance 550 White Grey Dark Grey is a fresh take on the original 1989 design from this famous sneaker company.

The New Balance 550 White Grey Dark Grey features a dark grey hue around the heel, back of the ankle, and tongue. The tread underfoot, which was made with basketball in mind, has two different shades of grey that alternate. The midsoles are clean and simple, colored in a fresh white, and featuring the iconic "N" symbol that has come to be associated with New Balance. Perfect for both sports and walking around town, the New Balance 550 White Grey Dark Grey also has a breathable tongue to provide airflow.

First released in May 2022 at the retail price of $120.

name: White Black (Women's)
title: New Balance 452 White Black (Women's)
description:
Having been released in April 2022, New Balance 452 White Black (Women) sneaker became one of New Balance's best market offers for women.

The New Balance 452 White Black (Women) offering features a white and black leather upper with a perforated detailing, logo accent, low-profile design, white lace-up fastening, padded tongue and cuff Signature, a white rubber midsole that is meant to provide lightweight cushioning, and a durable grip tread black and white rubber outsole. The New Balance 452 White Black (Women) design is completed by a black insole.

During its release in April 2022, New Balance 452 White Black (Women) retailed at $100.

name: Calcium Sea Salt
title: New Balance 9060 Calcium Sea Salt
description:
The New Balance 9060 Calcium Sea Salt is a mesh fabric and suede upper running sneaker crafted from an interplay of geometric overlays in Calcium and Sea Salt’s duo of gray and beige tones. The New Balance N adorns the sides in Metallic Silver, which coordinates with the sculpted, prominent midsole and black outsole and tongue branding.

American sneaker brand New Balance has been around since 1906, making a name for themselves with comfort driven running sneakers. New Balance’s signature aesthetic has implemented a layered blend of suede and mesh for decades, and the 9060 originated as a collaborative style with Joe Freshgoods. The chunky silhouette has been in such demand that numerous colorways have been released, such as Calcium Sea Salt's refined, neutral palette.

Our experts feel that the best feature of the 9060 is its chunky midsole, which gives it a hybrid of running and fashion appeal. The New Balance 9060 Calcium Sea Salt released on May 15, 2024, and retailed for $150.

name: Navy White
title: New Balance 9060 Navy White
description:
The New Balance 9060 Navy White takes design elements and function-first technology originally found in the 990 models and perfects them. Like other Y2K-inspired running shoes, the 9060 Navy White features visible tech that gives the running shoe a futuristic appearance.

The sway bars on the mesh upper are larger in the 9060 iteration than on the 990 model. The bulky midsole comes with both ABZORB and SBS cushioning. This reduces stress from impact and makes the bottom of the shoe look high-tech. ‘9060’ branding can be found on the tongue in bond red, while the New Balance ‘N’ is displayed across the side panel.

Our StockX experts love the subdued colorway of Grey, White, and Navy, which allows the shoe’s sway bars and exaggerated midsole to take the spotlight. The New Balance 9060 Navy White was released on January 14, 2023, and retailed at $150.

name: White Incense (Women's)
title: New Balance 550 White Incense (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 550 White Incense (Women's) finds inspiration in the original 550 basketball shoe from 1989. It brings the silhouette into the modern age by adding a neutral colorway of white and Incense.

This sneaker features a streamlined, low-top silhouette that’s less boxy than other basketball shoes inspired by the late 1980s and early 1990s. The upper is crafted entirely of synthetic leather with layers of overlays in white and tonal stitching. Incense accents can be found on overlays near the heel, part of the rubber outsole, the signature New Balance N, and the tongue’s trim. Tiny, pinprick-sized perforations decorate the forefoot overlays, while two lines of stitching outline the N. This sneaker features responsive foam cushioning and a durable rubber outsole underfoot.

Our experts at StockX like the oversized logo tag because it’s an appropriate size for the large tongue. The women’s size New Balance 550 White Incense (Women's) was released on June 21, 2023, and retailed at $110.

name: Cordura Black Magnet
title: New Balance 1906R Cordura Black Magnet
description:
The New Balance 1906R Cordura Black Magnet is a sleek and durable addition to the iconic 1906R line. This men's sneaker showcases a sophisticated black and magnet colorway, perfectly blending style with functionality. The upper is crafted from Cordura fabric, renowned for its exceptional strength and resistance to abrasions, tears, and scuffs. This innovative material ensures the shoe can withstand daily wear while maintaining its sharp appearance.

Designed with both aesthetics and performance in mind, the 1906R Cordura Black Magnet features New Balance's signature comfort technologies. The shoe incorporates a cushioned midsole for responsive support, making it ideal for all-day wear. Its versatile design seamlessly transitions from casual outings to more active pursuits, offering wearers a perfect balance of style and practicality. Our experts state this product is great for urban explorers and fashion-forward individuals seeking a reliable, long-lasting sneaker that doesn't compromise on style.

name: MX Sand Grey
title: adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR MX Sand Grey
description:
The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR MX Sand Grey borrows an adjacent camouflage styling as the MX Moon Grey, but implements a new color mix. Swirls of beige, dark brown, and grey smother the sculptural EVA foam design, offering as similar visual appeal as the process of mixing paint. Please note that the pattern may vary.

The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR MX Sand Grey released in December of 2021 and retailed for $80.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Macadamia Nut
title: New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Teddy Santis Macadamia Nut
description:
The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Teddy Santis Macadamia Nut is a performance sneaker designed as a collaboration with internet personality, Teddy Santis.
   
This version of the New Balance 990v4 has a mesh upper in a Cream Macadamia Nut color for breathability. Smooth leather overlays also in Macadamia Nut form the toecap, eyestays, side panels, and heel counter, with each panel attached to the upper with black stitching. Overlays in a lighter cream color can be seen accenting some of these panels. A thin New Balance N in a dark green color appears on both side panels, while the laces and the MiUSA logo patch on the tongue are also green. The lateral side of the heel counter features 990 branding, while there is a green NB logo and "Made in the USA" branding at the top of the heel. The New Balance brand name appears on the bottom of the heel, and the midsole and outsole are black.

The most intriguing features of this shoe are the green accents, which add a nice outdoorsy feel to the shoe. The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Teddy Santis Macadamia Nut was released on March 28, 2024, for $210.

name: Red White
title: New Balance 327 Red White
description:
The New Balance 327 Red White dresses the New Balance 327’s silhouette in bright red with red accents.

This running sneaker finds inspiration in New Balance sneaker designs from the 1970s. Specifically, the sneaker’s foam rubber midsole, flat tongue, and use of premium materials are throwbacks to its design roots. While the upper is made of synthetic material with a satin finish, the overlays boast velvety suede. Both the satin-like underlays and the suede overlays come in a vibrant red. An oversized New Balance ‘N’ occupies the lateral side panel and is one of the white elements. The ‘NEW BALANCE’ lettering embroidered near the heel, the cushioning midsole, and the tongue’s logo tag also come in white.

Something our StockX experts appreciate about the "Red White" version is the padded collar and the lug rubber outsole that goes up the heel. The New Balance 327 Red White was released on February 27th, 2023, and retailed at $100.

name: 8ON8 Black Green
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 8ON8 Black Green
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 8ON8 Black Green marks a return of the very well-received original Gel-Kayano running shoe, which captured the attention of fitness enthusiasts in the 2000s.

The unique ASICS GEL cushioning technology is the key to the model's success. This latest version also features an enhanced and flexible upper. It's made from layered panels of genuine leather and textile mesh. The effect is that it molds to your foot to provide high levels of support and comfort. The bouncy soles are made from durable synthetics, and provide reliable grip on all training surfaces.

We really like this model for its standout shock absorption properties. The GEL technology makes a discernible difference when running. This is complemented by a proprietary TRUSSTIC lateral support system, which provides excellent stability. The throwback 2000s design also adds visual appeal, with aggressive athletic styling. Contrasting colors enhance this effect. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 8ON8 Black Green was released on 23 June 2024, priced at $190.

name: White Taro
title: New Balance 9060 White Taro
description:
The New Balance 9060 White Taro features a bold white and Taro green color scheme, blending athletic heritage with modern flair. The White Taro color scheme brings a fresh touch to the 9060's classic design. This sleek design combines a supportive ride with a fresh, eye-catching look.

The White Taro New Balance 9060 features a premium upper constructed from a combination of full-grain leather and mesh panels, providing a balance of durability and breathability. A low-profile silhouette, rounded toe cap, and subtle branding elements characterize the shoe's sleek design. 

As experts, one of our favorite things about the New Balance 9060 White Taro is the mixed-material upper and ABZORB cushioning technology. The combination of leather and synthetic materials provides a durable yet breathable upper, while the ABZORB technology offers superior shock absorption and support. This shoe was released on May 7, 2024, at a retail price of $150.

name: Pure Silver Cream
title: Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD Pure Silver Cream
description:
The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD Pure Silver Cream is a supportive shoe with a bold colorway designed by the Japanese brand.
  
This version of the Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 has an upper made of calf leather in Pure Silver throughout. The toe cap also appears in Pure Silver, as do the eyestays and heel counter. Cream leather racing stripes cross each side of the shoe. A silver crisscross design appears at the heel for support, and there’s a Tiger-branded silver tag doubling as the heel pull tab at the top. The tongue also features Onitsuka Tiger branding. The shoe sits on a cream midsole with a chunkier layer of support under the toe and a patterned cream outsole. 
 
What we like best about this shoe is the Pure Silver colorway, which makes it stand out and gives it a pop of elegance. The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD Pure Silver Cream was released on September 10, 2023, for $160.

name: Clay
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Clay
description: If you're searching for a new sneaker with major drip, then cop the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Clay. This Yeezy Boost 350 comes with a clay upper with orange accents, translucent stripe with orange accents, clay midsole, and clay sole. These sneakers released in March 2019 and retailed for $220. Add another swaggy 350 V2 to the rotation and buy them on StockX today.

name: Core
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Core
description:
DISCLAIMER: US and UK sizing is the same and does not require any conversion.

The adidas Yeezy Slide Core is composed of a Core EVA foam throughout the design to provide lightweight comfort. From there, a soft footbed offers cushioning. An outsole with accentuated grooves for traction and support completes the design.

The adidas Yeezy Slide Core released in April of 2021 and retailed for $60.

name: MX Cream Clay
title: adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR MX Cream Clay
description:
Following previous monochromatic Foam RNNR's, the adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR MX Cream Clay is the first Foam RNNR to feature a multicolor palette. Cream, clay, and grey colors are all prominent on the upper in a streaked camo pattern, making the design a true statement piece.

The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR MX Cream Clay released in August of 2021 and retailed for $80.

name: Kith 101 Quarry
title: New Balance 1000 Kith 101 Quarry
description:
The New Balance 1000 Kith 101 Quarry is an athletic shoe with a suede upper done in the Quarry and Weathervane palette, which mixes cool gray suede with shades of cream and warm gray in the midsole and outsole. The upper features curvilinear overlays, which coordinate with the Kith and New Balance branded suede lace keeper on the tongue. Additional branding appears as the N logo on the sides and on the rear heel.

New Balance, founded in 1906, is an American athletic shoe brand known for their trusted running sneakers and signature styles. Kith, founded in 2011, is an American lifestyle brand known for the curation of streetwear that commingles with their signature clothing output found in their signature boutiques around the world.

In our opinion, the best feature of the 1000 Kith 101 is its nuanced, neutral aesthetic, which expresses both brands’ design philosophies. The New Balance 1000 Kith 101 Quarry released on October 8, 2024, and retailed for $160.

name: Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone Linen Black Coffee
title: New Balance 9060 Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone Linen Black Coffee
description:
The New Balance 9060 Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone Linen Black Coffee is a collaboration New Balance 9060 sneaker that was released as part of Sydney’s Signature Collection, a line of athletic apparel and accessories for track and other sports.

Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone is an American athlete that competed in the 2020 and 2024 Summer Olympics. This colorway features neutral tones that she handpicked, namely Linen, Stoneware, and Licorice. The 9060 is a stylish and functional low-top silhouette that has a premium feel thanks to the leather and suede upper. As for tech, there is New Balance’s proprietary ABZORB midsole, an ABZORB SBS heel, and a translucent CR device on the heel. Multiple branding hits are seen throughout, including the side panels, tongue, heel, and outsole.

We particularly like the shaggy suede and matching shaggy laces, which ooze comfort and softness, something soft to touch after a hard day of training. The New Balance 9060 Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone Linen Black Coffee was released on March 7, 2024, with a $150 retail price.

name: Black Sea Salt (Women's)
title: New Balance 327 Black Sea Salt (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 327 Black Sea Salt W is inspired by vintage running shoes from the 1970s for women. This model features an upper body that is made from leather and designed to have a chunky feel.

This New Balance 327 model has a gum rubber sole that is meant to provide traction and limit the possibility of slipping. The midsole is made from supportive foam and is a mixture of bright white and cream colors. The body of this New Balance model is completely black and is composed of breathable materials. On the side there is a large "N" with minimal perforations for breathability and branding.

A feature that our team of experts particularly love about the New Balance 327 Black Sea Salt for women is the serrated sole that provides additional comfort and traction. This shoe first released for sale on the market on October 31st, 2022, for a starting retail price of $100.

name: White Juniper
title: New Balance 550 White Juniper
description:
The New Balance 550 White Juniper is a sneaker with a minimalist paneled design in a simple and light colorway.

This iteration of the New Balance 550 is constructed with a premium leather upper in white. White adorns the sides, outlining the bubble-lettered green New Balance N on each side, on top of the toebox, and as a perforated panel running from the laces to the sole on the side. White also forms the heel counter. Overlays in Juniper round out the toebox, form the N, and form the heel collar. The New Balance logo can be seen on the tongue and on the heel, while 550 branding appears on the white strap near the laces. Dark Juniper rubber supports the heel above the off-white sole, which also contains embossed branding.

Our favorite feature of this sneaker is the Juniper colorway, as it’s muted and gives the shoe a clean look. The New Balance 550 White Juniper was released on August 23, 2023, for a retail price of $120.

name: Slate Marine (Kids)
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Slate Marine (Kids)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Slide Slate Marine (Kids) is a modern, ultra-casual shoe that your child can wear virtually anywhere. It's comfortable, flexible and very low maintenance.

These contoured slip-ons come in an interesting shade of slate gray that has an almost iridescent quality. A stripped-down version of the adidas Yeezy trainer, the body is made from EVA foam, melded to a soft footbed. This makes them at once lightweight and very comfortable. Deep, staggered grooves on the undersole provide high levels of traction, even on wet surfaces.

Our team really enjoys both the look of these slides and the way they seem to embrace kids' feet. They're waterproof, which makes them ideal for wearing to the beach or poolside. The open toe makes them nice and airy too, and their non-slip outsoles are also a plus. The one-piece construction makes them very easy to clean. The adidas Yeezy Slide Slate Marine (Kids) was released on May 27, 2024, at a price of $50.

name: Mineral Blue
title: adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Mineral Blue
description:
DISCLAIMER: US and UK sizing is the same and does not require any conversion.

The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Mineral Blue is made of a Mineral Blue foam that blends EVA with harvested algae. Oval cut-outs throughout the upper add ventilation to finish off the design.

The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Mineral Blue released in May of 2021 and retailed for $75.

name: Imperfection Pack Cream
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Imperfection Pack Cream
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Imperfection Pack Cream features a woven fabric and distressed leather upper in Cream, accented by multiple textures and tones on the fabric, leather, and midsole. ASICS branding appears on the exposed foam tongue, while Gel and Kayano 14 branding adorn the heel. The textured and paint speckled midsole features Gel technology inserts in dark gray, grounded by a Cream outsole.

ASICS, the Japanese athletic wear brand, created the Gel-Kayano 14 for a series called the Imperfection Pack, which salutes what might otherwise be considered flawed. The Gel-Kayano 14’s cracked leather, speckled midsole and exposed foam tongue were inspired by the aging of clay pots over time. This aesthetic has also been accompanied by advancements in the Gel-Kayano 14's performance evolution for increased cushioning.

In our opinion, the best feature of the Gel-Kayano 14 is its multiple textures, which make the shoe’s Cream color palette sing. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Imperfection Pack Cream released on March 22, 2024, and retailed for $160.

name: Butter
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Butter
description: "The most beautiful thoughts are always besides the darkest." Following his polarizing #1 album, ye, the Yeezy Boost 350 V2 is back and better than ever. With various shades of butter covering the upper, laces, and midsole, the shoe is finished with a classic gum bottom. Noticeably, this pair is lacking the famous SPLY-350 text found on most 350 V2s. This pair released in June, 2018 for a cool $220. Stay locked to StockX to cop a pair.

name: Kith Madison Square Garden Tan Orange
title: New Balance Numeric 480 Kith Madison Square Garden Tan Orange
description:
The New Balance Numeric 480 Kith Madison Square Garden Tan Orange is an understated trainer in a New York Knicks colorway. This collaboration commemorates the third "Kith Night" at Madison Square Gardens. It's a premium trainer made from top-class materials.

This New Balance Numeric 480 model has a breathable white mesh upper, rounded toe cap, and beige suede leather overlays at the heel and forefoot. The trademark "N" is in contrasting orange. The tongue has Jacquard embroidered Kith branding. A tough rubber outsole blends cream and gray, with a light blue inner ankle collar completing the look.

The commemorative angle makes this a collectible shoe for Kith followers and New Balance fans. Our reviewers quickly point to its high-quality credentials as another reason to own a pair. They're practical, everyday sneakers with elevated comfort and definite brand panache. The New Balance Numeric 480 Kith Madison Square Garden Tan Orange was released on November 4, 2024, at a retail price of $120.

name: Salehe Bembury Sand Be The Time
title: New Balance 990v2 Salehe Bembury Sand Be The Time
description:
The New Balance 990v2 Salehe Bembury Sand Be The Time is a collaboration between streetwear designer Salehe Bembury and New Balance.

The upper of this 990v2  running shoe sports terra cotta spacer mesh underlays, misty rose hairy suede overlays, reflective silver hits on the toe box, and a purple passion chenille "N" on the side panel. The ABZORB midsole is terra cotta and the insole is cork with New Balance and Salehe Bembury branding. The rubber outsole is also purple passion.

The New Balance 990v2 Salehe Bembury Sand Be The Time debuted on December 8th, 2022 for a retail price of $200.

name: Hylte
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Hylte
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Hylte Glow Reflective was part of a shock drop by the German brand and American musician Kanye West.

Made using semi-perforated Primeknit material on the upper with a monofilament strip on the lateral side, this Yeezy Boost 380 model has a Boost material interior sole for cushioning.The outer sole is made with rubber and herringbone traction on the bottom. The color palette combines shades of beige, white, grey and a light Hylte  green that reflects light.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Hylte Glow Reflective was originally released on the 11th of December 2020, at a retail price of $250.

name: Baked Pink Cream (Women's)
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Baked Pink Cream (Women's)
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Baked Pink Cream for women is a stunning blend of style and performance. This eye-catching sneaker features a soft, feminine colorway that combines baked pink and cream hues, creating a visually appealing design that's perfect for both athletic pursuits and casual wear. The upper is crafted with a mix of premium materials, including breathable mesh and supportive overlays, ensuring comfort and durability throughout your day.

Engineered for optimal performance, the Gel-Kayano 14 incorporates ASICS' renowned GEL technology in the heel and forefoot, providing superior shock absorption and cushioning. The shoe's midsole is designed with FLYTEFOAM technology, offering lightweight responsiveness and energy return with each step. A structured heel counter and Dynamic DuoMax support system work together to enhance stability and reduce overpronation, making this shoe an excellent choice for runners and fitness enthusiasts alike. Our experts state this product is great for women seeking a versatile sneaker that combines cutting-edge technology with fashionable aesthetics, perfect for long-distance runs or all-day comfort.

name: Gore-Tex Concrete
title: New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Concrete
description:
The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Concrete gives the 2002R a winter-ready makeover with a water-resistant Gore-Tex membrane and a colorway that brings to mind gray winter skies.

The upper construction is much the same as the original New Balance 2002R; however, it includes an inner membrane made of Gore-Tex. Although this material is water-resistant, it also protects against wind and other winter conditions. The base is made of lightweight mesh with layers of suede overlays in various shades of gray, ranging from Harbor Gray to Slate Gray. The tooling matches the original 2002R and includes impact-absorbing ABZORB cushioning and stabilizing ABZORB SBS heel cushioning. The sneaker displays a combination of New Balance and Gore-Tex branding on the upper and sole unit.
