Our experts at StockX like that the 860v2 sole unit features Concrete Gray, which matches the upper and completes the winter aesthetic. The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Concrete was released on September 22, 2023, and retailed for $180.

name: P. Andrade Gradation Green
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 P. Andrade Gradation Green
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 P. Andrade Gradation Green is an athletic shoe designed in collaboration with ASICS and Brazilian menswear brand P. Andrade. 
    
This iteration of the ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 has a mesh upper. The mesh that makes up the toe box is a hunter green, which fades to a lighter green before becoming a more blue-green shade on the sides and at the heel. Supportive polyurethane overlays cross the shoe in metallic blue, black, green, and silver, forming the classic ASICS design on both sides and also forming the eyestays and heel counter. P. Andrade branding is on the lateral heel, while Gel branding is on the back. More ASICS branding can be found on the tongue. The shoe’s midsole contains Gel technology for energy return. 

What stands out about this shoe is the color gradient, which makes it pop and gives it visual interest. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 P. Andrade Gradation Green was released on August 17, 2024, for $180.

name: MiUSA Auralee Grey
title: New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Auralee Grey
description:
The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Auralee Grey is a premium collaboration that combines classic American craftsmanship with Japanese design sensibilities. This sleek sneaker features a sophisticated grey colorway with subtle white and blue accents, creating a versatile and stylish look. The upper is crafted from high-quality suede and mesh materials, ensuring both durability and breathability for all-day comfort.

Built on the iconic 990v4 silhouette, this shoe offers superior cushioning and support thanks to its ENCAP midsole technology and sturdy rubber outsole. The Made in USA construction guarantees exceptional quality and attention to detail, making it a standout choice for sneaker enthusiasts and fashion-forward individuals alike. With its perfect balance of style and functionality, the New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Auralee Grey is an excellent addition to any footwear collection.

Us at StockX believe this product is great for those seeking a premium, comfortable sneaker that seamlessly blends retro charm with modern performance.

name: Aime Leon Dore White Leather
title: New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore White Leather
description:
The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore White Leather is dressed in an all-white color scheme.

This collaborative sneaker has a leather base. The toe box of the shoe is cream, and it has white as well as light grey overlays throughout. In addition to the ALD as well as the New Balance co-branding on the tongue tag, the "N" logo and heel overlay are also visible on this model in grey textured suede. The rubber midsole features cream, while the outsole of the shoe is rubber.

The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore White Leather first launched on November 2nd, 2022, with a retail price set at $130.

name: Volt Black
title: New Balance 1906R Volt Black
description:
The New Balance 1906R Volt Black offers a high-performance running shoe in an eye-catching colorway.

This iteration of the New Balance 1906R is built upon volt-colored, open-hole mesh. Synthetic leather overlays and metallic silver accented with black streak across the upper, providing extra reinforcement at the toe cap. A black TPU heel cage offers rear foot support and matches a black heel pull loop that eases on/off. The side-panel N in black features N-lock branding, referring to the integrated lacing system. This vibrant shoe rides on a black and volt N-ergy outsole constructed with Stability Web technology for added arch support.

The aspect of this running shoe that we most enjoy is its high-tech and stylish midsole. Composed of ACTEVA LITE undulating foam cushioning in black, the midsole contains ABZORB SBS pods in the heel for extra comfort and bounce. The New Balance 1906R Volt Black was released on July 11, 2023, for $155 retail.

name: Terracotta
title: New Balance 550 Terracotta
description:
The New Balance 550 Terracotta is the re-release of a heritage basketball sneaker that first burst onto the scene in 1989.

This low-top sneaker features an upper of layered white leather. The panel extending from the lower eye stays down to the mudguard and then up toward the collar sports perforations to facilitate ventilation and enhance comfort. The iconic side panel "N" is made of puffy white leather. Other hits of branding include an embroidered "550" near the bottom most eyestays, a flying red "NB" on the white leather heel overlay, and red New Balance basketball branding on the tongue. The white cupsole midsole provides cushioning and sports tonal embossed branding. A red rubber outsole is grooved for multidirectional traction.

Our favorite aspects of this sneaker are the upper overlays at the collar and toe cap that give this shoe an added look of distinction. The New Balance 550 Terracotta was released on June 21, 2023, for a retail price of $120.

name: MiUSA Grey Day (2023)
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Grey Day (2023)
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Gray Day (2023) is a running sneaker from the New Balance ‘Gray Day’ 2023 lineup featuring the 990v6 MiUSA silhouette.

This New Balance 990v6 MiUSA (Made in USA) offering features an Off-White mesh base with navy suede overlays and gray pigskin suede on the mudguard and eyestays. More navy blue hits feature on the signature ‘N’ logo on the sides, which has a white outline. Other details include ‘990’ branding on the lateral heel, a mesh tongue with a branded patch, cream-colored laces, and the signature ‘NB’ logo at the heel with ‘MADE IN USA’ typography beneath it. A sole unit with an ENCAP-cushioned midsole and a rubber outsole completes the design.

Something we love about this New Balance sneaker is its unique design, cushioning technology, and colorway, which make it perfect for everyday wear. The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Gray Day (2023) was made available on May 12th, 2023. Initially, it retailed at $220.

name: Triple Black Leather
title: New Balance 530 Triple Black Leather
description:
The New Balance 530 Triple Black Leather is a sophisticated rendition of a classic running shoe that combines retro style with modern comfort.

It features a full leather upper, which enhances its durability and offers a high-quality appearance, and an all-black colorway which gives it a sleek and versatile aesthetic. It employs New Balance’s standard ENCAP midsole technology, combining lightweight foam with a durable polyurethane rim to deliver all-day comfort and support. A rubber outsole ensures excellent traction and stability. Other details include perforations in the body for breathability, a heel tab for convenient on-and-off wear, and a standard lacing system.

What our experts especially enjoy about the New Balance 530 Triple Black Leather is that it is modeled after 90s fashion trends to provide a vintage yet timeless aesthetic. This shoe originally retailed with a price tag of $100 when it was released on August 5, 2023.

name: Kith Malibu
title: New Balance 580 Kith Malibu
description:
The New Balance 580 Kith Malibu is a New Balance 580 colorway that was released in conjunction with Kith to celebrate the opening of their Malibu, California location.

The design of this sneaker was influenced by the design of the flagship store in Malibu and beachy sunsets. This colorway features Agate Gray and moon rock color combination with peachy tans and Earth Green accents. The Agate Gray wraps around the toe, while moon rock graces the lower mid-panel and heel counter. Branding takes on a peachy tan color in the form of a leather patch on the tongue, debossed New Balance on the heel tab, and the iconic tilted N on the side panels. The midsole houses the ABZORB and C-CAP cushioning.

Here at StockX, we think that the earth-friendly tones aren’t overbearing and the combination of many textures, including suede, leather, and canvas, make this shoe standout. The New Balance 580 Kith Malibu debuted on July 4, 2024, with a recommended price of $135.

name: Grey Day (2023)
title: New Balance 550 Grey Day (2023)
description:
The New Balance 550 Grey Day (2023) is a unique colorway of the New Balance 550 silhouette, which combines retro basketball aesthetics with modern streetwear sensibilities.

The shoe’s upper features a suede construction with leather underlays. Both materials blend seamlessly to give the shoe some texture, which is further enhanced by the Nimbus Cloud color scheme – resembling a soft and pale shade of gray. It also has black and navy accents on the side panels and tongue. The shoe retains some iconic New Balance 550 branding elements, such as the ‘N’ logo on the side panels, the ‘NB’ on the tongue and heel, and the number ‘550’ on the lateral side.

What we love most about the New Balance 550 Grey Day (2023) is the design, which easily transitions from sporty to casual and back, giving you the versatility to work with a range of different styles and outfits. The shoe was released for retail on May 12th, 2023, at $120.

name: Reflection Sepia
title: New Balance 2002R Reflection Sepia
description:
The New Balance 2002R Reflection Sepia takes inspiration from running shoes from the early 2000s and creates a stylish pair of kicks in a subtle, elegant colorway.

The Reflection Sepia New Balance 2002R begins with an upper base of grayish-white denim. Overlays in tonal suede and leather are layered across the upper, offering the classic New Balance style as well as support. The suede overlay at the heel is perforated for increased breathability, and the side-panel N pops in white denim. An off-white ABZORB midsole features ABZORB SBS at the heel in order to provide ultimate cushioning as well as energy return. The black rubber outsole is composed of N-ergy for optimum shock absorption and Stability Web technology for enhanced arch support.

The details we most appreciate about this pair of sneakers are the golden brown hits of contrast in the tumbled leather heel tab, as well as in the branding on the midsole and outsole. The New Balance 2002R Reflection Sepia was released on January 19, 2023, for a retail price of $140.

name: Super Moon Yellow
title: adidas Yeezy 500 Super Moon Yellow
description: These new Yeezy 500 Super Moon Yellows are coming in hotter than a Jackson Hole bonfire. The latest colorway in the Yeezy 500 line, these use adiPrene cushioning in place of BOOST and feature a chunkier look that will grow on you (trust us). This all-moon yellow pair was the first colorway that dropped, as part of the Yeezy season 6 bundle, followed by a wider release in June of 2018. Fans of Ye need to make "No Mistakes" and add this Yeezy 500 colorway into the collection asap.

name: Titanium
title: New Balance 1906R Titanium
description:
The New Balance 1906R Titanium offers an '80s running shoe–inspired silhouette in a modern, edgy colorway that will turn heads.

This Titanium New Balance 1906R running shoe has an upper base of bluish-gray mesh for lightweight breathability with every step. Deeper gray suede overlays course across the upper and match the gray TPU heel counter that offers stability. The lateral collar overlay sports 1906R branding, while the heel features an understated NB patch. This steely upper rides atop a two-toned midsole in off-white and gray made of Nergy, which provides ultimate cushioning and energy return. This midsole also houses ABZORB and SBS ABZORB units underfoot and in the heel for extra cushioning. The black rubber outsole provides grip and impact absorption.

Our favorite aspect of this sneaker is the design of the side panel N. Gray webbing threads through the white N, integrating into the eye stays to offer a locked-down midfoot feel. The New Balance 1906R Titanium was released on February 3, 2023, for $155 retail.

name: Carhartt WIP Sculpture Center
title: New Balance 990v6 Carhartt WIP Sculpture Center
description:
The New Balance 990v6 Carhartt WIP Sculpture Center represents a collaboration between Nike, the iconic sneaker company, and Carhartt, the menswear brand that recreates a work clothing aesthetic into high-end fashion. This sports shoe infuses refinement with a ruggedness to create a style matched by high performance.

The New Balance Carhartt WIP 990v6 Sculpture Center features an upper with a gray base made of mesh and synthetics overlaid with rich brown suede. The signature "N" on the side panel ties the look of the upper together, with a dark green suede that contrasts the Sail-colored laces while it complements the tonal hues of the tongue and sock liner.

Our sneaker experts particularly enjoy the sole unit of this shoe for fusion of its graceful appearance and high-octane performance. The Sail and tan FuelCell midsole provides support, cushioning, and reactive energy return. The black rubber outsole grounds the shoe with grip and traction. The New Balance 990v6 Carhartt WIP Sculpture Center was released on October 20, 2023, for a retail price of $220.

name: Alvah
title: adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Alvah
description:
This adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Alvah is composed of a black and grey upper composed of monofilament engineered mesh with RPU overlays for structure and durability. The RPU cage has glow-in-the-dark features, along with 3M reflective detailing on the toe. The EVA midsole and herringbone rubber outsole complete the design.

The adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Alvah released in February of 2020 and retailed for $200.

name: Pink Granite (GS)
title: New Balance 2002R Pink Granite (GS)
description:
The New Balance 2002R Pink Granite (GS) combines subtle pastel tones with the performance-inspired design of the 2002R series, tailored for grade school sizing. This model offers a modern look and feel while sticking to the brand's commitment to practical, wearable products.

The Pink Granite 2002R (GS) by New Balance has a breathable mesh upper layered with suede accents in pink and muted gray tones. The ABZORB midsole technology absorbs extra shock, while the N-ergy outsole improves traction. This model draws inspiration from the early 2000s running shoe silhouettes, adapted with updated cushioning and materials. It shows off the New Balance logo subtly stitched on the sides and tongue.

As experts, one thing we love about the New Balance 2002R Pink Granite (GS) is its durable suede overlays, which improve the shoe's longevity. Additionally, the toe cab and laces offer reliable comfort during extended use. This model retailed for $100 when it was released on May 18, 2024​.

name: Sea Salt Linen (Women's)
title: New Balance 550 Sea Salt Linen (Women's)
description:
The timeless coloring and design of the New Balance 550 Sea Salt Linen (Women's) sneakers make them a must-have in every active woman’s athleisure wear wardrobe. Simple and classic, these New Balance sneakers for women bring a contemporary yet retro feel to a beloved shape.

With an old-school basketball-inspired design, the Sea Salt white base color blends with Linen beige to keep it a clean and sleek shoe. The sneakers come with leather uppers, a cushioned midsole, and perforations for detail. The rubber outsole is great for sporting traction on the court or street. A chunky, fashionable shape, the shoe has the New Balance "N" branding on the sides, with the number "550" on the colorways. The full NB logo sits on the heel.

We love the subtle design and color blend on these New Balances, which lend a soft, feminine edge to the shoes. The New Balance 550 Sea Salt Linen (Women's) was released on April 1, 2024, for $110.

name: Concepts Hours and Days
title: New Balance 1906U Concepts Hours and Days
description:
The New Balance 1906U Concepts Hours and Days brings a fresh take to collaborative footwear by blending premium materials with a visually engaging color palette. Inspired by historical releases, this sneaker is a seamless fusion of storytelling and modern makeup.

The Concepts Hours and Days 1906U by New Balance reimagines the 1906U silhouette with ocean blue colors, earthy tan overlays, and cream accents. The upper combines breathable mesh and textured materials that give the multi-layered design some depth. The sneaker’s reflective highlights and subtle Concepts branding add to its distinct look to create a meaningful tribute to the themes of time and movement.

One thing we, the experts, love about the New Balance 1906U Concepts Hours and Days is the striking use of color transitions between cream, beige, and blue across the midsole. We also love the Fresh Foam and CUSH+ midsole that give you some added comfort—this release, retailing at $170, launched on 2nd August 2024.

name: Airy Green
title: Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 Airy Green
description:
The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 Airy Green is a performance shoe with a slim build that takes inspiration from the style of the 1960s. 
   
The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 in Airy Green is constructed with a grained leather upper in the pale Airy Green color. A slightly darker green colors the suede overlays that form the t-shaped toe cap, eyestays, and the crisscross at the heel. Verdigris Green racing stripes, which have become synonymous with the shoe, cross each side in leather. Tiger branding is seen on the heel collar, and there is a white and green logo patch on the tongue. The shoe has a thick off-white rubber toe cap and sits on a thin off-white midsole and outsole.

What we think stands out here is the tonal green colorway, which is perfect for seasonal wear. The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 Airy Green was released on August 13, 2023, for $120.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Grey Black Cream
title: New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Teddy Santis Grey Black Cream
description:
The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Teddy Santis Grey Black Cream is a version that pays homage to the original design of the running shoe.

This iteration of the New Balance 990v4 is constructed with a white textile upper for comfort and flexibility. White dominates the midsole and toe box while black and gray leather overlays round out the toe box and cross the midsole from the arches to the laces. The New Balance signature "N" appears on the midsole in white outlined in black on top of the gray overlay. The heel collar is darker gray and contains an NB logo at the top, while the black heel counter contains the New Balance brand name. A branded off-white rubber outsole completes the look, and the midsole contains ENCAP cushioning.

What stands out about this shoe is the sleek design of the white textile and leather overlays. The muted design makes the shoe versatile. The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Teddy Santis Grey Black Cream was released on February 8, 2024, for a price of $200.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Chive
title: New Balance 993 MiUSA Teddy Santis Chive
description:
The New Balance 993 MiUSA Teddy Santis Chive is an earthy-toned colorway, namely a Chive Green and Sea Salt color combo, from the Made in the USA (MiUSA) line by New Balance.

This sneaker is a New Balance 993 silhouette that uses premium materials, which are put into action with supreme craftsmanship. The upper is an energizing Chive Green color that balances well with the Sea Salt accents. This sneaker has lots of breathable mesh, also in the Chive Green, which ensures that your foot stays cool and crisp. Slanted "N" logos flank both sides, 993 branding is seen on the lateral right heel and the tongue. A "USA" peeks out of the heel counter, and is also mentioned on the tongue.

What we love about this shoe is New Balance’s commitment to making shoes in the USA and using locally sourced materials. The New Balance 993 MiUSA Teddy Santis Chive debuted on May 2, 2024, with a retail price of $220.

name: Stone Onyx
title: adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Stone Onyx
description:
Elevate everyday footwear with the adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Stone Onyx. Simple, comfy, and oh-so-cool, these sock-like sneakers are a futuristic look at minimalist fashion. The Yeezy Knit Runner sneakers are a great comfortable shoe that takes style seriously.

With the Yeezy adidas sub-brand known for minimalism and futuristic looks, the Knit RNR is no different. Made from a knit textile on the upper, with lightweight foam for the midsole, the outsole has durable rubber for traction. Suitable for loungewear or streetwear, these Stone Onyx colored sneakers are light, breathable, and make a style statement. The wording of the size and the country of origin are embroidered on the top of the sock-like structure to give an industrial look to the design, and there is no adidas branding, which is synonymous with the Yeezy range.

We love the way the Yeezy range strips away all branding to pull focus to the design and luxury textiles used in these shoes. The adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Stone Onyx sneakers were released on May 27, 2024, for $210.

name: Bricks & Wood Echoes of a Butterfly
title: New Balance 1906U Bricks & Wood Echoes of a Butterfly
description:
The New Balance 1906U Bricks & Wood Echoes of a Butterfly is a striking collaboration that merges style and comfort. This men's sneaker features a bold black and multi-color design, showcasing the creative vision of Bricks & Wood. The shoe's upper combines premium materials with intricate detailing, creating a visually captivating silhouette that stands out in any crowd.

Built on New Balance's renowned 1906 platform, this sneaker offers exceptional comfort and support for all-day wear. The innovative cushioning system provides responsive shock absorption, while the durable outsole ensures reliable traction on various surfaces. With its unique colorway and eye-catching design elements, the 1906U Bricks & Wood Echoes of a Butterfly is a testament to New Balance's commitment to pushing boundaries in sneaker design.

Us at StockX believe this product is great for sneaker enthusiasts and fashion-forward individuals looking for a comfortable yet stylish option that makes a statement.

name: Ash Stone
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Ash Stone
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 ash stone features subtle earth tones over the re-engineered Primeknit Upper. It features a complementary blend of tan, grey, and brown fibers arranged in several different weaves that offer adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 ash stone an intricate design. Its patchwork design is offset by the coral-colored side stripe on the shoe’s lateral side. It also has a sock-like build mounted on a full-length Boost midsole covered in a semi-translucent rubber for added support and durability.

adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 ash stone was released in February 2021 at a retail price of $220.

name: Rick and Morty
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Rick and Morty
description:
The Puma MB.01 received its first collaboration courtesy of LaMelo Ball's favorite Adult Swim cartoon, Rick and Morty.

Sporting a mismatched neon two-tone look, the Puma MB.01 Rick and Morty draws inspiration from otherworldly adventures of Rick and Morty. The left shoe features a slime green palette, while the right shoe is smothered in the neon red tones. On the back of the tongues, illustrations of both Rick and Morty contribute a customized feel.

The Puma MB.01 Rick and Morty released in February of 2022 and retailed for $135.

name: Kith Marvel X-Men Mystery Sealed Box (Trading Card Included)
title: ASICS Gel-Lyte III '07 Remastered Kith Marvel X-Men Mystery Sealed Box (Trading Card Included)
description:
Introduced on July 28, 2023, the ASICS Gel-Lyte III Kith Marvel X-Men Mystery Sealed Box is an enigma wrapped in a shoebox. Kith and Marvel unite to bring sneaker and comic book fandoms together.

Packed inside each sealed mystery box is the iconic Gel-Lyte III silhouette, reimagined with one of seven possible Marvel X-Men themed variations. Each pair captures the essence of a different X-Men character, adding an extra layer of excitement as you unbox. To enhance the collector's experience, each box also includes a special edition trading card - a nod to the captivating lore of X-Men and Marvel's legendary storytelling.

A box of surprises, the ASICS Gel-Lyte III Kith Marvel X-Men Mystery Sealed Box was released on July 28, 2023, with a retail price of $195. Experience the thrill of unboxing your very own superhero story with this piece of sneaker and comic book history.

name: Pleasures Black Frosted Ivory
title: Puma Suede XL Pleasures Black Frosted Ivory
description:
The Puma Suede XL Pleasures Black Frosted Ivory is an oversized shoe designed as a collaboration between Puma and the metal streetwear brand Pleasures.

This iteration of the Puma Suede XL is made with a black suede upper. White artificial leather forms the signature Puma Formstrip logo design across the midsoles, and the shoes feature extra wide laces to add to the oversized aesthetic. The tongue features a Puma and Pleasures co-branded tag, while the heel collar features the Puma logo in black on a white background. The shoe also features a thickly padded design, adding not only comfort but contributing to the oversized look. A thick white rubber sole and outsole complete the look.

The standout feature of these shoes is the extra padding that adds both functionality and comfort to the shoe. The Puma Suede XL Pleasures Black Frosted Ivory was released on January 6, 2024, for a price of $120.

name: Onyx (Infants)
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Onyx (Infants)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Slide Onyx (Infant) does not have any laces or an ankle strap, but rather stays on the foot through one thick strap.

The sole of the adidas Yeezy Slide Onyx Infants is designed to provide ultimate comfort and traction so the wearer can move as easily as possible. The entire body of the shoe is constructed from one piece of EVA foam composite. The material has a rough finish that allows for more grip when they are being worn.

The adidas Yeezy Slide Onyx (Infant) were first introduced in May of 2022. The starting retail price at the time of its release was $70.

name: Violet Noir
title: New Balance 9060 Violet Noir
description:
Meet the New Balance 9060 in the captivating Violet Noir colorway - a game-changing addition to any sneaker collection. This sneaker dropped on April 15, 2023.

The Violet and Noir hues grace the uppers, imparting a sense of mystery and allure to the sneaker. Designed with New Balance's timeless dedication to comfort, quality, and style, this pair is not just about aesthetics; it's about lifestyle. Perfect for a chill hangout or an adventurous city walk

This intriguing colorway Released on April 15, 2023 for $150.

name: Steel Grey Pure Silver
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Steel Grey Pure Silver
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 Steel Grey Pure Silver is a sleek and stylish sneaker that combines comfort and performance. Featuring a steel grey upper with pure silver accents, this shoe offers a modern and versatile look suitable for various occasions. The Gel-1130 model incorporates ASICS' renowned GEL technology in the heel, providing excellent shock absorption and cushioning for all-day comfort.

Designed with both style and functionality in mind, the Gel-1130 boasts a breathable mesh upper that ensures proper ventilation during wear. The durable rubber outsole offers reliable traction on various surfaces, making it an ideal choice for everyday use. With its classic ASICS design elements and contemporary colorway, this sneaker effortlessly bridges the gap between athletic performance and casual style.

Our experts state this product is great for those seeking a versatile sneaker that can transition seamlessly from casual outings to light athletic activities while providing exceptional comfort and support.

name: Black Leopard (Women's)
title: New Balance 327 Black Leopard (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 327 Black Leopard (Women's) represents a blend of traditional aesthetics and contemporary comfort, accentuated by a striking modern "N" detail.

A reinterpretation of New Balance's running legacy, the New Balance 327 Black Leopard (Women's) features an angular take on the classic wedge silhouette. The shoe showcases an oversized and asymmetrically placed "N" emblem that enhances its bold style with an eye-catching leopard print. Constructed with synthetic, suede, and nylon materials, the upper ensures a combination of durability and fashion-forward appeal. The shoe incorporates a rugged lug outsole inspired by trail footwear, ensuring both traction and durability. Sitting atop a thick white midsole that contrasts with the black upper, the design is completed with a black rubber outsole.

In our opinion, the standout characteristic of the New Balance 327 Black Leopard for women is its oversized and asymmetrically applied "N" branding. This daring design element not only distinguishes the shoe but also adds a contemporary flair, elevating its overall style. The sneaker debuted for $95 on February 14, 2023.

name: Cream Ironclad
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Cream Ironclad
description:
Inspired by the GEL-Kayano 14 sneaker, the ASICS Gel-1130 Cream Ironclad is a running shoe from the ASICS Gel-1130 lineup in a " Cream Ironclad" colorway.

This ASICS Gel-1130 shoe features an upper built with a cream mesh base and synthetic leather overlays in a Silver metallic finish. Other details include Cream round laces, a padded collar, a mesh tongue with "GEL CELL" branding, Grey branded insoles, and the ASICS logo on the vamp in Navy Blue. A sole unit featuring a White midsole with GEL® cushioning technology in the heel, TRUSSTIC™ support technology, and a Cream and Grey rubber outsole with multidirectional treads for traction rounds out the design.

What our experts love about this running shoe is its design and comfort. The upper construction offers breathability and extra comfort, while the support and cushioning technology guarantee a stabilized stride. The ASICS Gel-1130 Cream Ironclad was released on July 1, 2023, retailing at $95.

name: Alien
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Alien
description:
Yeezy has introduced a new silhouette to their product line with the adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Alien, now available on StockX. This model was originally known to be the Yeezy Boost 350 V3, but upon release it was given its own name.

This 380 Alien features a never before seen Primeknit pattern on its upper and lacks the traditional lateral side strip. An upgraded thicker Boost midsole and engineered outsole grip complete the design. These sneakers released in November of 2019 and retailed for $230.

name: MXT Moon Gray
title: adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR MXT Moon Gray
description:
DISCLAIMER: US and UK sizing is the same and does not require any conversion.

The Yeezy Foam RNNR MXT Moon Grey delivers a new color layout, making it different from the original, neutral Ararat. Constructed partially from algae, the entire shoe is hit with a mix of Sand and Moon Grey colors in a psychedelic mashup.

The Yeezy Foam RNNR MXT Moon Grey released in March of 2021 for $80.

name: Neon Nights
title: New Balance 9060 Neon Nights
description:
The New Balance 9060 Purple Red Blue is a visually dynamic sneaker that blends layered materials and daring color combinations. This design was released in July 2024 and reflects New Balance’s innovation in modern footwear​.

The Neon Nights 9060 by New Balance uses a mix of mesh, leather, and suede in its upper makeup. The color scheme combines purple, red, blue, yellow, and black, offering sharp contrasts. The sneaker’s sole has chunky rubber layers, translucent details, and angular patterns to show off a modern look and feel. Reflective accents, including the oversized "N" logo, are there to improve the visual design. This model reinterprets elements from classic New Balance running styles for a lifestyle-focused appeal​.

One element we appreciate about the New Balance 9060 Purple Red Blue is its use of translucent rubber in the sole, adding a futuristic design layer. The reflective oversized logo also provides an added aesthetic appeal. This model was priced at $150 at its launch on July 12, 2024​.

name: Grey
title: New Balance 992 Grey
description:
Originally released in 2006 to celebrate the brand’s 100th anniversary, the New Balance 992 Grey was the first New Balance shoe to incorporate ABZORB stability technology. The shoe, which was designed by Jonathan Bacon, was crafted to offer support and comfort for either casual daily wear or athletic activities such as running.

The New Balance 992 Grey is made with suede and mesh uppers, which offer both support and a snug fit as well as plenty of airflow. The ABZORB cushioning material, found in the sole and heel of the shoe, is designed to absorb impact, reducing stress on the joints.

The New Balance 992 grey released in February of 2006 and retailed for $175.

name: White Rain Cloud
title: New Balance 550 White Rain Cloud
description:
The New Balance 550 White Rain Cloud is a remake of the 550 basketball shoe of the late 1980s. It is a leather sneaker with a low-top silhouette. Other style attributes include suede accents and a mesh top for better comfort and ventilation.

White and gray, it has plenty of versatility, whether you're just kicking it with friends or playing a game against your rival team. The New Balance logo and name are embossed on the sidewall, the outsole, and the back of the heel. The "550" symbol is also incorporated in the design.

The New Balance 550 White Rain Cloud has a padded collar and rubber outsole for better support and durability when going for the jump shot. Our team is most impressed with how often the "NB" logo and name are shown on this shoe. New Balance released this shoe on August 23, 2023. It originally retailed for $120.

name: Nightwatch Green
title: New Balance 2002R Nightwatch Green
description:
This fresh take on one of the original New Balance styles, the New Balance 2002R Nightwatch Green comes in a rich forest green that will add a pop of color to any outfit. With extra cushioning and support in the sole, you can easily use these shoes for either exercising or simply walking throughout town.

The New Balance 2002R Nightwatch Green is embellished with leather accents and has mesh pieces to help with breathability. There are also soft-to-touch suede overlays that help to add texture and depth to the model. 

Initially released in February of 2022, the New Balance 2002R Nightwatch Green was sold at a starting retail price of $150.

name: Gallery Dept. Mental Energy Multi-Color
title: ASICS Gel-K1011 Gallery Dept. Mental Energy Multi-Color
description:
The ASICS Gel-K1011 Gallery Dept. Mental Energy Multi-Color is a striking collaboration that merges performance and style. This innovative sneaker showcases a captivating white and pure silver colorway, creating a visually appealing design that stands out in any setting. The shoe's upper features a blend of premium materials, ensuring both durability and comfort for the wearer. With its unique aesthetic, this model represents a perfect fusion of ASICS' renowned athletic heritage and Gallery Dept.'s avant-garde approach to fashion.

Engineered for optimal performance, the Gel-K1011 incorporates ASICS' signature GEL technology in the midsole, providing superior cushioning and shock absorption. The sneaker's design also includes a responsive sole unit, offering enhanced energy return with every step. Its carefully crafted silhouette not only delivers on functionality but also makes a bold fashion statement, making it versatile enough for both athletic pursuits and casual wear. Our experts state this product is great for sneaker enthusiasts looking for a perfect blend of cutting-edge design and athletic performance in their footwear.

name: Cecilie Bahnsen Black
title: ASICS Gel-Terrain Cecilie Bahnsen Black
description:
The ASICS Gel-Terrain Cecilie Bahnsen Black is a striking collaboration between the renowned Japanese sportswear brand and the Danish fashion designer. This men's sneaker seamlessly blends performance technology with high-fashion aesthetics, resulting in a unique and versatile footwear option. The all-black colorway exudes sophistication, making it suitable for both athletic pursuits and urban styling. Featuring ASICS' signature Gel cushioning technology, these shoes offer superior comfort and shock absorption, ideal for various terrains and activities.

The upper of the Gel-Terrain showcases Cecilie Bahnsen's distinctive design elements, likely incorporating luxurious materials and intricate detailing that elevate the shoe's appearance. The collaboration brings together ASICS' expertise in performance footwear with Bahnsen's avant-garde approach to fashion, creating a truly exceptional product. With a retail price of $255, this limited-edition release is set to drop on October 16, 2024, making it a highly anticipated item for sneaker enthusiasts and fashion-forward individuals alike. Our experts state this product is great for those seeking a perfect balance between style and functionality, offering a unique addition to any sneaker collection.

name: Washed Burgundy
title: New Balance 9060 Washed Burgundy
description:
The New Balance 9060 Washed Burgundy takes inspiration from the signature 99X series and reimagines this classic silhouette with futuristic elements, an asymmetrical design, and an exaggerated sensibility that adds both comfort and eye-catching style.

This Washed Burgundy New Balance 9060 running shoe features an upper base of washed burgundy mesh on the lateral side of the sneaker and cream-colored mesh on the medial. Washed Burgundy suede and gray leather form the overlays that course across the upper, providing style and structure. A shiny pinkish-purple CRT device adds heel stability as well as a touch of sheen. The two-toned cream-colored midsole features ABZORB underfoot to provide cushioning as well as energy return. The gray rubber outsole appears in pods with diamond grooves on both the forefoot and the heel.

What we enjoy most on this sneaker is the design of the signature side panel N. The lateral side sports an N in cream-colored leather while the medial features cream-colored embroidery in the pattern of a flying N. The New Balance 9060 Washed Burgundy was released on September 7th, 2023 for $150 retail.

name: White Red
title: New Balance 1906R White Red
description:
The New Balance 1906R White Red is a running sneaker built for comfort and performance with every stride and dressed in a sleek, subtle colorway.

The White Red New Balance 1906R sports an upper with a base of white mesh. Synthetic white leather overlays cross the upper, adding both style and structural support. A gray synthetic heel counter stabilizes the foot and sports NB branding. The red side-panel N features N-Lock branding. The mesh tongue sports NB Running branding, and the gray laces match the gray sock liner, completing the aesthetic of this upper.

But what we appreciate most about this running shoe is the high-octane sole unit. The tannish-gray ABZORB midsole also features ABZORB SBS in the heel and N-ergy, providing springy cushioning and energy return. The gum-rubber outsole absorbs impact and provides traction on both the road and track. The New Balance 1906R White Red was released on October 1, 2022, for a retail price of $120.

name: Birch Metropolis
title: Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD Birch Metropolis
description:
The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD Birch Metropolis is a Super Deluxe iteration of the Onitsuka Tiger’s beloved silhouette. This high-end sneaker is dressed in a subtle colorway that exudes elegance.

This low-riding lifestyle sneaker begins with an upper base of Birch tumbled leather. Birch suede forms a T-toe overlay, the eyestay overlay, the rim around the collar, a heel counter, and the signature serrated strips that cross at the heel. Warm gray suede in a Metropolis shade is used to craft the stripes that of course both vertically and horizontally over the side panel. Birch-colored rubber is used to help reinforce the toecap. A foam midsole in both Birch and rests atop a Birch rubber outsole.

The detail of this sneaker we most enjoy is the fold-over heel flap in Birch suede. It sports Metropolis Tiger branding that locks in the elegant dual colorway of this shoe. The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD Birch Metropolis was released on September 1, 2023, for retail price of $180.

name: Protection Pack Dark Navy
title: New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Dark Navy
description:
The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Dark Navy features an upper blue mesh with hits of white leather and overlays of navy suede with jagged edges.

The laces of the New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Dark Navy are light gray and the tongue is black with a yellow-gold underside, the same gold as the center of the heel with its "NB" branding. The "N" on the quarter panel is embroidered in dark and light gray and "2002R" is stamped on a white leather hit below the blue mesh collar. The ABZORB midsole surrounds the N-ergy columns in the heel and the outsole features blue-black traction. 

The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Dark Navy debuted in April 2022 and retailed for $150.

name: Teddy Santis MiUSA Sadow Grey Driftwood
title: New Balance 993 Teddy Santis MiUSA Sadow Grey Driftwood
description:
The New Balance 993 Teddy Santis MiUSA Sadow Grey Driftwood combines refined handiwork with a muted earthy palette that shows off the designer’s innovative approach to footwear. Part of the Made in USA collection, it's created with useful design elements ideal for seasonal use.

This Teddy Santis MiUSA Sadow Grey Driftwood 993 iteration features a breathable mesh upper layered with grey suede overlays for texture and to make the shoe more sturdy. Synthetic panels improve structural integrity, while terrycloth lining offers a soft, comfortable fit. Its neutral ACTEVA midsole gives you responsive cushioning, complemented by Ndurance rubber for added outsole structure. This model integrates subtle branding, including the signature "N" logo and star-spangled details on the heel.

As the experts, one thing we love about the New Balance 993 Teddy Santis MiUSA Sadow Grey Driftwood is its breathable mesh and grey suede makeup that combines a sturdy structure with lightweight usefulness. This pair retailed at $220 upon its release on 15 August 2024​.

name: Team Light Blue Club Navy
title: Puma Speedcat Archive Team Light Blue Club Navy
description:
The Puma Speedcat Archive Team Light Blue Club Navy is a stylish revival of a classic racing-inspired silhouette. This men's sneaker features a sleek low-top design with a premium suede upper in a striking team light blue colorway, complemented by club navy accents. The iconic formstrip logo adorns the sides, while the slim rubber outsole provides excellent traction and a distinctive look.

Designed for both style and comfort, the Speedcat Archive boasts a padded collar and tongue for enhanced support. The shoe's streamlined profile and rounded toe box pay homage to its motorsport heritage, making it a perfect blend of retro charm and modern appeal. With its eye-catching color combination and timeless design, this Puma sneaker is versatile enough for casual wear or as a statement piece in your outfit.

Us at StockX believe this product is great for those seeking a unique, sporty-chic look with a touch of nostalgia. The Puma Speedcat Archive offers both comfort and style, making it an excellent choice for everyday wear or as a standout addition to your sneaker collection.

name: Kith Madison Square Garden White Orange
title: New Balance Numeric 480 Kith Madison Square Garden White Orange
description:
The New Balance Numeric 480 Kith Madison Square Garden White Orange is a striking collaboration that pays homage to one of New York City's most iconic venues. This sleek sneaker features a pristine white leather upper, accented with vibrant orange details that capture the energy and excitement of Madison Square Garden. The shoe's design seamlessly blends classic New Balance aesthetics with modern skateboarding functionality, making it a versatile choice for both street style and performance.

Crafted with precision, the Numeric 480 boasts a durable rubber outsole that provides excellent grip and board feel, essential for skaters seeking optimal control. The shoe's padded collar and tongue offer enhanced comfort and support, while the streamlined silhouette ensures a stylish look that transcends the skate park. With its eye-catching colorway and premium materials, this Kith collaboration elevates the Numeric 480 to new heights of style and performance.

Us at StockX believe this product is great for skateboarding enthusiasts and fashion-forward individuals alike, offering a perfect blend of functionality and street-ready style.

name: Bone
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Bone
description:
The Yeezy Slide Bone features a triple-Bone EVA foam upper with the stark white color of Bone covering the entirety of the silhouette in one monochromatic hue that goes from the single, wide sandal strap down to the unique sole of the shoe. From there, the deep footbed uses the same plush foam EVA for comfort, and the outsole features a toothy construction that is intended to make the sandals rugged enough for different weather conditions, with the look finishing up using a small adidas logo on the heel to complete the design.

The Yeezy Slide Bone released in December of 2019 and retailed for $55.

To shop the 2022 re-issue of the adidas Yeezy Slide Bone, click here.

name: Khaki
title: adidas Yeezy NSLTD Boot Khaki
description:
The adidas Yeezy NSLTD Boot Khaki focuses on retaining heat with its construction. Its heavily insulated Khaki upper is reminiscent of a puffer jacket with its heavy padding and enigmatic shape. Also, the design is completely laceless. A hidden velcro enclosure on the lateral side secures your feet without the hassle of lacing up.

The adidas Yeezy NSLTD Boot Khaki released in November of 2021 and retailed for $340.

name: Navy Blue
title: New Balance 550 Navy Blue
description:
The New Balance 550 Navy Blue features a white smooth leather upper with perforated overlays and a grey suede toe wrap. From there, hits of navy blue on the New Balance logos, collar piping, woven tongue label, and sole complete the design.

The New Balance 550 Navy Blue released in June of 2021 and retailed for $120.

name: White Winter Fog Navy
title: New Balance 550 White Winter Fog Navy
description:
Originally designed as a performance basketball shoe, the New Balance 550 White Winter Fog Navy updates the OG model with an airy colorway of white, NB Navy, and Winter Fog.

Compared to the OG sneaker, the White Winter Fog Navy New Balance 550 features a much cleaner design. The ENCAP cushioning system increases comfort on the court, while the rubber outsole features a grippy traction pattern. Something that makes this sneaker stand out is the color blocking on the outsole. It comes in light green and Winter Fog, complementing the upper’s neutral tones. Leather and soft synthetic suede complete the upper construction, including layered overlays with double lines of reinforced stitching.

Our experts at StockX like the heritage branding details, including the signature New Balance "N" on the side panel, "550" on the overlays, and a large New Balance logo tag on the tongue. The New Balance 550 White Winter Fog Navy was released on September 2, 2023, and sold for $110.

name: Sea Salt Team Royal
title: New Balance 550 Sea Salt Team Royal
description:
The New Balance 550 Sea Salt Team Royal is an offering of the New Balance 550 silhouette in a "Sea Salt Team Royal" colorway.

This New Balance 550 features a predominantly Sea Salt White upper constructed with a mix of materials, including mesh and suede. Contrasting royal blue accents on the signature "N" logo on the sides, "550" branding on the lateral forefoot, ankle collar, and tongue branding. Black hues feature on the inner lining, "NB" branding on the heel, the outline of the "N" logo, and the TPU heel counter. Finishing off the design is a white midsole and a two-tone royal blue and light gray rubber outsole.

What our experts particularly love about this New Balance 550 sneaker is its distinctive colorway and classic design, which give it a retro aesthetic, contributing to its standout appeal. The New Balance 550 Sea Salt Team Royal was made available on February 5th, 2023, retailing at $120.

name: Birch Peacoat
title: Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD Birch Peacoat
description:
The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD Birch Peacoat merges vintage design with modern enhancements as a stylish nod to the athletic heritage of Onitsuka Tiger and ASICS brands. Its distinct colors and updated structure make it an ideal addition to the iconic Mexico 66 lineup.

The Birch Peacoat Mexico 66 SD by ASICS and Onitsuka Tiger comes with premium leather in soft-beige tones paired with contrasting dark brown stripes for a clean look. A suede heel accent and perforated details improve longevity and breathability, while the updated rubber outsole gives you superior grip. This design draws inspiration from the original Mexico 66, a silhouette first introduced for the 1968 Olympics.

One thing we love about the Birch Peacoat Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 SD is its Ortholite insole, offering exceptional comfort for all-day wear. We also appreciate the reinforced heel counter, which provides extra support for a secure fit. Released on January 26, 2022, this model was priced at $160.

name: Enflame
title: adidas Yeezy 500 Enflame
description:
The adidas Yeezy 500 Enflame arrives in a tonal-brown, dark blue, and orange color scheme. Its upper is constructed of mesh with leather and suede overlays throughout the silhouette. To complete the design, an orange AdiPRENE sole offers premium cushioning.

The adidas Yeezy 500 Enflame released in May of 2021 and retailed for $200.

name: Oyster Grey
title: ASICS Gel-1130 Oyster Grey
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 Oyster Grey is a stability running shoe designed for both the track and the streets that pays homage to the 2008 iteration of the GEL-1000 series.

The Oyster Grey colorway of the ASICS GEL-1130 features an upper that begins with a base of loosely woven white mesh, underlaid by more tightly woven gray mesh. This base is overlaid with strips of leather in shades of gray, brown, tan, and ivory to offer the signature ASICS style and foot support. The white mesh tongue sports GEL-1130 ASICS branding, while the brown mesh sock liner surrounds a tonal insole that sports white ASICS branding. The ASICS logo also appears at the bottom of the laces.

The most impressive aspect of this running shoe is its sole. A foam midsole in shades of tan features GEL technology for ultimate cushioning, as well as a TRUSSTIC support system at the midfoot to help prevent the foot from twisting. This rests on an outsole of tan and dark brown rubber that adds to the impact absorption and provides durable traction. The ASICS Gel-1130 Oyster Grey was released on September 7, 2022, for $95 retail.

name: White Light Sage
title: Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 White Light Sage
description:
The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 White Light Sage is a performance running shoe that also contains elements from the LIMBER-UP shoe that debuted in 1961.
  
The White Light Sage Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 has an upper made of grained leather in white. A thin, t-shaped toe cap appears as an overlay in the same color, and another panel forms the eyestays. There are crisscrosses at the heel for support. The typical tiger stripes that have become synonymous with the brand cross the sides in Light Sage suede, and Tiger branding is found on the heel collar. The tongue bears a subtle logo patch. The shoe sits on a thin, white midsole and outsole.

What we think stands out about this sneaker are the Light Sage accents, which are so pale that they almost blend into the white. The Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 White Light Sage was released on August 1, 2023, for $130.

name: Aime Leon Dore Olive
title: New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Olive
description:
The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Olive is another design from Aime Leon Dore's collection sporting a neutral, two-tone styling of plain-white and dark-olive colorway. The unassuming yet streamlined silhouette is complemented by a mesh-leather upper, a co-branded tongue, and New Balance "NB" logo on the lateral atop a cracked leather finish.

A dark-olive rubber outsole and an aged-out midsole with a matching heel and collar detailing give off the 80s ‘retro look’ that offers the New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Olive sneaker a distinct personality.

New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Olive was launched in June 2022, retailing at $130.

name: Triple Black
title: New Balance 993 Triple Black
description:
The New Balance 993 Triple Black is a classic unisex running shoe that has been a staple in New Balance's lineup since its debut in 2008.

The shoe has a classic and timeless design featuring a layered upper made from a combination of suede, mesh and other synthetic materials. It has a monochromatic color scheme with black all over, including the sole unit and underfoot. The shoe bears classic New Balance branding, with the iconic "N" logo appearing on the sides, and number 993 on the lateral heel. It also has a USA badge on the heel to signify it is part of the "Made in the USA" series, which emphasizes domestic manufacturing and quality craftsmanship.

What our experts love about the New Balance 993 Triple Black is the incorporation of New Balance's proprietary ENCAP technology, which is uses soft cushioning EVA in the midsole, with a more robust polyurethane rim for durability and mainly support. The shoes were initially released for retail on May 25, 2022, at $200.

name: Mist Slate
title: adidas Yeezy QNTM Mist Slate
description:
The adidas Yeezy QNTM Mist Slate sneaker is a collaboration between adidas and Kayne West that sports a style inspired by basketball. Adidas regularly releases new colorways in the Yeezy QNTM line, and this adidas Yeezy QNTM features a neutral palette debuting a mist slate color scheme.

This iteration has a predominantly mist slate upper with unique side panels that utilize mesh waves to provide a glimpse of the black and white striped liner inside. The seamless heel counter enhances stability and boasts a silver color. White neoprene houses the high ankle collar, while black laces, tongue, and lining provide color balance.

Our experts note the lack of outer visible adidas branding, but that’s not a minus in our book. Given these shoes’ daring design, it’s a standout feature. Released on August 4, 2023, the adidas Yeezy QNTM Mist Slate sold for a retail price of $250.

name: Aime Leon Dore White
title: New Balance 860v2 Aime Leon Dore White
description:
The New Balance 860v2 Aime Leon Dore White is a running shoe designed as a collaboration with the fashion and lifestyle brand Aime Leon Dore.

This model of the New Balance 860v2 is made mostly with a white mesh upper for breathability and flexibility. Textured and patterned white synthetic overlays round out the toe box and cross the midsole. The overlays are reflective for safety at nighttime. The typically New Balance "N" shows up on both sides in white, and the heel has a subtle support system void of branding. The tongue sports Aime Leon Dore branding also in white and the patterned midsole is made of ABZORB cushioning. A rubber outsole completes the look.

What we love most about this shoe is the reflective elements, which allow for both style and safety. The New Balance 860v2 Aime Leon Dore White was released on February 1, 2024, for a price of $150.

name: Taupe Black
title: adidas Yeezy 500 High Taupe Black
description:
The adidas Yeezy 500 High Taupe Black is part of the collaboration between adidas and artist Kanye West.

The High Taupe Black Yeezy 500 version comes in a taupe/black colorway. The sneaker features a padded collar that provides comfort and support around the ankle. It also has a lace-up closure that helps to keep the foot secure and comfortable. The sneaker is made from a combination of suede, leather, and mesh materials that are seamlessly blended together. The insole is made of OrthoLite® material, which is known for its moisture-wicking and breathability properties.

Our experts say that the best feature of the adidas Yeezy 500 High Taupe Black is its thick and chunky sole. The midsole is made using adidas' lightweight Adiprene technology, which delivers cushioning. It helps to absorb impact and reduce foot fatigue. The outsole is made of durable rubber, providing traction and support. The shoe was released on October 17th, 2022, at a retail price of $220.

name: Iridescent Dreams
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Iridescent Dreams
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 Iridescent Dreams was NBA´s player first model done in collaboration with the German sport and lifestyle brand.

The LaMelo Ball MB01 sneaker has a monochromatic design in all black, coupled with luminous accents. The shoe is primarily made from a mixture of plastic, rubber, and mesh materials. The midsole is made out of foam, while the sole is made out of non-slip rubber. The tongue features silver designs and several small inscriptions, as well as black laces on top.

The Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 Iridescent Dreams was initially released on August 22nd, 2022, with a retail price of $125.

name: MiUSA Black White
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Black White
description:
The New Balance 990v3 Black White sneaker comes in a black, grey, and white color scheme and is covered in fine pig suede a breathable mesh, and high-quality leather. 

The majority of the top panels on the upper are dressed in dark black colors, while the foam ENCAP cushioning on its midsole, and heel tab features a combination of grey and white. Further details include the grey traditional with white outline "N" logos on the medial and lateral sides  Apart from the red "NB" logo on the spine, Made in USA, and New Balance, 990v3 branding, on the tongue, the New Balance text is also featured on the heel counter.

The New Balance 990v3 Black White was released on 1st October 2021 and retailed at $180.

name: Triple White
title: New Balance 650R Triple White
description:
The New Balance 650R Triple White reconfigures the classic 550 silhouette as a high-top and dresses it in a monochromatic colorway that works for both sports and leisure.

The Triple White New Balance 650R features a white upper constructed of mesh on the collar and ankle and smooth leather on the forefoot. Overlays in white leather, both smooth and perforated, course across the upper, adding style as well as durable support. A side-panel N appears in smooth white leather through a cut-out window, while New Balance branding appears on a collar overlay and 650 branding on a midfoot overlay. Classic NB branding is debossed on the heel counter and printed on the white tongue tag and insole.

What we appreciate most about this sneaker is its white and gray sole. A midsole of white EVA foam provides cushioning and sports embossed branding. The gray rubber outsole features grooves for multi-directional traction and impact absorption. The New Balance 650R Triple White was released on November 10, 2022, for $140 retail.

name: White Moonrock (Women's)
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 White Moonrock (Women's)
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 White Moonrock (Women's) is a women’s running shoe that takes its inspiration from the late 2000s design but with updated materials.
  
This version of the ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 is made with a base of white mesh. Textured silver leather overlays round out the toe box and run down from the eyestays, while the ASICS design across each side of the shoe appears in Moonrock. The heel supports are also silver, with Gel-Kayano 14 branding appearing on the lateral side. Gel branding is also found on the heel, with accents of Moonrock. The tongue features ASICS branding in Moonrock, as well, and the shoe sits on a white midsole with an upgraded TRUSSTIC support system. Gel technology in Moonrock is seen in the midsole under the heel and forefoot. 

Our favorite feature of this shoe is the Moonrock Gel seen underfoot, as it adds a nice contrast to the white color in addition to its functionality. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 White Moonrock (Women's) was released on March 2, 2023, for $150.

name: Paris
title: ASICS GT-2160 Paris
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 Paris is a stylish and performance-driven sneaker that pays homage to the City of Light. Featuring a sleek cream colorway accented with vibrant safety yellow details, this shoe captures the essence of Parisian elegance and energy. The GT-2160 model combines ASICS' renowned comfort technology with a modern aesthetic, making it perfect for both athletic pursuits and casual wear.

Designed with the urban explorer in mind, the GT-2160 Paris offers superior cushioning and support for all-day comfort. The shoe's responsive midsole and strategic gel placement provide excellent shock absorption, while the durable outsole ensures reliable traction on various surfaces. With its breathable upper and ergonomic fit, this sneaker delivers a premium wearing experience that caters to both style-conscious individuals and performance-oriented athletes.

Our experts state this product is great for those seeking a versatile sneaker that seamlessly blends fashion-forward design with functional performance, ideal for navigating city streets or tackling your daily workout routine.

name: MiUSA Joe Freshgoods 1998 Outro
title: New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods 1998 Outro
description:
The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods 1998 Outro is a striking sneaker that represents a collaboration between the streetwear designer and the iconic sneaker company. The Outro running shoe design is inspired by the films, magazines, and artistic influences Joe Robinson, founder of Joe Freshgoods, appreciates from the 1990s.

The Outro sneaker from the Joe Freshgoods x New Balance 990v4 Made in USA 1998 features an upper with a base of white mesh that is overlaid with black patent leather and black suede. New Balance branding appears as a large white N on the side panel and white script on the heel. White New Balance branding appears on one black insole, while Joe Freshgoods branding appears on the other. 990v4 branding graces the tongue, while Joe Freshgoods branding accents the lateral heel.

Our favorite aspects of this sneaker are the black ENCAP midsole that provides energy return and cushioning and the black rubber outsole that delivers impact absorption as well as traction. The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods 1998 Outro was released on December 15, 2023, for $220 retail.

name: Sean Wotherspoon x atmos
title: ASICS Gel-Lyte III Sean Wotherspoon x atmos
description:
The "ASICS Gel Lyte III Sean Wotherspoon x atmos" is a collaboration between Sean Wotherspoon with Atmos and ASICS.

This Gel Lyte III  model comes in a multi-color. The sneaker features corduroy upper and interchangeable side stripes, finished in a mismatched color palette. The left pair has light and dark purple on the toe-box, dark brown on the heel, dark navy on the quarter panels, and mint green across the collar and lace-stays. The right pair has light and dark orange toe-box, pastel blue quarter panels, a teal heel, and light gray collar and lace-stays.

The ASICS Gel Lyte III Sean Wotherspoon x atmos was released on the 27th of June 2020, retailing for $165.

name: Synth (Reflective)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Synth (Reflective)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Synth features a pale reddish-pink tint on the Primeknit upper, translucent monofilament stripes, and a translucent rubber sole. It also has a gray Primeknit upper with reflective material woven in an intricate design. It uses eco-friendly materials while the majority of cotton used is from sustainable sources. When hit with reflective light, the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Synth Reflective has a reflective detail on the upper and the laces.

It was released in June 2019 and retailed at a price of $220.

name: Blue Haze
title: New Balance 9060 Blue Haze
description:
The New Balance 9060 Blue Haze comes in a blue haze, beige color palette.

The New Balance 9060 Blue Haze updates a classic silhouette with an upper that is constructed from a breathable blend of synthetic and mesh materials, while the tongue and collar are cushioned for comfort. The shoe features a midsole made from EVA and rubber for padding and impact reduction. The sneaker's outsole is constructed with a tough rubber tread that is both grippy and durable. The shoe has the signature "N" on the lateral sides, "NB 9060" on the tongue, and "NB" branding on the heel.

The New Balance 9060 Blue Haze was released on February 3, 2023, and retailed for $150.

name: Grey
title: New Balance 2002R Grey
description:
In 2010, the New Balance 2002R Grey was first made available, over a decade later the sneaker introduces shades of grey in its design.

Multiple shades of grey are used on the New Balance 2002R Grey top. The platinum fabric serves as the design's foundation, with suede overlays, and the details are in soft leather. It has an ashy imitation leather surface with a basic, perforated netting top. Additionally, it gets a matching outsole to complete the styling, and the shoe displays the iconic New Balance logo draped in grey.

The New Balance 2002R Grey debuted on 1st January 2022. Originally, it retailed at $250.

name: Pure Silver
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano Legacy Pure Silver
description:
Available in a "Pure Silver" colorway, the ASICS Gel-Kayano Legacy Pure Silver is a sneaker from the ASICS GEL-KAYANO Legacy collection that celebrates the 30th anniversary of the GEL-KAYANO series.

Inspired by the GEL-KAYANO 14, this GEL-KAYANO Legacy offering features a reflective silver upper made of a mesh base and leather overlays. Black accents on the tongue, laces, and branding contrast the monochromatic upper. Branding details include "GEL-KAYANO LEGACY" lettering on the lateral heel, "GEL" wording on the heel tab, and the "Kayano" name etched in Kanji on the tongue. Other details include a "30th Anniversary" graphic on the black insoles and 3M reflective hits.  A black and light silver sole unit with ASICS Gel cushioning and a rubber outsole complete the design.

Our experts particularly love this sneaker’s design elements and colorway, which add a touch of uniqueness to its overall aesthetic appeal. The ASICS Gel-Kayano Legacy Pure Silver was made available on September 15th, 2023. Initially, it retailed at $200.

name: White Illusion Blue
title: ASICS GT-2160 White Illusion Blue
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 White Illusion Blue is a technical running sneaker that pays homage to various performance running shoes from the 2010s.

Like its predecessor, the GT-2000, this sneaker boasts wavy sculpting on the forefoot that creates the illusion of motion. While the upper is crafted from lightweight mesh with a wide weave, the synthetic overlays form an almost grid-like design that supports the shoe. The colorway features White and Illusion Blue, which manifests as a White base with Illusion Blue piping and splashes of color. A segmented midsole underfoot also pays tribute to previous models, and gel technology inserts provide advanced cushioning. Both the heel collar and the tongue are padded for additional comfort.

Our experts like how the outsole incorporated vivid Illusion Blue on the tread. The ASICS GT-2160 White Illusion Blue was released on July 15th, 2023, and retailed for a price of $120.

name: Rain Cloud
title: New Balance 2002R Mule Rain Cloud
description:
The New Balance 2002R Mule Rain Cloud is an updated version of the 2002R that offers a slip-on design without a heel.

Like other 2002R models, the mule variation in Rain Cloud provides a mesh upper, overlapping suede and leather overlays, and cutouts. The mule does not house a lace cage, laces, any part of the heel, or a collar. The underfoot includes an ABZORB midsole that adds a slightly technical look. A rubber outsole grips the ground and provides a pop of black against the otherwise grey-toned base. The New Balance "N" is embroidered on the side panel, and perforations decorate the area that usually contains the laces.

Our experts like the Rain Cloud and Marblehead colorway, which is slightly lighter than other grey-toned versions of the sneaker. The New Balance 2002R Mule Rain Cloud was released on December 20th, 2022, and retailed at $120.

name: Black Clay Grey
title: ASICS Gel-NYC Black Clay Grey
description:
The ASICS Gel-NYC Black Clay Gray finds inspiration in performance running shoes from the early 2000s with visible technology, including the Gel NIMBUS-3 and the MC-PLUS V.

The inclusion of ASICS’ gel cushioning technology in the midsole absorbs impact and increases energy return. In addition, the durable rubber outsole provides superior traction without creating a bulky feel. The upper is made of lightweight mesh with a wide weave that allows the foot to breathe, while a variety of leather and suede overlays maintain the sneaker’s form. Padding around the collar and tongue protects the foot and gives the area near the ankle a slightly padded appearance.

Our experts at StockX like the metallic details on the overlays. They pay homage to the shoe’s 2000s origins and add a hint of sparkle in the sunlight. The ASICS Gel-NYC Black Clay Gray was released on March 3rd, 2023, and retailed at $160.

name: Concrete Silver Metallic
title: New Balance 1906A Concrete Silver Metallic
description:
The New Balance 1906A Concrete Silver Metallic is a striking addition to the brand's lineup, combining style and performance in one sleek package. This men's sneaker features a sophisticated color palette of concrete, silver metallic, and Brighton grey, creating a versatile look that seamlessly transitions from casual to athletic wear. The upper is crafted with premium materials, ensuring durability and comfort for everyday use, while the iconic New Balance 'N' logo adorns the sides, adding a touch of brand recognition.

Designed with the modern wearer in mind, the 1906A boasts advanced cushioning technology in the midsole, providing exceptional support and energy return with every step. The rubber outsole offers superior traction on various surfaces, making these sneakers ideal for both urban environments and light athletic activities. With its sleek silhouette and attention to detail, the New Balance 1906A Concrete Silver Metallic is a testament to the brand's commitment to quality and style.

Our experts state this product is great for those seeking a balance between fashion-forward design and all-day comfort, making it an excellent choice for active individuals who don't want to compromise on style.

name: Nimbus Cloud White (Women's)
title: New Balance 574 Nimbus Cloud White (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 574 Nimbus Cloud White (W) comes in a color palette that is somewhat lighter in hue than the brand's grey color scheme crafted in suede and mesh materials inspired by its predecessor.

The heel stabilizer and sole have been dyed monochromatically in white and dark grey. The model is covered in a faded grey. Other features include reflective "N" emblems on the side, woven labels with their customary branding, and a black typeface "New Balance" at the heel tab. Additional brandings include the NB logo and "574" text on its padded tongue.

The women's iteration of the New Balance 574 Nimbus Cloud White (W) was released on 16th March 2022 and retailed at $85.

name: Black Grey Silver
title: New Balance 740v2 Black Grey Silver
description:
The New Balance 740v2 Black Grey Silver is a sleek and stylish addition to the renowned New Balance lineup. This men's sneaker showcases a sophisticated color palette, combining black, grey, and silver hues for a versatile and modern aesthetic. The 740v2 model builds upon the success of its predecessor, offering enhanced comfort and performance features that cater to both casual wear and athletic pursuits.

Crafted with New Balance's signature attention to detail, the 740v2 boasts a durable construction that ensures longevity. The upper is designed with a combination of premium materials, providing both support and breathability for all-day comfort. The shoe's cushioning system offers responsive support, making it ideal for various activities, from daily walks to light workouts. Us at StockX believe this product is great for those seeking a balance between style and functionality in their footwear, as it seamlessly transitions from casual outings to more active scenarios.

name: Warped Multi-Color
title: New Balance 9060 Warped Multi-Color
description:
The New Balance 9060 Warped Multi-Colour debuted following its collaboration with Joe Freshgoods. This also marked the first time the two joined forces for the release of the sneakers.

Featured on the New Balance 9060 is a blend of mint collecting along the mesh base layer and suede overlays, while a light shade of teal extends through the nubuck consoles up above. Ingrained all over the sock liner is a touch of lavender followed by the cream nylon laces above. The ABZORB midsole with an array of pink, lava red, and bubble gum tones sits just below the mix of yellow-red N logo filling the midfoot.

The New Balance 9060 Warped Multi-Colour debuted on March 31st, 2023, and retailed for $150.

name: MiUSA Ronnie Fieg Madison Square Garden Sandrift
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Ronnie Fieg Madison Square Garden Sandrift
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Ronnie Fieg Madison Square Garden Sandrift is part of the first collaboration between New Balance, Madison Square Garden, and Ronnie Fieg, a New York-based footwear designer known for his bold color combinations.

Ronnie Fieg’s influence can be seen in the bright orange and blue accents across the otherwise neutral-toned sneaker. The colorway of Cream, Sandrift, and Orange was inspired by the exciting atmosphere of Madison Square Garden and the New York Knicks. The upper features a combination of mesh and suede with some reflective details. Branding details include the New Balance "N" along the side panel, "990" on an overlay, "MADE IN USA" on the heel, and the New Balance logo on the tongue tag.

Our experts like the sneaker’s technical design, which utilizes New Balance’s superior running technologies. The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Ronnie Fieg Madison Square Garden Sandrift was released on November 6th, 2023, and retailed at $220.

name: Bodega Age of Discovery
title: New Balance 9060 Bodega Age of Discovery
description:
The New Balance 9060 Bodega Age of Discovery incorporates elements from the classic 990 running shoe series.

The upper section of this collaborative sneaker combines several textures in a three-color scheme. The base is Blue mesh with overlays in Sea Salt smooth leather, brown suede, and Beige hairy suede. The lateral "N" and the medial "N" are the main branding details. Other hits appear throughout the upper and the tongue sports a tag. The midsole features N-ergy and ABZORB technology, and the rubber outsole is for traction.  

The New Balance 9060 Bodega Age of Discovery debuted on December 10, 2022 for a retail price of $180.

name: UNC White University Blue
title: New Balance 550 UNC White University Blue
description:
The classic styling of the New Balance 550 UNC White University Blue offers a retro look with traditional basketball oxford styling elements. They feature the classic "N" styling on the sides of the sneaker plus traditional New Balance branding on the tongue of the shoes. These predominantly white shoes have subtle yet distinct touches of North Carolina baby blue on the soles, tongue, and logo to give them an understated yet vibrant look.

With a release date of January 2022, the New Balance 550 UNC White University Blue retailed for $110.

name: Queen City Fade
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Queen City Fade
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Queen City Fade is a basketball sneaker from the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 lineup in a "Queen City Fade" colorway.

Inspired by the colors of LaMelo Ball's franchise, the Charlotte Hornets, this Puma LaMelo Ball sneaker features a super breathable technical mesh material dressed in the team’s light blue and violet accents. Feather-like synthetic overlays that pay homage to the basketball player’s trademark wings and a gradient honeycomb pattern that fades at the heel offer a unique and stylish aesthetic. Other details include LaMelo Ball’s signature wings logo on the tongue and the  Silver TPU (thermoplastic polyurethane) heel counter, blue laces, and a co-branded heel tab. A NITRO foam midsole rests on a white rubber outsole with herringbone traction treads.

Our experts particularly love this sneaker’s colorway and construction, which add a meaningful and stylish element to the design. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Queen City Fade was made available on July 7th, 2023, for a retail price of $130.

name: Protection Pack Sea Salt
title: New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Sea Salt
description:
The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Sea Salt features a Sea Salt textile upper with tonal jagged suede overlays and unfinished edges. From there, a cream Nrgy midsole and grey outsole complete the design.

The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Sea Salt released in August of 2021 and retailed for $150.

name: White Silver Metallic
title: New Balance 530 White Silver Metallic
description:
The New Balance 530 White Silver Metallic is a sneaker that was released in a retro-silhouette as part of the New Balance 530 collection.

Featuring a predominately white colorway with silver metallic accents, the Balance 530 White Silver Metallic includes a predominantly mesh construction. The shoe features a cushioned midsole that provides excellent support and impact resistance. In addition, the shoe has a rubber outsole, which offers excellent traction and grip. Moreover, the sneaker also has a low-laying collar that is padded and a pull tag on the heel. The tongue is padded as well and is finished off with a New Balance running logo. The 530 label can also be seen on the side.

We think that one of the standout features of the New Balance 530 White Silver Metallic is the leather overlay that is designed to encase the mesh structure. The shoe was released on January 4th, 2023, at a retail price of $100.

name: Driftwood Sandstone
title: New Balance 2002R Driftwood Sandstone
description:
The New Balance 2002R Driftwood Sandstone features a multi-material upper that combines pigskin and textiles. An ABZORB midsole in white and Sandstone balances a foam-padded insole. An N-ergy outsole in Sandstone ties the sole together. A reflective N logo, 2002R, and N-ergy branding appear on the sides, tongue, rear, and toe wrap.

Designed to be a lifestyle shoe, the 2002R is a refinement of previous 2002 generations. The mixed material upper remains, while the sole is adapted from the 860v2. Never straying far from its classic branding style, the 2002R offers signature N branding amidst a more futuristic aesthetic, due to its graceful curves and cutouts.

Our experts feel that the best feature of the 2002R is its comfort combined with refined style, which looks great while being suitable for all day wear. The New Balance 2002R Driftwood Sandstone released on July 13, 2023, and retailed for $140.

name: Bodega Better Days
title: New Balance 997S Bodega Better Days
description:
