The New Balance 997S Bodega Better Days is a collaboration between New Balance and the Bodega streetwear brand.

The New Balance 997S Bodega Better Days has a gray palette with touches of orange, red, yellow, and white embellishments. The upper of the shoe is composed of leather, suede, and mesh. The shoe features the trademark "N" branding of New Balance on the sides and a durable rubber outsole for increased traction. This sneaker's midsole is constructed with New Balance's ENCAP technology, which offers lightweight cushioning and stability. The midsole also features the innovative ABZORB cushioning technology developed by New Balance.

The New Balance 997S Bodega Better Days was released on September 25th, 2020, for a retail price of $160.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis White Black Plum
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Teddy Santis White Black Plum
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Teddy Santis White Black Plum is a shoe designed as a collaboration between the brand and designer and Internet personality Teddy Santis.
    
This iteration of the New Balance 990v6 features a white textile upper as the base. Synthetic overlays cross the upper in black, while the company’s logo, a letter "N," appears on each side in a Black Plum (dark purple) color. A dark tan suede overlay forms the large toe cap, another forms the heel counter, and a lighter tan forms the mudguard in the middle. 990 branding is seen on the lateral heel counter, while Made in the USA branding is on the heel's back. The tongue bears a New Balance 990 patch. The shoe sits on a chunky tan and white midsole and black outsole. 

What stands out about this shoe is the contrast between the black and dark purple and the tans of the bottom of the shoe. The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Teddy Santis White Black Plum was released on June 27, 2024, for $220.

name: Pyrite
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Pyrite
description:
The upper of the adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Pyrite is constructed of tonal grey camo Primeknit with perforations on each lateral side. At the base, a white semi-translucent Boost midsole provides structure and support for the woven design.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Pyrite released in October of 2021 and retailed for $230.

name: Mist
title: adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Mist
description:
In a monochromatic Mist styling, the adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Mist features a sculptural EVA foam and algae blended construction. At the base, a grooved outsole provides traction and support.

The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Mist released in March of 2022 and retailed for $90.

name: Sea Salt Black Gum (Women's)
title: New Balance 327 Sea Salt Black Gum (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 327 Sea Salt Black Gum W comes in a pigskin suede overlay and a nylon base.

The upper of this women’s sneaker is dressed majorly in a sea salt color scheme. While its white padded tongue is adorned by a black NB logo, its N logo on the lateral side is dressed in white with mesh. Other brandings include the "New Balance" text on the heel counter completing its appearance. Finally, it features cushioning technologies such as the brand's signature EVA foam midsole, and gum outsole, which provides a balance of cushioning and responsiveness.

This New Balance 327 Sea Salt Black Gum W was released on 7th September 2022. This women’s shoe retailed at $95.

name: Sea Teal
title: adidas Yeezy QNTM Sea Teal
description:
The adidas Yeezy QNTM Sea Teal was released in part of a continued collaboration between adidas and rapper/fashion designer Kanye West through his Yeezy brand. It is part of the Quantum line, which features basketball inspired sneakers.

The shoe’s upper is constructed with a PrimeKnit material and features a teal color scheme with very subtle accents of black. The tongue has a contrasting black, which extends to the ankle and heel area creating a half-and-half design on the shoe. Similar to other models in the QNTM line, the Sea Teal iteration incorporates adidas' Boost cushioning technology in the midsole, providing responsive and comfortable cushioning. Interestingly, the shoe doesn’t have any branding elements.

What we love about the adidas Yeezy QNTM Sea Teal is its bold design with the completely blacked out rear half that sharply contrasts the sea teal forefoot. The sneaker was released for retail on March 19, 2021 priced at $250.

name: Linen
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Linen
description:
Yeezy adds another colorway of its most popular design with the adidas Yeezy 350 V2 Linen, now available on StockX. This 350 V2 stays true to Yeezy’s signature palette, sporting earth tones that provide a natural feeling.

This Yeezy 350 V2 is composed of a Linen Primeknit upper with a tonal side stripe. A Linen Boost cushioned midsole sole and gum outsole completes the design. These sneakers released in Spring of 2020 and retailed for $220.

name: Light Grey
title: New Balance 2002R Light Grey
description:
The New Balance 2002R Light Grey is a modern twist on 2000s running designs produced by the Boston footwear brand. The colorway of this shoe is light grey/​silver.
​
The New Balance 2002R Light Grey features a mesh base. On top of that, it is crafted from premium suede and nubuck. It also has a grey material on the rubber outsole that makes it look intentionally worn and faded. The sneaker’s tongue features New Balance branding, and a light grey "N" logo can be seen on the quarter panel. The lowest part of the outsole comes in black.
​
This shoe retailed at $140 at the time of its release on September 3rd, 2020.

name: Mantle Green Cream
title: Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 Mantle Green Cream
description:
The Mantle Green Cream Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 combines vintage-inspired design with refined colors all around. This timeless silhouette, rooted in 1960s sportswear, continues to captivate by effortlessly blending a traditional shoe with a more modern appeal.

The Mantle Green Cream Mexico 66 by Onitsuka Tiger & ASICS has a smooth leather upper accented by suede overlays in a mantle green shade, contrasted by cream stripes on the sides. The heel tab includes a stitched Tiger emblem, while perforations are there for subtle detailing. A padded collar and cushioned insole enhance comfort. Initially introduced in 1966 as a training shoe, the Mexico 66 remains a staple of Onitsuka Tiger's heritage collection.

What our experts love about the Onitsuka Tiger Mexico 66 Mantle Green Cream is its suede overlays that add strength and texture, as well as the stitched emblems on the tongue and the heel to show off the brands. Released on 10th September 2023, it retailed at $120.

name: Aime Leon Dore White Grey
title: New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore White Grey
description:
Aimè Leon Dore teamed up with New Balance to bring back the New Balance 550, a low-top basketball silhouette originally introduced in 1989 as the New Balance P550.

The New Balance 550 Aimè Leon Dore features a white leather upper with grey cracked New Balance logos and mesh collars. A thick, woven New Balance Basketball tongue tag with ALD branding adds a custom touch. At the base, a yellowed sole provides a vintage feel.

The New Balance 550 Aimè Leon Dore released in October of 2020 and retailed for $130.

name: MiUSA Sulphur Green
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Sulphur Green
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Sulphur Green benefits from design input from Teddy Santis, often a collaborator in the Made in the USA (MiUSA) New Balance line. This colorway featuring gold, green, and soft brown provides a perfect transition from summer to fall footwear.

The upper of the comfortable lifestyle MiUSA Pale Yellow New Balance 990v6 sneaker begins with a base of golden mesh overlaid with cream-colored and cocoa-brown leather, along with darker golden suede at the mud guard and eyestays. Butter-yellow laces offer a soft touch and a snug closure. The white-and-gray ENCAP midsole offers elite cushioning and rides on a rubber outsole patterned for traction.

What we enjoy most about this sneaker are the hits of forest green on the side panel N, the tongue tag, the eyestay accents, and the outsole, providing a hint of the forest. The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Sulphur Green was released on September 7, 2023, for a retail price of $220.

name: Taupe Blue
title: adidas Yeezy Desert Boot Taupe Blue
description:
After nearly a year and a half hiatus, Yeezy brought back the Desert Boot silhouette in 2021 with the adidas Yeezy Desert Boot Taupe Blue. The Taupe Blue separates itself from previous Yeezy Desert Boots by presenting a design with strong contrast in its elements.

While previous Desert Boot releases have primarily featured colorways of subtle earth tones, the Taupe Blue taps into a more saturated palette. It features a tonal-brown upper that is composed of a mix of suede, nubuck, and mesh. From there, a solid Taupe Blue mudguard and sole seamlessly grip the upper to provide a sturdy base for traction and support. Olive rope laces add the finishing touches to this utilitarian design.

The adidas Yeezy Desert Boot Taupe Blue released in March of 2021 and retailed for $200.

name: Protection Pack Lunar New Year Dusty Lilac
title: New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Lunar New Year Dusty Lilac
description:
The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Dusty Lilac features a subtle pinkish-purple color inspired by the Lunar New Year.

The upper section of this 2002R Protection sneaker is a mauve mesh with leather overlays in dark purple and light gray and jagged suede overlays in dusty lilac. The laces are white, the insole is red, and the New Balance branding on the side panel is a dusty lilac outlined in purple and white. The midsole and heel cushioning are made of ABZORB and the outsole is constructed with N-ergy and Stability Web.

The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Dusty Lilac was released on December 30th, 2022 for a retail price of $170.

name: Flash Orange
title: adidas Yeezy QNTM Flash Orange
description:
The adidas Yeezy QNTM Flash Orange arrives in an arrangement of Flash Orange, black, and tan hues. Primeknit, nubuck, and mesh make up the upper. A full-length Boost midsole and translucent outsole wrap up the design.

The adidas Yeezy QNTM Flash Orange released in May of 2021 and retailed for $250.

name: A$AP Rocky Distressed Pack Black Pop Red
title: Puma Inhale OG A$AP Rocky Distressed Pack Black Pop Red
description:
The Puma Inhale OG A$AP Rocky Distressed Pack Black Pop Red is an aggressive-looking shoe that adds extra bite to the pouncing cougar brand. Its extreme motorsport styling and dramatic colorway immediately catch the eye.

These OG Puma and ASAP Rocky trainers are made from premium materials with a distressed design to emulate the effect of working in a racing pit crew. The suede upper combines contrasting waves of black and red with a highly stylized Puma logo in gray-white with a mild reflective effect. A mesh lining provides all-round breathability.

Our reviewers couldn't wait to get their hands on this shoe. The design is unique, and the distressed look provides the right touch for the motor-racing theme. The premium materials should give them excellent durability. This could be one of our favorite releases from the brand in a long while. The Puma Inhale OG A$AP Rocky Distressed Pack Black Pop Red was released on September 26, 2024, at a price of $130.

name: Cream Oatmeal
title: ASICS Gel-NYC Cream Oatmeal
description:
The ASICS Gel-NYC Cream Oatmeal is a performance athletic shoe that takes design inspiration from the early 2000s with some technology updates.

This version of the ASICS Gel-NYC is made with a Cream-colored off-white mesh upper for breathability. Suede uppers in a darker shade of the color cross the upper, forming the mudguard and toe cap as well as the typical ASICS logo on each side. The ASICS brand name appears in red on the lateral heel, while the heel contains GEL branding in red. Another red ASICS logo can be found on the tongue. A yellow and off-white midsole and outsole infused with gel technology round out the design.

Our favorite element of this shoe is the muted colorway, which allows the red and yellow accents to stand out. The ASICS Gel-NYC Cream Oatmeal was released on August 11, 2023, for a retail price of $150.

name: Black Pink Moon
title: New Balance 1906R Black Pink Moon
description:
The New Balance 1906R Black Pink Moon is an everyday sneaker for light activity and daily wear that is available in a black, Pink Moon, and Magnet color combination.

This low-top silhouette Black Pink Moon New Balance 1906R is a versatile sneaker that boasts a retro inspired design with plenty of sneaker tech. Dressed in a sleek black tone with Pink Moon branding accents and Magnet-colored lines throughout, it sports an upper made of mesh and synthetic materials. Notice the perforated toebox and mudguard areas for breathability. Then there is the ABZORB midsole and ABZORB SBS heel cushioning, there to provide both stability and comfort. A reinforced heel cage and N-ergy outsole round out this shoe.

We are just loving how the signature tilted "N" of the New Balance brand is worked into the design of the eyestay and doubles as eyelets. The New Balance 1906R Black Pink Moon debuted on October 17, 2023, with a recommended price of $155.

name: Inertia
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Inertia
description: Add heavy pressure on your favorite sneakerhead and cop the adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Inertia. This Yeezy Boost 700 comes with a grey upper, grey midsole with orange accents, and a white sole. These sneakers released in March 2019 and retailed for $300. Grab a pair of these fire sneakers on StockX ASAP.

name: Season 2 Brown
title: New Balance 990v2 MiUSA Season 2 Brown
description:
The New Balance 990v2 MiUSA Season 2 Brown is a performance shoe released as part of the brand’s Made In USA line.

This iteration of the New Balance 990v2 MiUSA features a base of light-brown mesh for breathability. A brown nubuck overlay forms the toe cap, while dark-brown overlays support the sides of the shoe. An even darker-brown color snakes from the toe cap to the eyestays on the forefoot. The New Balance N appears on each side in black, outlined in white, while a hairy brown support forms the heel. The cream tongue features brown embroidered 990 New Balance Made in USA branding, while the heel bears USA branding. The shoe sits on a cream rubber outsole with visible supports under the heel.

What we like best about this shoe is the multi-tonal brown color scheme, which adds neutrality and elegance. The New Balance 990v2 MiUSA Season 2 Brown was released on April 27, 2023, for $195.

name: White Green Cream
title: New Balance 1906R White Green Cream
description:
The New Balance 1906R White Green Cream base is made of breathable mesh with a white upper and leather paneling on top. 

While the rest of the shoe is accentuated in light grey, the midsole is cream, and the outsole is gum for a classic look. The green woven laces are interlaced with the distinctive "N" emblem on its lateral side, and a light grey TPU cage surrounds the heel. The cream N-ERGY unit beneath the foot is adorned with further green embellishments, and this is lined with a good amount of gum rubber, which offers incredible amounts of traction with each stride.

The New Balance 1906R White Green Cream was released on the market on 30th September 2022 and retailed at the price of $155.

name: Kith Grey
title: New Balance 991 Kith Grey
description:
The New Balance 991 Kith Grey comes in a grey-and-white color scheme.

The New Balance 991 Kith Grey features a grey upper that is made of suede and mesh. The shoe's ENCAP midsole cushioning technology and the mesh upper panels both offer comfort. The shoe has a rubber outsole for grip and traction. The shoe has an "N" logo in a contrasting grey and white colorway on either side. The sneaker also has a " new balance 991 N" on the tongue and "991" on the heel.

The New Balance 991 Kith Grey was made available on August 21, 2018, and retailed for $210.

name: Salt
title: adidas Yeezy 500 Salt
description: Don’t be salty, get out of your feelings, and cop a pair of the adidas Yeezy 500 Salt. With the potential of being the best Yeezy 500 colorway, these come with a salt upper, a salt midsole, and a salt sole.

name: Black White Silver
title: New Balance 860v2 Black White Silver
description:
The New Balance 860v2 Black White Silver is an athletic performance shoe whose design was inspired by the style of the 1990s.
 
This version of the New Balance 860v2 is made with a white mesh upper for breathability. Silver overlays dotted with black form the toe cap and run up to the laces. Silver overlays also form the eyelets and run down across each side of the shoe, revealing a black panel on each side where the New Balance "N" appears in silver and black. The heel is also supported by silver overlays with 860 branding on the lateral side and red NB branding on the heel. The tongue features the New Balance brand name, while the shoe sits on a white N-ergy midsole for energy return. The black and gray outsole complete the look. 

What stands out about this shoe are the metallic silver overlays, which give a pop of visual interest to the otherwise black and white shoe. The New Balance 860v2 Black White Silver was released on May 9, 2023, for $140.

name: Black Dark Grey White
title: New Balance 2002R Black Dark Grey White
description: The New Balance 2002R Black Dark Grey White is a sleek and stylish sneaker that combines comfort and performance. The upper is made of premium suede and mesh materials, providing breathability and durability. The black, dark grey, and white colorway gives the shoe a classic and versatile look that can be worn with any outfit. The shoe features ABZORB cushioning technology in the midsole, providing superior shock absorption and comfort. The outsole is made of durable rubber, providing excellent traction and durability. The New Balance 2002R Black Dark Grey White was released on February 20, 2022, and retails for $150. This sneaker is perfect for anyone looking for a comfortable and stylish shoe that can be worn for any occasion.

name: MiUSA Magenta Pop
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Magenta Pop
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Magenta Pop is a premium running and lifestyle sneaker that features suede details across the mesh upper.

While the flexible mesh construction comes in Limestone, a selection of suede overlays and panels create a design across the upper. While some of the thin suede overlays come in Magenta, the layered mudguard that wraps around the sneaker boasts a light-tan hue. In addition, splashes of dark purple add pops of color on the signature N logo, the branding on the tongue tab, the midsole, and the overlays near the collar. Padding around the collar and in the tongue helps protect against impact and contributes to the sneaker’s technical silhouette.

Our experts at StockX like the wavy traction pattern on the outsole, which comes in white and black. The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Magenta Pop was originally released on June 16, 2023, and retailed at $220.

name: Navy White
title: New Balance 480 Navy White
description:
The New Balance 480 Navy White is a shoe made with a mix of materials with a classic skateboarding design.

This version of the New Balance 480 features an upper made mostly of white leather. The white leather toe box is perforated for breathability, and white leather also forms the heel collar. Navy suede overlays form the toe cap, cross the midsole, and form the heel counter, creating a paneled look. The New Balance N appears on each midsole in beige outlined in white, while the New Balance brand name also appears on the heel collar. The tongue also sports an NB 480 logo patch. The shoe sits on top of an off-white and navy rubber outsole.

Our favorite thing about this sneaker is the way the overlays form different panels, creating an iconic skateboarding look. The New Balance 480 Navy White was released on August 21, 2023, for a retail price of $100.

name: Lundmark (Non Reflective)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Lundmark (Non Reflective)
description:
Like newer 350 V2 models, the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Lundmark sports a subtle summer color with the back heel tab removed. Replacing the SPLY-350 boost stripe that was traditionally found on the original 350s is a transparent stripe that reveals a more cream colored inner. A Boost midsole is covered by a light tan rubber outsole that features a pink middle stripe. Adding to the exclusivity of these is the fact this colorway is a North and Latin America exclusive.

The Lundmark Yeezy Boost 350 V2 released on July 11, 2019 at a retail price of $220.

name: Mushroom Brown
title: New Balance 9060 Mushroom Brown
description:
Chunky, durable, and made for long wear, these New Balance 9060 Mushroom Brown sneakers bring new meaning to hardworking shoes. 

New Balance brings a rough-and-ready aesthetic with these mushroom brown 9060s shoes, combining hardworking textiles such as suede and mesh, a cushioned, two-tone midsole, and a rubberized outsole. Perfect for hiking, long walking trips, and strenuous sports, they are breathable and offer a supportive middle to keep foot fatigue at bay. In two shades of brown, including mushroom brown, they present as earthy and ready to rumble. The iconic N logo of New Balance sits in its traditional spot outside the medial of the shoe. With a lace enclosure, the 9060 logo sits on the tongue of the shoe.

We love the rugged appearance of these NB sneakers. An excellent shoe for exploring the outdoor world, the New Balance 9060 Mushroom Brown was released on 6 October 2023, priced at $150.

name: Timberwolf Nightwatch Green
title: New Balance 327 Timberwolf Nightwatch Green
description:
The New Balance 327 Timberwolf Nightwatch Green comes in a green color scheme.

The New Balance 327 Timberwolf Nightwatch Green has an upper made up of a mix of mesh, suede, and leather. The top is completed in a pale grey hue. A durable EVA foam is featured in the midsole for strength and durability. The outsole has a textured traction pattern for grip and stability. An oversized "N" logo is shown on one side of the shoe, while a "NB" logo is displayed on the tongue.

The New Balance 327 Timberwolf Nightwatch Green was made available on July 18th, 2021, and retailed for $120.

name: MiUSA Black Grey White (Women's)
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Black Grey White (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Black Grey White (Women's) redefines footwear with a bold mix of design and heritage. As part of New Balance's "Made in USA" line, this sneaker combines premium materials with detailed design so it's more versatile.

The MiUSA Black Grey White 990v6 for women by New Balance comes with a breathable mesh upper layered with pigskin-suede overlays in shades of black, gray, and white. A padded collar and reflective detailing improve the look and feel. The ENCAP midsole, paired with FuelCell cushioning, gives you responsive support. This model is part of the celebrated 990 series, first introduced in 1982 to redefine athletic footwear. There is the 990 number displayed on the sides of the shoe in white.

Something we love about the New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Black Grey White (Women's) is its US-made design, reflecting the high standards that were followed while making the shoe. The chunky style and cross lacing is another highlight. When it was released on April 7, 2024, it retailed for $200.

name: Faded Azure
title: adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Faded Azure
description:
The adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Faded Azure is known for its two-toned and sock-like design.

The Yeezy Knit RNR Fade Azure is the third colorway launched by the brand, offering a slip-on, one-piece upper, creating the sock-like look. It also features a solid blue collar, an ombre blend of green gradient on the lower part of the upper, and a light sage green rubber outsole. The sneaker has an EVA midsole for lightweight cushioning, while the PU toe reinforcement is related to durability and structure.

The adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Faded Azure was first released in August 2022 at a retail price of $210.

name: Burgundy Cyan
title: New Balance 550 Burgundy Cyan
description:
The New Balance 550 Burgundy Cyan features a smooth white leather upper with perforated overlays and burgundy canvas collars. From there, bold New Balance logos with cyan trim and a mesh tongue complete the design.

The New Balance 550 Burgundy Cyan released in January of 2021 and retailed for $120.

name: White Jade (Women's)
title: ASICS Gel-1130 White Jade (Women's)
description:
Stepping into the spotlight, the ASICS Gel-1130 shines in its latest White/Jade colorway, seamlessly blending heritage and hype.

This model beautifully showcases an ensemble of top-notch materials, with the immaculate White base setting the stage. Adding zest, the Jade accents pop, making this silhouette a standout in any sneaker collection. Beyond the fresh aesthetics, the Gel-1130 remains true to ASICS' commitment to exceptional comfort and fit. The integrated cushioning system is designed to keep you moving in style without skipping a beat on comfort.

Make a statement with every step. The ASICS Gel-1130 in White/Jade dropped on March 15, 2023, at a retail price of $95. Grab yours and wear this iconic ASICS legend.

name: Grey Fog
title: New Balance 574 Grey Fog
description:
The New Balance 574 Gray Fog adds a subtle colorway of gray and Gray Fog to the New Balance 574's lifestyle silhouette.

This unassuming shoe showcases New Balance’s dedication to creating shoes that can be worn in everyday life. Although the upper is made of mesh and soft suede, premium materials and cutting-edge technology don’t define this sneaker. Like other versions of the 547, the "Gray Fog" iteration features a two-tone EVA foam midsole and ENCAP cushioning. The gray rubber outsole displays light tread and is made from five percent recycled materials. While gray suede and mesh dominate the upper, Gray Fog can be found on the New Balance ‘N’, the laces, the liner, and peeking out from behind the overlays.

Our experts at StockX like the traditional New Balance branding, including the large logo tag on the tongue that reads ‘NB new balance 574’ in black lettering. The New Balance 574 Gray Fog was released on July 13th, 2023, and retailed at $90.

name: White Black Rain Cloud
title: New Balance 550 White Black Rain Cloud
description:
In New Balance, you can find sneakers for everyone like the New Balance 550 White Black Rain Cloud (GS). These shoes come in a two-tone leather upper.
​
​The sneaker is a new version of its predecessor. The midsole of the shoe features the New Balance logo and the name of the brand, while the overlays on the sneaker are in a grey and black color scheme. A white "N" logo with a black outline embellishes the medial sides of the shoes. A mesh collar, a stitched New Balance tag, and a nylon tongue made of permeable material help with a comfortable fit. A medial side EVA wedge is seen on this model low-top.
​
​The New Balance 550 White Black Rain Cloud (GS) was released on 19th January 2023 and retailed at $80.

name: Azure
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Azure
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Azure was a collaboration between the Yeezy collection, designed with rapper Kanye West, and adidas.

The Yeezy Boost 380 features a PrimeKnit upper in various shades of blue with a stripe pattern that blends into the midsole. The midsole is made using Boost technology. The laces of the Yeezy Boost 380 are designed with each lace thread running through multiple eyelets, and the outsole is made of durable rubber to provide traction on a wide range of surfaces.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Azure was released on December 12, 2020, at a retail price of $230.

name: Castlerock
title: New Balance XC-72 Castlerock
description:
The New Balance XC 72 Castlerock is a running shoe with a gray and black color scheme.

A product of innovation, this sneaker features a nylon upper with chrome-free suede overlays, a stability heel clip with a herringbone outsole pattern, and a single-layer microfiber tongue. It also boasts a vertically split outsole with three distinctive traction patterns – two hard ground traction designs and a studded pattern. Branding-wise, this sneaker features oversized slanted "N" logos on its sidewalls, NB banding on its exposed tongue, and an XC 72 print on its insole.

The New Balance XC 72 Castlerock made its debut on 12th September 2021. At the time, it retailed at $120.

name: White Pink (Women's)
title: New Balance 550 White Pink (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 550 White Pink (Women's) has a white midsole with pink highlights at the back and front, plus New Balance branding on the outer side of the midsole.

This shoe is made with a leather suede and mesh construction, featuring a white and pink colorway exclusively for women. It is a low-top sneaker with lace-up closure style and white laces. The majority of the shoe’s upper is white, but has pink details around the toes, heels, and on the big "NB" New Balance logo that appears on both sides.

The New Balance 550 White Pink (Women's) shoe was released in March of 2022 at the retail price of $110.

name: White Black Rain Cloud (GS)
title: New Balance 550 White Black Rain Cloud (GS)
description:
In New Balance, you can find sneakers for everyone like the New Balance 550 White Black Rain Cloud (GS). These shoes come in a two-tone leather upper.

The sneaker is a new version of its predecessor. The midsole of the shoe features some deterioration, while the overlays on the sneaker are in a grey and black color scheme. A white "N" logo with a black outline embellishes the medial sides of the shoes. A mesh collar, a stitched New Balance tag, and a nylon tongue made of permeable material help with a comfortable fit. A medial side EVA wedge is seen on this model low-top.

The New Balance 550 White Black Rain Cloud (GS) was released on 19th January 2023 and retailed at $80.

name: Barium
title: adidas Yeezy QNTM Barium
description: Yeezy added a new colorway to their growing QNTM line with the adidas Yeezy QNTM Barium, now available on StockX. The QNTM Barium is composed of a dark grey Primeknit upper with suede overlays and reflective detailing. A translucent sole, extended ankle collar, and reinforced heel cap complete the design. These YZY QNTMs released in June of 2020 and retailed for $250 USD.

name: MiUSA Grey
title: New Balance 990v2 MiUSA Grey
description:
The New Balance 990v2 MiUSA Grey features the brand materials and incorporates them into its design with Made in USA construction.

The sneaker’s upper is dressed in suede grey including its overlays, eye stays, and quarters. The 'N' logo in silver is featured on the quarter panel of this vintage runner, which has a breathable grey mesh upper with matching suede overlays. '990 New Balance Made in USA' is embroidered in grey letters above the tongue. For a comfortable ride, it is crafted with an ABZORB-cushioned ENCAP white midsole.

The New Balance 990v2 MiUSA Grey was released on 11th August 2021 and retailed at $185.

name: Black Silver
title: New Balance 860v2 Black Silver
description:
Designed by Teddy Santis, the New Balance 860v2 Black Silver dresses the recognizable 860v2 silhouette in a stealthy colorway of black and shiny silver.

At the Black Silver New Balance 860v2, the upper combines breathable Airmesh and an unexpected material—patent leather. Both come in black, providing continuity across the upper and allowing the silver accents to stand out. The durable rope laces mirror the upper, with a black base and silver stripes. The sneaker displays classic New Balance branding, including the signature ‘N’ with black and silver strips on the side panels and ‘NEW BALANCE’ printed on the mesh tongue. In addition, ‘860v2’ appears on the lateral side panel and ‘NB’ in red lettering decorates the heel. Active Lite foam arrives underfoot, complements the Abzorb and N-ergy cushioning systems.

Our experts at StockX like the choice of matte black on the midsole because it is a deviation from New Balance's off-white and cream sole units. The New Balance 860v2 Black Silver was released on November 8, 2019, and sold for $140.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Olive Incense
title: New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Teddy Santis Olive Incense
description:
The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Teddy Santis Olive Incense allows Teddy Santis, the creative director of Aimé Leon Dore, to reinterpret the New Balance 990v4’s performance running silhouette.

The MiUSA Teddy Santis Olive Incense New Balance 990v4 boasts a fine mesh upper in Olive with layers of pigskin suede overlays in Olive and Incense. Stitched on top of the overlays, the New Balance ‘N’ stands out with an unexpected pop of off-white. Harking back to the first 990 designs from the 1980s and 1990s, this version of the 990v4 refines modernizations to the silhouette seen in the previous models. Using lightweight foam, the ENCAP midsole gives the sneaker a less chunky appearance and adds responsive cushioning.

Our experts at StockX like the addition of off-white tones in the midsole. These hues complement the warmth found in the Olive and Incense accents. The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Teddy Santis Olive Incense was released on October 26, 2023, and sold for $210.

name: MiUSA JJJJound Brown Black
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA JJJJound Brown Black
description:
The New Balance 990v3 JJJJound Brown utilizes a tonal earthy palette to emphasize its premium mesh and nubuck construction. Hits of black on the New Balance logo and overlays complement the brown base, while subtle JJJJound logo applications on the insole and heel add a custom feel. Finally, a triple black ENCAP sole adds the finishing touch.

The New Balance 990v3 JJJJound Brown released in May of 2022 and retailed for $250

name: Aime Leon Dore Grey Suede
title: New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Grey Suede
description:
The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Grey Suede takes on a 1980s retro hoops design and neutral colorway.

The shoe is covered in low-top grey suede and has a padded textile collar and a smooth leather lining on the toe box. The contrasting blue embellishments on the braided tongue tag break up the polished one-note finish. A cracked leather "N" logo and misaligned ALD and NB logos on the rear heel are additional branding cues. The sneaker has an exposed EVA wedge on the medial side and is supported by a cream-colored rubber cup sole.

The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Grey Suede debuted on November 2nd, 2022, and retailed at $180.

name: Bone (Kids)
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Bone (Kids)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Slide Bone (K) is dressed in an all-bone hue. The slip-on shoe is made of injected EVA foam and has a neutral ivory finish.

The open-toe, breezy design of the slide and the soft top layer of the footbed are the distinguishing characteristics of this Bone Yeezy Slide for kids. Only the adidas 3-Stripes logo, which is imprinted at the heel of the footbed, is used as exterior branding on these bone-colored shoes. The outsole of the slip-on design has strategically placed grooves and good traction. The shoe also has a top soft layer in its footbed.

The adidas Yeezy Slide Bone (K) was launched on December 6, 2019, with a suggested market price of $45.

name: Triple White
title: New Balance CT302 Triple White
description:
The New Balance CT302 Triple White takes a heritage court silhouette and styles it with a chunky sole unit to create a trendy, eye-catching, comfortable lifestyle shoe.

The Triple White colorway of the New Balance CT302 features an upper that begins with a base of smooth white leather. There are smooth white leather overlays at the heel, the side panel N, and white suede overlays at the eyestays and vamp. The collar is padded, and the white tongue has exposed foam. White-on-white New Balance branding hits the tongue tag, and CT branding appears on the white outsole. The laces and sockliner are also white, locking in the snowy look of this upper. 

What we appreciate most about this monochromatic shoe is how the upper becomes a part of the sole unit. The white rubber toecap blends seamlessly into the sidewall, covering the thick midsole that sports embossed New Balance branding. The rubber outsole features concentric circles and wavy lines to provide impact absorption and traction, and features debossed New Balance branding as well. The New Balance CT302 Triple White was released on March 15, 2022, for a $100 retail price.

name: Truffle Rich Earth Magnet
title: New Balance 9060 Truffle Rich Earth Magnet
description:
The New Balance 9060 Truffle Rich Earth Magnet is embellished with earth and truffle color schemes. The sneaker is crafted of a mixture of materials as a result of the inspiration from futuristic elements.

The 9060 model comes in pigskin suede overlays with a warm truffle hue, mesh upper, TPU eyelets, flat cotton laces, NB 9060 logo on its tongue, and a padded collar for comfort. The trainer also features ABZORB, SBS cushioning technologies in the sole, and ENCAP, which provide dynamic and lightweight cushioning. Capping off the appearance of the sneaker is an embroidered NB logo on the rear and stitched N branding on its front. 

The New Balance 9060 Truffle Rich Earth Magnet was released on 6th, December 2022, and retailed at $150.

name: Bone (2022) (Kids)
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Bone (2022) (Kids)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Slide Bone 2022 Kids with an FZ5903 style code is back in 2022 with a neutral ivory finish on a slip-on constructed of injected EVA foam.

The slide's open-toe, airy construction and the footbed's soft top layer are its standout features. The shoes feature a resin colorway with only the adidas three-stripe emblem embossed at the heel of the footbed, serving as exterior branding. The slip-on style rests atop an outsole with excellent traction and well-placed grooves. It is lightweight with a top soft layer in its footbed.

The adidas Yeezy Slide Bone 2022 Kids was released on September 24. It originally retailed at a price of $45.

name: Aime Leon Dore Masaryk Community Gym Green
title: New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Masaryk Community Gym Green
description:
The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Masaryk Community Gym Green is part of a collaboration between New Balance and Aime Leon Dore, a New York-based lifestyle brand known for its preppy, vintage streetwear.

This chunky sneaker draws inspiration from Masaryk Community Gym, in New York, and incorporates elements of retro gym style. For example, the sneaker boasts a slightly yellow leather base, which is reminiscent of aged, white leather. Tiny perforations across the side panels and vamp, as well as the Classic Pine details, also contribute to the sneaker’s vintage appeal. The padded, mesh collar displays a logo tag that celebrates both New Balance and Aime Leon Dore.

Our StockX experts like the use of mesh to fill in the New Balance ‘N’ cutout on the side panel. The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Masaryk Community Gym Green was released on October 25th, 2023, and retailed at $130.

name: MiUSA Joe Freshgoods Outside Clothes
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods Outside Clothes
description:
The New Balance 990v3 Joe Freshgoods Outside Clothes features a light blue mesh upper with tonal brown suede overlays and a blue New Balance logo. From there, green hardware, "JFG" text on the heel, and a multicolor ENCAP sole completes the design.

The New Balance 990v3 Joe Freshgoods Outside Clothes released in August of 2021 and retailed for $220.

name: Heaven by Marc Jacobs Kiko Kostadinov Graphite Grey (Women's)
title: ASICS Gel-Lokros Heaven by Marc Jacobs Kiko Kostadinov Graphite Grey (Women's)
description:
The ASICS Gel-Lokros Heaven by Marc Jacobs Kiko Kostadinov Graphite Grey (Women's) is a slip-on shoe for women designed as a collaboration between the brands.

This version of the ASICS Gel-Lokros is made with a black textile upper featuring a star pattern formed by a white thread. This material forms the forefoot and part of the heel. Leather accents adorn the lateral side in the form of silver and gray overlays that work together with the adjustment straps to form the ASICS design. Black leather also appears underneath. The shoe features buckle fastening with elastic straps over the forefoot in silver, gray, and tan. The heel features an ASICS logo, and a chunky black textured rubber outsole completes the appearance.

What we like most about this shoe are the multiple elastic straps that appear over the forefoot. The ASICS Gel-Lokros Heaven by Marc Jacobs Kiko Kostadinov Graphite Grey (Women's) was released on March 7, 2024, for $195.

name: Light Arctic Grey
title: New Balance T500 Light Arctic Grey
description:
The New Balance T500 Light Arctic Grey is a sleek trainer with the classic low-profile. This is a high-quality tennis shoe, made from pigskin suede combined with durable nubuck. Its simple elegance has made it a staple among players.

The New Balance T500 model has remained popular since 1982, thanks to its reliability and understated good looks. It has a light grey and white colorway, accented with a reflective silver heel collar strip. The perforated toes provide excellent breathability while you're playing, and the polyurethane midsole provides flexible comfort.

Putting these trainers through their paces on the court, we were impressed by the robust support they provide. Their high traction soles with a pivot circle give the confidence to make sharp turns, and perform well on all surfaces. This is a versatile tennis shoe for all types of players, with the elite credentials to perform at the highest levels. The New Balance T500 Light Arctic Grey was launched 14 March 14, 2024, retailing at $110.

name: Vintage Indigo Arctic Grey
title: New Balance 327 Vintage Indigo Arctic Grey
description:
The New Balance 327 Vintage Indigo Arctic Gray is modeled after running shoes from the 1970s and features an upper crafted from premium materials.

With a foam midsole and suede overlays inspired by classic sneakers in the New Balance catalog, this version of the 327 also boasts contemporary upgrades. For example, the silhouette has a more angular design and a rubber outsole with lugs inspired by trail running sneakers wraps up and over the heel. The running shoe also features an oversized ‘N’ on the lateral side panel. The base is crafted from lightweight mesh in a light beige, while the overlays come in Vintage Indigo. Panels by the lace cage and the ‘N’ display a soft Arctic Gray that complements the Vintage Indigo.

Our StockX experts like the split eye row, which divides the panels of the lace cage into two parts. The New Balance 327 Vintage Indigo Arctic Gray was released on November 27th, 2022, and retailed at $100.

name: Protection Pack Pink
title: New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Pink
description:
The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Pink has a two-toned colorway.

The 2002R Protection Pack sneaker in pink by New Balance has an embellishment of candy-bright colors with an unfinished aesthetic. The lavender and pink revamped upper has ragged-edged suede overlays on the heel, forefoot, and quarter panel. The shoe has touches of aged yellow on the heel matching the inner side of the tongue, while a thin film white theme dresses the outsoles. The shock-absorbing energy technology used in the shoe heel, predistressed midsole, and ABZORB cushioning complete the design.

The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Pink was first released in September 2022 at a suggested retail price of $150.

name: Adrift Moonbeam
title: New Balance 2002R Adrift Moonbeam
description:
The New Balance 2002R Adrift Moonbeam arrived in shades of brown pig suede. It is crafted from a mix of materials like mesh, suede, and leather.

A suede mesh design predominates beneath grey leather eyelets and overlays while the remaining parts utilize a warm brown tint across its suede panels of the quarter overlay, midfoot, mudguard, and perforated heel counter. The inner lining, upper tab, and tongue are all color-coordinated to complete the castle rock look, and the laces and off-white "N" emblems on the trim support the traditional ivory color. The midsole bearing the N-ERGY trademark is covered in the latter neutral shade, with light grey accents and a coordinating brown tread.

The New Balance 2002R Adrift Moonbeam was released on the market on 15th October 2022 and retailed at $140.

name: Nightwatch Green
title: New Balance 1906R Nightwatch Green
description:
Using a sneaker silhouette named for the year that the New Balance sneaker company was founded, the New Balance 1906R Nightwatch Green offers a running shoe inspired by the aesthetics of the early 2000s and dressed in a vibrant, verdant colorway.

This eye-catching running shoe sports a lightweight, breathable upper of tightly woven green mesh. Green suede overlays course across the upper, adding both style and overall foot support. A darker green synthetic heel counter adds locked-in foot stability. The N-lock integrated lacing system provides a snug closure and a secure feeling with every stride. For ultimate cushioning and springy energy return, the primarily cream-colored midsole is crafted from ACTEVA LITE foam with ABZORB SBS heel cushioning. The black N-ergy outsole provides shock absorption and grip and uses Stability Web technology for arch support.

The aspects of this running shoe we enjoy the most are the branding hits on the upper. 1906R branding in white hits the lateral collar, while N-lock branding is emblazoned on the iconic side panel N. The New Balance 1906R Nightwatch Green was released on February 18, 2023, for $155 retail.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Green Purple
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Green Purple
description:
The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Green Purple debuted in the winter season and features a black mesh base that is permeable. 

The sneaker is covered in bold purple accents that are added to the inner sock liner and "N" logo, while subdued green suede gracefully envelops the side panels, toebox, and heel. A hefty ENCAP midsole underfoot gives wearers an insane amount of comfort with each stride, while a waffle pattern adds depth to the tongue. Finally, "Made In USA" is proudly stamped on the reverse to complete the design. 

The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Green Purple was released on December 27th, 2022, and retailed for $200.

name: Grey Black JD Sports Exclusive
title: New Balance 2002R Grey Black JD Sports Exclusive
description:
The New Balance 2002R Grey Black JD Sports Exclusive comes in a grey and black color scheme.

The New Balance 2002R Grey Black JD Sports Exclusive has an upper constructed from leather and textile elements for long-lasting wear and breathability. The sneaker's midsole is composed of EVA foam, which is both lightweight and responsive, providing padding and comfort. The shoe's outsole features durable rubber used for grip and longevity. The shoe features an "N" logo on the lateral sides and "NB" on the heel. A "2002R" is displayed on one side of the shoe. The sneaker's design is completed by a "new balance running" lettering on the tongue.

The New Balance 2002R Grey Black JD Sports Exclusive was released on January 1, 2022, and retailed for $140.

name: Yecoraite Reflective
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Yecoraite Reflective
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Yecoraite Reflective is an iteration of the adidas Yeezy Boost 380 in a ‘Yecoraite Reflective’ colorway. 

This sneaker features a Primeknit upper dressed in a camo-like colorway with Off-White and Neutral Grey accents. Other details include an opening with a sock-like build, a Pale Orange, a post-dyed monofilament side stripe, decorative rope laces, and ‘adidas x YEEZY’ branding on the insole. The upper rests on a full-length BOOST midsole covered by a salmon-like semi-translucent rubber and an orange gum-hued rubber outsole with herringbone traction patterns. 

What our experts love about this adidas Yeezy Boost 380 is its design and comfort. A futuristic design with a camo-like upper dressed in orange, Natural Grey, and white hues give this sneaker a stylish look. The Primeknit upper, a full-length Boost midsole, and a unique lacing system guarantee comfort. The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Yecoraite Reflective was released on January 16, 2021 retailing at $250.

name: Slate
title: adidas Yeezy 500 High Slate
description:
Yeezy enlists a new variation of a popular design with the adidas Yeezy 500 Slate High, now available on StockX. This is the first high-top sneaker silhouette Yeezy has released since the 750. Similar to the 500 Stone release, Yeezy replaces mesh with neoprene to add a sleek look to this high-top model.

This Yeezy 500 High is composed of a Slate neoprene and suede with reflective piping. A matching Adiprene midsole and gum rubber outsole completes the design. These sneakers released in December of 2019 and retailed for $200.

name: Wave Runner (Infants)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Wave Runner (Infants)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Wave Runner (Infant) comes in a Solid Gray, Chalk White, and Core Black color palette.

The Wave Runner adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Grey for infants adopts a classic silhouette with an upper that is crafted with a mix of materials, including suede overlays, mesh panels, and synthetic leather elements, offering durability and breathability. The sneaker features adidas' Boost technology in the midsole, which provides responsive cushioning and impact reduction. The shoe's design is completed with a rubber outsole that provides stability and grip.

Our experts love the adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Wave Runner and its chunky and retro-inspired design. These sneakers feature a mix of gray, blue, and orange hues on the upper, creating a visually dynamic and stylish look. The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Wave Runner (Infant) was released on August 17, 2019, and sold for a retail price of $150.

name: Phantom Dark Grey Metallic Silver
title: New Balance 1906R Phantom Dark Grey Metallic Silver
description:
The New Balance 1906R Phantom Dark Grey Metallic Silver is a sleek and stylish addition to the renowned 1906R lineup. This men's sneaker showcases a sophisticated color palette, combining phantom black, dark grey, and metallic silver hues for a versatile and eye-catching design. The upper features a mix of premium materials, including breathable mesh and durable synthetic overlays, ensuring both comfort and durability for everyday wear.

Engineered for optimal performance, the 1906R boasts New Balance's innovative cushioning technology, providing exceptional support and responsiveness with every step. The shoe's streamlined silhouette is complemented by subtle branding elements, including the iconic 'N' logo on the side panels. With its perfect blend of style and functionality, this sneaker is ideal for both casual outings and light athletic activities.

Us at StockX believe this product is great for those seeking a modern, versatile sneaker that seamlessly transitions from day to night. The New Balance 1906R Phantom Dark Grey Metallic Silver offers unparalleled comfort, striking aesthetics, and the quality craftsmanship that New Balance is known for.

name: Metallic Silver Blue
title: New Balance 1906R Metallic Silver Blue
description:
The New Balance 1906R Metallic Silver Blue takes aesthetic inspiration from the running shoes of the early 2000s. This silhouette combines style and function to offer runners a smooth, comfortable ride with every step.

The Metallic Silver Blue iteration of the New Balance 1906R features an upper with a white mesh base that facilitates a lightweight stride and offers increased ventilation. Synthetic overlays in metallic silver and blue run across the shoe from the toebox to the collar, adding support and streamlined style. A black synthetic leather N on the side panel offers a hit of contrast to the off-white midsole composed of N-ergy and ABZORB that offers ultimate cushioning and impact resistance. The black and blue rubber outsole with Stability Web technology offers grip and allows for midsole expansion.

The aspect of this running shoe that we most appreciate is the glossy black synthetic heel counter. The lattice-work pattern adds to the aesthetic even as it provides lockdown heel support. The New Balance 1906R Metallic Silver Blue was released on June 6, 2023, for $150 retail.

name: Concrete Grey
title: New Balance 2002R Concrete Grey
description:
The New Balance 2002R Concrete Gray is a low-top sneaker from the Boston brand that boasts a Concrete Gray color scheme.

Dressed in gray tones, this shoe’s upper sports a myriad of materials from leather, suede, and mesh. The front part of the shoe has mesh in the toebox area for breathability, which leads into the plush suede and leather overlay and eyestay. The gray heel counter is perforated, and not something you see often. A Cork Brown color with colored flecks is seen on the heel, collar, and tongue. The signature tilted "N" adorns both side panels and is stitched on in white. A padded collar and white midsole round out this footwear.

Our experts think that the ABZORB midsole and ABZORB SBS heel cushioning that provide stability and comfort are what makes this stylish silhouette stand out. The New Balance 2002R Concrete Grey debuted on March 16, 2023, with a recommended price of $140.

name: Salt and Pepper
title: New Balance 550 Salt and Pepper
description:
The New Balance 550 Salt and Papper takes on a retro-inspired silhouette and is dressed in a white, beige, and dark gray colorway.

It features a mixed upper constructed with smooth leather, mesh, and perforations in various places. Black details are visible around the N logo and the quarter trim. Other highlights include a low-cut cream collar made of mesh, 550 branding on the side close to the toe box, and NB branding on the tongue, heel, and midsole. A white midsole that sits on a rubber outsole with varying shades of gray completes the design.

The New Balance 550 Salt and Papper was released on October 19th, 2022. Initially, it retailed at $110.

name: Chino Hills
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Chino Hills
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Chino Hills is a basketball sneaker designed in collaboration with American basketball star LaMelo Ball.

This iteration of the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 features a textile and synthetic leather upper. White synthetic leather covers most of the upper, with jagged openings that look like claw marks revealing Lime Smash mesh underneath. A wavy light gray mudguard stretches from the lateral midsole around the toe box. Lime Smash designs appear under the laces, while the tongue sports the number 92 and 1 to 1. The cushioned heel features more of LaMelo Ball’s branding, as well as a small Puma logo in Lime Smash. A chunky and wavy dark gray sole and outsole complete the look.

Our favorite thing about this shoe is the chunky outsole, which bears a unique design as it also has the words "Not From Here" imprinted into it on the toe. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Chino Hills was released on November 17, 2023, for a retail price of $125.

name: atmos Yakoutake
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 atmos Yakoutake
description: DISCLAIMER: Due to this shoe having glow in the dark components, colors may appear slightly different depending on the lighting that the shoes are photographed or viewed.

name: Grey
title: New Balance 327 Grey
description:
The New Balance 327 Grey features a grey and white suede and nylon upper with plain white acting as a color base for the thick midsole, lining, and trim at the collar of the New Balance 327. From there, a deep, smooth grey covers the base, wrapped in suede overlays, and a bright white New Balance logo complete the design.

The New Balance 327 Grey released in May of 2020 and retailed for $100.

name: MiUSA JJJJound Olive
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA JJJJound Olive
description:
JJJJound and New Balance teamed up again for their second 990v3 design with the New Balance 990v3 JJJJound Olive.

Arriving with olive mesh and premium suede uppers, the New Balance 990v3 JJJJound Olive uses a minimalist approach to create a shoe geared for everyday wear. Black New Balance logos and overlays bring sharp contrast to the tonal green background. A silver reflective heel wrap with JJJJound branding adds a custom touch. From there, a cream ENCAP sole at the base completes the design.

The New Balance 990v3 JJJJound Olive released in March of 2022 and retailed for $250.

name: White Midnight
title: ASICS Gel-1130 White Midnight
description:
Using an iconic silhouette launched in 2008, the ASICS Gel-1130 White Midnight takes its inspiration from the GEL-KAYANO 14 and designs the reimagined sneaker with a late 2000s runner aesthetic.

The White Midnight ASICS Gel-1130 starts with a lightweight, breathable upper crafted from white mesh. The synthetic leather overlays in midnight and silvery gray lock in the signature style while offering all-over foot support. The white foam midsole is enhanced by the TRUSSTIC support system at the midfoot for stability and gel cushioning technology in the heel for shock absorption. The outsole is composed of pods of rubber that provide multidirectional and multi-surface grip.

The standout aspect of this sneaker that we enjoy the most is the infusion of neon orange accents into the colorway. The outsole, heel, and tongue pop with hits of bright color. The ASICS Gel-1130 White Midnight was released on April 1, 2022, for a retail price of $80.

name: Mako Blue
title: ASICS ACTIBREEZE 3D Sandal Mako Blue
description:
The ASICS ACTIBREEZE 3D Sandal in Mako Blue offers a striking MAKO BLUE/MAKO BLUE colorway and a three-dimensional design, ensuring eye-catching aesthetics and ergonomic support for your feet.

The ACTIBREEZE 3D sandal boasts a parametrically designed construction, delivering zoned comfort and enhanced breathability. Crafted entirely through 3D printing, the sandal showcases an extra thick lattice structure that promotes relaxation for your body and feet, ensuring you're primed for optimal performance in style.

At StockX, we're captivated by the sandal's remarkable parametrically designed construction. This innovative approach provides zoned comfort and breathability, ensuring an unrivaled wearing experience. The standout feature, however, is the entirely 3D-printed extra-thick lattice structure. Our team adores how it optimally relaxes the body and feet, reflecting a cutting-edge design that seamlessly merges comfort with performance. The ASICS ACTIBREEZE 3D Sandal in Mako Blue was released on the 12th of April, 2023, and sold for $80.

name: Stone Pink
title: New Balance 530 Stone Pink
description:
The New Balance 530 Stone Pink draws inspiration from 2000s running shoe designs.

The predominant Stone Pink color on the upper is complemented by accents of Gray Matter and white in the New Balance 530. The shoe's base is constructed from mesh, while synthetic leather overlays embellish the eye stay panel, mid-panels, toe cap, and heel panel. A homage to one of New Balance's classic running styles, this shoe incorporates a lace-up closure for a secure fit. Featuring ABZORB midsole technology, it effectively absorbs impact through a combination of cushioning and compression resistance. The sporty Y2K style is rounded off with traction rubber outsoles, along with brand accents on the sidewalls and tongue.

The most noteworthy aspect of the New Balance 530 Stone Pink is its ABZORB midsole technology, ensuring exceptional underfoot comfort and making it a superb choice for both running and everyday wear. The sneaker debuted for $95 on March 30th, 2023.

name: Light Grey White
title: New Balance 9060 Light Grey White
description:
The New Balance 9060 Light Grey White is a sleek and stylish addition to the popular 9060 line. This men's sneaker features a harmonious blend of light grey and white hues, creating a versatile and timeless aesthetic. The upper is crafted with a combination of premium materials, including breathable mesh and soft suede overlays, ensuring both comfort and durability. The distinctive New Balance 'N' logo adorns the side panels, adding a touch of brand recognition to the design.

Built on New Balance's innovative cushioning technology, the 9060 model offers exceptional comfort for all-day wear. The chunky midsole not only provides superior shock absorption but also contributes to the shoe's trendy, retro-inspired silhouette. With its clean colorway and modern interpretation of classic running shoe elements, this New Balance 9060 seamlessly bridges the gap between athletic performance and casual street style.

Us at StockX believe this product is great for those seeking a comfortable, versatile sneaker that effortlessly combines retro charm with contemporary design.

name: White Pure Gold
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 White Pure Gold
description:
The ASICS Gel Kayano 14 White Pure Gold combines a clean white design with accents of pure gold, offering both comfort and support for runners. Drawing inspiration from its 2008 predecessor, the sneaker reimagines the past by mirroring the original midsole tooling, seamlessly integrating modern GEL technology cushioning.

The Kayano 14 White Pure Gold features a predominantly white upper with elegant accents of pure gold, creating a striking visual contrast. Crafted with high-quality materials, it offers durability and breathability. This innovative running shoe incorporates ASICS' advanced Gel cushioning technology for superior comfort and shock absorption, enhancing the overall running experience. It has a visibly prominent Gel cushioning unit in the heel, providing responsive support and a distinctive look.

Our team appreciates the captivating combination of pristine white and luxurious pure gold accents and the integration of ASICS' renowned Gel cushioning technology that ensures exceptional comfort and impact absorption. The ASICS Gel Kayano 14 White Pure Gold was released on the 12th of January, 2021, and retailed at $150.

name: Sandstone
title: New Balance 2002R Sandstone
description:
The New Balance 2002R Sandstone incorporates the iconic sneaker designs made famous in the 2000s with revamped technical features.

This running shoe comes with ABZORB SBS heel cushioning, an ABZORB midsole, a Stability Web outsole, and responsive N-ergy cushioning. These inclusions decrease impact while adding stability that does not weigh the shoe down. The sneaker features a neutral colorway of Sandstone and Incense that manifests as off-white and tan. The off-white mesh upper boasts soft suede overlays in an overlapping, dual design. In terms of branding, the shoe comes with the ‘N’ patch on the side panel, New Balance branding on the heel and tongue, as well as the 2002R logo below the collar.

One of the features our StockX experts love is the sandstone-colored outsole, which complements the suede overlays. The New Balance 2002R Sandstone was released on March 16, 2023, and retailed at $140

name: Workwear
title: New Balance 9060 Workwear
description:
The New Balance 9060 Workwear comes in a workwear, rich earth, and angora color palette.

The New Balance 9060 Workwear has a durable leather upper and a slip-resistant, traction-enhancing rubber outsole. In addition, the shoe features an ABZORB midsole cushioning system, which absorbs motion and provides padding and support. The sneaker has the trademark "N" branding on the lateral sides. The shoe's design is finished off with "NB 9060" branding on the tongue and an "NB" logo on the heel.

The New Balance 9060 Workwear was made available on September 9, 2022, and sold for a retail price of $150.

name: Moonbeam December Sky (Women's)
title: New Balance 327 Moonbeam December Sky (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 327 Moonbeam December Sky (Women's) offers a reimagined version of the 1970s running shoe, when recreational running became an established pastime. This runner is specifically sized for women.

This eye-catching running shoe builds upon a smooth textile upper of lightweight white mesh overlaid with pale gray suede that hits the heel, eye stays, and forefoot in a split eyebrow configuration. New Balance embroidered text hits the medial heel, while New Balance branding also hits the tongue. The white foam midsole offers cushioning with each stride, and the gum rubber outsole is lugged and grooved with circles. This outsole wraps up the heel in a style inspired by the 355 trail running shoe.

The aspect of this women’s sneaker that we enjoy the most is the side panel " N." Not only is it oversized, but it is made of tumbled leather, and it is pale pink, adding a subtle hit of contrast to this sneaker. The New Balance 327 Moonbeam December Sky (Women's) was released on August 13, 2023, for a retail price of $100.

name: (Lifestyle Model)
title: adidas Yeezy QNTM (Lifestyle Model)
description:
The adidas Yzy QNTM was made available as a part of a shock release collaboration between the American rapper and German brand.

The QNTM basketball sneaker features a knit upper with wavy cut-out strips that reveal a breathable mesh base underneath. The grey and white tones used on both layers are complemented by reflective accents, an Off-White suede toe cap and solid black hits at the collar, tongue and heel. The mid-top is supported by a Boost midsole and a herringbone-tread rubber outsole.

The adidas Yzy QNTM was first released on the 16th of February 2020, and retailed at a price of $250.

name: Be You
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Be You
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Be You was released in collaboration with LaMelo Ball. The shoe is designed for basketball players.

The LaMelo Ball MB.02 Be You by Puma features an upper engineered with a woven mesh for breathability. The logo for the point guard "1 of 1" is visible on the tongue and heel of the shoe. Having been designed for field activities, the shoe is cushioned with a lightweight material. Its non-slip rubber outsole supports player security on the court.

We think that The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Be You is unique due to its standout features, like the NITRO Infused midsole, which give an elevated feel. The shoe also has a TPU heel clip that adds heel and ankle stability. Its multicolor combination of the pair’s interiors makes it look more vibrant. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Be You was originally released on June 9th, 2023, at a retail price of $175.

name: HAL Studio Glacier
title: ASICS Gel-1130 HAL Studio Glacier
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 in HAL Studio Glacier is a collaboration between ASICS and HAL Studios, a leading brand for fashion and streetwear. This design takes its inspiration from glaciers found around the world.

This iteration of the ASICS Gel-1130 comes in a colorway paying homage to snow, ice, black, sandy beaches, and mountain glaciers. The white mesh upper is overlaid by a Birch shade suede and black and white leather. Rope laces secure a snug fit, while the ASICS logo appears near the bottom of one of the suede overlays. HAL Studios branding is present on a tag at the bottom of the heel. This design is completed with a round toe.

What we enjoy most about this shoe is the unique suede overlays on the midsole and toe that add a bit of texture to an otherwise simple shoe. The ASICS Gel-1130 in HAL Studio Glacier was initially released on July 29th, 2022, for a retail price of $190.

name: White Silver Metallic Black
title: New Balance 530 White Silver Metallic Black
description:
The New Balance 530 White Silver Metallic Black is a classic sneaker that blends retro style with modern comfort and performance features.

This shoe features a sleek and minimalist design that draws inspiration from the retro running shoes of the 1990s. The upper is constructed from a combination of premium suede, leather, and mesh to offer durability, breathability, and flexibility. A low-top profile allows for a broad range of motion while a cushioned midsole delivers support and shock absorption. A padded collar and tongue further add to the overall comfort of the shoe, while a mesh lining helps to regulate temperature. Other details include a perforated toe for ventilation, a standard lacing system for a secure fit, and a pull tab at the heel for easy on-and-off wear.

What our experts especially enjoy about the New Balance 530 White Silver Metallic Black, however, is its predominantly white colorway against which metallic silver and black accents pop. This shoe was originally released on August 28, 2023, with a price tag of $120.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Sea Salt
title: New Balance 990v2 MiUSA Teddy Santis Sea Salt
description:
The New Balance 990v2 Sea Salt arrives with a smooth white leather and cream mesh upper with grey leather detailing and monochromatic suede toe wraps. Heel tabs with "USA" embroidery nods to the Made in USA collection, which is composed of at least 70% US-grown materials. From there, a signature Abzorb midsole provides cushioning at the base.

The New Balance 990v2 Sea Salt released in July of 2022 and retailed for $195.

name: Simple Brown
title: adidas Yeezy Powerphase Simple Brown
description:
The adidas Yeezy Powerphase Simple Brown is one of the adidas Yeezy Powerphase sneakers featuring a Simple Brown color throughout.

The adidas Yeezy Powerphase Simple Brown sneaker’s design is inspired by Kanye West’s preference for earth-toned shoes, a common theme in his adidas Yeezy line. The sneaker’s entire upper appears in light brown suede, including the perforated midpanel, the toe, the heel, and the signature three stripes. The color scheme is contrasted with the visible Calabasas detailing in gold foil on the outer side of the sneaker and the green embroidered adidas branding next to the eyelets, a mesh sock liner, and laces. Completing the design is the brown treaded rubber sole for cushioning and traction.

The adidas Yeezy Powerphase Simple Brown debuted on September 18th, 2019, with a retail price of $120.

name: Pepper Reflective
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Pepper Reflective
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Pepper Reflective is part of the original Yeezy Boost 380 line created by adidas in collaboration with Kanye West.

The Pepper adidas Yeezy Boost 380 has an upper that is constructed from premium materials to provide durability. The Primeknit textile used on the upper is both breathable and stretchable to mold to the foot. The sneaker features reflective detailing and comes in a Pepper colorway with beige laces. The sneaker is also equipped with adidas' signature Boost technology and has a gum-like translucent rubber outsole with a herringbone pattern.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Pepper Reflective was released on September 11, 2020 at a retail price of $250.

name: Aime Leon Dore Purple
title: New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Purple
description:
The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Purple falls under the category of fashion and athletic sneakers.

This 550 New Balance by Aime Leon Dore in Purple is dressed in an elementary two-tone color scheme that features vintage-inspired details. The low-top features a violet-colored "N" emblem in cracked leather and a white leather upper with a microperforated midfoot overlay. The left and right heels each have mismatched NB and ALD branding. A classic rubber cupsole with worn sidewalls and an exposed EVA wedge on the medial side finishes the design of this sneaker.

The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Purple was released on the 21st of May, 2022, at a retail price of $130.

name: Nightwatch
title: New Balance 9060 Nightwatch
description:
The New Balance 9060 Nightwatch is constructed from a mixture of materials featuring a diamond-shaped outsole.

The suede color scheme merges with a meshed base and leather overlays, ranging from purple to green to dark grey all over the upper. Its branding elements like the N emblems make their return and a uniquely stitched "New Balance" text stretches from the left heel to the right in a bold yellow hue. From there its ABZORB and SBS stacked sole unit in shades of grey and green touches on the rubber outsole rounds out the shoe. 

Following its release on November 5th, 2022, the New Balance 9060 Nightwatch retailed at a price of $150.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Sepia Orange
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Teddy Santis Sepia Orange
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Teddy Santis Sepia Orange is a low-top running shoe made of synthetic leather with added mesh for breathability. Suede accents give this shoe a luxurious style.

Keeping with the New Balance brand, the logo is featured on the shoe's sidewall and beautifully embossed on its heel. The 990 symbol is also grafted on the back side of the shoe. It has a semi-rounded toe cap and cross laces. Its innovative construction includes a foam midsole for great support and protection. You don't have to stop running when you own this shoe because it is raining outside. This shoe is crafted with a mudguard to keep it from getting wet.

The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Teddy Santis Sepia Orange has similar features to the first-generation New Balance running shoe. Our team most appreciates its classic design and sophisticated color palette of reddish-brown and orange. The Boston company released this athletic shoe on December 15, 2023. Its original retail price was $220.

name: Calabasas Grey
title: adidas Yeezy Powerphase Calabasas Grey
description: The kicks of Kimye royalty, a pair of the Yeezy Powerphase Calabasas will have you feeling like you too are getting some of that E! money. A part of Kanye's "Calabasas" Collection, these come in a clean all-grey colorway and feature a full leather upper with "Calabasas" written in gold on the sides. Their release date was December 9th, 2017 where they were available at select adidas Originals retailers worldwide. If you're looking to step up your Erewhon outfit game, buy the grey adidas Yeezy Powerphase Calabasas grey colorway online today by placing a Bid on StockX.

name: Action Bronson Scorpius
title: New Balance 1906R Action Bronson Scorpius
description:
The New Balance 1906R Action Bronson Scorpius combines bold style with New Balance's performance-driven design. It features a unique blend of materials and colors inspired by Bronson's Scorpius persona. New Balance, founded in 1906, has a rich history of innovative footwear. This collaboration blends the brand's performance-driven style with Bronson's eclectic personality, resulting in a unique fusion of music, fashion, and sneaker culture. 

This limited-edition release brings together music, fashion, and sneaker culture. It features a bold, scorpion-inspired design with a predominantly black upper accented by metallic gold and red hues. The 1906R's mixed-material upper and supportive sole reflect New Balance's commitment to quality and comfort.

Our favorite thing about the New Balance 1906R Action Bronson Scorpius is its scorpion-inspired design and mixed-material upper. The bold, metallic accents and graphics add a unique touch to the classic 1906R silhouette. When these shoes hit the market on June 7, 2024, they retailed for $185.

name: Black Gum White
title: New Balance 550 Black Gum White
description:
The New Balance 550 Black Gum White channels a retro basketball feel from the 80s and boasts a black, gum, and white color combination.

The original New Balance 550 debuted in 1989 and was reintroduced with great fanfare and numerous colorways. This particular colorway features a tonal black upper that is made out of premium suede and leather. The suede appears on the toe guard and the heel counter, looking a bit distressed and giving the shoe a bit of edge. New Balance branding hits include the original capital letter ‘N’ on the side panels, with other NB branding on the midsole, heel tab, and tongue. You’ll spot 550 in white on the lateral eyestay.

What we love about this shoe is its nod to the heavy basketball footwear designs of the past, yet it presents a fresh, streamlined aesthetic. This lends to its versatility as a being a performance shoe for on the court or a lifestyle shoe for athleisure looks. The New Balance 550 Black Gum White debuted on November 1, 2022, and sold at retail price of $120.

name: Marquette
title: New Balance 550 Marquette
description:
The New Balance 550 Marquette comes in a white, university blue, and yellow color scheme.

The New Balance 550 Marquette features breathable synthetic and mesh material, a classic lace-up fastening system, and padding around the tongue and collar. The shoe's midsole features cushioning technology to serve as a shock absorber and cushion and provides steadiness. The sneaker's outsole is constructed from slip-resistant rubber for grip. The shoe features "new balance 550 NB" on the tongue and "NB" on the heel. The sneaker also has an "N" logo on the lateral sides and "550" lettering on one side.

The New Balance 550 Marquette was released on October 19, 2022, at a retail price of $110.

name: Cordura Pocket Black
title: New Balance 1906R Cordura Pocket Black
description:
The New Balance 1906R Cordura Pocket Black takes the recognizable 1906R silhouette and adds a new upper material and a removable pocket.

The removable pocket is secured over the lace cage and large enough to keep a key, a small amount of cash, or credit cards. Inspired by running sneakers from the 2000s, this version of the 1906R comes with a Cordura upper. This synthetic material is resistant to wear and more durable than other types of mesh used in sneaker uppers. ABZORB SBS cushioning in the heel and a ACTEVA LITE midsole increase comfort and stability without weighing down the shoes.

Something our StockX experts love is the dark colorway, which features a black upper with the New Balance ‘N’ outlined in white and a dark grey, speckled midsole. The New Balance 1906R Cordura Pocket Black was released on February 27, 2023, and retailed at $175.

name: Stone Carbon
title: adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Stone Carbon
description:
In a two-tone yellow and Stone Carbon knit construction, the Yeezy Knit RNR Stone Carbon hugs the foot like a sock. The base of the upper offers a more rugged feel than the collar, similar to the styling of nitride-dipped gardening gloves. On the collar, size information is printed in black to denote the size of each pair externally.

The adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Stone Carbon released in March of 2022 and retailed for $200.

name: Grey
title: New Balance 725 Grey
description:
The New Balance 725 Grey are sneakers inspired by the early 2000s running shoes silhouette.

The New Balance 725 is available in a grey colorway all through its synthetic upper. These trainers have a low-profile design featuring lace-up fastening and a padded tongue and cuff. The signature New Balance 'N' branding runs across the sides in Grey with white accents. For lightweight cushioning, this sneaker has an ABZORB midsole and the textured rubber outsole provides traction.

The New Balance 725 Grey was released on 24th January 2022 and originally sold for a retail price set at $135.

name: Kith By Invitation Only
title: ASICS Gel-Lyte III '07 Remastered Kith By Invitation Only
description:
The ASICS Gel-Lyte III '07 Remastered Kith By Invitation Only is part of a limited-edition collaboration between American designer Ronnie Fieg and ASICS.

The shoe was released in limited quantities and could only be purchased at a Kith store, with a special QR code, and after following specific directions on the brand’s website.
