It’s also the one-hundredth shoe released by ASICS in partnership with Kith. The sneaker boasts an upper made of pigskin suede in five different shades of blush, ranging from light to bold. The lightest colors can be found at the toe, while the shades on the heel are deeper. The vamp and side panels feature a collection of stylized perforations that allow the foot to breathe and create texture.

Our StockX experts like the off-white color of the midsole and outsole, which gives the sneaker a retro feel. The ASICS Gel-Lyte III '07 Remastered Kith By Invitation Only was released on November 28th, 2023, and retailed at $195.

name: Light Grey
title: New Balance 878 Light Grey
description:
The upper of this New Balance 878 Light Grey features a base of steel gray mesh and an extensively layered blend of mesh and suede, with trademark gray suede covering the majority of the overlays. 

Additionally, gray leather is thrown into the mix of the overlays, striking the midfoot and the two top eye stays. In terms of branding, the 878 features a typical silver N on its quarter along with two text graphics, "878" under the collar and on the tongue. A New Balance logo is also seen on the heels. A two-accent black and tan Ndurance midsole with a little splash of blue and a monochrome sail midsole with ABZORB cushioning technology to complete the design.

The New Balance 878 Light Grey was released on 1st January 2021. It retailed at $115.

name: Nightwatch Green
title: New Balance 327 Nightwatch Green
description:
The New Balance 327 Nightwatch Green is a performance shoe that fuses modern design elements with the legacy of the original shoe from the 1970s.

This version of the New Balance 327 comes with a paneled white upper as its base. Nightwatch Green suede forms the T-shaped toe cap, but it extends further around the foot than normal in a wave to form the mudguard. The New Balance N appears on the lateral midsole in a large green letter, and the heel is also made of green suede. The New Balance brand name also appears in white on the inside heel. Light gray suede sections are found under the eyelets, and a green NB logo can be found on the tongue. A white and beige sole and green outsole finish off the look, with the green outsole extending up the heel.

Our favorite feature of this particular shoe is the way the green outsole extends up the heel and partially over the toe, adding both functionality and unique style. The New Balance 327 Nightwatch Green was released on June 28, 2023, for $110.

name: Aime Leon Dore Jade
title: New Balance 1906R Aime Leon Dore Jade
description:
The New Balance 1906R Aime Leon Dore Green is a stylish and comfortable sneaker that is perfect for everyday wear.

The shoe features a green suede upper with white leather accents and a gum sole. The materials used in the construction of the shoe are of high quality, ensuring durability and longevity. The shoe is a collaboration between New Balance and Aime Leon Dore, a New York-based fashion brand known for its minimalist designs and attention to detail.

One of the standout features of the New Balance 1906R Aime Leon Dore Green is its unique colorway. The green suede upper is eye-catching and adds a pop of color to any outfit. The gum sole also adds a nice touch of contrast to the shoe. The release date for the New Balance 1906R Aime Leon Dore Green is May 4th, 2023, and the retail price is $170.

name: Salehe Bembury Water Be The Guide
title: New Balance 2002R Salehe Bembury Water Be The Guide
description:
Inspired by aquatic journeys, the New Balance 2002R Salehe Bembury Water Be The Guide features a pale orange mesh upper with hairy cyan suede overlays and dark green velour New Balance logos. A speckled white sole and lime green heel patch adds the finishing touches.

The New Balance 2002R Salehe Bembury Water Be The Guide released in June of 2021 and retailed for $150.

name: Burnt Orange
title: New Balance 550 Burnt Orange
description:
The New Balance 550 in Burnt Orange presents a minimalistic two-color design for this retro basketball silhouette that made its debut in 1989.

The Burnt Orange New Balance 550 low-top showcases a white leather upper, subtly complemented by accents in a Muted Orange hue. These accents can be found in the raised 'N' logo on the side panel, the Flying NB emblem on the heel, and the stitched New Balance tag atop the tongue. Additionally, a light gray suede overlay enhances the forefoot. The sneaker's foundation consists of a classic rubber cupsole, with an exposed foam wedge detail on the inner side.

What our experts love about the New Balance 550 Burnt Orange is its rich basketball heritage. Originally introduced as a basketball shoe, the 550 carries with it a legacy deeply rooted in the sport. Its classic design and court-ready silhouette pay homage to an era when footwear was evolving, and this colorway, Burnt Orange, celebrates its vintage roots. The sneaker debuted for $120 on February 23rd, 2023.

name: Joe Freshgoods Beneath the Surface Lil' Desert
title: New Balance 610 Joe Freshgoods Beneath the Surface Lil' Desert
description:
The New Balance 610 Joe Freshgoods Beneath the Surface Lil’ Desert is a distinctive sneaker resulting from the collaboration between New Balance and Joe Freshgoods, highlighting a unique camouflage design.

Inspired by the desert's landscape, the Joe Freshgoods Beneath the Surface Lil’ Desert New Balance 610 incorporates earthy tones and rugged textures that mirror the natural allure of the desert. Freshgoods brings his creative touch by fashioning a personalized camouflage print specifically for the silhouette. The 610 shoe is structured with an upper combining nubuck and mesh overlays. The camouflage motif runs throughout the shoe, employing a mesh base of olive, black, and gray shades, intersecting with brown and orange panels. It also includes an ABZORB midsole and a rubber Ndurance outsole to enhance comfort.

The distinguishing characteristic of the New Balance 610 Joe Freshgoods Beneath the Surface Lil’ Desert lies in its camouflage design. Originally utilized for concealment, this custom pattern contains hidden elements that not only enhance the shoe's aesthetic but also pay homage to the relationship between hip hop and this distinct pattern. The sneaker was released on the 20th of April, 2023, for $160.

name: Cloud White (Reflective)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cloud White (Reflective)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cloud White (Reflective) features a Cloud White Primeknit upper with the white tones remaining mostly monochromatic throughout the uniform design of this Yeezy Boost V2 offering against contrasting threads. From there, the chunky sole has a slight yellowish tinge to it, and the thick stripe running through the center of the Primeknit upper adds yet another splash of contrast to complete the design.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cloud White (Reflective) released in September of 2019 and retailed for $220.

name: Glow
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Glow
description: Hit the function and glow while wearing the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Glow. This Yeezy Boost 350 comes with a green upper, green midsole, and a green sole. These sneakers released in May 2019 and retailed for $250. Glow crazy and buy these on StockX today.

name: Syracuse
title: New Balance 550 Syracuse
description:
Drawing a subtle resemblance to the University of Syracuse school colors, the New Balance 550 Syracuse features a white leather upper with sharp orange mesh collars and detailing. A puffed white New Balance logo outlined in orange embellishes each quarter panel. From there, a woven tongue label with basketball imagery completes the design.

The New Balance 550 Syracuse released in September of 2021 and retailed for $110.

name: Sea Salt True Red
title: New Balance 550 Sea Salt True Red
description:
The New Balance 550 Sea Salt True Red presents a blend of classic 1980s charm with contemporary design, offering both style and comfort.

This iteration of the New Balance 550 Sea Salt True Red revitalizes the vintage ’80s basketball shoe with a fundamental two-toned appearance. Adorned in layered white leather, the sneaker incorporates black and red textile elements within the padded collar. Improved airflow is facilitated through a nylon tongue, while support for the rearfoot is delivered by a TPU heel clip. Notable branding features encompass an elevated "N" on the quarter panel and embossed on the heel overlay is a flying NB logo. Atop a rubber cup sole, the low-top structure displays an exposed EVA wedge on the medial sidewall.

The standout quality of the New Balance 550 Sea Salt True Red lies in its premium leather upper. Combined with the striking Sea Salt/True Red color scheme, this attribute contributes to the shoe's distinctive and fashionable appearance. The sneaker retailed for $120 when it was released on February 5, 2023.

name: Bodega No Bad Days
title: New Balance 997S Bodega No Bad Days
description:
Originally released exclusively at Bodega locations and their online store, the New Balance 997S Bodega No Bad Days is now available to customers around the world on StockX. As part of an ongoing collaboration between these two Boston-born companies, this model of the 997 is a sequel to the previously released No Days Off 997S.

This 997S features rubber and synthetic materials on the tongue and heel, highlighted with aqua, yellow, and red accents on the branding, tongue, and heel. A New Balance signature two-tone ENCAP midsole finalizes this new installment in the extensive history of these two companies. These sneakers released in September of 2019 for $160.

name: Black Marblehead
title: New Balance 574 Legacy Black Marblehead
description:
The New Balance 574 Legacy Black Marblehead channels a retro 80s feel while boasting a black and marblehead color scheme.

New Balance’s 574 Legacy silhouette presents a modern, streamlined aesthetic of a classic, unpretentious sneaker. This colorway boasts a tonal black upper that is made with premium suede. The reinforced toe box and heels play a part in its versatility as a shoe made for the road or trails. There are multiple branding hits throughout, including the original style cut out ‘N’ on the side panels in grey and white, with other NB branding on the heel counter, heel tab, and tongue. You’ll spot the ENCAP tech reference on the midsole, meaning the sneaker has New Balance’s cushioned midsole with PU reinforcement.

What we love about this shoe is its gold NB lettering on the tongue patch. It adds a bit of sparkle and is a nod to the "Legacy" in its name. When it debuted on June 16, 2022, the New Balance 574 Legacy Black Marblehead retailed for $90.

name: Slate Blue
title: adidas Yeezy 350 V2 CMPCT Slate Blue
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 CMPCT Slate Blue builds off of the original 350 V2 design by refreshing the knit upper. The CMPCT Primeknit upper arrives with a higher ankle collar than its predecessor, and ditches the traditional side stripe for a sock-like, woven pattern. Also, the lacing system is more voluminous than previous models, with lace loops extending out of the upper to hold its rope laces.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 CMPCT Slate Blue released in December of 2021 and retailed for $220.

name: White Nightwatch Green
title: New Balance 550 White Nightwatch Green
description:
The New Balance 550 White Nightwatch Green is the new addition to the New Balance colorway collection.

The leather sneakers have a white background with yellow and green accents to add depth to the design. The recognizable N emblem is located on the medial and lateral surfaces in addition to the 550 markings. Additional features include a perforated toe box, basketball branding at the tongue, and ankle padding. A white cushioned midsole completes the look. The tongues are finished off with further New Balance designs and basketball images. White sole components with two-toned rubber outsoles nestle beneath the design.

The New Balance 550 White Nightwatch Green debuted on October 19, 2022, and retailed at $100.

name: MiUSA Limestone
title: New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Limestone
description:
The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Limestone is a running shoe that’s part of the brand’s "Made in the USA" line.

The MiUSA Cream New Balance 990v4 features an upper made of Limestone-beige mesh for breathability. Limestone suede overlays cross the upper, forming the toe box and supporting the side panels, some of which are outlined in white. The New Balance "N" on each side is gray and white, and the tongue features 990v4 MiUSA branding. The heel is made of a slightly darker tan color with 990v4 branding on the outer side. Further NB and MiUSA branding is found at the top of the heel. The shoe has a Limestone and white midsole complete with ENCAP cushioning.

Our favorite thing about this shoe is the color scheme, which is neutral yet elegant. The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Limestone was released on July 27, 2023, for $210.

name: Lunar New Year Jade
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Lunar New Year Jade
description:
Puma and LaMelo Ball are celebrating Lunar New Year on court with the release of their Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Lunar New Year Jade sneakers. Lunar New Year celebrates its year of the rabbit in 2023.

LaMelo Balls Puma MB.02 basketball sneaker is dressed in a Jade green colorway with gold accents. The limited edition sneakers are made up of a breathable mesh material that sits atop jade rubber outsole.In Chinese culture, jade symbolizes well-being, longevity and good luck, making it the perfect choice for this MB.02 colorway.

The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Lunar New Year Jade released February 3, 2023, with a retail price of $140.

name: Ronnie Fieg & Frank Lloyd Wright Foundation Broadacre City Aloe Wash
title: New Balance 998 Ronnie Fieg & Frank Lloyd Wright Foundation Broadacre City Aloe Wash
description:
The New Balance 998 Ronnie Fieg & Frank Lloyd Wright Foundation Broadacre City Aloe Wash is a silhouette of the early 80s running shoe with an Aloe Wash and Apricot Buff color scheme.

This sneaker features a classic mesh upper, with suede panels, mesh underlays, and TPU eyelets. Its upper sits on an Encap midsole which sits on a rubber outsole. Logo-wise, it has a hairy suede saddle with the N logo, a 998 NB logo on the tongue, an NB logo on the heel, and an Encap logo on the midsole. This shoe’s design is finished with the Broadcare City sketch on its insole and packaging.

The New Balance 998 Ronnie Fieg & Frank Lloyd Wright Foundation Broadacre City Aloe Wash was released on 17th April 2023 at a retail price of $220.

name: Sea Salt Sandstone Blacktop
title: New Balance WRPD Runner Sea Salt Sandstone Blacktop
description:
The New Balance WRPD Runner Sea Salt Sandstone Blacktop is a sneaker with exaggerated proportions and a complementary colorway of Sea Salt, Sandstone, and Blacktop.

The sneaker boasts an oversized silhouette with padding in the tongue and around the collar and a bulky FuelCell midsole. This midsole has a stability post and a rubber outsole that wraps around the heel and toe. The base is made of white mesh, while the overlays display shaggy suede in Sandstone. However, the standout feature is the large New Balance "N" on the side panels. It comes in a dark Blacktop and is printed across the mesh quarter panel.

Our StockX experts like the curved lines of the midsole, which complement the cut of the shaggy suede overlays. The New Balance WRPD Runner Sea Salt Sandstone Blacktop was released on August 16, 2023, and retailed for a price of $150.

name: Phantom
title: New Balance 2002R Mule Phantom
description:
The New Balance 2002R Mule Phantom has taken the 2002R running shoe silhouette and re-created it as a comfortable slide-on lifestyle shoe without a heel or laces.

The Phantom colorway of the New Balance 2002R Mule features an upper that begins with a base of black mesh. From the abbreviated heel counter to the side panel to the toe cap, black suede overlays adorn the upper. Gray leather overlays accent the toe box, and a gray mesh N outlined in white graces the side panel. In place of a tongue and laces, a black mesh panel is overlaid with perforated black suede that features a patch with New Balance Running branding. The sock liner is soft gray textile, and the insole features ghostly NB branding.

What we enjoy most about this modified running sneaker is the consistency of the sole unit. An ABZORB midsole provides cushioning and energy return, while Stability Web technology provides arch support. Black rubber pods on the outsole are lugged for traction and add to the sneaker’s ability to absorb impact with every step. The New Balance 2002R Mule Phantom was released on December 20, 2022, for $140 retail.

name: White Periwinkle Blue (Women's)
title: ASICS Gel-1130 White Periwinkle Blue (Women's)
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 White Periwinkle Blue (Women's) fuses aspects of the GEL-1000 series and the GEL-KAYANO 14 to create a running shoe that provides all-day comfort for everyday wear. This running and lifestyle shoe is specifically sized for women.

The White Periwinkle Blue ASICS Gel-1130 for Women has an upper where a base of white mesh is overlaid with strips of gray, navy, and periwinkle blue synthetic material. These overlays offer both comfort and support. The foam midsole incorporates GEL technology for cushioning and shock absorption and uses the TRUSSTIC support system to improve stability at the midfoot. The black and blue rubber outsole is divided into a forefoot and a rear foot section.

What we appreciate most about this sneaker are the environmental concerns that go into its creation. More than 20% of the upper is crafted with recycled material and the dope-dyed sock liner reduces overall water usage and carbon emissions. The ASICS Gel-1130 White Periwinkle Blue (Women's) was released on August 27, 2021, for a retail price of $70.

name: Lunar New Year Timberwolf Grey
title: New Balance 9060 Lunar New Year Timberwolf Grey
description:
The Year 2000-inspired design of the Lunar New Year 9060 is upgraded by combining a mesh top with hairy suede overlays on the New Balance 9060 Lunar New Year Timberwolf Grey.

Its wavy patterns and dimensions atop a sculpted chambered midsole emphasize in a way the well-known cushioning platforms of ABZORB and SBS. Further details include a chunky rubber sole, round toe, and front lace-up fastening. Completing the sneaker’s appearance are its brandings including, the NB branded insole and the "N" logo patch in metallic silver on both sides.

The New Balance 9060 Lunar New Year Timberwolf Grey was released on 2nd January 2023 and retailed at the price of $160.

name: MiUSA Dark Ember Afterglow
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Dark Ember Afterglow
description:
The New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Dark Ember Afterglow showcases a striking blend of style and performance. This men's sneaker features a rich dark ember colorway accented with afterglow highlights, creating a visually appealing design that stands out. Crafted with New Balance's renowned attention to detail, the 990v6 continues the legacy of the iconic 990 series, offering superior comfort and support for everyday wear.

Designed and manufactured in the USA, this sneaker embodies New Balance's commitment to quality craftsmanship. The 990v6 incorporates advanced cushioning technology and a supportive midsole, ensuring all-day comfort whether you're running errands or hitting the gym. With its premium materials and expert construction, this shoe delivers the perfect balance of durability and style, making it a versatile addition to any sneaker collection.

Us at StockX believe this product is great for those seeking a high-quality, American-made sneaker that combines classic New Balance aesthetics with modern performance features.

name: Sulfur
title: adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Sulfur
description:
The Yeezy Knit RNR Sulfur features a two-tone cream and Sulfur knit upper that hugs the foot in a sock-like way. On the collar, size information is printed in black to denote the size of each pair externally. A thin Sulfur herringbone outsole completes the design.

The Yeezy Knit RNR Sulfur released in September of 2021 and retailed for $200.

name: Up There 2000's Tropes
title: New Balance 860v2 Up There 2000's Tropes
description:
The New Balance 860v2 Up There 2000's Tropes is a striking collaboration that pays homage to the iconic Y2K era. This men's sneaker showcases a vibrant blue colorway that captures the essence of early 2000s fashion. The shoe's design incorporates premium materials and expert craftsmanship, resulting in a visually appealing and comfortable footwear option.

Featuring New Balance's renowned cushioning technology, the 860v2 offers superior support and stability for all-day wear. The upper combines mesh and suede overlays, creating a textured look that's both stylish and functional. With its chunky silhouette and bold branding, this sneaker perfectly embodies the nostalgic charm of the 2000s while maintaining a modern edge.

Us at StockX believe this product is great for sneaker enthusiasts looking to make a statement with their footwear. The New Balance 860v2 Up There 2000's Tropes effortlessly blends retro aesthetics with contemporary comfort, making it an excellent choice for both casual wear and fashion-forward outfits.

name: Nickelodeon Slime
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Nickelodeon Slime
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB02 Slime is a collaborative sneaker inspired by Nickelodeon’s green slime.

Dressed in a Fluro green colorway that blends into a lime squeeze near the collar, this sneaker features an upper constructed with woven mesh and multizone mixed materials. Nickelodeon’s drippy slime details are visible on the PUMA Formstrip, sock liner, and toe box. LaMelo Ball’s signature wings logo is on the TPU heel clip, sock liner, and tongue, ‘SLIME’ and ‘RARE’ graphics are on the translucent outsole and ‘M.E.L.O.’ branding is on the heel counter. A NITRO foam-infused midsole rests on a non-slip rubber outsole.

The Puma LaMelo Ball MB02 Slime was made available on December 23rd, 2022. Initially, it retailed at $140.

name: Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Sage
title: New Balance 993 Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Sage
description:
The New Balance 993 Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Sage is a collaboration between New Balance and Joe Freshgoods.

The Performance Art Sage New Balance 993 Joe Freshgoods comes in a margarita and vintage rose color palette. The upper is made up of a mixture of suede and mesh. The sneaker has the signature New Balance ENCAP midsole technology for padding, support, and sturdiness. The rubber outsole provides grip and traction. The shoe features "N" on the lateral sides, "new balance Made in USA N" on the tongue, and "993" on one side of the heel. The design is completed with a "JFG" inscription on the heel.

The New Balance 993 Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Sage was released at a retail price of $220 on October 7, 2022.

name: White Pure Silver
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 White Pure Silver
description: The ASICS Gel Kayano 14 White Pure Silver is a sleek and stylish running shoe that offers both comfort and performance. The shoe features a white and pure silver colorway that is perfect for those who want a clean and minimalist look. The upper is made of a breathable mesh material that allows for maximum airflow, keeping your feet cool and dry during even the most intense workouts. The Gel Kayano 14 also features ASICS' signature Gel technology, which provides superior cushioning and shock absorption. This technology is located in the heel and forefoot of the shoe, ensuring that your feet stay protected and comfortable throughout your entire run. The shoe's outsole is made of a durable rubber material that provides excellent traction on a variety of surfaces. This makes the Gel Kayano 14 a great choice for runners who like to switch up their terrain. The ASICS Gel Kayano 14 White Pure Silver was released on April 22, 2022, and retails for $150. Something we love about this shoe is its combination of style and performance. Our experts think the best features of the Gel Kayano 14 are its Gel technology and breathable mesh upper. Overall, we think the standout feature of the ASICS Gel Kayano 14 White Pure Silver is its ability to provide both comfort and performance in a stylish package.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Sea Salt
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Sea Salt
description:
The New Balance 990v3 Sea Salt is a viable alternative to the classic grey suede low-top sneaker. It boasts an off white premium mesh, leather, and suede build atop an ENCAP cushioned sole. Reflective material on the New Balance logo and heel cap add the finishing touch.

The New Balance 990v3 Sea Salt released in May of 2022 and retailed for $210.

name: White Sky Blue
title: New Balance 530 White Sky Blue
description:
The New Balance 530 White Sky Blue is a sneaker that has its origins as a running shoe but has quickly risen to become a staple in the New Balance lineup.

The shoes have a sleek streamlined silhouette featuring a layered upper made from a mix of breathable mesh and leather overlays. They are predominantly white with blue accents adding some color to the design. The shoes also have a chunky sole unit with a fully white midsole and black outsole to enhance the contrast effect on the shoes. As for branding, the shoes have the iconic ‘N’ logo on the sides in grey with a blue outline and a New Balance logo on the tongue.

One thing our experts love about the New Balance 530 White Sky Blue is the incorporation of ENCAP technology in the midsole. It is a cushioning system that combines soft EVA foam with a polyurethane rim for added support and durability. The shoes released on the 22nd of August, 2022, retailed at $95.

name: Hi-Res Coral
title: adidas Yeezy QNTM Hi-Res Coral
description:
The adidas Yeezy QNTM Hi-Res Coral infuses vibrant energy into the basketball-inspired silhouette, characterized by an animated color scheme.

The Hi-Res Coral adidas Yeezy QNTM distinctive design revolves around the dynamic yellow RPU cage, layered on a semi-translucent jacquard mesh upper. Beige synthetic suede adds extra durability to the toe area, while the collar and heel incorporate a subtle sage green neoprene material for flexibility and comfort. Sitting atop a full-length Boost midsole, it's encased in an orange TPU cage and supported by a matching rubber outsole. Minimal branding is evident with the discreet Yeezy Globe logo imprinted on the insoles.

What our experts like about the adidas Yeezy QNTM Hi-Res Coral is its futuristic silhouette. This sneaker pushes the boundaries of design with its avant-garde and high-tech appearance. The combination of Primeknit, suede, and neoprene materials, along with the distinct orange accents and heat-welded taping, creates a look that feels straight out of the future. The sneaker was released on the 10th of October 2022 for $260.

name: White Black
title: New Balance 327 White Black
description:
The New Balance 327 White Black takes inspiration from a '70s classic New Balance running silhouette and reimagines it. The resulting shoe has a modern feel with heritage details.

The upper of this retro runner features a tightly woven textile base in snowy white. Grayish-white suede forms a T-toe overlay, eye stay overlays, and a heel overlay with wavy edges. White laces cross over a white textile tongue with black flying NB branding. The New Balance 327 White Black sneaker sits on a white foam midsole that offers easy landings and springy takeoffs. Patterned throughout with circular lugs, the black rubber outsole extends up the toe and all the way up the heel, giving this shoe a singular look.

Our favorite aspect of this vintage-inspired pair of shoes is the bold oversized N in black that hits the side panel. Its textured leather adds a style that makes a statement. The New Balance 327 White Black was released on July 27, 2022, for a retail price of $100.

name: Whispers
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Whispers
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Whispers is part of a "Not From Here" collaboration between Puma Hoops and NBA player LaMelo Ball.

This performance basketball shoe boasts a mid-top design and a sleek silhouette. The sneaker stands out due to its neutral colorway of Ivory and Whisper. The shoe is predominantly off-white on the base with Ivory overlays. While the tongue and heel feature the signature wings "1" logo in black and black lines grace the medial side panel, most of the shoe is dominated by light tones. In terms of performance, the NITRO foam midsole protects against impact and provides a slight bounce. In addition, the rubber outsole provides traction to grip the court.

Our experts love the traction design on the bottom of the shoe that resembles overlapping feathers. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Whispers was released on May 26th, 2023, and retailed at $130.

name: MiUSA Action Bronson Baklava
title: New Balance 990v6 MiUSA Action Bronson Baklava
description:
Action Bronson is teaming up with New Balance for his debut sneaker collaboration that features the New Balance 990v6.

Action Bronson added his own flavor on the New Balance 990v6 with a neon yellow mesh base, with green, silver and orange overlays. New Balance used a premium brown suede mudguard that sits on top of a blue sole. Action Bronson's Baklava New Balance sneakers are laced up with two-tone pink and purple rope laces, and feature Baklava branding on the insoles.

The New Balance 990v6 Action Bronson Baklava released March 17, 2023 with a retail price of $220.

name: JJJJound Navy
title: New Balance 990v4 JJJJound Navy
description:
Like other New Balance x JJJJound collaborations, the New Balance 990v4 JJJJound Navy boasts a simple palette. Tonal navy mesh and suede comprise the upper, while a black ENCAP sole sets the base. From there, two different lacing options are available for wearers to choose from: standard shoe laces and or an elastic drawstring with a JJJJound branded toggle.

The New Balance 990v4 JJJJound Navy released in October of 2021 and retailed for $265.

name: Concrete Oatmeal
title: ASICS Gel-NYC Concrete Oatmeal
description:
The ASICS Gel-NYC Concrete Oatmeal is a synthetic and suede upper running sneaker with a silver mesh base and overlays in Concrete and Oatmeal’s shades of cream and gray.

The Gel-NYC was designed for ASICS AnGELo Baque and crew, taking inspiration from previous ASICS shoes. The GEL-NYC combines aspects of earlier GEL-NIMBUS 3 styles and features ASICS’ signature linear overlay motif to create an evolution that is both familiar and novel among ASICS’ well known performance silhouettes. The midsole is crafted from a blend of lightweight foams, featuring GEL technology inserts and a curved, buoyant aesthetic. ASICS and GEL branding appears on the tongue, side, and heel in gray and white.

Our experts feel that the best feature of the Gel-NYC is the silver base, which adds a metallic pop to the neutral color palette. The ASICS Gel-NYC Concrete Oatmeal released on July 22, 2023, and retailed for $130.

name: Ronnie Fieg & Frank Lloyd Wright Foundation Broadacre City Chutney
title: New Balance 998 Ronnie Fieg & Frank Lloyd Wright Foundation Broadacre City Chutney
description:
The  New Balance 998 Ronnie Fieg & Frank Lloyd Wright Foundation Broadacre City Chutney shoe has a traditional mesh top and overlay panels made of hairy suede and pigskin suede. 

The sneaker features a traditional suede and mesh upper with a color-blocked panel. Its upper is made of a warm apricot color scheme with olive green accents on the heel orange mudguards and a beige hue on the tongue. Additional detailing includes the white N logos on the lateral and medial sides and the New balance text on its tongue. The design is finished with the Broadacre City graphic on the insole and has an ENCAP technology midsole that provides stability and shock absorption.

The New Balance 998 Ronnie Fieg & Frank Lloyd Wright Foundation Broadacre City Chutney was released on 17th April 2023 and retailed at $220.

name: Black
title: New Balance 990v5 Black
description:
The New Balance 990v5 Black arrives in a black and silver color palette.

The New Balance 990v5 Black is entirely black and features faint 990 and N branding details in silver. An NB logo is featured on the heel. The shoe has a synthetic mesh upper and a lightweight foam midsole to provide cushioning and support. The outsole is made of rubber for grip and stability. The 990v5 also incorporates shock-absorbing ABZORB cushioning in the heel and forefoot. The adjustable midfoot pad and cushioned tongue offer a secure and comfortable fit.

The New Balance 990v5 Black was released for a retail price of $175 on May 8th, 2019.

name: Stone Island
title: New Balance 574 Legacy Stone Island
description:
Stone Island was ready to make their move into the footwear space this year, collaborating with New Balance on their classic 574 silhouette.

New Balance’s Stone Island collaboration derives from military inspiration, highlighted by various shades of grey and green throughout the uppers. The sneakers are constructed of premium suede and mesh, and sit on top of a two-toned grey and white midsole. Stone island branding on the tongue tops off this sneaker of the year candidate.

The New Balance 574 Legacy Stone Island released February 16, 2023, with a retail price of $140.

name: Tyrian
title: adidas Yeezy 500 High Tyrian
description:
Yeezy adds a new colorway to its growing Yeezy 500 High line with the adidas Yeezy 500 Tyrian, now available on StockX. This is the first high-top sneaker silhouette Yeezy has released since the 750. Similar to the 500 High Slate release, Yeezy replaces mesh with neoprene to add a sleek look to this high-top model.

This Yeezy 500 High is composed of a Tyrian neoprene with brown suede overlays with black tumbled leather detailing. A dark grey Adiprene midsole and matching rubber outsole completes the design. These sneakers released in May of 2020 and retailed for $220 USD.

name: Grey Day (2023)
title: New Balance 9060 Grey Day (2023)
description:
Drawing inspiration from the futuristic design trends of the Y2K era, the New Balance 9060 Grey Day (2023) sneaker seamlessly combines elements from iconic 99X models. This silhouette integrates the 990's distinctive sway bars into its upper design, and the tongue logo pays homage to the lace jewel found on the original 991 model.

The Gray Day New Balance 9060 (2023) silhouette features a mesh upper with suede overlays and a padded collar for comfort. It includes TPU eyelets and NB 9060 banding on the tongue for a secure fit. The sneaker showcases embroidered N branding on the front, an N patch on the side panel, and embroidered NB branding on the rear – adding to its distinctive style. With a TPU heel counter for stability, flat cotton laces, and a durable rubber outsole, these sneakers offer both a fashionable design and practical functionality.

What our experts love about the New Balance 9060 Grey Day (2023) is its timeless silhouette. This sneaker effortlessly blends classic design elements with a modern touch, making it a versatile and enduring choice for enthusiasts. The sneaker debuted for $150 on May 12th, 2023.

name: White Silver Green
title: New Balance 530 White Silver Green
description:
The New Balance 530 White Silver Green encapsulates the classic running shoe style through its mesh and synthetic upper, featuring reflective side N logos, metallic accents, and Abzorb cushioning technology.

Constructed from a blend of lightweight leather and breathable mesh panels, the White Silver Green New Balance 530 incorporates vivid green detailing on the trim, heel, and sidewall. The iconic N logo appears in a muted gray hue while additional branding embellishes the tongue and rear sections. Metallic silver highlights further enhance the sneaker's appeal on the paneling and toe cap. Ensuring comfort and support, the ABZORB midsole, complete with a practical lace-up closure and functional pull tab, delivers exceptional cushioning.

We think the standout characteristic of the New Balance 530 White Silver Green lies in its midsole technology. Engineered with ABZORB innovation and a plush cushioning core, it provides unmatched shock absorption and stability. The sneaker debuted on February 24, 2023, for $100.

name: Bone Light Aluminum
title: New Balance 2002R Bone Light Aluminum
description:
The New Balance 2002R Bone Light Aluminum sneaker features a bone-colored mesh upper with overlays of tonal bone suede and tonal bone synthetic leather.

The "N" on the quarter is a synthetic material. The tongue is tonal bone mesh and suede and the laces are bone cotton. The aluminum color appears in the "2002R" branding on the quarter, the "NB" branding on the heel, and the tab on the back of the collar. The insole is light gray with dark gray writing, the bone midsole has energy columns that are visible on the lateral side only, and the outsole is black and bone rubber.

The New Balance 2002R Bone Light Aluminum was released in September 2020 at a retail price of $140.

name: Oreo (GS)
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Oreo (GS)
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Oreo (GS) is a shoe for grade schoolers designed together with American basketball star LaMelo Ball.
  
This version of the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 has a black technical mesh upper for added breathability. The upper is covered by shiny black overlays that invoke the shape of flames, while white outlines of these flames appear on the inner ankle. The LaMelo Ball logo appears on the tongue in white, while the heel features this same branding alongside M.E.L.O and Puma branding in white. The shoe sits on a black and white speckled midsole and a black outsole. 
 
In our opinion, what stands out about this sneaker is the speckled midsole, which adds even more of an "Oreo" look to the shoe. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Oreo (GS) was first introduced for sale on August 11, 2023, with an initial retail price of $110.

name: Glow Green (Kids)
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Glow Green (Kids)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Slide Glow Green (Kids) was launched as part of the kids’ wear in the sports collection of the adidas Yeezy Slide Glow series.

The adidas Yeezy Slide Glow Green (Kids) is a product of lightweight injected EVA foam material featuring a Glow Green colorway throughout. This slip-on shoe has a bigger front upper with an opening that covers the front part of the foot, its grooves are deep and horizontal on the sole. The footbed features a small trefoil logo that completes the design.

The adidas Yeezy Slide Glow Green (Kids) was released on September 6, 2021 at a retail price of $45.

name: Tactile Orange
title: adidas Yeezy 500 High Tactile Orange
description:
The adidas Yeezy 500 High Tactile Orange arrives in a mix of mesh, leather, suede, and neoprene. Shades of brown make up the upper along with hits of navy and indigo on the overlays. A Tactile Orange adiprene sole wraps this hiking-inspired shoe.

The adidas Yeezy 500 High Tactile Orange released in May of 2021 and retailed for $220.

name: Cordura Magnet
title: New Balance 1906R Cordura Magnet
description:
Similar to the original 1906 from 2010, this New Balance 1906R Cordura Magnet features TPU and leather panels construction across its upper, which is built on top of a ballistic mesh base. 

The sneaker comes in an all-black color scheme, with a magnet hue on its vamp and quarter panels. The emphasized "N" logo features NLOCK detailing, while the midsole's combination of ABZORB and N-ERGY technology provides the ideal combination of cushioning and comfort. A tag is embroidered onto the lateral heel to state that this shoe was created in collaboration with Cordura, completing the vintage appearance.

The New Balance 1906R Cordura Magnet was released on 12th November 2022. It retailed at $155.

name: Mist Stone
title: adidas Yeezy 500 High Mist Stone
description:
With a leather, neoprene, and suede construction, the upper of the adidas Yeezy 500 High Mist Stone resembles hiking boots of the 90s. At the base, an adiPRENE midsole provides support and responsiveness for daily wear.

The adidas Yeezy 500 High Mist Stone released in October of 2021 and retailed for $220.

name: Moonbeam Shadow Grey
title: New Balance 327 Moonbeam Shadow Grey
description:
The New Balance 327 Moonbeam Shadow Gray features an ultra-lightweight design for comfortable wear and breathability. It also has a lugged outsole for running on trails or outdoors. A flared midsole and rubber heel wrap further provide added protection and safety for runners.

New Balance is a leading manufacturer of athletic footwear and clothing. The oversized "N" logo on the side of the shoe makes it clear that this is a New Balance shoe. It has a neutral color scheme that includes soft gray and off-white tones. You can use its lace closure to tighten and get the perfect fit in these running shoes.

Our team is most impressed with the classic look and mixed materials used to make the New Balance 327 Moonbeam Shadow Gray running shoe. It is a nylon upper with suede trim and mesh accents. This shoe was released on June 27, 2023. Its original price was $100.

name: Olive Brown
title: New Balance 2002R Olive Brown
description:
Collaborations with the likes of Joe Freshgoods, Salehe Bembury, and A Bathing Ape contributed to the release of the New Balance 2002R Olive Brown.

  The New Balance 2002R’s upper features an all-olive brown colorway throughout its upper part and mainly on its various base layers and meshes, with contrasting army-colored overlays. The heel tab and the "N" emblem complete the look with silver-shaded reflective covers, while the midsole mixes a cream with a white base. To cap off this sneaker, it features a dark grey rubber outsole.

The New Balance 2002R Olive Brown was released to the market on June 18th, 2022. It retailed at a price of $140.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Navy Castlerock
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Navy Castlerock
description: The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Navy Castlerock is a premium sneaker that combines style and comfort. The upper is made of a mix of suede and mesh, providing breathability and durability. The navy and castlerock colorway gives the shoe a classic and versatile look. The sneaker features the iconic \"N\" logo on the side and a cushioned sole for maximum comfort. The release date for this shoe is August 25th, 2022, and it retails for $200. This sneaker is perfect for those who want a high-quality shoe that can be worn for both casual and athletic activities. The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Navy Castlerock is a must-have for any sneaker enthusiast looking for a timeless and comfortable shoe.

name: Sea Salt Rust Oxide (Women's)
title: New Balance 327 Sea Salt Rust Oxide (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 327 Sea Salt Rust Oxide (Women's) upper features durable leather and breathable mesh material for comfort. The rubber outsole offers optimal traction, while the sock-like fit reinforces heel integrity.

The New Balance 327 Sea Salt Rust Oxide (W) has a 4mm drop and a lightweight upper for a quick, responsive feel. The sneaker also features enhanced dampness control for reduced risk of blistering, which also prevents moisture retention and increased breathability. The sneaker is available in women’s sizing.

The women’s New Balance 327 Sea Salt Rust Oxide (W) was released in March 2022 and retailed at $110.

name: Black Moonbeam
title: New Balance XC-72 Black Moonbeam
description:
The New Balance XC-72 Black Moonbeam is crafted in a mesh upper with suede overlays, nylon vamp, and a single-layer microfiber tongue.

It comes dressed in a stealthy black color scheme with a  leather "N" branding printed on the side panels. Sail on "Moonbeam" has been used on the toebox, tongue, laces, and inside lining to create a sharp contrast. Its tongue has also been embellished with silver NB emblems. This New Balance XC-72's sole unit is made completely of black rubber, and to complete the design, it uses three traction outsole patterns, and a Sail stripe runs across it.

The New Balance XC-72 Black Moonbeam was released on 12th November 2021 and retailed at $100.

name: Lunar New Year Rich Earth
title: New Balance 2002R Lunar New Year Rich Earth
description:
The New Balance 2002R Lunar New Year Rich Earth updates a classic running shoe silhouette from the early 2000s to celebrate the Lunar New Year in the Year of the Rabbit.

This running shoe features a breathable, lightweight, tightly woven dark gray mesh base. Overlays undulate and layer over each other across the upper in light gray leather, light gray suede, brown suede, and dark gray hairy suede. The iconic side panel "N" is in puffy light gray leather and is outlined in darker gray embroidery. A four-toned midsole features ABZORB and SBS ABZORB in the heel to provide springy cushioning and energy return. The primarily black N-Ergy outsole with Stability Web tech is lugged for traction and impact absorption and grooved for flexibility.

Our favorite detail on this shoe is the one hit of color on this upper's otherwise subtle colorway. In deep red embroidery, NB branding hits the heel. The New Balance 2002R Lunar New Year Rich Earth, a limited edition release, was launched on December 30, 2022, for $150 retail.

name: White Summer Fog
title: New Balance 550 White Summer Fog
description:
The New Balance 550 White Summer Fog was delivered in a simple two-tone color scheme- white and lightly shaded beige, covering an artificially made leather.

The White Summer Fog’s upper comprises white suede and light beige overlays. Also featured on the sneakers is the white rubber midsole which is fitted with an EVA wedge for light cushioning. Additionally, the lining is made entirely of cotton fabric and is completed with an NB signature symbol on the inner soles. From there on the "N" and the NB symbols found at the side panels and rear respectively, complete the sneakers' look.

The New Balance 550 White Summer Fog debuted on the market on September 7th, 2022, and retailed at a price of $110.

name: Cecilie Bahnsen Habanero
title: ASICS GT-2160 Cecilie Bahnsen Habanero
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 Cecilie Bahnsen Habanero is a performance shoe designed in collaboration with the Copenhagen-based fashion designer.

This version of the ASICS GT-2160 features a white mesh upper. Polyurethane overlays decorate the toe box in the form of small pink flowers while pink, white, and red overlays run from the toe to the laces. The traditional ASICS design appears on the sides of the shoe in white and orange. A semi-transparent pink mudguard wraps around the forefoot. The heel features a layered design with silver, white, and pink overlays and is branded with the word GEL. A thick, shiny pink strap appears over the tongue, and a bright red sole equipped with Gel technology completes the look.

Our favorite feature of this shoe is the red sole, as it adds another pop of color next to all the pink and orange elements. The ASICS GT-2160 Cecilie Bahnsen Habanero was released on November 22, 2023, for $230.

name: White Pure Silver Gold
title: ASICS GT-2160 White Pure Silver Gold
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 White Pure Silver Gold is a running shoe featuring a sleek silhouette created by a White mesh upper overlaid with metallic cage overlays in Pure Silver and Gold.

ASICS, the Japanese athletic wear brand, is known for the fine-tuning of their running shoe technology, revisiting and refining previous iterations with technological advancements. The GT-2160 sneaker recalls the GT-2000 series circa 2010, which has been updated to have a technical aesthetic combined with superior comfort and cushioning. A sculptural midsole in white with Pure Silver and Gold accents blends with the overlays. ASICS branding appears on the tongue and heel, and a gold GEL unit and black and Pure Silver outsole complete the fluid aesthetic.

Our experts feel that the best feature of the GT-2160 is its metallic color palette, which has both lifestyle and running appeal. The ASICS GT-2160 White Pure Silver Gold was released on August 1, 2023, and retailed for $130.

name: White Steel Grey
title: ASICS Gel-NYC White Steel Grey
description:
The ASICS Gel-NYC White Steel Grey strikes a seamless balance between urban performance and refined styling, cementing its place as a standout in ASICS’ lifestyle lineup. Inspired by classic running profiles, this iteration combines retro design elements with cutting-edge technology, embodying the brand’s dedication to innovation and timeless aesthetics.

This design’s White and Steel Grey colorway offers a crisp, versatile look that easily transitions between casual and active settings. The upper features a combination of breathable white mesh and Steel Grey synthetic overlays, delivering a sleek design. Subtle branding details and reflective accents enhance the shoe's dynamic appearance, while the durable outsole, inspired by ASICS’ performance heritage, ensures reliable traction for everyday wear.

Comfort is at the forefront, with the inclusion of ASICS’ signature Gel cushioning in the midsole, which provides exceptional support and shock absorption. Perfect for both style-conscious wearers and those seeking all-day comfort, the Gel-NYC White Steel Grey exemplifies ASICS’ commitment to merging functionality with contemporary fashion. The ASICS Gel-NYC White Steel Grey was released on March 3, 2023, and retailed at $120.

name: Fade Indigo
title: adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Fade Indigo
description:
The adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Fade Indigo is a unique colorway of the Yeezy Knit RNR, a slip-on running shoe released by adidas in collaboration with the Yeezy brand which is owned by global superstar Kanye West.

The shoe has a knitted upper and a stretchy cuff that gives it a snug sock-like fit. The upper showcases a gradient pattern with solid blue covering the collar area, while the rest of the upper fades from navy to varying shades of brown, green, and indigo. The outsole of this adidas Yeezy Knit RNR has a rubber construction plus a herringbone pattern to improve traction.

What our experts love the most about the adidas Yeezy Knit RNR Fade Indigo is its minimalist and futuristic design featuring a one-piece knitted upper that offers a sock-like fit and a sleek, streamlined look. This not only works aesthetically, but also improves the overall comfort of the shoes. The shoes were released for retail in October 2022 for $210.

name: Pure (Restock Pair) (Kids)
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Pure (Restock Pair) (Kids)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Slide Pure Restock Pair Kids is, as its name suggests, a kid-sized slide which is an addition to the long line of adidas and Yeezy collaboration products.

This slide varies a bit from the initial adidas Yeezy Slide Pure that was released in 2021, given that it has a pebbled construction, unlike the original, which had a smooth EVA foam construction. Other than having slightly different compositions, these slides are pretty similar. Like the OG version, this restock pair for kids features a ridged sole and a softened footbed.

The adidas Yeezy Slide Pure Restock Pair Kids was released on 7th March 2022. Initially, its retail price was $50.

name: Sea Salt Marblehead
title: New Balance 1906R Sea Salt Marblehead
description:
The New Balance 1906R Sea Salt Marblehead is a retro-inspired running shoe from the New Balance 1906R  lineup in a Sea Salt Marblehead colorway.

The sneaker features a White mesh base that runs throughout the upper cut out by tonal grain leather overlays. A Marblehead Grey TPU heel counter provides support. Other details include a Grey ‘N’ logo on the sides, tongue and heel branding, and ‘1906R’ branding on the lateral heel. A Pebble Grey  ACTEVA LITE midsole with ABZORB cushioning and a Black N-ergy shock-absorbing rubber outsole complete the design.

The New Balance 1906R Sea Salt Marblehead was made available on October 1st, 2022, for a retail price of $155.

name: Cordura Workwear
title: New Balance 997H Cordura Workwear
description: The New Balance 997H Cordura Workwear is a durable and stylish sneaker that is perfect for everyday wear. Made with Cordura fabric, these sneakers are built to withstand the toughest conditions and provide long-lasting comfort. The upper is a mix of suede and mesh, with a classic New Balance design that is both timeless and modern. The colorway is a mix of black, grey, and orange, giving the sneaker a rugged and industrial look. These sneakers were released on January 25th, 2022, with a retail price of $90. With their high-quality materials and attention to detail, the New Balance 997H Cordura Workwear is a must-have for anyone looking for a reliable and stylish sneaker.

name: Earth Brown
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Earth Brown
description: DISCLAIMER: US and UK sizing is the same and does not require any conversion.

name: MiUSA Grey Blue
title: New Balance 990v1 MiUSA Grey Blue
description:
The New Balance 990v1 MiUSA Grey Blue has the classic look of the NB running shoe. It is made of a combination of quality suede, mesh, and other quality materials. A thick black rubber outsole gives these low-top sneakers excellent traction and increased durability. The front has a lace-up closure for a better fit, stability, and support.

The combination of grey and dark blue gives it a charming, sporty, and rustic look. The New Balance logo is embossed on the side of the shoe, and the NB label is sewn on the tongue to identify the brand. The 990v1 MiUSA Grey Blue is lightweight with strong arch protection.

Our team most likes its microfiber lining and midsole cushioning, which make it more comfortable and help with odor and sweaty feet. New Balance released the New Balance 990v1 MiUSA Grey Blue on October 27, 2022, at the original retail price of $190.

name: Galaxy
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Galaxy
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Galaxy arrives with a galaxy-patterned mesh upper with reinforced purple overlays and sharp orange detailing. On the tongue, LaMelo's signature "One of One" graphic boasts neon colors, contrasting its dark, spacey background. At the base, a neon green sole offers enhanced court grip and durability.

The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Galaxy released in April of 2022 and retailed for $125.

name: Aime Leon Dore Green
title: New Balance 860v2 Aime Leon Dore Green
description:
The New Balance 860v2 Aime Leon Dore Green is dressed in green, and sea salt accents that also have metallic gold and silver trim alongside what seems to be modified tongue branding. 

The pair chooses a cream-colored mesh on the vamp for further contrast, while the sides rest on top of white mesh bases. Base layers in shades of grey and cream provide the backdrop for either red, green, or blue highlights. The branding features Santis' popular imprint on the top of the tongue, and co-branding is featured on the sock liners in the company's signature font. The well-known N-energy sole unit maintains its SBS insert, dependable outsole, and greyscale color scheme underneath the foot.

New Balance 860v2 Aime Leon Dore Green was released on 4th April 2023 and retailed at $150.

name: Aime Leon Dore White Green
title: New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore White Green
description:
The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore in White-Green is a result of a partnership between New Balance and Aime Leon Dore.

The shoe draws inspiration from the New Balance 550 and remains faithful to its predecessor by featuring a perforated leather upper and breathable mesh. This low-top basketball silhouette comes with a white upper paired with a green, cracked New Balance logo. The shoe sits on a pre-yellowed midsole, providing a vintage look.

The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore White-Green was released for sale on October 9, 2020, and retailed at about $130 in most outlets.

name: Gallery Dept. ComplexCon
title: ASICS GT-2160 Gallery Dept. ComplexCon
description:
The ASICS GT-2160 Gallery Dept. ComplexCon is part of a collaboration between ASICS and Gallery Dept., an LA-based artists collective and gallery known for its apparel designs.

This sneaker takes the GT-2160 silhouette and splatters it with yellow, orange, black, and blue paint. While the heel area remains untouched, the vamp and EVA midsole boasts a concentration of paint speckles. The EVA midsole houses visible gel cushioning that protects against impact without weighing down the shoe. Like other GT-2160 models, the exclusive ComplexCon variation boasts a white mesh upper with suede and leather detailing. The overlays give the sneaker a technical aesthetic and are made of a synthetic material in blue and Pure Silver.

Our StockX experts like the choice to keep the white laces paint-free. It gives the sneaker a polished look. The ASICS GT-2160 Gallery Dept. ComplexCon was released on December 15, 2023, and retailed at $295.

name: DIME Arctic Wolf
title: ASICS GT-2160 DIME Arctic Wolf
description:
The ASICS GT 2160 DIME Arctic Wolf is a versatile and reliable running shoe designed as a collaboration between Canadian skateboarding brand, "DIME," and Japanese sportswear brand, ASICS. Together, these brands have reimagined the 2000s era ASICS GT-2160.

These shoes feature the ASICS’ signature DuoMax Support System and IGS technology in the midsole, as well as GEL cushioning in the heel. The upper is made from breathable mesh, while the outsole is made from a high-abrasion rubber. You can find "ASICS" detailing on the shoe's tongue, and the "DIME" logo is embossed on the heel's lateral side.

What our experts love most about the ASICS GT 2160 DIME Arctic Wolf, however, is its ombre gray coloration, which incorporates reflective accents to enhance visibility for added safety during nighttime jogs. These sneakers released for the first time on July 22, 2023, with a price tag of $160.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Navy Castlerock
title: New Balance 990v2 MiUSA Teddy Santis Navy Castlerock
description:
The New Balance 990v2 MiUSA Teddy Santis Navy Castlerock colorway carries a variety of blue tones with complimenting shades of gray on its upper, which balances fine pig suede and mesh.

The sneaker features hairy accents layered over its porous counterpart in either a deep navy or cool grey color scheme, with its upper part being dominated by deep blue hues. The "N" logo opts for a light gray finish, in contrast to the "USA" embroidery on the heel, which is done in black. Moving on, the ABZORB sole unit is subtly referenced in the off-white midsole, while the "New Balance 990" text is branded on its tongue in dark gray.

The  New Balance 990v2 MiUSA Teddy Santis Navy Castlerock was released on 25th August 2022 and retailed at the price of $195.

name: White Moonbeam (Women's)
title: New Balance 327 White Moonbeam (Women's)
description:
The women's New Balance 327 White Moonbeam (W) features a Munsell White and Moonbeam nylon and suede upper with the bright tones of Munsell White acting as a base, overlaid with suede panels that feature the brownish Moonbeam hue at the toebox and heel panels of the silhouette. From there, an oversized New Balance logo in Moonbeam and a white tread runs the full length of the outsole and up the back of the heel to complete the design.

The women's New Balance 327 White Moonbeam (W) released in August of 2020 and retailed for $100.

name: MiUSA Varsity Green Gold
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Varsity Green Gold
description:
The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Varsity Green Gold covers the 990v3 silhouette in multiple green hues, ranging from light Varsity Green to deep Team Forest Green.

Inspired by the original 990 from 1982, the MiUSA Varsity Green Gold New Balance 990v3 carries technical elements that speak to its technical running roots. For instance, the ENCAP midsole supports the arch and provides cushioning stability. In addition to creating a chunky silhouette, padding in the collar and tongue increases comfort and protects the ankle. Boasting a premium upper construction, lightweight mesh underlays in Varsity Green allow the foot to breathe, while suede overlays in Team Forest Green support the build. Both the mudguard and heel overlays come in shaggy suede, adding a textured contrast.

Our experts at StockX like the signature New Balance "N," which comes in contrasting gold. The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Varsity Green Gold was released on March 30, 2023, and sold for $200.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Marblehead Incense
title: New Balance 990v1 MiUSA Teddy Santis Marblehead Incense
description:
The New Balance 990v1MiUSA Teddy Santis Marblehead Incense sneaker features an upper made primarily of fuzzy gray suede that overlays an olive-green mesh that is visible in the toe-box, the collar, and the tongue.

The laces of the New Balance 990v1 MiUSA are cream-colored to match a plastic clip on the bottom of the heel. The top of the heel has "New Balance" debossed in soft brown suede and the "N" on the quarter is soft white leather. The insole is cream-white, as is the foam midsole with a gray accent. The outsole completes the picture in black rubber. 

The New Balance 990v1MiUSA Teddy Santis Marblehead Incense with its Marblehead/Incense colorway came out in April 2022 at a retail price of $190.

name: MiUK JJJJound Grey Olive (Women's)
title: New Balance 991 MiUK JJJJound Grey Olive (Women's)
description:
JJJJound joined forces with New Balance in the release of the New Balance 991 MiUK JJJJound Grey Olive (W), marking their first time designing a collaborative sneaker.

  The women’s sneaker is constructed of a grey and brown premium mesh and suede upper. Sitting on the heel of the shoe and insole is the JJJJound branding in a neutral tone, whilst its tongue and quarter are the New Balance and N logos respectively. The sneakers also feature an air-cushioned midsole dressed in a cream hue.

The New Balance 991 MiUK JJJJound Grey Olive (W) was released on February 17th, 2023, and retailed at $250.

name: Blue Oat
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Blue Oat
description:
Yeezy added a new colorway to their Boost 380 product line with the adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Bloarf, now available on StockX. This model was originally known to be the Yeezy Boost 350 V3, but upon release it was given its own silhouette name.

This 380 Bloarf features a Bloarf Primeknit pattern on its upper with a fitted ankle collar. An upgraded translucent Boost midsole and engineered gum outsole grip completes the design. These sneakers released in Spring of 2020 and retailed for $230.

name: White Grey (GS)
title: New Balance 550 White Grey (GS)
description:
The New Balance 550 White Grey GS shoe was originally designed by Aimé Leon Dore in 1989, and this model is by Teddy Santis.

The 550 White Grey for grade-schoolers has a smaller size release with smaller price tags. The 80’s-era and vintage look sneakers feature an anti-skid grey outsole and white uppers made of smooth leather. They feature the 550 New Balance branding on the front lace, New Balance logo on the tongue, and a large N logo on the lateral and medial sidewalls.

The New Balance 550 White Grey GS Grade School shoe was released in July 2022 and retaialed for $80.

name: Sulfur
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Sulfur
description:
Yeezy adds another colorway of its most popular design with the adidas Yeezy 350 V2 Sulfur now available on StockX. This 350 V2 stays true to Yeezy’s signature palette, sporting light earth tones that provide a natural feeling.

This Yeezy 350 V2 is composed of a Sulfur Primeknit upper with a tonal mesh side stripe. A Sulfur Boost cushioned midsole sole and light brown outsole completes the design. These sneakers released in May of 2020 and retailed for $220 USD.

name: Aime Leon Dore Brown
title: New Balance 993 Aime Leon Dore Brown
description:
The New Balance 993 Aimé Leon Dore Brown features a brown mesh upper with brown premium pig suede and dark green tumbled leather overlays. At the base, a black responsive ABZORB midsole and rubber outsole is geared for daily wear. Aimé Leon Dore branding on the heels and inserts add a custom feel.

The New Balance 993 Aimé Leon Dore Brown released in November of 2021 and retailed for $200.

name: MiUSA Grey White
title: New Balance 990 MiUSA Grey White
description:
The New Balance 990 MiUSA Gray White is an athletic shoe featuring a gray upper in suede and textile mesh. The New Balance N logo appears on the side in white. A white midsole is accented by gray and white detailing at the heel, displaying the New Balance logo. New Balance branding appears on the rear collar and the tongue. A black midsole ties the aesthetic together.

The New Balance 990 debuted in 1982, and since then it has been a game changer for runners. Known for its technology and performance, the 990 transcended the track to become a popular lifestyle shoe as well. With an American heritage that dates to 1906 in Boston, this model of the 990 is made in the USA.

Our experts feel that the best features of the 990 MiUSA Gray are the silver accents, which bring the gray color palette to life. The New Balance 990 MiUSA Gray White released on May 17, 2022, and retailed for $175.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Plum Purple
title: New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Teddy Santis Plum Purple
description:
The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Teddy Santis Plum Purple is part of a collaboration between New Balance and Teddy Santis, the founder of menswear line Aimé Leon Dore.

The MiUSA Teddy Santis Plum Purple New Balance 990v4 comes in a vibrant Plum Purple colorway with white and black detailing. The upper construction boasts black mesh underlays with supportive overlays crafted from hairy suede in Plum Purple. The hairy suede adds a contrasting texture that pops against the mesh base. In terms of technology, the dual-tone ENCAP midsole houses EVA foam for superior comfort and responsive energy return. Finally, the Ndurance outsole comes in black and provides grippy traction underfoot.

Our experts at StockX like the heritage New Balance branding, including the matte gray and white "N" on the side panel and the subtle "990" printed on the overlays. The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Teddy Santis Plum Purple was released on June 29, 2023, and originally retailed at $210.

name: Mauve
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 V2 Mauve
description:
The adidas Yeezy 700 V2 Mauve arrives with a brown mesh upper with dark grey Nubuck overlays and tonal adidas three stripe detailing. At the base, a sculptural Boost midsole atop a gum outsole provides the renowned cushioning Yeezy is known for.
The adidas Yeezy 700 V2 Mauve released in September of 2021 and retailed for $240.

name: Kith Salmon Toe
title: ASICS Gel-Lyte V Kith Salmon Toe
description:
The ASICS Gel-Lyte V Kith Salmon Toe has been a recognizable color scheme in the ASICS Gel series since its debut.

The ASICS Gel-Lyte V Kith Salmon Toe comes with a light salmon color that runs from the toe roll, toe box, and nylon upper. The Oxford blue color runs from the middle quarter to the rest of the shoe hind. The ASICS logo rests on the tongue of the shoe. The ASICS Gel-Lyte V Kith Salmon Toe is made from suede and rubber materials.

The ASICS Gel-Lyte V Kith Salmon Toe retailed at $165 during its release on November 24th, 2021.

name: Navy White
title: New Balance 574 Navy White
description:
The New Balance 574 Navy White offers a comfortable lifestyle shoe in a classic colorway.

The Navy White New Balance 574 has an upper that builds upon a base of navy-blue mesh. This airy base is overlaid at the toe cap, midfoot, eyestays, and heel with tonal suede. Off-white leather that matches the laces forms a collar overlay and also matches a TPU heel counter that provides rear foot stability. The blue side-panel N outlined in white offers the brand's signature style, while the padded tongue and collar offer comfort. The two-toned EVA midsole in gray and blue is constructed with ENCAP technology for comfort and support, and rides atop a black rubber outsole.

The aspect of this lifestyle shoe we enjoy the most is the heel tab. White tumbled leather sports blue New Balance branding for classic simplicity. The New Balance 574 Navy White was released on February 21, 2022, for a retail price of $95.

name: Hospital Blue
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 V2 Hospital Blue
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 V2 Hospital Blue features a Hospital Blue canvas and suede upper, with all materials taking on light blue tones that can appear almost grayish. From there, a bulky midsole of the V2 takes on a streamlined, sporty appearance atop a black outsole and a full-length Boost midsole complete the design.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 V2 Hospital Blue released in September of 2019 and retailed for $300.

name: Joe Freshgoods Conversations Amongst Us
title: New Balance 2002R Joe Freshgoods Conversations Amongst Us
description:
In collaboration with Joe Freshgoods, the New Balance 2002R Joe Freshgoods Conversations Amongst Us draws inspiration from crucial dialogues that connect the Black community. It arrives with a neutral-toned upper constructed with nylon, leather, and premium suede. Hits of orange and yellow add a subtle contrast. On the insole, graphics of two figures conversing nod to the collection's theme of communication. From there, a cream and orange NERGY sole provides cushioning and support.

The New Balance 550 Joe Freshgoods Conversations Amongst Us released in April of 2022 and retailed for $130.

name: Joe Freshgoods Inside Voices Penny Cookie Pink
title: New Balance 9060 Joe Freshgoods Inside Voices Penny Cookie Pink
description:
The New Balance 9060 Joe Freshgoods Inside Voices Cookie Pink features a Cookie Pink mesh construction with light brown suede overlays and matching New Balance logos. At the heel, subtle "Inside Voices" embroidery is prominent in a monotone style. From there, a white, green, and beige sculptural sole completes the design.

The New Balance 9060 Joe Freshgoods Inside Voices Cookie Pink released in May of 2022 and retailed for $180.

name: Stone
title: adidas Yeezy 500 Stone
description:
Yeezy added new materials to a fan favorite with the adidas Yeezy 500 Stone, now available on StockX. Following the Bone White and Soft Vision releases, Yeezy is staying true to its pallette with the Stone 500s. The materials that comprise this model is where the difference lies. Yeezy replaces mesh with neoprene to add a twist to this popular design.

This Yeezy 500 is composed of a Stone neoprene and suede with reflective piping. A matching Adiprene midsole and Gum rubber outsole completes the design. These sneakers released in November of 2019 and retailed for $200.

name: Grey White
title: New Balance 2002R Grey White
description:
The New Balance 2002R Grey White has a design inspired by the high-end 2010 iconic model, the MR2002.

The 2002R model has a perforated leather underlay construction having pig suede overlays all around to add a layer of detail. The shoes come in a grey-white colorway with dark grey lace-up closure for a secure fit. Cushioning and compression resistance is provided by the ABZORB midsole and heel cushioning. The combination of the N-nergy and Stability Web outsole technology provides added arch support and superior shock absorption.

The New Balance 2002R Grey White was released on 23rd March 2022 with its retail price set at $140.

name: Static Reflective
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Static Reflective
description: Before 2018 is over, reflect back on your sneaker resume and add the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Static Reflective to the collection. This Yeezy 350 comes with a grey upper, grey midsole, and a grey sole. These sneakers released in December 2018 and retailed for $220. Clear the static in the air and grab these now on StockX.

name: Supernova
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Supernova
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB02 Supernova is a sneaker resulting from a collaboration between the lifestyle brand and NBA player LaMelo LaFrance Ball.

It is finished in a fiery orange hue, while the engineered mesh upper is fortified with tonal no-sew overlays. The shoe also features a TPU heel clip marked with LaMelo’s signature Wings logo. PUMA’s Formstrip adorns the lateral side, while the opposite side features a hidden "RARE" graphic in contrasting blue lettering. The shoe rides on PUMA’s NITRO foam midsole, built with compression-molded EVA foam for cushioning. Underfoot, a second "RARE" graphic embellishes the feather-tread rubber outsole.

The Puma LaMelo Ball MB02 Supernova was released on October 21st, 2022, at a retail price of $130.

name: Military Green
title: New Balance 327 Military Green
description:
The New Balance 327 Military Green features a silhouette inspired by 1970s running shoes combined with contemporary design elements, including exaggerated studs on the rubber outsole.

These studs run all the way up the heel and give the sneaker a trail-ready appearance that matches the Military Green colorway. However, what makes this sneaker stand out is the oversized New Balance ‘N’ on the side of the shoe. It’s so large that the overlays overlap the letter’s edges. The upper is made of canvas-like mesh with suede overlays, while the lace closure system is adjustable. Branding elements include ‘NEW BALANCE’ embossed on the suede heel overlay and the ‘NB’ logo tag on the tongue.

Our experts at StockX like the shoe’s monochromatic colorway, which allows the contrasting textures to take center stage. The New Balance 327 Military Green was released on November 19th, 2022, and retailed at $100.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Marblehead Incense
title: New Balance 990v2 MiUSA Teddy Santis Marblehead Incense
description:
As part of Teddy Santis' New Balance Made In USA Spring 2022 collection, the New Balance 990v2 MIUSA Marblehead Incense features a brown mesh upper with grey and beige suede overlays and a reflective New Balance side logo. From there, an ABZORB sole provides cushioning and responsiveness.

The New Balance 990v2 MIUSA Marblehead Incense released in April of 2022 and retailed for $195.

name: White Vibrant Orange
title: New Balance 550 White Vibrant Orange
description:
The New Balance 550 White Vibrant Orange is a great running shoe for those who are looking for a durable and comfortable option.

As the name suggests, the shoe has Vibrant Orange shades on the lower side of the sole. However, the upper part of the shoe is white and is made of a sturdy synthetic material that can withstand a lot of wear and tear, and the vibrant orange color is conspicuous and stylish. The midsole is cushioned for additional support, while the outsole is grippy for extra footing.
 
  The New Balance 550 White Vibrant Orange had a retail price of $100 when it was released in January 2022.

name: MiUSA Black Tan
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Black Tan
description:
The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Black Tan is a shoe that was released as part of the brand’s iconic Made in the USA collection.

This version of the New Balance 990v3 features an upper of dark brown mesh for breathability. Black suede overlays form the mudguard, while tan overlays outline the toe box heading toward the laces. The eyestays are black suede, and the sides are also supported with black suede. This material also forms the heel counter, while tan suede appears on both sides of the ankle. The New Balance " N" appears in a light gray color on each side outlined in white. Silver 990 branding can be seen on the lateral heel, while a red NB logo adorns the heel. "Made in the USA" appears on the heel collar, and the tongue also sports New Balance USA branding. The shoe features an ENCAP-supported midsole and a black rubber outsole.

What stands out about this shoe is its dark and elegant colorway, adding some extra style to the athletic design. The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Black Tan was released on April 27, 2023, for $200.

name: Sun
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Sun
description:
After a year hiatus with no new colorways, Yeezy brought back the original 700 silhouette in 2021 with the adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Sun.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Sun is primarily composed of a bright yellow mesh, leather, and suede upper with back and teal overlays located over the forefoot. 3M detailing on the heel, a bright orange Boost midsole, and a dark grey outsole adds the finishing touches to this vibrant design.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Sun released in January of 2021 and retailed for $240.

name: True Form
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 True Form
description: Get a Yeezy 350 in its truest form and grab the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Trfrm. This Yeezy Boost 350 comes with a grey upper plus orange accents, translucent stripe with orange accents, grey midsole with orange accents, and a grey sole. These sneakers released in March 2019 and retailed for $220. Only true sneakerheads wear Yeezy’s so place a Bid on StockX today.

name: Cream Kale
title: ASICS Gel-NYC Cream Kale
description:
The ASICS Gel-NYC Cream Kale draws inspiration from the GEL-NIMBUS 3 and GEL-MC PLUS V, showcasing an upper characterized by off-white mesh and leather overlays in a gleaming metallic silver finish—a familiar detail reminiscent of ASICS' early 2000s running style.

The iconic side stripes of the Cream Kale ASICS Gel-NYC are bordered in a vibrant Kale Green, extending to the eyelets and branding details. Serving as the foundational layer of the upper, the cream-colored open mesh offers breathability while creating a stylish contrast with the metallic overlays. The Gel-NYC features embroidered Kale Green logos on the tongue, adding a touch of sophistication. The shoe is completed with a white midsole featuring accents of Kale Green and a cream-colored outsole.

The standout element of the ASICS Gel-NYC Cream Kale undeniably lies in its color scheme. The harmonious fusion of cream, metallic silver, and Kale Green generates a visually appealing aesthetic that seamlessly blends the modern and retro influences. The sneaker debuted for $130 on September 23rd, 2023.

name: Not From Here Red Blast
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Not From Here Red Blast
description:
Presented in a vibrant Red Blast color scheme, the Puma MB.01 takes cues from LaMelo Ball's "1 of 1" chest tattoo. Embroidery on the mesh upper represents the bird wings found in the tattoo, while the illustration on the tongue depicts a toned-down rendition of the exact design.

The Puma MB.01 Red Blast released in December of 2021 and retailed for $125.

name: White Pink Sea Salt (GS)
title: New Balance 550 White Pink Sea Salt (GS)
description:
The New Balance 550 White Pink Sea Salt GS is a grade school edition sneaker from the New Balance 550 collection in a White/Pink/Sea Salt colorway.

This low-cut sneaker features a leather upper made of a White base with Pink overlays on the forefoot, heel, and ankle collar. Other details include a unique ‘NB’ branding on the tongue accented in Grey and Pink, the ‘N’ logo on the sides highlighted by a Pink trim, and additional branding on the heel, outsole, and side of the toe. A White midsole and Pink and White rubber outsole round out the design. 

The New Balance 550 White Pink Sea Salt GS was released on 8th July 2022, it retailed at $80.

name: Grey Day
title: New Balance 57/40 Grey Day
description:
The New Balance 57/40 Grey White dons a grey-and-white color palette.

The New Balance 57/40 Grey White has an upper that is grey with white accents. The upper is constructed from a combination of materials, including suede, mesh, and leather, for durability and comfort.
