The shoe also has a sturdy rubber outsole and a foam midsole for extra comfort and grip. The sneaker includes a cushioned tongue and collar and the sneaker's side panels feature the brand's hallmark "N" logo.

The New Balance 57/40 Grey White was released on May 15th, 2021, for $120.

name: Queen City
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Queen City
description:
The Puma MB.01 LaMelo Ball Purple Glimmer tributes the Charlotte Hornets with a monochromatic Purple Glimmer woven upper. Hits of light blue on the Puma toe logo and tongue complement the design's rich palette. At the base, a grooved outsole is geared for explosive styles for play.

The Puma MB.01 LaMelo Ball Purple Glimmer released in March of 2022 and retailed for $125.

name: Honeycomb
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Honeycomb
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Honeycomb is LaMelo Ball's sophomore signature sneaker. It arrives meticulously engineered to provide traction and well-rounded responsiveness.

The Honeycomb Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 boasts a woven mesh upper for enhanced breathability. It is supported by a comfortable midsole featuring NITRO foam for lightweight responsiveness. The design features an eye-catching black and Elektro Aqua colorway. It has mesh paneling and an all-over graphic print that is complemented by a secure lace-up front and branded insole. The rubber sole incorporates a feather-inspired tread pattern that offers improved durability and traction while paying homage to Melo's signature wings.

What our experts love about the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Honeycomb are the mid-top cut, engineered mesh upper, TPU heel clip, and MB.02 branding that complete the distinctive look. This sneaker is a stylish and high-performance addition to PUMA's lineup. The was released on the 10th of March 2023 for $130.

name: White Dark Mercury (Women's)
title: New Balance 550 White Dark Mercury (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 550 White Dark Mercury (W) has a neutral two-tone color scheme and comes in a women's sizing.

Its midsole extends the full-white leather upper, which is paired with a dark mercury blue hue, a front lace fastening, branded insole, and perforated detailing. The sneakers' many logo features, including the raised 'N' branding on the quarter panel and a vintage NB stamped on the back heel, are finished with contrasting mercury blue panels that are detailed on the white leather uppers. Finishing off the sneaker’s appearance is a round toe and a 550 text on the panel.

The New Balance 550 White Dark Mercury (W) was released on the market on 1st February 2023 and retailed at the price of $110.

name: Black Off White (2023)
title: New Balance 574 Black Off White (2023)
description:
With the New Balance 574 Black Off White (2023), the renowned sneaker company offers a versatile, lightweight, comfortable lifestyle shoe that will keep your feet happy as you're on the go.

This sneaker features an upper of airy black mesh. Black suede overlays cover the eye stays, side panels, toe cap, and heel. Off white suede forms a V-shaped overlay at the collar, giving this silhouette its distinctive look. White leather with black New Balance branding forms the heel tab, while black leather outlined in white leather forms the iconic side panel N. The soft, supportive midsole is constructed of white EVA foam with a wedge of gray ENCAP cushioning. The black speckled outsole sports lugs that help absorb shock and provide grip.

Our favorite standout detail on this pair of kicks is the branded tongue tag, which features a flying NB, the word "Classic" in script, and "574" set apart in a black rectangle. The New Balance 574 Black Off White (2023) was released on April 1, 2020, for $95 retail.

name: Mowalola Burglarwear Black Teal Pink
title: New Balance 9060 Mowalola Burglarwear Black Teal Pink
description:
The New Balance 9060 Mowalola Burglarwear Black Teal Pink is a sleek and striking shoe designed to blend the durability and comfort of the New Balance brand with the aesthetic of Lagos-born fashion designer Mowalola Ogunlesi.

With a design inspired by the high-speed foot chases of the big screen, this cinematic shoe combines a dark black base with pops of teal and pink. This shoe also features a leather overlay in its construction, as well as synthetic mesh – a combination that ensures both durability and breathability. A standard lacing system delivers a customizable fit.

What our experts agree is the most standout feature of the New Balance 9060 Mowalola Burglarwear Black Teal Pink, however, is the silicone details that add visual appeal on the tongue and in the iconic New Balance logo on the lateral sides. These shoes originally retailed with a price of $180 when they were first released on November 18th, 2022.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Marblehead Incense
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Marblehead Incense
description:
Arriving as the first release of Teddy Santis' New Balance Made In USA Spring 2022 collection, the New Balance 990v3 MIUSA Marblehead Incense features a light brown mesh upper with grey suede overlays and beige leather piping. At the base, a responsive ENCAP midsole and black outsole completes the design,

The New Balance 990v3 MIUSA Marblehead Incense released in April of 2022 and retailed for $200.

name: Yeshaya (Non-Reflective)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Yeshaya (Non-Reflective)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Yeshaya (Non-Reflective) features gray-and-white Primeknit upper with a mesh side stripe and rope laces. At the base, translucent Boost sole with a hint of yellow offer a neutral color palette.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Yeshaya (Non-Reflective) released in January of 2020 and retailed for $220.

name: Cream White (Infants)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cream White (Infants)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cream White (I) comes in a cream-white color scheme in infant-sizing.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cream White (I) includes a Primeknit upper in a light cream hue and a tonal midsole. The sneaker also features a distinctive lacing system and a ribbed outsole for stability and comfort. The shoe's rubber outsole and Boost midsole provide comfort and durability. The shoe also has a heel pull button and a pair of flat shoelaces for convenience.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cream White (I) was released on April 29, 2017, and sold for a retail price of $140.

name: Green Punch
title: New Balance 610 Green Punch
description:
The New Balance 610 Green Punch showcases a trail-inspired aesthetic, sporting a vibrant Green Punch color scheme.

The Green Punch New Balance 610 arrives crafted with breathable mesh panels for optimal ventilation. These sneakers come in a sleek black and green color combination. They feature a logo print on the side, a rounded toe, and a front lace-up fastening for a secure fit. Additionally, the double pull-tab at the opening allows for easy on and off, while the branded insole enhances comfort. These shoes are supported by a durable rubber sole with C-CAP cushioning, ensuring great comfort and traction with every step.

The standout feature of the New Balance 610 Green Punch is its vibrant Green Punch colorway. This bold and eye-catching hue sets these sneakers apart, making them a striking and distinctive choice for individuals who want to make a statement with their footwear. The sneaker sold for $110 in April 2023.

name: White Silver (GS)
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 White Silver (GS)
description: The Puma MB01 LaMelo Ball White Silver GS is a sleek and stylish basketball shoe that is perfect for young athletes. Made with high-quality materials, this shoe features a white and silver colorway that is both eye-catching and versatile. The release date for this shoe is July 13th, 2022, and with a retail price of $95. With its comfortable fit and durable construction, the Puma MB01 LaMelo Ball White Silver GS is sure to become a favorite among basketball players of all skill levels. Whether you're hitting the court for a game or just looking for a stylish and comfortable shoe to wear around town, this is the perfect choice.

name: Lunar New Year Concrete
title: New Balance 2002R Lunar New Year Concrete
description:
The New Balance 2002R Lunar New Year Concrete is part of the New Balance’s top-tier collection, and this retro rendition is inspired by Year of the Rabbit.

A mesh underlay in a calm taupe hue traverses from the upper of this New Balance 2002R and is visible on the quarter panels and heel. The mudguard is a concrete-colored suede overlay. On the textile upper, slate grey strips of an underlay are visible. The concrete colorway adorns most of the shoe, making appearances on the quarter panels, eye stay, and part of the heel counter. The New Balance "N" logo is embossed on the quarters and is embellished with embroidery on its outlines.

Our experts think the red accents on the New Balance 2002R Lunar New Year Concrete add a vibrant feel to the neutral concrete, slate grey, and taupe colorway. The New Balance branding on the tongue and the "NB" logo on the counter have a red hue. This shoe's release date was marked as December 30, 2022, and its price was $150.

name: Rain Cloud
title: New Balance 57/40 Rain Cloud
description:
The New Balance 57/40 Rain Cloud layers shades and textures of gray and white to create a retro shoe that updates and reimagines 1988’s iconic NB 574.
 
The upper of the New Balance 57/40 Rain Cloud is constructed from gray mesh with light gray suede overlays and oversized white leather N branding on the side panel. The eyebrow and mudguard harken back to the 1980s with their distinct undulating wave pattern while the updated white stacked midsole provides cushioning and the black rubber outsole offers a modified traction pattern. A slimmer last along with reflective hits complete this silhouette.

  Released on January 6, 2021, the New Balance 57/40 Rain Cloud sold at a retail price of $100.

name: x Pleasures AC Milan 2023/24 Light Version
title: Puma x Pleasures AC Milan 2023/24 Light Version Jersey Multicolor
description:
AC Milan is no stranger to collaborating to create fresh takes on its uniforms, as the legendary soccer club has teamed up with many brands over time to do it. The club partners with Los Angeles streetwear staple PLEASURES to assemble the PUMA x PLEASURES AC Milan 2023/24 Light Version Jersey Multicolor.

This limited-edition jersey blends the grunge, metal, and punk influences that make PLEASURES unique and combines them with the gothic architecture found in Milan . The result is an AC Milan x PLEASURES jersey covered in a pattern based on the Milan Cathedral. This is more than just a statement piece, too, as the jersey also includes PUMA's patented dryCELL technology designed to help those who wear it stay dry under even the most challenging conditions.

Our experts like the direction in which AC Milan and PLEASURES took this jersey and appreciate the subtle nuances injected into its design. It once again demonstrates AC Milan's knack for creating collaborative jerseys that are both fashionable and functional. The PUMA x PLEASURES AC Milan 2023/24 Light Version Jersey Multicolor was released on February 11, 2024, for a $120 retail price.

name: Black Grey White
title: New Balance 725 Black Grey White
description:
Style fuses with practicality in the New Balance 725 Black Grey White, a head-turning lifestyle shoe inspired by running shoe designs popular in the early 2000s. The reimagination of classic elements results in a modern look with retro vibes.

The black, gray, and white New Balance 725 builds upon an upper base of black mesh that features quilted stitching across the toe box and midfoot. Overlays in both black and gray leather course across the upper, giving the shoe both a dynamic style and a durable structure. The two-toned gray webbing eyestays complement the tongue and the gray and white side panel N. This upper rides on a gray and white C-CAP midsole that offers support and cushioning. The black rubber outsole features grooves for grip and vents for flexibility.

The details we enjoy most on this sneaker are the tooth-like white graphics on the toe and heel of the upper that add a sense of motion to this sneaker. The New Balance 725 Black Grey White was released on October 31, 2021, for $100 retail.

name: Grey Matter White
title: New Balance 327 Grey Matter White
description:
The New Balance 327 Grey Matter White redefines retro running aesthetics with a modern twist, delivering a bold yet versatile addition to New Balance’s lifestyle sneaker range. Drawing inspiration from 1970s running shoes, the 327 combines nostalgia with contemporary design elements, making it a standout choice if you’re looking for a casual but stylish shoe.

This Grey Matter and White colorway offers a clean and neutral palette, ideal for everyday versatility. The upper features a combination of lightweight nylon and premium suede overlays, creating a sleek design. The oversized italic-styled "N" logo and angular midsole provide a fresh, statement-making edge. Studded-serrated rubber outsole, taken from trail-running designs, adds rugged flair, reliable grip for all types of surfaces, and a touch of panache with the triangular studded rubber.

Comfort is a key focus of the 327, with its cushioned EVA midsole ensuring support and shock absorption for all-day wear, and that is valuable. This model is perfect for those who appreciate classic silhouettes with modern updates. Released on March 1, 2023, the New Balance 327 Grey Matter White retailed at $100.

name: White Beige Gum (Women's)
title: New Balance 327 White Beige Gum (Women's)
description:
Drawing inspiration from vintage runners, the New Balance 327 White Beige Gum (Women's) features a combination of textile and suede uppers dressed in white and beige. These low-cut silhouettes adopt a lightweight construction with treads on the outsole designed for traction.

The 327 White Beige Gum for women flaunts a white textile upper with suede overlays, arriving in beige. The overlays round the eyestays, toebox, and heel wraps. The sneaker continues with the look, featuring white laces and a white EVA foam midsole. A beefed-up gum outsole has shock-absorbing properties that pair with the cushioned insole to deliver the comfort you need around your feet. These runners feature rubber rivets on the gum outsole designed for traction. The outsole extends up the heel and the toecap to round out the aesthetic. A large N on the sidewalls completes the New Balance 327 Beige design.

What our experts love about the sneakers are the rubber outsole pods that increase traction and absorb shock while running. The New Balance 327 White Beige Gum (Women's) was released on January 25, 2023, retailing for $130.

name: Lunar New Year Sea Salt
title: New Balance 550 Lunar New Year Sea Salt
description:
The New Balance 550 Lunar New Year Cream was released as a special edition in a cream colorway.

This 550 sneaker’s upper has a smooth leather toe cap and heel, while perforated leather comprises the laterals of the upper, with some contrast arriving in the form of off-white and beige hues at the mid-foot, collar, and lower heel areas. Maroon appears on the New Balance branding on the top of the tongue and spine. A cream-colored midsole and a gray rubber outsole with a linear pattern finish off the design.

The New Balance 550 Lunar New Year Cream was released on December 30th, 2022, at a retail price of $130.

name: JJJJound Silver White
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 JJJJound Silver White
description:
The ASICS Gel Kayano 14 JJJJound Silver White is a redesigned version of the original ASICS GEL-KAYANO™ 14.

This shoe boasts an upper with a white mesh base and silver synthetic leather overlays. The upper lies on a midsole with GEL Technology cushioning and ASICS' TRUSSTIC support system for a comfortable fit. nMeanwhile, the midsole lies on a rubber outsole. It features details such as the ASICS logo on its tongue, a white JJJJound logo on its lateral side, and a GEL-KAYANO 14 logo on the rear of its heel.

The ASICS Gel Kayano 14 JJJJound Silver White was released on August 26, 2022. Initially, it had a retail price of $180.

name: Rich Paul Forever Yours
title: New Balance 550 Rich Paul Forever Yours
description:
The New Balance 550 Rich Paul Forever Yours was released as part of a collaboration between NBA agent Rich Paul and New Balance.

The 550 Rich Paul Forever Yours is made with high-quality materials, including suede, mesh, and leather. The upper is constructed with overlays, which provide structure and support, and perforations on the sides, which enhance breathability. The shoe sits on a rubber outsole, which is designed to provide traction and durability. The outsole features a herringbone pattern, a common design element in basketball shoes. The shoe also has a padded tongue and collar, providing a comfortable fit and added support.

We think that one of the best features of the New Balance 550 Rich Paul Forever Yours is its colorway. The shoe features a predominantly violet colorway with gray and Midnight Violet accents throughout. The shoe was released on July 14, 2023, at a retail price of $130.

name: MiUSA Navy Denim
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Navy Denim
description:
The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Navy Denim is an addition to the long-running collaboration collection of New Balance and Teddy Santis, the founder and creative mind behind Aime Leon Dore.

Done in a Navy and Castlerock color scheme, this shoe boasts an upper constructed using mesh, suede, and leather materials. Its upper lays on a midsole infused with ENCAP technology and a rubber outsole. Detail-wise, it has a red-lettered New Balance logo on the tongue, "N" logos, and "Made in USA" branding on the ventilated heel tab.

The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Navy Denim made its way into the market on October 1st, 2021. At the time, this sneaker had a retail price of $185.

name: White Natural Indigo Burgundy
title: New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy
description:
The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy comes in a white, natural indigo, and burgundy color scheme.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy has an upper constructed from leather with a deep indigo burgundy hue. The shoe features an EVA midsole for padding and comfort. The sneaker also has a cushioned tongue and collar. The shoe features a rubber outsole for grip and stability. The sneaker has a "new balance 550" lettering on the tongue and "NB'" branding on the heel. The shoe also features an "N" logo on the lateral sides and "550" lettering on one side. The shoe's midsole features "NB" and "new balance" lettering on it.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy was released at a retail price of $110 on October 19, 2022.

name: Navy
title: New Balance 990v5 Navy
description: The New Balance 990 v5 Navy is a classic sneaker that combines style and comfort. The shoe features a navy blue suede and mesh upper, with reflective accents for added visibility. The ENCAP midsole provides cushioning and support, while the rubber outsole offers durability and traction. The shoe was released on May 8, 2019, and retails for $175. The New Balance 990 v5 Navy is a versatile sneaker that can be worn for both casual and athletic occasions. Its timeless design and high-quality materials make it a must-have for sneaker enthusiasts and New Balance fans alike.

name: Hylte Glow
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Hylte Glow
description:
Yeezy added to their glow-in-the-dark catalog by releasing a new colorway of the 380 with the Yeezy Boost 380 Hylte Glow. This is the second time in 2020 that Yeezy added glow-in-the-dark attributes to a 380, the first being the Yeezy Boost 380 Calcite that was released earlier in the fall.

The Yeezy Boost 380 Hylte Glow features a tonal yellow camo-print Primeknit upper with a flat neon green side spot. In typical Yeezy fashion, a dark grey translucent Boost sole and rope laces gear this release for daily wear.

The Yeezy Boost 380 Hylte Glow released in December of 2020 and retailed for $230.

name: MiUSA White Blue
title: New Balance 990v2 MiUSA White Blue
description:
The New Balance 990v2 MiUSA White Blue combines a clean white base with neutral tan, black, and electric blue accents.

Adding comfort and increasing breathability, the upper of the MiUSA White Blue New Balance 990v2 is crafted from lightweight mesh with suede overlays. The overlays feature tonal stitching and display the signature New Balance "N" logo patch in black leather with a blue outline. The Abzorb midsole provides soft cushioning and reveals the same color palette as the upper. Completing the look, the grippy rubber outsole comes in black, highlighting the black leather details on the upper.

Our experts at StockX like the bold New Balance Made In USA branding. For instance, the plush tongue displays "990 NEW BALANCE MADE IN USA," while the heel showcases "USA." Both branding elements come in blue, complementing the "NEW BALANCE ATHLETIC SHOES" lettering on the insole. The New Balance 990v2 MiUSA White Blue was released on November 23, 2022, and sold for $195.

name: HAL Studio Forest
title: ASICS Gel-1130 MK-II HAL Studio Forest
description: The Asics Gel 1130 MK II HAL Studio Forest is a highly anticipated release that is sure to impress sneaker enthusiasts and athletes alike. This shoe boasts a sleek forest green colorway that is both stylish and versatile, making it a great choice for any occasion. The Gel cushioning system provides exceptional comfort and support, while the durable rubber outsole ensures long-lasting wear. Crafted from high-quality materials, the Asics Gel 1130 MK II HAL Studio Forest is built to withstand even the toughest workouts. The breathable mesh upper allows for maximum airflow, keeping your feet cool and dry during intense training sessions. The lace-up closure ensures a secure and comfortable fit, while the padded collar and tongue provide added support and cushioning. Something we love about Asics Gel 1130 MK II HAL Studio Forest is its versatility. Whether you're hitting the gym or running errands, this shoe is the perfect choice. Our experts think the standout feature of the Asics Gel 1130 MK II HAL Studio Forest is its Gel cushioning system, which provides exceptional comfort and support. Overall, we love the Asics Gel 1130 MK II HAL Studio Forest for its style, comfort, and durability, making it a must-have for any sneaker collection.

name: White Light Cliff Grey (Women's)
title: New Balance 452 White Light Cliff Grey (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 452 White Light Cliff Grey (Women’s) is a running shoe with a 90s retro design in a white and light cliff grey color combination.

The low-cut New Balance 452 is an all-season shoe committed to delivering comfort with all sorts of sneaker tech. First, there is ABZORB® midfoot cushioning for shock absorption and secondly, the New Balance ultra-comfortable insert cradles the foot and reduces shifting. The leather and synthetic upper provide flexibility to the foot cage. This women’s colorway is nearly all white and is infused with light cliff grey accents primarily on the edges of overlays and the heel. The chunky outsole adds height.

What we love about this shoe is its crisp, fresh aesthetic that lends to its versatility whether going for an all-day athleisure look, a sweats outfit, or pairing them with other neutral tones for a soft, casual look. The New Balance 452 White Light Cliff Grey (Women’s) debuted on December 8, 2021, and sold at a retail price of $100.

name: Geode
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 V2 Geode
description: Take your swag to a hundred, a thousand, maybe even a trillion after copping the adidas Yeezy Boost 700 V2 Geode. This 700 V2 comes with a brown upper plus grey accents, grey midsole, and a gum sole. These sneakers released in March 2019 and retailed for $300. Try getting these 700’s before Yandhi drops and cop them today on StockX ASAP.

name: Pokémon Squirtle
title: Puma Suede PokÃ©mon Squirtle
description:
The Petit Four and Nitro Blue featuring Puma Suede Pokémon Squirtle is part of a wider collection of the Pokémon x PUMA Suede sneakers appearing in full family sizing.

The Puma Suede Pokémon Squirtle features patent leather heels and suede upper in various shades of blue. Its suede upper design features midfoot panels to reinforce the upper construction, PUMA branding on the lateral side in black, Nitro Blue lacing system for a comfortable fit, midfoot perforations for aerations, and the PUMA branding on the tongue tag in black colors. The sneaker’s lower construction features an Icy Blue shell-colored midsole for cushioning and support through impact absorption. The Squirtle hangtags, insoles, and tongue tags further pay respect to the beginning of Pokémon.

The Puma Suede Pokémon Squirtle became a broader collection of Pokémon x PUMA Suede sneakers on November 12, 2022 with a recommended retail price of $80.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Moonbeam
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Moonbeam
description:
The New Balance 990v3 MIUSA Moonbeam Macadamia features a tonal brown suede and mesh upper with grey leather piping, black New Balance logos, and reflective detailing. At the base, the responsive ENCAP midsole offers step-in comfort, maximizing its utility as a daily driver.

The New Balance 990v3 MIUSA Moonbeam Macadamia released in June of 2022 and retailed for $200.

name: Oil (Kids)
title: adidas Yeezy Desert Boot Oil (Kids)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Desert Boot Oil (Kids) is a military-inspired boot released in part of a continuous collaborative effort between adidas and the Yeezy brand which was founded by popular artist Kanye West.

The shoe has a high-top silhouette and features a minimalistic upper made from a combination of leather, suede, and mesh materials. It has a dark earthy-toned colorway that covers the entire shoe, giving it a rugged monochromatic aesthetic. The Yeezy Desert Boot also has a classic lacing system with a padded collar to keep your ankles secure and comfortable.

One thing our experts love about the adidas Yeezy Desert Boot Oil (Kids) is the rubber sole unit which is reinforced to protect your feet even when walking on the roughest terrain and keep them dry when navigating wet or muddy areas. The kids-sized shoe was released at the retail price of $130 on 14th September 2019.

name: Rock (Infants)
title: adidas Yeezy Desert Boot Rock (Infants)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Desert Boot Rock (Infant) is a shoe for young kids created in a collaboration between adidas and Kanye West’s Yeezy brand.

The Rock adidas Yeezy Desert Boot has a military-inspired silhouette in a Rock colorway, reminiscent of a rocky landscape. The upper of this shoe combines suede, mesh, and nubuck. The nubuck and suede materials seen on the toe, eyelet, and heel provide rugged reliability, and the mesh enhances breathability in different climates. The rigged rubber outsoles maintain this monochromatic pattern, guaranteeing maximum durability, ample traction, and stability. Meanwhile, the thick midsole adds to the comfort and cushioning of feet. This sneaker also has reflective elements on the pull tab, tongue, and rope laces.

Our experts consider the best feature of the adidas Yeezy Desert Boot Rock (Infant) to be the 3M stripe running along the length of the tongue. The shoe was released on September 14th, 2019, retailing at $85.

name: Core Black Red (Kids)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Core Black Red (Kids)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Core Black Red Kids is a sneaker that resulted from a collaboration between adidas and Yeezy.

The adidas Yeezy features a distinct center stitching on its upper as well as the signature ribbed outsoles. The sneakers have a black and core-red colorway. In addition, there's a core-black "SPLY-350" branding across a scorching hot core-red stripe on both sides. The sneaker is mainly designed for kids and comes in a variety of sizes.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Core Black Red Kids was released on August 2, 2022, at a retail price of $160.

name: Salehe Bembury Universal Communication Workwear White
title: New Balance 574 YURT Salehe Bembury Universal Communication Workwear White
description:
The New Balance 574 YURT Salehe Bembury Universal Communication Workwear Bone Pink combines colors and materials in a hiking shoe-like sneaker.

This Bembury/New Balance collab features a pink mesh upper with cream-colored suede overlays. Hits of bright blue leather appear on the forefoot and toe box, with a matching blue nylon tongue. The heel and midsole rollbar are maroon TPU, while the medial side of the toecap is maroon leather. The sock lining, leather N on the quarter, midsole hits, and speckled rubber of the outsole are all bright pink. This shoe features SBS ABZORB cushioning and a working rescue whistle on the heel.

The New Balance 574 YURT Salehe Bembury Universal Communication Workwear Bone Pink was released in April 2022 for $150 retail.

name: Shadow
title: New Balance 550 Shadow
description:
The New Balance 550 Shadow features a black and grey leather upper with mesh paneling around the collars. A puffed New Balance logo and "550" branding on the quarter panels nods to the origins of New Balance's basketball line. At the base, a white midsole with a black and grey outsole completes the design.

The New Balance 550 Shadow released in 2021 and retailed for $110.

name: Aime Leon Dore Natural Green
title: New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Natural Green
description:
Streetwear label Aime Leon Dore adds their touch yet again to the New Balance 550. Still holding true to its vintage aesthetic, their 2021 collaboration presented two new colorways, one of which donning a Natural Green look.

The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Natural Green features smooth white leather uppers. Natural Green leather overlays are on the collar, heel, and inner lining. A pilled, yellow leather "N" logo is embossed on each side of the sneaker. Bringing it all together is a off-white, Natural Green, and yellow outsole.

The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Natural Green released in April of 2021 for $130.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Raw Amethyst
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Raw Amethyst
description:
The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Raw Amethyst name is related to the amethyst crystal. This is why the sneaker's colorway is primarily purple suede overlay. 

The purple suede overlay on the New Balance 990v3 Santis Raw Amethyst is complemented with a tongue logo and a red-colored letter "N" accent. Additionally, the sneaker has black inserts that wonderfully complement the navy mesh base layer and give the model a lot of flair. The midsole of this sneaker is pre-whitened.

New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Raw Amethyst, at the time of its debut on July 15th, 2022, had a suggested retail price of $200.

name: White Mid Grey Lime Green
title: ASICS Gel-1130 White Mid Grey Lime Green
description:
The ASICS Gel-1130 White Mid Grey Lime Green is a performance shoe inspired by the Gel Kayano 14 model.

This version of the ASICS Gel-1130 features a white mesh upper for breathability and air flow. Polyurethane overlays in silver form the toe cap and mudguard and run up to the eyestays. The typical ASICS design is formed across each side in overlays of black, white, and gray. A Mid Grey overlay also runs from the bottom of the laces back to the heel of the lateral side, gaining Lime Green accents as it reaches the heel collar. The tongue features ASICS branding, and the shoe sits on a white rubber midsole with Lime Green supports at the arches. The heel is infused with Gel technology.

What we like best about this shoe are the Lime Green accents, which add a pop of color to the otherwise monotone shoe. The ASICS Gel-1130 White Mid Grey Lime Green was released on July 1, 2023, for $95.

name: Black Taupe
title: New Balance 1906R Black Taupe
description:
The New Balance 1906R Black Taupe gives a refined look to some of the heritage details borrowed from the 2002R and the 860v2. This updated hybrid sneaker is then dressed in an arresting colorway.

The streamlined Black Taupe New Balance 1906R features an upper that starts with a base of airy black mesh that reduces the weight of the sneaker and promotes maximum air flow. Black suede overlays course across the upper in asymmetrical patterns. A black TPU heel counter provides rear foot stability, while an N-Lock lacing system helps support the midfoot. The midsole in shades of vanilla is composed of ACTEVA LITE cushioning as well as ABZORB SBS cushioning in the heel. N-ergy in the midsole and outsole absorbs shock, while the outsole Stretchweb technology helps provide arch support.

Our favorite standout detail on this pair of kicks is the branding that hits the heel. Rather than a conventional flying NB, this is a small NB framed by a red square outline, giving the shoe a look of distinction. The New Balance 1906R Black Taupe was released on August 29, 2022, for $120 retail.

name: Soft Vision
title: adidas Yeezy 500 Soft Vision
description:
Yeezy has expanded its line of 500 designs with the adidas Yeezy 500 Soft Vision, now available on StockX. Among the many silhouettes Yeezy has continuously added new colorways to, this year has been a year of growth of the 500.
This Yeezy 500 is composed of a soft vision mesh, leather, and suede upper. A gum rubber outsole completes the design. These sneakers released in November of 2019 and retailed for $200.

name: J. Crew Incense
title: New Balance 2002R J. Crew Incense
description:
Since its debut, the New Balance 2002R J Crew Incense continues to record high sells within the Crew Incense catalog.

The New Balance 2002R J Crew Incense upper is a synthetic leather product dressed with an incense or heliotrope colorway with a mesh netting at the vamp and collar. The quarter panel, heel tab, and lining of the New Balance 2002R J Crew Incense are dressed in a slate grey. The heel is embellished with vibrant purple and blue with a suede style that mixes coffee tones and tan.

New Balance 2002R J Crew Incense became available on September 9, 2021, at a retail price of $140.

name: Aime Leon Dore Taupe
title: New Balance 993 Aime Leon Dore Taupe
description:
The New Balance 993 Aimé Leon Dore Taupe features a blue mesh and taupe premium pig suede upper with dark purple tumbled leather overlays. At the base, a black responsive ABZORB midsole and rubber outsole adds support. Aimé Leon Dore branding on the heels and inserts complete the design.

The New Balance 993 Aimé Leon Dore Taupe released in November of 2021 and retailed for $200.

name: Onyx Reflective
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Onyx Reflective
description:
The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Onyx Reflective is a part of the adidas Yeezy Boost series, designed in collaboration between adidas and very notable figure, Kanye West.

The Yeezy adidas Boost 380 Onyx Reflective upper is composed of a semi-translucent woven material and is engineered using Primeknit technology for flexibility. The shoe features reflective detailing and has a rubber sole that is made from adidas' patented Boost technology. The sneaker is designed with an onyx colorway and black and round races. The shoe also features a sock-like fit, with a distinctive pattern throughout the upper.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Onyx Reflective were released on November 27, 2020 at a retail price of $250.

name: Aime Leon Dore Brown Suede
title: New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Brown Suede
description:
The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Brown Suede is a collaborative sneaker from the New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore lineup in a brown suede colorway.

This ALD x New Balance 550 sneaker features an upper made of a Sandstone canvas textile base and True Brown hairy suede overlays. New Balance’s signature "N" logo is etched on the sides in a matching True Brown hue with a Taupe outline. Other details include a co-branded tongue, white laces, "550" branding on the sides, and more co-branding on the insoles and the heel with the Aimé Leon Dore basketball logo on the heel and insole of the left shoe and the "NB" logo on both areas in the right shoe. An aged Cream midsole and an Off-White rubber outsole complete the design. Each pair comes with an extra set of brown and Sail laces. 

Something we love about this ALD x New Balance collaboration is its high-quality materials and distinctive colorway, which contribute to its stylish and versatile appeal. The New Balance 550 Aime Leon Dore Brown Suede was released on May 8th, 2023, retailing at $130.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Black True Camo
title: New Balance 990v2 MiUSA Teddy Santis Black True Camo
description:
The New Balance 990v2 Black True Camo features a plush black suede and grey mesh upper with dark grey suede piping and New Balance logo patches. Heel tabs with "USA" embroidery nods to the Made in USA collection, which is composed of at least 70% US-grown materials. From there, a signature Abzorb midsole provides cushioning at the base.

The New Balance 990v2 Black True Camo released in July of 2022 and retailed for $195.

name: Antlia (Non-Reflective)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Antlia (Non-Reflective)
description:
Exclusive to Europe for its retail release, the Antlia Yeezy Boost 350 V2 is now available to customers around the world on StockX. Following successful regional releases of the Clay, Trfrm, and Hyperspace colorways, along with the universal popularity of the glow and black 350 V2s, the Antlia Yeezy Boost 350 V2 looks to be another summer ready Yeezy.

This 350 V2 comes with a Primeknit upper that combines canary yellow and cool grey tones, sits on top of a gum sole, removes the traditional heel tab, and has the translucent side stripe which has become a staple of the V2 line. These sneakers released in June of 2019 for $220.

name: Urbancore Silver
title: New Balance 1906R Urbancore Silver
description:
The New Balance 1906R Urbancore Silver is a technical running shoe with a performance-first design and a futuristic colorway of silver and white.

The Urbancore Silver New Balance 1906R running shoe features tooling found in the 2002R and 860v2, including N-ergy cushioning for absorbing shock and flexible ACTEVA LITE cushioning for added softness underfoot. Other high-tech additions include segmented ABZORB SBS pods that increase energy return in the heel area. The upper is constructed from large-holed mesh in white with synthetic leather overlays in metallic silver. Instead of coming in a straight design, the overlays bend into a slight curve for better support that follows the natural shape of the foot.

Our experts at StockX like how the sneaker combines technical elements while maintaining a refined aesthetic. In particular, the sleek lines created by the overlays lend themselves to the shiny metallic silver. The New Balance 1906R Urbancore Silver was released on April 3, 2023, and retailed at $155.

name: Clear Brown
title: adidas Yeezy Powerphase Clear Brown
description:
The adidas Yeezy Powerphase Clear Brown was designed by Kanye West as part of a continued collaboration with adidas.

The shoe is primarily brown with a leather and suede upper featuring perforated detailing on the side in the same pattern as the three stripes synonymous with adidas, as well as the adidas logo and "Calabasas" branding in Gold Foil. It has a rubber outsole which features some stitching detail on the front and back plus more adidas branding on the base of the heel.

The adidas Yeezy Powerphase Clear Brown was first made available for retail at the price of $120 on September 18, 2019.

name: MiUSA Kith Daytona (with Socks)
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Kith Daytona (with Socks)
description:
The next version of the renowned New Balance 990v3 series debuted in 2013 as the New Balance 990v3 Kith Daytona. It has become one of the most coveted colorways in the New Balance 990 series catalog.

The New Balance 990v3 Kith Daytona displays sand suede quarters and an ocean blue toe box. It also features a deep tan heel counter, which is present at the back. The iconic "N" from New Balance is draped in vibrant pink.

The New Balance 990v3 Kith Daytona was originally released in June of 2022 at a retail price of $235.

name: Kith United Arrows & Sons (with Socks)
title: New Balance 990v4 Kith United Arrows & Sons (with Socks)
description:
Since the debut of the 997s model in 2018, the New Balance 990v4 x Kith United Arrows & Sons has become popular among all genders and sizes.

New Balance 990v4 x Kith United Arrows & Sons is made of pigskin suede with pony hair accents and extended blacks. New Balance 990v4 x Kith United Arrows & Sons' upper is dressed in a gray, purple, pink, and black colorway with a mesh netting at the vamp. It features a black rubber outsole and a 990 figure at the side of the heel counter. The New Balance "N" symbol rests at the quarter panel of this sneaker.

New Balance 990v4 x Kith United Arrows & Sons was released on July 15, 2022, at a retail price of $235.

name: Joe Freshgoods Inside Voices Baby Shower Blue
title: New Balance 9060 Joe Freshgoods Inside Voices Baby Shower Blue
description:
Released as a Joe Freshgoods exclusive, the New Balance 9060 Joe Freshgoods Inside Voices Baby Shower Blue features a pale yellow mesh construction with Baby Shower Blue suede overlays and gold New Balance logos. At the heel, subtle "Inside Voices'' embroidery is prominent in a monotone style. From there, hits of pink on the sockliner and sculptural sole add the finishing touch.

The New Balance 9060 Joe Freshgoods Inside Voices Baby Shower Blue released in May of 2022 and retailed for $180.

name: Frozen Blue
title: adidas Yeezy QNTM BSKTBL Frozen Blue
description:
The adidas Yeezy QNTM BSKTBL Frozen Blue is a basketball-inspired mid-top sneaker from the adidas Yeezy QNTM lineup in a Frozen Blue color scheme.

The sneaker upper comprises a White/Grey mesh and textile knit base, a suede toebox, and Rigid Polyurethane (RPU) overlays in Frozen Blue wavy lines. Other details include a Black neoprene-padded collar and a seamless Black/Grey/White heel counter extending to the sole unit. A semi-translucent TPU midsole with full-length BOOST cushioning and a Creamy rubber outsole round out the design.

The adidas Yeezy QNTM BSKTBL Frozen Blue was made available on December 23rd, 2020. Initially, it retailed at $250.

name: White Natural Indigo
title: New Balance 2002R White Natural Indigo
description:
The New Balance 2002R White Natural Indigo has a low-top leather upper designed for casual or competitive running. Many of the sneaker's features were borrowed from the earlier New Balance shoe, such as its colored or dark blue accents and use of mesh for ventilation in the upper structure and toe cap.

It has special cushioning for comfort and shock protection for better performance when running on the track, streets, or the treadmill. The New Balance symbol is on the upper sidewalls, and the NB logo is on the heel. The 2002R emblem is also added to the design for brand identity.

The New Balance 2002R White Natural Indigo has a black rubber outsole that enhances its style and provides great traction and durability. Our team is most impressed with this shoe's classic and clean look. New Balance released this running shoe on September 20, 2022. It originally retailed for $140.

name: Mist Slate
title: adidas Yeezy 500 High Mist Slate
description:
The adidas Yeezy 500 High Mist Slate was released as part of Kanye West's collaborative line with adidas.

The Yeezy adidas 500 High Mist Slate is made from a mixed upper composed of cow suede, premium leather, and elastane. The upper has a molded construction that provides support and comfort, while the padded collar adds additional cushioning. It also features a colorway that is primarily Mist Slate and Anthracite on the midsole, with gum rubber detailing on the outsole. The shoe also has an oversized adiPRENE+ midsole, which provides extra cushioning, and the outsole is made of rubber, with a herringbone pattern that provides traction on a variety of surfaces.

The adidas Yeezy 500 High Mist Slate was released on February 8th, 2021, at a retail price of $220.

name: MiUSA Joe Freshgoods 1998 Keisha Blue
title: New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods 1998 Keisha Blue
description:
The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods 1998 Keisha Blue is a vibrant blue colorway from the co-branded New Balance and Joe Freshgoods line featuring the 990v4 silhouette.

The Keisha Blue colorway was released as part of a three pack, together with the other two colorways named Intro and Outro, they made up the "1998 Pack." Made in the USA (MiUSA), the mainly suede upper is a bold blue color that pairs well with the black accents. Where there isn’t suede, there is breathable mesh, also in tonal blue that ensures the foot stays crisp and cool. Iconic "N" logos in black are on both sides and JFG branding is seen on the lateral right heel.

What we love about this shoe are the lime mint shoelaces, which add a bit of light to an otherwise dark colored sneaker. When it debuted on December 15, 2023, the New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Joe Freshgoods 1998 Keisha Blue colorway sold at retail price of $220.

name: Grey (GS)
title: New Balance 990v5 Grey (GS)
description:
Now sporting fewer but larger mesh breathable zones, the New Balance 990 v5 Grey (GS) arrives in grade school sizing.

The New Balance 990 v5 Grey (GS) upper is crafted from pig suede with breathable mesh in targeted areas and 360 reflective accents for added safety in low-light running conditions. The shoe maintains the clean silhouette from previous generations but adds a plastic power strap component on the sides near the ankle area. Additionally, the encap midsole support area gets a PU Ring for a sleeker design.

The New Balance 990 v5 Grey (GS) was released in May 2019 and retailed for $110.

name: White Pure Silver Slate Grey Sage
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 White Pure Silver Slate Grey Sage
description:
The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 White Pure Silver Slate Grey is a running shoe that is part of ASICS' Gel-Kayano series, known for its stability and support features.

The shoes have a predominantly grey color scheme with silver overlays. The upper is crafted using mesh and synthetic materials for their breathability and lightweight properties. It also uses FluidFit technology, which is designed to adapt to the runner's foot for a personalized fit. The midsole of the shoe is white with green gel units and the outsole fully black with a pattern to improve grip and traction when running on different surfaces.

One thing we like about the shoes is the midsole, which uses a combination of Gel cushioning and ASICS' FlyteFoam technology, a lightweight and responsive foam, to provide cushioning without adding extra weight to the shoe. The ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 White Pure Silver Slate Grey was released for retail on the 26th of January, 2023, priced at $150.

name: Mist Reflective
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Mist Reflective
description:
Yeezy added a new colorway to their Boost 380 product line with the adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Mist Reflective, now available on StockX. This model was originally known to be the Yeezy Boost 350 V3, but upon release it was given its own silhouette name. The mist colorway released in both reflective and non-reflective variations.

This 380 Mist Reflective features a reflective Mist Primeknit pattern on its upper and lacks the traditional lateral side stripe. An upgraded translucent Boost midsole and engineered gum outsole grip complete the design. These sneakers released in February of 2020 and retailed for $250.

name: Phenom
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Phenom
description: The Puma LaMelo Ball MB02 Phenom is a highly anticipated basketball sneaker that is set to release on November 23, 2022, with a retail price of $130. This sneaker is designed to meet the needs of basketball players who demand both style and performance. The upper of the Puma LaMelo Ball MB02 Phenom is made of a combination of synthetic leather and mesh, which provides both durability and breathability. The midsole is made of Puma's proprietary foam, which offers excellent cushioning and support. The outsole is made of rubber, which provides excellent traction on the court. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB02 Phenom comes in a sleek black and white colorway, with subtle Puma branding on the side and tongue. The design is simple yet stylish, making it a versatile sneaker that can be worn both on and off the court. Something we love about the Puma LaMelo Ball MB02 Phenom is its combination of style and performance. Our experts think that the best features of this sneaker are its durable upper, comfortable midsole, and excellent traction. We also love the sleek black and white colorway, which makes it a versatile sneaker that can be worn with a variety of outfits. Overall, the standout feature of the Puma LaMelo Ball MB02 Phenom is its ability to meet the needs of basketball players who demand both style and performance.

name: Concepts Low Hanging Fruit
title: New Balance 992 Concepts Low Hanging Fruit
description:
Boston-based boutique CONCEPTS and New Balance joined forces to honor pioneering fruit seller Frieda Rapoport Caplan, also known as the "Kiwi Queen", with the New Balance 992 Low Hanging Fruit.

In the 1990s, the entrepreneurial spirit of Frieda Rapoport Caplan helped the kiwi become the most celebrated exotic commercial fruit. In commemoration of this history, the New Balance 992 Low Hanging Fruit takes cues from the kiwi with its hairy brown suede upper with hits of neon green. A strawberry graphic foot bed nods to the intertwining relationship of the two fruits.

The New Balance 992 Low Hanging Fruit released in November of 2021 and retailed for $240.

DISALCAIMER: Please note that the majority of these shoes come in the normal New Balance MiUSA box an not the Concepts special box. Special boxes are only guaranteed on product pages that specifically note "Special Box" in the product name.

name: Navy White Beige
title: New Balance 574 Navy White Beige
description:
The New Balance 574 Navy White Beige has a streamlined design and an iconic toe shape.
 
This version of the New Balance 574 has an upper made of dark gray textile on the toe box and around the ankles, and thick overlays of navy suede. These overlays round out the toe and cross the sides, also where the New Balance "N" appears outlined in white. The heel features a beige support with New Balance branding on the bottom and a white heel collar with the "New Balance" in a burgundy color. The tongue also contains gold NB branding. Polyurethane foam forms the midsole, and a black outsole completes the look.

In our opinion, what stands out about this shoe is the foam midsole, which provides cushioning and energy return. The New Balance 574 Navy White Beige was released on July 30, 2022, for a retail price of $85.

name: White Sea Salt
title: New Balance 2002R White Sea Salt
description:
The New Balance 2002R White Sea Salt is a colorway of the NB 2002R, first released in 2010.

Dressed in a white, sea salt, and raw cashew color scheme, this sneaker features an upper with a grey mesh base contrasted with white leather overlays. Its upper sits on a cream rubber midsole, which, in turn, lays on a grey rubber outsole. Detail-wise, it boasts 2002R branding on the lateral ankle, slanted signature "N" logo on its sidewalls, and New Balance Running branding on its tongue tag.

The New Balance 2002R White Sea Salt made its debut on 4th August 2022. Originally, this sneaker retailed at $170.

name: Black Grey Suede
title: New Balance 992 Black Grey Suede
description:
The New Balance 992 Black Grey Suede arrives in a black and gray color palette.

The New Balance 992 Black Grey Suede upper is constructed from black suede and grey accents, and it is adorned with white leather with an "N" emblem on both lateral sides. The shoe features a black rubber outsole and a white midsole with gray embellishments. The midsole is constructed of ENCAP technology, which provides stability and cushioning. In addition, the shoe has a padded tongue and collar to provide more comfort.

The New Balance 992 Black Grey Suede was released on April 23rd, 2021, for a retail price of $175.

name: Bordeaux
title: New Balance 2002R Bordeaux
description:
The New Balance 2002R Bordeaux is a throwback silhouette running-inspired design.

The New Balance 2002R Bordeaux's upper comprises a premium pig suede and breathable mesh. This sets a tonal arrangement of deep red mesh at the base, wine red suede overlays, and light red accents on top. It also features a prominent silver N logo on the outer side, accompanied by adjustable white lace closure for a secure fit. The off-white rubber midsole is made of ABZORB cushioning technology, while the N-ergy outsole has Stability Web support for a foot arch.

The New Balance released the 2002R Bordeaux on 15th February 2022 at a retail price of $130.

name: Bone White (2019)
title: adidas Yeezy 500 Bone White (2019)
description:
Yeezy expands its 500 color pallette once again with the adidas Yeezy 500 "Bone White", now available on StockX. Despite an existing long line of Yeezy 500s assorted in five colorways, the "Bone White" colorway is the first 500 to release in 2019.

This 500 features a bone white mesh upper with suede overlays. Its chunky midsole is inspired by the Adidas KB3 atop a tonal-cream outsole completes the design. These sneakers released in August of 2019 and retailed for $200.

name: White Black
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Lo White Black
description: The Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 Lo White Black is a sleek and stylish sneaker that combines performance and fashion. The upper is made of premium leather and features a black and white colorway that is both classic and modern. The midsole is made of lightweight foam that provides cushioning and support, while the outsole is made of durable rubber that offers traction and grip. The Puma logo is prominently displayed on the side of the shoe, adding a touch of branding to the design. This sneaker was released on October 27, 2022, and retails for $120. Whether you're hitting the court or the streets, the Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 Lo White Black is a versatile and stylish choice.

name: Blue Haze
title: New Balance 530 Blue Haze
description:
At first glance, it's clear that New Balance used some of its late 1990s and early 2000s models as inspiration for the New Balance 530 Blue Haze. But it includes a variety of modern features that make it look right at home in the present day.

This New Balance 530 has a light blue suede upper that is accented with mesh panels to make it more aesthetically pleasing, while also making the sneaker as a whole more breathable. It has a white ABZORB midsole as well that is designed to provide the sneaker with more cushioning and comfort. The sneaker is finished off with a convenient pull tab on the heel and the usual New Balance "N" branding on both sides.

Our experts appreciate that New Balance found a way to blend the old with the new when creating this sneaker. It gives the sneaker a more timeless appearance overall. The New Balance 530 Blue Haze was released on February 14, 2023, when it retailed for $95.

name: AURALEE Bone White
title: New Balance 1906R AURALEE Bone White
description:
The New Balance 1906R AURALEE Bone White is a lightweight running shoe. Its low-top silhouette is made of a combination of mesh, suede, and leather for enhanced style. Further embellishments include decorative outlays and a wavy outsole.

This shoe comes from a collaboration with Nike and the Auralee fashion label. The look of this athletic shoe is inspired by the earlier NB 1906 sneakers. However, its monochromatic color palette of shades of beige is very modern and fashion-forward. In addition to its mesh body, which gives it plenty of breathability, details like plush lining and added cushioning in the center and on the heel provide exceptional comfort and protection for your feet, ankles, and heels.

The New Balance 1906R AURALEE Bone White has the iconic logo on the sidewalls and toe of the shoe. New Balance released this shoe on October 11, 2023. It originally retailed for $170.

name: Rich Earth (Women's)
title: New Balance 327 Rich Earth (Women's)
description:
The New Balance 327 Rich Earth (Women's) borrows a '70s running shoe aesthetic and infuses it with features from various NB running silhouettes. The result is an eye-catching, high-performance running and lifestyle sneaker specifically sized for women.

The Rich Earth colorway of the Women's New Balance 327 features an upper of tightly woven brown textile overlaid with darker brown suede at the eyestays, toe cap, mud guard, and heel. An oversized white suede N adorns each side panel and matches the tongue and sock liners and insole. NB branding appears on the tongue patch and insole, while New Balance is written out along the medial heel overlay.

What we enjoy most about this sneaker is the sole unit designed for comfort and traction. The flared white foam midsole flecked with brown provides cushioning with every step. Inspired by the 320, 355, and Supercomp, the brown rubber outsole sneaks up the toe and all the way up the heel. The New Balance 327 Rich Earth (Women's) debuted on February 9, 2023, for $100 retail.

name: Dazzling Blue (Kids)
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Dazzling Blue (Kids)
description:
This adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Dazzling Blue (Kids) updates the casual sneaker with a bold flash of color.

The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Dazzling Blue (Kids) features rope laces that secure the black Primeknit upper, featuring sock-like construction designed to hug the foot in flexible support. ‘SPLY-350’ is printed on a streak of royal blue that livens up the sneaker’s lateral side. The lightweight upper sits atop a full-length Boost midsole, wrapped in a smoky TPU cage and exposed through cut-outs in the durable rubber outsole.

The kid-sized adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Dazzling Blue (Kids) was released in February 2022 and retailed for $160.

name: Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Powder Pink
title: New Balance 993 Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Powder Pink
description:
The New Balance 993 Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Powder Pink is a collaboration between Joe Freshgoods and New Balance.

The Performance Art Powder Pink New Balance 993 Joe Freshgoods comes in a powder pink colorway. The upper is made from a combination of materials, such as suede and mesh, to ensure both sturdiness and comfort. The shoe's cushioned midsole offers responsive cushioning, comfort, and support. The sneaker's rubber outsole is slip-resistant and durable. The sneaker features an "N" insignia on either side, "new balance Made in USA 993 N" on the tongue, and "993" on one side of the heel. The shoe's design is completed with "JFG" branding on the heel.

The New Balance 993 Joe Freshgoods Performance Art Powder Pink was released on October 7, 2022, and retailed for $220.

name: Triple Black
title: New Balance XC-72 Triple Black
description:
The New Balance XC-72 Triple Black takes a silhouette inspired by concept cars from the 1970s, adds New Balance signature touches, and dresses it in a stealthy colorway of Unrelieved Black.

The Triple Black iteration of the New Balance XC-72 features an upper with a base of nylon mesh that offers a lightweight, breathable feel. A ribbed overlay at the heel provides structure as well as singular style. Suede-like synthetic overlays adorn the toecap and eyestays, while synthetic leather comprises the signature side-panel N.

The most impressive and eye-catching part of this sneaker is its sole unit. The black foam midsole extends past the heel to create a rear bumper. The black rubber outsole with thick traction lugs curves all the way up to the top of the upper on both the lateral and medial sides of the forefoot. The New Balance XC-72 Triple Black was released on March 4th, 2022, for a retail price of $100.

name: Kith Cream Scarab (2023)
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Kith Cream Scarab (2023)
description:
The ASICS Gel Kayano 14 Kith Cream Scarab presents a sophisticated color palette to the casual running sneaker, launching as part of a collaborative quartet of designs.

Drawing inspiration from the late 2000s vibe, the Cream Scarab ASICS Gel Kayano 14 Kith's upper melds glossy synthetic leather overlays in a reflective silver hue with an airy off-white mesh backdrop. Eye-catching pops of color emerge from the signature side stripes painted in a rich green shade. The EVA midsole, lightweight in nature, receives a traditional treatment and houses visible Gel cushioning in the heel, guaranteeing a comfortable and seamless encounter.

At StockX, we are particularly enamored with the Gel Kayano 14 Kith Cream Scarab's innovative Gel cushioning technology. This feature offers exceptional support and shock absorption, perfect for individuals seeking comfort during their daily activities. The ASICS Gel Kayano 14 Kith Cream Scarab was released on the 23rd of June, 2023, at a retail price of $160.

name: MiUSA Grey Day (2023)
title: New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Grey Day (2023)
description:
The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Grey Day (2023) is an eye-catching collaboration between the renowned sneaker company and designer Teddy Santis, founder of the fashion brand Aime Leon Dore.

This classic New Balance silhouette is built upon an upper base of off-white mesh that provides maximum airflow and lightweight comfort. Gray hairy suede overlays adorn the toe cap, heel, side panel, and eye stays. These overlays are lined and accented with a medium blue leather that complements the medium blue side-panel N outlined in white. The white matches the laces and the mesh sock liner. The midsole, which is made of shades of vanilla and white, is comprised of cushy ENCAP for a springy bounce with every step. The grippy outsole features a ring of black rubber that surrounds pods of vanilla-colored rubber.

The detail we enjoy most about this premium pair of sneakers is the vanilla-colored suede heel tab, which hearkens back to the hits of vanilla on the midsole and outsole and ties together the look of this shoe. The New Balance 990v4 MiUSA Grey Day (2023) was released on May 12th, 2023, for a retail price of $210.

name: Ivory Cream Pink Sand
title: New Balance 9060 Ivory Cream Pink Sand
description:
The New Balance 9060 Ivory Cream Pink Sand upper is made of a meshed undercover with suede and fabricated reflective overlays.

The colorway of the sneaker includes ivory cream with pink sand covering the upper and light moon stones running along the heel and the side panel. The "N" logo is also printed on the mudguard. Other than that, the NB signature symbol is embroidered on the rear of the tongue and at the back of the shoes. The midsole of the shoes is carved with ABZORB, ENCAP, and SBS cushioning. 

The New Balance 9060 Ivory Cream Pink Sand was released on December 6th, 2022, and retailed for $150.

name: Marsh
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Marsh
description:
Yeezy adds another colorway of its most well-known design with the adidas Yeezy 350 Marsh, now available on StockX. This 350 V2 picks up where the Antlia colorway left off, sporting yellow tones that have been prevalent in Yeezy’s palette. This model was released as a Yeezy Supply exclusive.

This Yeezy 350 V2 Marsh is composed of a bright yellow Primeknit upper with a reflective outer side stripe. A translucent Boost cushioned sole and gold interior completes the design. These sneakers released in February of 2020 and retailed for $220.

name: Teal Blue
title: adidas Yeezy QNTM Teal Blue
description:
Yeezy added a new colorway to their QNTM line with the Yeezy QNTM Teal Blue, now on StockX. The QNTM is the first of its kind to stray away from primarily grey uppers by adding hits of teal to provide the aquatic vibes.

The Yeezy QNTM Teal Blue features a marbled olive Primeknit upper with teal blue and dark grey accents woven in. Unlike the performance model, this lifestyle design does not feature additional TPU caging on the upper for a more relaxed fit. A black reflective heel, dark grey toe guard, and translucent white sole midsole complete the design.

The Yeezy QNTM Teal Blue released in October of 2020 and retailed for $250.

name: Rookie Of The Year
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Rookie Of The Year
description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB02 Rookie Of The Year is a collaborative sneaker between the iconic lifestyle brand and this rising star in the NBA.
​
​Inspired by the Buzz City colorway, the Rookie of the Year version features a Blue Atoll woven mesh upper sporting LaMelo’s signature wings in Ultra Blue and White. Atoll Blue also comprises the foam-infused NITRO midsole, TPU heel clip, and rubber outsole, while the player´s branding on the tongue and heel, and "ROTY" (As in Rookie Of The Year") on the outsole are Ultra Blue.
​
​The Puma LaMelo Ball MB02 Rookie Of The Year debuted on December 9th, 2022 for $130 retail.

name: Aime Leon Dore Blue
title: New Balance 860v2 Aime Leon Dore Blue
description:
The New Balance 860v2 Aime Leon Dore Blue sneaker is a collaborative effort between New Balance and Aimé Leon Dore. New Balance hired Teddy Santis, founder of Aimé Leon Dore, to be the creative director for their MADE in USA line that launched in 2021.

The shoe nods to each company in its design. It has New Balance’s iconic "N" logo set against the backdrop of a cream mesh upper with silver and tan overlays. It also has "Aimé Leon Dore" inscribed on the sneaker’s tongue, as well as Aimé Leon Dore’s floral motif on the heel.

There is a lot to like about this New Balance 860v2 Aime Leon Dore Blue collaboration. Our experts believe the busyness of its design works in its favor. It injects new life into a New Balance shoe that sometimes gets overlooked and introduced many New Balance fans to Aimé Leon Dore for the first time. The New Balance 860v2 Aimé Leon Dore was released on 4th April 2023 and retailed for $150.

name: MiUSA Teddy Santis Scarlet
title: New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Scarlet
description:
The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Scarlet is a modern iteration of the classic 990, designed by Teddy Santis, the creative mind behind the nostalgia-drenched menswear line Aimé Leon Dore.

Like many other 990 renditions, this rendition boasts a straightforward presentation. Its scarlet shade is visible across the base layer as it masks the pigskin suede overlays from the forefront to the rear. The suede overlays are contrasted by burgundy mesh, thin Marblehead suede overlays, and New Balance branding. This shoe’s upper is anchored by an ENCAP midsole, white towards the foot and  Marblehead towards the rear, and a black rubber outsole.

The New Balance 990v3 MiUSA Teddy Santis Scarlet was released on 28th July 2022. Originally, its retail price was $200.

name: Beluga
title: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Beluga
description: The adidas Yeezy 350 Boost V2 takes the silhouette that Kanye West made famous for adidas Originals and gives it new life. The Yeezy Boost releases have been some of the most notable driving forces in the resurgence of adidas' popularity around the world. The low top Yeezy Boost 350 features a full length Boost cushioning system and a high end feel that has made it the go-to sneaker for everyone from celebrities like Kim Kardashian-West, Jay-Z, 2 Chainz and Future, as well as for athletes like Nick "Swaggy P" Young, Andrew Wiggins, Lewis Hamilton and anyone else who can get their feet in a pair. The Yeezy Boost 350 V2 adds a bold twist to Kanye's design with a bright orange (officially Solar Red) stripe across the Steel Grey/Beluga zebra-striped upper with the text YZY SPLY. The Steeple Gray/Beluga/Solar Red adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 is the first of the 2nd version colorways that release in 2016.

name: Bricks & Wood
title: New Balance 9060 Bricks & Wood
description:
The New Balance 9060 Bricks & Wood arrives in a beige, grey, and green color palette.

The New Balance 9060 Bricks & Wood has a mesh upper that is breathable and lightweight for comfort and breathability. The shoe's rubber outsole offers grip and stability. The shoe's midsole is designed to offer padding and comfort. The shoe's lacing system ensures a secure fit. Additionally, the shoe's tongue and collar are padded for comfort. The sneaker features an "N" emblem on the lateral sides.

The New Balance 9060 Bricks & Wood was released on January 20, 2023, and sold for a retail price of $180.

name: Vermillion (Kids)
title: adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Vermillion (Kids)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Vermilion (K) modernizes Kanye West's futuristic slip-on with a monochromatic color scheme. It features a molded foam upper and clog-like patterns.

The slip-on kid's shoe is Kanye West's continuous homage to the "Red October" colorway and expresses a tonal and vivid vermillion aspect. The slip-on is made with a design that is highlighted by a single piece of EVA foam that was made in part with algae that were produced hydroponically, in keeping with the brand. Several oval-shaped holes have been punched out of the vamp's upper and side panels to serve as aeration vents and give breathable comfort. The sculpted heel is designed to hug the back of the foot for a snug fit. For the best grip, the bottom of the shoe has a molded outsole with a wavy traction pattern rounding off its design.

This adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Vermilion (K) released on 29th October 2021 retailed at a price of $60.

name: Gore-Tex Navy Arctic Grey
title: New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Navy Arctic Grey
description:
The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Navy Arctic Gray paints the recognizable 2002R silhouette with a dark blue colorway of NB Navy, Arctic Gray, and Vintage Indigo. However, what makes this sneaker stand out is the addition of durable Gore-Tex material.

This performance running shoe boasts an upper made of mesh and soft suede. Gore-Tex waterproof fabric keeps the foot dry during rainy or snowy weather without decreasing the shoe’s breathability. Designed with performance in mind, the ABZORB midsole and the N-ergy outsole work in concert to decrease impact with every step. In addition, Stability Web technology underfoot provides arch support that spans the distance from the heel to the toe.

Something our experts like is the way the upper’s technical design pays homage to the running shoes of the early 2000s. The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Navy Arctic Gray was released on April 3rd, 2023, and retailed at $180.

name: Black Castlerock Incense
title: New Balance XC-72 Black Castlerock Incense
description:
The New Balance XC-72 Black Castlerock Incense showcases a striking blend of retro and modern influences, making it a standout design in the brand's catalog. Drawing inspiration from 1970s concept cars, this iteration features a sleek and angular design, embodying New Balance’s commitment to pushing boundaries in style and innovation.

This bold colorway of Black, Castlerock, and Incense creates a versatile yet eye-catching look with such tan tones. The Black mesh and suede upper provide a textured, layered aesthetic, complemented by Castlerock overlays for added structure. Meanwhile, Incense-colored accents on the sole and heel tab deliver subtle contrast, seamlessly tying the color palette together. The shoe’s split outsole is a nod to experimental design, offering dual traction patterns that enhance performance and grip on various surfaces.

Comfort is prioritized with the inclusion of a foam midsole for cushioning, ensuring all-day wearability. Something we love about the XC 72 Black Castlerock Incense is the forward-thinking approach to lifestyle footwear, combining function with modern fashion trends, and that's something we like about this shoe. The New Balance XC-72 Black Castlerock Incense was released on January 2o, 2022, and retailed at $120.

name: Joe Freshgoods Conversations Amongst Us
title: New Balance 550 Joe Freshgoods Conversations Amongst Us
description:
Joe Freshgoods and New Balance teamed up once again to deliver the New Balance 550 Joe Freshgoods Conversations Amongst Us.

The New Balance 550 Joe Freshgoods Conversations Amongst Us draws inspiration from crucial dialogues that connect the Black community. It features a simple cream canvas upper with hairy suede overlays and yellowed New Balance logos. At the base, a yellowed sole completes the design.

The New Balance 550 Joe Freshgoods Conversations Amongst Us released in April of 2022 and retailed for $120.

name: Grey Suede
title: New Balance 550 Grey Suede
description:
The New Balance 550 Grey Suede is a sneaker from the New Balance 550 lineup in a Grey Suede colorway.

This sneaker features a Grey Suede upper with White detailing on the leather collar, mesh ankle collar, the ‘N’ logo, padded mesh tongue, laces, and the New Balance heel branding. Other details include tiny perforations on the side and forefoot, a tonal ‘550’ branding close to the lower eyestays, and a branded tongue tag. A White branded midsole rests on a Cream rubber outsole. 

The New Balance 550 Grey Suede was released on November 1st, 2022, for a retail price of $120.

name: Grey Indigo
title: New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo
description:
Inspired by 2000s runners, the New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo is an iteration of the New Balance 1906R  in a ‘Grey Indigo’ colorway.

The upper is made of a Natural Indigo mesh base with Castlerock leather overlays. Other upper details include the Navy Blue ‘N’ logo on the sides with a Silver outline, ‘1906’ branding on the lateral, tongue and heel branding, and a TPU heel counter. The sole unit features ABZORB and N-ergy cushioning and a Navy Blue rubber outsole with multidirectional treads for traction.

The New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, for a retail price of $155.

name: JJJJound Silver Black
title: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 JJJJound Silver Black
description:
The ASICS Gel Kayano 14 JJJJound Silver Black was created in collaboration between the Montreal design studio and the Japanese sportswear brand. The shoe has retro-inspired color patterns.

These Gel Kayano 14 by ASICS in Silver Black sneakers give a Y2K-era performance footwear vibe from the synthetic leather upper combining white open mesh construction and contrasting black tiger stripes. The mismatched JJJJound and ASICS branding on the lateral heel and sock liner and the off-white accents midsoles complement this design. These shoes have GEL technology pockets in the forefoot and rearfoot for extra cushioning.

The ASICS Gel Kayano 14 JJJJound Silver Black was released in August 2022 for $180 as the retail price.

name: Prism Purple
title: New Balance 9060 Prism Purple
description:
The New Balance 9060 Prism Purple is a brightly colored variation of the original 9060 model that was designed for running. This vintage-inspired pair of shoes is made of breathable materials.
​
​This 9060 New Balance model has a body that is composed of a variety of mesh and plastic materials. There are multiple bright colors featured, including purple, orange, yellow, and blue. There are also a few light touches of Pastel Green that can be seen on the heel. On top of the body, there are bright orange shoelaces, as well as a New Balance logo in the same orange on the tongue.
​
​A component of the New Balance 9060 Prism Purple that our team of experts enjoys is the bright orange and Pastel Green New Balance ‘N’ symbol that provides contrast on the side of the shoe. This pair of shoes was first made available for purchase on July 1st, 2023, for a starting retail price of $150.

name: Rain Cloud
title: New Balance 2002R Rain Cloud
description:
The majority of the New Balance 2002R Rain Cloud upper is covered by a rain cloud hue, which flows over the hairy suede overlays that are situated on the toe tips, heels, and quarters.

The lower heels are equipped with perforations and "Sweet Caramel" heal counters, and the laces, breathable mesh underlays, and N emblems are all given an "Angora" color scheme. The midsoles are filled with N-ERGY cushioning to offer a stable and responsive ride. Further details include the raw-edged rain cloud exposed padded tongue with NB branded logo in sweet caramel, NB, and New balance text branding on the insoles.

The New Balance 2002R Rain Cloud was released on 12th August 2022 and retailed at $130.

name: Desert Sand (Kids)
title: adidas Yeezy Slide Desert Sand (Kids)
description:
The adidas Yeezy Slide Desert Sand (Kids) presents a simplistic and chic sandal design suitable for casual wear.

The kid-sized adidas Yeezy Slide features a subtle tan hue, contributing to its clean and uncomplicated appearance. Fashioned from robust EVA foam, the upper ensures enduring comfort and durability. The only visible branding comes from adidas' three-stripes logo debossed onto the soft footbed. Additionally, the outsole is engineered with strategically positioned horizontal grooves, enhancing both traction and comfort. This slide serves as a testament to the collaborative effort between adidas and Kanye West, seamlessly merging comfort with understated elegance.

The notable attribute of the adidas Yeezy Slide Desert Sand (Kids) resides in its sturdy construction using EVA foam. This aspect guarantees prolonged comfort and resilience, making the slide not only a stylish choice but also a practical option for everyday casual attire. The slide debuted on December 6, 2019, for $45.

name: JJJJound Grey
title: New Balance 992 JJJJound Grey
description:
The New Balance 992 JJJJound Grey comes in a brown and black colorway.

The New Balance 992 JJJJound adopts the classic silhouette portrayed in a black and cream colorway. The shoe's upper is constructed from suede and mesh, and the heel features a faint JJJJound insignia. The midsole is made using New Balance's distinctive ABZORB cushioning technology, which ensures comfortable and supportive wear by absorbing impacts and providing cushioning. The outsole is comprised of durable rubber that offers grip and stability.

The New Balance 992 JJJJound Grey was released on August 7th, 2020, for a retail price of $260.

name: Bodega Arrival
title: New Balance 574 Legacy Bodega Arrival
description:
The New Balance 574 Legacy Bodega Arrival is a collaborative sneaker from Boston-based streetwear boutique Bodega and New Balance, featuring the New Balance 574 silhouette released to celebrate Bodega’s 15th anniversary.

Dressed in Lemon Curry, Reflective Silver, and blue, this Bodega x New Balance 574  sneaker features a mixed-material upper made of breathable mesh on the toebox and tongue, a perforated suede collar, and hairy suede overlays. Lemon Curry dominates the upper, while hits of Reflective Silver on the lateral "N" logos, vamp, and heel tab and blue hues on the inner tongue and collar lining offer a contrasting tone. Other details include white laces, New Balance branding on the heel, a co-branded tongue, and red insoles with co-branded details and a 15th-anniversary celebrations graphic. The upper rests on a white and silver ENCAP midsole atop a black rubber outsole. 

Our experts particularly love this sneaker’s unique design, vibrant color scheme, the collaborative nature of its creation, which make it stylish and versatile. The New Balance 574 Legacy Bodega Arrival was made available on July 15th, 2022. Initially, it retailed at $130.

name: Be You
title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Be You
description:
